{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r735607245", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What a start to Christmas", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "30 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "KeithE694", "reviewer_origin": ["Westerham"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r735607245-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["had a table at the Frank and Dean show event on both the 14th and 21st December. Both evenings were fantastic and really set the scene for Xmas for us. Show was great however, the food and service were even better.", "Well done Boisdale for a great job on packed evenings."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r735671382", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Disappointing especially given the price paid", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "30 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "StephanieTsangLDN", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r735671382-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We expected a lot more from Boisdale but we left feeling underwhelmed and disappointed. Firstly the menu we were given was a reduced menu, we had to ask three waiters before the manager came to explain why the normal December a la carte menu was not available. My partner and I ordered a medium rare ribeye steak each but when it came, it was the wrong order. We then had to wait another 15 minutes for our steaks and when they came, we were disappointed that they were medium rather than medium rare (for steak lovers, this is a big deal!). Our bill was over \u00a3200 for two courses and four cocktails. We were expecting a fantastic experience for the price we paid but we were left feeling disappointed."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r734816254", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Had the best night at the Frank & Dean xmas show", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "26 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "JackieE279", "reviewer_origin": ["Brasted, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r734816254-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had the best night at the Frank and Dean xmas show this Christmas. The restaurant was buzzing and the staff were so attentive. They managed to whiz around serving loads of tables and even joining in the dancing! Brilliant. The good was great as always and Frank and Dean were superb - such a great night. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r737932304", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Dirty plate, silent waiter, no refund as promised, no response to email.", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "8 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "922nigelc", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r737932304-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I had to send the dessert back twice as the plate was very dirty and greasy \u2013 the second time via the Manager. The first time the waiter (who did not talk at all!) disappeared for a few seconds and brought back exactly the same dirty plate.", "The wonderful waitress (Roxanna) later told me that the Manager said that I would not be getting a bill for any of the lunch. I explained that I had pre-paid online by charge card and she said that that was not a problem.", "I checked my charge card account and no refund had been made so I emailed them on 24 December. To date they have not even bothered to reply let alone refund me.", "This is a regular Sunday lunch spot for a number of us and this is the third time where it has been necessary to complain."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r739676981", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good standard steak and sides,", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "17 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LondonsReviews", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r739676981-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Good standard steak and sides, gets lively on a Thursday when the band come out about 9. Wouldn\u2019t say service is most attentive "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r740865307", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Lovely setting, disappointing food", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "23 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "AC2025", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r740865307-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Lovely setting and location. The food was too salty, way beyond health standards. Restaurants should be fully aware that too much salt or sugar causes health problems even if the customer is not diabetic. It is a common knowledge. Was surprised the waiter did not offer to change the dishes for a non-salted one, as other restaurants do. No extra water was offered and only a small percentage was taken off the bill. Usually waiters won\u2019t let you pay for food at all if it does not match customer satisfaction. ", "Also I requested for the service charge to be removed. Under the Consumer Rights Act, no one has to pay service charge and especially if you aren\u2019t happy with the meal. It is another way of enforcing compulsory tipping. Tipping should always be optional and out of generosity otherwise how else do restaurants get business if they keep adding service charges? They are already paid to serve customers. It is like saying if a customer browses and already purchases clothes in a shop, does he or she need to leave a tip?"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r741029567", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Mediocre", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "24 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "421cathya", "reviewer_origin": ["London, England, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r741029567-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited with a friend tonight. Lovely decor and view. However arrived at 1753 to be told they don\u2019t open until 6pm but we could go downstairs to their other bar. Waiter was pleasant enough but didn\u2019t have the wine we wanted suggested another but no suggestion of reducing the price to the wine we originally ordered that they didn\u2019t have so was charged nearly \u00a350. Food average and totally over-priced. Then as the jazz band came on we asked for bill. We paid was finishing our drinks & waiter came back to say he\u2019d made a mistake & didn\u2019t include charge for music which we obviously said we weren\u2019t paying & left. Not impressed."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r741178215", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Slow service, below average food", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "25 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "robdriver", "reviewer_origin": ["Marlow, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "121"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "53"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r741178215-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["7 of us went for dinner on Wednesday night with a customer. The location and the view was excellent. The service started well but quickly deteriorated. It was a quiet evening in the restaurant so there did not appear to be a rational reason for slowness. The starters were average, the mains were poor. I personally had a steak that was not hot, it was warm as if had been sat waiting to be brought to our table. The customer was unimpressed with her meal and another person on our table had cold mash potato as a side dish. ", "This was my first and last visit to this restaurant. We were booked to visit on Wednesday night but cancelled the reservation and went to Gaucho in Canary Wharf which was significantly better.", "If you enjoy steak, you will find better experiences for the same price elsewhere."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r739952658", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic place , offers u", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "19 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ScorpionScorpion2020", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r739952658-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Fantastic place , offers u all . The cigar room was great and the Balcony and Bar was fantastic for winter . The bar service was fast and the service was great in General . "]}
