{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r716274498", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Awful service", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "8 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jojobm", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r716274498-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited as a party of eight on Sunday for a family birthday. So sorry to say that everything was a bit mediocre. The food, by the time it arrived, was lukewarm. Multiple attempts to get (very straight forward) drinks and other simple requests forgotten. The service was just dreadful - so so so slow and it actually spoiled what should have been a lovely family occasion. I'm not sure I'd go back and wouldn't recommend it to anyone else - certainly not at a cost of \u00a3450."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r711919385", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great music and food, really poor service", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "22 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Wiz B", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r711919385-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The food and music were great. It was only about half full which surprised me for a busy restaurant. But the service was a real disappointment. It took half an hour from being seated to getting our drinks and having the food order taken. At one point we waited half an hour for G&T despite chasing it up three times. Still not as bad as the guy on the other table who had been waiting forty minutes for his drinks and started following the head waiter round - who literally ran away from him.", "Service issues were blamed on a trainee barman - but honestly I don't care. Get another barman. The place wasn't full and the still we had to wait and wait.", "So yeah it was a nice meal, but when I'm dropping \u00a3500 on a meal for four I'd like some half reasonable service."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r716792992", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great night with great music and food but uneccessarily expensive", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "9 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Travelloverexrep", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r716792992-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["What can I say other than what a great night out.", "My only complaint was that we were sat right by the bar and when we tried to buy drinks were told we could not be served at the bar and had to order drinks from the waiters, this meant we had to wait for a waiter to come over and take our order to stand at the side of us to give the barman who was 2 feet from us our order to then have to wait for the barman to fill the order that was then put on a tray to be delivered to our table 2 of our seats were actually touching the front of the bar. This took 3 times as long as it would of if the barman had just served us, and then we were charged \u00a34.95 service charge for each round of drinks.", "This is not on when although a great night is already expensive as there is an entrance fee then meals to buy and of course the drinks and service charge.", "I ordered a pint of beer, 1 glass of wine 1 coke and a sambucca cost of this round including the \u00a34.95 service charge was \u00a345.95. ", "So very expensive."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r716216887", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Good food, good music, terrible service ...", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "8 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Nortsat46", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "101"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r716216887-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The food, including the steaks, was good. The music (Courtney Pine) was very good.", "The service was unbelievably slow. It took more than 20 mins to order.", "When we had finished our main course, we had dirty plates on our table for 25 minutes before they were cleared.", "It was too late to order a pudding because everyone was leaving and tables were being cleared and we did not want to eat a pudding, or drink another glass of wine or a coffee in that melee.", "The slow service ruined our evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r710565897", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Visited twice last week.", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "17 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Robin L", "reviewer_origin": ["Lausanne, Switzerland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r710565897-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My son & I had supper and enjoyed excellent food, wine and beer. The second visit also included a blues band. Would have preferred a female singer.", "The atmosphere was great with attentive service. Great value."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r702767252", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "20th Anniversary meal", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "25 August 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Gayna S", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "25"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r702767252-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We decided to book tickets for Boisdale after it was recommended by a friend, my husband likes Pink Floyd so as they had a tribute band there it was a perfect choice. ", "We arrived early as I'd read you could have drinks on level 1 which we did, the prices are very reasonable which is always a bonus. We sat taking in our surroundings and enjoying the drinks feeling very relaxed, there is a terrace area on level 1 but the seating was full as it was a lovely evening, I noticed people were ordering from a food menu too, we also had no trouble getting served at the bar (I'd seen people had in other reviews).", "We made our way to the main restaurant on level 2 for our meal, I'd prepared using an app called Fever, we had two courses paid and then dessert and drinks to be paid at the end, the service charge was included and was well worth the charge, we had the best service from start to finish, the food was amazing and the band was great, we will definitely be going back. "]}
