{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r686347491", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Atmosphere could be more Scottish", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "3 July 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Gardener2014", "reviewer_origin": ["Saint Joseph, Michigan"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "318"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "70"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r686347491-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited Boisdale for my husband\u2019s birthday since he loves Scotland. It is a beautifully decorated restaurant and the food was very good. However, the male waiter was arrogant and inefficient. He approached our table asking if we were ready to order prior to asking for a drink order. After the meal several of our table were served dessert while two of us waited and waited for a dram of Scotch. Since it advertises its large selection of Scotch it didn\u2019t seem it would take that long to find. I was appalled as I observed him roughly grab a female waitress by the arm when asking her a question. The female who waited on us was very nice and efficient. We visit Scotland often and always enjoy their waiters. Perhaps Boisdale should recruit one of them to add authenticity to the atmosphere. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r687064997", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Disappointing lunch ", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "5 July 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "caribbeanbusinessman", "reviewer_origin": ["Barbados"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "122"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "47"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r687064997-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Ordered the special. Had cod. Was very average and extremely salty. 250 quid for 4 people for lunch and only 2 people had a glass of wine... sorry. Won\u2019t rush back "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r686650843", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Beautiful Bar/Restaurant/Live Music", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "4 July 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Sharmaine G", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r686650843-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went to Boisdale for the first time 2 weeks ago. Absolutely love this place. When we got there we did not have a reservation and it was very busy. But the lovely staff there really went out of their way to help and gave us a table before the other people arrived. The food was very good. We went on a Saturday night and had West Indian food with Reggae/Soul music playing. Great evening and it finishes late at 1.00am so perfect for us. Everybody loved their food. Drinks a bit pricey but we are in Canary Wharf!! Will definitely be going again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r679721794", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Gob smacked", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "7 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SharonHarp", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r679721794-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The Boisdale has always been a favourite choice of ours for business lunches and special occasions so we booked for a birthday meal for 6 people in the bar and grill but as it was quite busy the manager kindly seated us in the restaurant which was a lovely start to the evening. Unfortunately that was the only nice thing about the night. The restaurant was not very busy but we were left waiting for over half an hour to order any drinks. We gave up in the end and ordered at the bar. We were eventually approached by the waiter to take our order. ", "When the food arrived it was with poor service and two of our party have ended up with suspected food poisoning, having both eaten the truffle burger. At one point a member of staff approached our table and said that if we didn't keep the noise down they would call security! We were not being rowdy at all and were just talking amongst ourselves. To say we were gob smacked was an understatement. In all the times we\u2019ve visited the restaurant we\u2019ve never been treated this way. ", "Then to add insult to injury, they slapped a service charge on the bill when the service and general attitude of the staff had been appalling. ", "This will be the last time that we ever use the Boisdale and will never recommend."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r671800440", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Mixed feelings", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "6 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "bogi1", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "52"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "51"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r671800440-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife booked this joint as the meal was accompanied by a with a live band,our table booked for 7.30pm got seated ordered wine and champagne bottle of each both were very nice but a bit pricey,we ordered starters Haggis which was wonderful with the whisky,we then had the Chateaubriand for 2 that was enough not stingy with the portions ", "9.30 band started we had finished our mains and deserts by then,band was very good a lot better than the food i must say.", "would i go back again YES I WOULD."]}
