{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r679449486", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A party of 10 had Sunday Brunch/Lunch , Amazing service Restaurant Manager Wael fantastic service", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "6 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Fearless774388", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r679449486-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The service was exceptional ,attentive, polite considerate and amenable . the staff could not do enough to ensure that we had a wonderful experience. the food was very well presented and was of a very good standard as i would expect. the cool ambiance of the Jazz band added to a wonderful weekend"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r679678229", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Dinner & Show Boisdale Canary Wharf - No rush to go back", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "7 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Susiewils", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "26"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "20", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r679678229-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for dinner & show option as heard it was a good night out. Started out well, greeted by a lovely Manager who said the 1st show was lively. Had a table near the stage, in the beginning staff were attentative. It went downhill from there. The food was so disappointing, as it was a \"special occasion\" we had a bottle of special Boisdale pink champagne!!! We've have had better Cava. Bottle of Chablis, would not have been happy if we'd paid \u00a38-10 in a supermarket for it & we paid a lot more for it!!! The Bohemians were brilliant & encouraged us to join in & dance. 4 \"Managers\" were milling about, told us to sit down; the lovely staff we started with disappeared (two private parties); it was extremely chaotic we ordered dessert, 5 staff passed us & did everything to avoid eye contact as it was coming up to finishing time, finally got dessert they forgot one, we were trying to finish up and they started stripping the tables around us.... Very unprofessional. So much so we paid up and left and will be in no hurry to return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r679024764", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Brilliant Food, Brilliant Entertainment", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "5 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "tahlullah t", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r679024764-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked the three course dinner on the Rod Stewart tribute night last Saturday. The meal was delicious with very experienced, professional and friendly waiters. A very good tribute band far exceeding expectations completed a very enjoyable night. Just make sure that when you book the three course meal you get the three course menu on arrival as your confirmation email doesn't specify and you have to provide evidence of your original offer to the resteraunt manager."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r670102072", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "\u201cMarathon Brunch\u201d a with no TV\u2019s to watch the marathon... Terrible breakfast for \u00a330, egg had hair in it, rude manager.", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "29 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "christopherw718", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "80"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "84"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r670102072-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This was advertised as a Marathon Brunch, we have actually been coming to this place for the last 6 years and there\u2019s always at least 30 of us. We\u2019re all different ages and generations, Mum/Dads, Nans/Grandads and children so not a rowdy bunch or troublesome group in any way! We pay \u00a330 each just for the breakfast plus additionally a whole day of drinking as well so we spend an absolute fortune with these guys year in year out (easily over \u00a31500 in total). I\u2019d expect some kind of service for such loyal customers especially as the place was empty apart from us!!!", "I\u2019ll admit that \u00a330 is a very expensive breakfast especially as the food has never been great but in previous years it\u2019s worked for us because we could watch the Marathon on the tv, and with so many of us it\u2019s a good base where you can easily get a drink and use the facilities all day so we invest in the whole experience really rather than just the breakfast. ", "This year was an absolute nightmare, we arrived at 10 o\u2019clock to find out that the \u201cMarathon Brunch\u201d did not have any tv\u2019s that work so we couldn\u2019t actually watch the marathon at all\u2026 The staff half heartedly tried to get the tv\u2019s to work but it was clear that they had no clue and they never got them to work. The breakfast arrived in buffet trays and we were all told to help ourselves like school dinners. There was no toast and when I asked they said that they would see if there was any bread upstairs. They got some bread by which time as all of us had finished. I had a hair in my scrambled egg and they made no effort to apologise they just asked me to help myself to another breakfast from the buffet. I actually asked the waiter if he\u2019d pay that kind of money for a breakfast like that and he said no which says it all really. Then I overheard him telling the manager what had happened and the manager said he didn\u2019t want to talk to me. ", "A bit later on, I ventured out to the road with a glass in my hand which I probably shouldn\u2019t have done really but the TV\u2019s weren\u2019t on and I wanted to see the race considering that it had been such a shambles in Boisdale. I had every intention of coming back up to get another drink and bring the glass back with me too. The manager was in the lift with me and said nothing then as we left the lift he sarcastically barked at me, \u201cEnjoy your glass won\u2019t you!\u201d And walk off the other way. Because of his rude comment, I was rude back to him (perhaps I shouldn\u2019t have but I was just so disappointed that we\u2019d recommended this place to so many people and come back year in year out and spent thousands of pounds here). All he had to do was ask me like normal human being to leave my glass inside and I would have respected his request. No need for him to be sarcastic, very childish behaviour.", "Absolutely gutted and let down but this place which is a real shame. We\u2019ll be finding somewhere else to spend our money next year! Somewhere that actually appreciates us. Absolutely gutted and disgusted with the staff. They made absolutely no effort to help us at all and really didn't care that we're such loyal customers."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r661427854", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Scottish themed restaurant in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "26 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Colin O", "reviewer_origin": ["Newcastle, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "153"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "63"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r661427854-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A well know Scottish themed restaurant and cigar bar. The smell of cigars is always in the background not offensively. The restaurant itself is imposing and large, staff friendly. Menu could have been more extensive and food itself fine but not outstanding.."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r661620950", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "A disappointment", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "27 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Streatham50", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "20", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r661620950-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My husband and I went to have dinner and watch the Bob Marley tribute band Legend (who were wonderful) last Saturday. Our table was booked for 9:00pm and the band was due on at 9:45. Our table was not ready until 9:25. When we arrived we were told to go for a drink at the bar downstairs (where it was impossible to get served) so we didn't bother and we thought our table would be ready; unfortunately not - we had another wait. No one offered us a drink (complimentary or not) or even suggested we have a look at the menu so we could decide what to eat while we waited. The front of house staff could not have cared less. The delay meant that we were eating (what was very mediocre food) as the band performed and therefore not able to get up and dance. Our waiter, who was Brazilian or Portuguese, was great - helpful and very attentive; the only member of staff we came across who was any good. When the band finished the bass beat from the disco on the first floor could be felt through our chairs and totally drowned out the background music in the restaurant. I mentioned this on the way out but no one was interested. We have been twice before for music events and enjoyed ourselves; this was a big disappointment."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r661019792", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sunday lunch with live jazz", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "25 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "traveller106", "reviewer_origin": ["london"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "63"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "54"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r661019792-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Fabulous food, Sunday lunch menu was very good! Reasonably priced wine, lovely setting, good service, great entertainment . Would highly recommend!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r663557781", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Mixed feelings!", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "3 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "AndrewN424", "reviewer_origin": ["Tadley, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "798"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "242"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r663557781-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went along to Boisdales to see the Zombies before their induction into the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame. I really wanted to score the experience more highly but sadly the woeful service when we arrived led me to drop one star at least. We waited 20mins before any sort of waiter arrived. This meant we were thirsty and agitated from the off. ", "When it did arrive, the food was very good with the chilli squid and burgers being very tasty. ", "The gig itself was very good, but sadly that wait for service reduced our satisfaction."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r664810134", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Mixed bag", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "8 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Brian M", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r664810134-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked it though an offer on Groupon Although the food was superb the service left a lot to be desired, chateaubriand tool nearly an hour from order to be plated. Couple next to is orders theirs 10-15 mins after us and for served at almost the same time. Restaurant was half empty and they put a couple next to us which was snug at best, couldn\u2019t have a conversation as it felt like I was at a table for 4 instead of a table for 2. Asked for my bill and waited 15 mins. Saw about 20 serving staff not doing anything and decided to up and leave, knowing I only had the service to pay (which I didn\u2019t have a problem with ) at this moment two different severs approached me about my bill. I explained about my wait and they let me leave without paying it. It\u2019s my belief that they were trying to make us stay so they could incorporate the music charge into our bill."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r664310120", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Disappointed for the \u201ccuban\u201d night", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "6 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Huk_trip", "reviewer_origin": ["Amsterdam, The Netherlands"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "51"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r664310120-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Only good parts: starters and cocktails.", "The rest.. a disaster: chewy steak, dry gnocchi, slow waiters, horrendous tribute band - was supposed to be all cuban stars, I think they picked them up off the London Bridge, nothing like in the picture advertised; main vocal was more concerned with shouting in the microphone than singing -, no toilet paper in stalls, faulty water tap and hand dryer. All and all, a real carelessness in everything.", "One would accept this low quality from a 2 stars restaurant, but the prices here..."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r666983693", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "You have been warned!", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "16 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SJEL24", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r666983693-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This was one of the most appalling evenings I have ever experienced. The customer service provided by the waiting staff, restaurant manager and general manager is terrifyingly incompetent. After one waitress knocked my drink all over my food and the table I then asked her if I might have my food and drink replaced, which she did reluctantly with a confused look on her face. ", "You cannot see the stage unless you pay for VIP tickets, and the TV screens they have around the edge are out of time with the music, and you won't be able to move seats closer to the stage even though they are not occupied or booked for later in the evening, so don't bother asking! ", "The food is extremely poor quality and shockingly over-priced. We finished the evening and left early once I started vomit-burping into my mouth due to the acidity of the red wine. Fun times!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r668056814", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Extremely disappointed", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "21 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Andreea I", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r668056814-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I both 2 VIP tickets for the Michael Jackson Tribute show where I paid about \u00a3250(terrible decision). On the ticket is written that the performance starts at 9:45 and finishes at 11:45 and I was shocked to see that the band started to pack up at 11:00. I was also late 20 min(my bad) and all I had left to see was 30 min of show and extremely poor dishes. I have told the waiter that I am a bit disappointed as on the ticket is written clearly 11:45 and not 11:00 and he replied that the show before got cancelled and this being the reason. Well!!! I don\u2019t care!!!! I paid to see the show until 11:45 !!! Overall was a waste of money and time as I spend in total around \u00a3300 including drinks, drove 2 hours and haven\u2019t got any kind of experience. Don\u2019t waste your money here.."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r667503810", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "After dinner you can have cigars and whisky ", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "18 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "farhad684", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "79"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r667503810-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A very interesting establishment with a not very interesting cuisine in the restaurant based in the second floor. However the live music does help a little bit the restaurant has an interesting ambience very classy with a very high class infrastructure the display on the bar with the entire selection of whiskey is very pretty to look at. However the staff really need to be a bit more confident and interested in the clients. When I went downstairs on the first floor for cigars and whiskey everything changed. A very well educated staff member named Phillip who knows the product the establishment are selling the cigars and the whiskey Philip has a vast knowledge of both of the ski and cigars and recommend which cigars to have with which associated whiskey quite an extraordinary gentlemen who takes attention to detail very seriously excellent customer service provided by Philip I will definitely come again maybe not for dinner but for sure to see and visit Phillip again and to indulge in another cigar and under his recommendation perhaps another whiskey."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r660914185", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Jazz lunch", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "24 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "rachelsM5573ZQ", "reviewer_origin": ["Upminster, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r660914185-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Fantastic food + really good atmosphere. Service was excellent. We really enjoyed the music + had a really good view of the stage. Would recommend for a special occasion."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r655559023", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice visit", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "1 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Michael E", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "33"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r655559023-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for the 50% off anniversary prices on the steak and lobster. Food was tasty and the service was good also. Portion sizes do not justify the price however, in particular the gratin potato for \u00a39 and the dessert was also priced at \u00a39 and both plates were so incredibly small! Was excessively dark also, dimmed lights yes and but it was too much and could barely see the menu. Temperature was uncomfortably warm inside. The inside and the view is very and food was tasty but not as good as it can be."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r655503416", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Ok nice but pricey for the experience.", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "28 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jez D", "reviewer_origin": ["Gravesend, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r655503416-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I went to this restaurant tonight and have to say I was a little disappointed. The food was nice but not stunning. However, the little things let it down. Steak delivered but no steak knife. It was a comment on the medium rare that you simply couldn\u2019t proceed without asking for a different knife. We ordered spinach as an extra but got chips! ", "None of this is crazy bad but for the cost of the meal probably not really good enough."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r656016237", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "a definite place to grab a drink when in Canary Wharf...", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "3 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Wandering_ag", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r656016237-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["If you are in Canary Wharf and looking for a place to have a drink, look no further. Step in and you are taken back in time. The ambience is cozy, 1960's and classy. If you are looking to have dinner, reservation is recommended.", "If you are there just for a drink, head to the bar to read through one of the biggest scotch and whisky collections, if you want to keep it frugal, there's beer on tap too. ", "Head over to the cigar rooms if you do fancy a cigar. On occasional days, there's live music!! (blues/soul/jazz)"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r657016441", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Very disappointed with promise regarding Food Intolerance", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "7 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Humeyra75", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r657016441-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I and my sister went to the Boisdales on 23rd February it was a set menu with Queen tribute band so payment was made in advance. I spoke to a member of staff at Boisdales prior to the 23rd informing them of my sister's food intolerances I asked them if they can cater for my sister I.e. make gluten free chips.", "On the night of the 23rd there was nothing in the menu the my sister could have apart from steak because everything was pre-prepared. Not even gluten free chips. My sister hardly had a choice apart from steak and the chefs couldn't cater because we were told they are too busy and the manager only apologised when it ruined my sister's evening. ", "I'm very disappointed"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r659366224", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Nice enough", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "18 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MWJonesy-UK", "reviewer_origin": ["Basingstoke, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "67"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r659366224-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited for a business lunch. Venue is tastefully decorated inside with warm, attentive staff.", "Menu is fine as was the food however for the price I was expecting to be blown away...I wasn\u2019t so based on overall experience & value for money 3/5 is fair."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r659085846", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A great night out", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "17 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "KatyR281", "reviewer_origin": ["Wickford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "37"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r659085846-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I took my husband for his birthday we did one of the special offers so dinner and show were included, the food was lovely, the entertainment was great, we both thoroughly enjoyed it! My husband also loved the humidor and selections of whiskey! If you like cigars, whiskeys, good food, cocktails and great entertainment then you won\u2019t be disappointed "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r659427510", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "place looks amazing, but food just a huge disappointment", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "19 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Alexandra K", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r659427510-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Place looks nice and when you enter it does seem very promising. ", "Service is very good, they brought me cheesecake with candle and happy birthday signage on the plate. Waiter even sang me a little song. it was very sweet. But I only had one spoon of cheesecake as it is too awful to eat. Main was ok, but too small and definitely not worth money. Very poor presentation of food too. BAD BAD FOOD and inst it most important thing in the restaurant. Overpriced as well. Well perhaps you pay for interior, service and silver cutlery :DDD"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r660092823", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Disappointing experience", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "21 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "gracelimsh", "reviewer_origin": ["Horley, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "20", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r660092823-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were a group of 10 who went to Boisdale for a farewell lunch for a colleague. The restaurant itself is lovely but overall, the experience was very disappointing.", "the food was very mediocre. My starter was described as scallops but there was only one scallop! That is surely contrary to trading standards and I thought it was outrageous. As it was a group lunch with colleagues, I did not complain but a number of my colleagues also mentioned it afterwards. For my mains, I had the confit duck leg, which I found to be quite dry and very salty. I didn't fancy anything from the dessert menu but wanted a coffee. Unfortunately, the restaurant did not offer milk alternatives such as soya which I thought was surprising as milk alternatives are very common these days.", "I found the service below par as well. Our waitress was lovely enough, but quite why she did not write down everyone's orders against where we were seated is a mystery. We were reduced to putting our hand up whenever the waitress called out the drinks or food as they were served. Surely in a restaurant of this standard, the waiting staff should be trained to write down the orders against the relevant patron so that drinks and food can be served seamlessly.", "All in all, a very disappointing meal for a restaurant of this standard. I am just glad that I was not the one who paid the bill! Boisdale, you really must do better!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r660629104", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Dinner & Saxon Sound System", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "23 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Roam591524", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r660629104-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boo, hiss, fake news!! Food was pleasant namely the starter and dessert. ", "Saxon Sound System!?! Nope.... definitely not the Saxon I grew up with. Absolutely dire!!! The reggae and soul alike were as though I were listening to Heart FM. DJ ? Disgraceful.... Left 2hrs early .smdh. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r653748049", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "I really enjoy this place", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "20 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Busybee13579", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r653748049-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I come here pretty often for different occasions. Been here for lunch, dinner or just couple drinks - and pretty satisfied every single visit. ", "Food is quite good and definitely amazing for the price. ", "During summer, grabbing few drinks at the cigar balcony is relaxing. ", "Service can be a bit slow during peak lunch and dinner hours though - so you may need to wait for quite a long time to get your food served. But food is delicious."]}
