{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r653068719", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Disappointed", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "17 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Sarah P", "reviewer_origin": ["Isle of Wight, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r653068719-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This was our second visit to Boisdale. I took hubby and our kids for Jazz, Sunday lunch for hubby's birthday. The beef was more or less raw and very fatty, potatoes hard, no bread rolls (waiter forgot). TBH I have had better cavery at a fraction of the cost. It is a stunning restaurant with a great atmosphere. But on this occasion food was below the standard you would expect for the price."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r654244790", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Awful", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "23 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "paulp24972", "reviewer_origin": ["Dover, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "53"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r654244790-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Was told at the door was very busy & would be a long wait for food , which would of been fine if this specialty steak house had any decent chefs ! 2x medium & 1 well done . All came 2 hours after being there pissing blood , sent back, 10 minutes later, they actually made the cardinal sin, and sent the same, (yes they did ) back out, cooked a little more, 2 were still rare & the well done was creamated & tough as leather now , host & waitress were very apologising and genuinely looked embarrassed. Poor poor poor poor show "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r654558031", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Such a fantastic evening", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "24 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "catherinegog4", "reviewer_origin": ["Chelmsford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "25"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r654558031-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Our friends took us for dinner and show at the Boisdale Canary Wharf. For me it was reminiscent of a larger Ronnie Scott\u2019s. The show was a fantastic Queen tribute band, great muscians who really had the audience involved. The food and atmosphere was amazing and our waiting staff were impeccable. Will definitely have a return visit in the near future, maybe even to book one of the private dining rooms."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r654676773", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "The worst service - ever!!", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "25 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Marianne L", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "21"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "41"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r654676773-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["2nd time at Boisdales. Queen tribute band which were amazing. Table for 4 people booked for 8:45pm. Did not see sight nor sound of table staff until 9:30 when she took our drink order, which eventually arrived at 10pm. Food orders taken at 10pm - starter served at 10:15, however main course did not arrive until 10:50! Who wants to eat dinner not far short of midnight then to be presented with a bill that includes \u00a330 service charge?? I think not!!!! Could elaborate more, but to be honest I really don't think this place is worth any review at all. Shocking and most definitely won't be going back there"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r654580167", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great bar and restaurant ", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "24 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Sallprice", "reviewer_origin": ["Chelmsford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "304"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "84"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r654580167-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Love this bar great location in Canary Wharf ", "Great atmosphere for drinks and dinner ", "Nice outside balcony ... my husband also loves the cigar room "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r654732077", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Dinner and show", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "25 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "CityHolidayMaker", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "25"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r654732077-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to a trubute act for Barry White with dinner. Let's start by saying that the food was truly excellent. It was spoiled by poor service - we had pre-paid and booked a table but although they knew this they still presented a bill for the things we had paid for - nearly everything and took ages to put it right. After the music show had finished they still kept different music blaring so much so that conversation was difficult. When I asked to speak to the manager I had to shout to make myself heard. He had the cheek to tell me that I didn't need to shout at him. I REALLY DID HE WOULD NOT HAVE HEARD ANYTHING OVER THE MUSIC."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r645905682", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Poor service, poor food and poor value", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "15 January 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Tom E", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r645905682-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This was a poor customer experience from beginning to end occasionally descending into farce. Firstly, it was almost impossible to book, not because they were busy, this was purely due to incompetence. I initially tried to book in November 2018. I called several times leaving my number and a message requesting a table and no one called me back. If I hadn\u2019t already purchased a voucher I would have given up. Instead, I tried again in January. Assuming that the phone wouldn\u2019t work I contacted the email provided and requested a reservation. Again I got no response. So I tried to call and almost fell off my chair when someone answered. They could not find my email but made my reservation saying I would have to send a copy of my voucher. So I sent a copy of my voucher. The next thing I received was an email thanking me for my cancellation (!!!). I quickly responded saying I didn\u2019t wish to cancel. I was then asked to fill in a short questionnaire regarding my booking and providing more details of my voucher. On querying this I was told they had no details of my booking.", "The evening of the booking arrived and my partner and I were very much looking forward to our chateaubriand for two. We were encouraged to choose a starter and shared a calamari dish. The first alarm bell rang when it arrived a few moments later. Most likely preprepared and kept warm, it was just warm and a bit soggy. Most calamari dishes I\u2019ve eaten in pubs in recent years at almost half the price have been several times better.", "The chateaubriand came and was warm and not very big. The meat tasted slightly over. The sauces were tasteless. The spinach was dry and old. The chips were good as was the wine.", "Paying the bill. After waving at the staff for more than 5 minutes I had to get up and go over to them. They then had the cheek to stick a significant service charge on the bill.", "I used to enjoy the Boisdale in Victoria. Becoming a chain has cheapened the whole experience. After this last experience I won\u2019t be going to any Boisdale again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r654842307", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Live Music & Good Food?", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "25 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Carib08", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r654842307-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["YES. This place is truly one of my better experiences, absolutely enjoyed my evening on Friday with the live music and the food was excellent. I thought that the service was very good they changed our table to be nearer the stage at a moments notice and I will definitely be going back. After the dinner and show I then went downstairs to the bar and tried to work off some of the calories on the dance floor enjoying the music from their resident Friday night DJ Aitch B. The d\u00e9cor and the old photographs of people in the entertainment business is just fantastic. Loved it."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r646969859", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "For Whisky and Cigars", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "19 January 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "PeterAFI", "reviewer_origin": ["Helsinki, Finland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "128"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r646969859-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Probably the best Whisky bar in London with an added extra, cigar smoking room. Also Wine list is good.", "Place has a nice menu too and for summers a terrace."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r652907939", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Valentines night ", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "17 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "454craigm", "reviewer_origin": ["Corringham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r652907939-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a lovely evening at Boisdale. Our second visit and was very impressed again. Live music from a great Barry White tribute and band. The view overlooking Cabot Square and it's fountain was nice, the food was excellent. Their table service is first class too. Would highly recommend. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r647328517", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "21 January 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "happylilafrican", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r647328517-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a fantastic three course meal here while watching an excellent live performance. The service was spectacular and the whiskey range was to die for. I can\u2019t wait to visit again soon. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r647608360", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Haggis", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "22 January 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Lisey L", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "197"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "61"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r647608360-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I've never had Haggis before but loved it very tasty. A filling starter though. They forgot to serve the whiskey with it (it came afterwards) but I didn't think it necessary anyway. ", " The rib eye steak was large and juicy and very very good. A very enjoyable meal with good entertainment. Signs around the venue could be improved."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r647159430", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Brilliant night!", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "20 January 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "almost30something", "reviewer_origin": ["Leigh-on Sea, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "46"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r647159430-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["First time visiting Boisdale last night, we had purchased Groupon vouchers for Chateaubriand meal for 2 and then paid extra for the Madness tribute night. Dinner was really really good, wasn\u2019t sure what to expect as I\u2019ve visited restaurants using groupon deals before and found that you got a cheap version of their usual food, this was not the case at Boisdale. Chateaubriand was melt in the mouth and we were absolutely stuffed. Restaurant has a great atmosphere and vibe, tribute band was really good and we all had a really enjoyable night. It\u2019s a great place for Whiskey and Cigar fans too. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r648209740", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Really so not worth the money ", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "25 January 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "K4395VBcatherinel", "reviewer_origin": ["Worthing, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "201"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "97"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r648209740-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My friend & I booked a package to see Rebecca Ferguson who was amazing - shame the dinner wasn\u2019t! It was actually a farce. It took 45 minutes to even get a drink order in let alone order our food which by the way was \u00a345 per head for a set menu excluding drinks. Around 2 hours after being seated my squid starter turned up - solid as a rock but I hate to say better than the main of calves liver which was cold & full of sinew. We struggled to get drinks all evening including water, the waiters did not know what veg were on that evening & frankly I would never go back & eat there - I might go for a gig but that is it! Very poor to be honest & a shame as was looking forward to it. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r651300144", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Music and dinner", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "10 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Londoneyez", "reviewer_origin": ["london"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "34"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r651300144-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Good place, the music was not on for that long. The way the staff move around is cool, in dark clothes they certainly aren't intrusive although service was a bit slow at times. ", "Food menu is relatively limited but we all enjoyed. Haggis for starters is filling, so be warned! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r648445786", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "RIP off seats", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "27 January 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Kay H", "reviewer_origin": ["Brentwood, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "24"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r648445786-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Our seats for Rebecca Ferguson with a meal were \u00a3195.00 for 2. Ok - London, 3 course meal and an artist I enjoy. What I actually got for my money was a table near the waiters computer so every time a drink or item of food was ordered. Waiting staff walked in front of my view to enter onto the computer! Also during her performance a customer complained so we heard all about it, rather than hearing Rebecca. To make matters worse customers who hadn\u2019t paid for a table were allowed to come and stand next to our table (by the computer area) to watch the performance. This was not a good experience and vastly overpriced for the awful table. I have written a complaint email but they haven\u2019t even bothered to reply."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r650739465", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Groupon scam", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "7 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "wankfest", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r650739465-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["They let you book with small dates excluded and then when you call to book they have spaces! Until you ask to use a groupon and they say they are too busy for vouchers....", "Very poor show and won\u2019t even let you speak to a manager as they are too busy!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r645357949", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Fab Rebecca Ferguson. Can\u2019t say same about food.", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "12 January 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "katetibble", "reviewer_origin": ["Reading, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "40"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r645357949-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Rebecca Ferguson was amazing. She\u2019s better live than recorded even. Gave me goosebumps. ", "I thought the food was average, at best. The \u201ccheeseboard\u201d was awful. Service was dreadful. Only positive about food and drinks was the extensive wine menu, that we eventually got.", "We had a fantastic view of Rebecca, which you wouldn\u2019t get without food though."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r639180878", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Sunday lunch", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "12 December 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "eastendtyke", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "50"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r639180878-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I attended the venue for Sunday lunch with my family. We were unsure what to expect given we went with a 'voucher deal', but we're impressed from start to finish. The ambience and setting were lovely, the food was of a great standard and very good value, the wine supplement was a bargain and the service was attentive and personable...thoroughly enjoyable and recommended whether on a deal or not!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r638725231", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "GO SOMEWHERE ELSE !", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "11 December 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "jaynefrench1963", "reviewer_origin": ["Zakynthos, Greece"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r638725231-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Six of us have been here 5 times over the last 3 years some of those times for my husbands birthday and had great times , lovely food , good service and great entertainment but this year OMG it was a shambles!", "First the food was very late getting to us and when it did it was cold .. the people on the next table got their deserts at 23.45 ! ", "Trying to get a drink was near on impossible ,one took the wine order one took the beer order and one took the spirits order ! ", "Then when it came to the dancing on the dance floor there was no dance floor they had put tables on it craming everyone in so no one could dance except where they sat and the poor staff had a nightmare trying to get round everyone so we gave up and sat down . . ", "Such a shame I think it is down to just being greedy with no customer service . I also wrote a letter of complaint with a nice reply from a lady on reception assuring me someone would be in touch and of course no one did ! ", "So don\u2019t waste your time or money going here it no longer is worth it ."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r638018431", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great location - Great Burgers, Cigars if you please", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "7 December 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Gary R", "reviewer_origin": ["Rainham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "42"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r638018431-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great evening with a friend - for a few drinks and lite bite to eat.", "For me the Bar takes up way too much space yet for members a retreat to the balcony is an alfresco escape.", "The drinks are good and varied and the Burger I had was first rate; and my friend enjoyed his cigars.", "Overall a win win of a location."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r639557201", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great entertainment but average food", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "14 December 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "A-Surfer", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r639557201-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We came for my fianc\u00e9 Christmas dinner with he\u2019s work colleagues. Our table of 10 people was crammed onto the dance floor. So if you actually wanted to dance. There was only room for 2 people to dance at a time. This is a shame as you could see people did want to get on the none existence dance floor. The entertainment was very good. The band and singers where top quality! It\u2019s a real shame that this restaurant got greedy and crammed in too many tables. They would have been wiser keeping the dance floor free. So people would have stayed longer.. spending more on drinks, leaving with memories of a good night. ", "Instead I left remembering the very average food. Our table ordered a mixture of starters and mains. Everyone agreed that the food was very average. Not one person enjoyed anything they ate! Food is best described as mums cooking, comforting and plenty of left over to feed the family dog. ", "My rating is 2 star on food. 4 star for entertainment. So overall 3 stars. Unfortunately I will not be coming back. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r639711999", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Average food, overpriced. ", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "15 December 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "FoodPornStar", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "65"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "49"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r639711999-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Table of 3, we ordered the scallops, squid and bisque. The bisque really stood out. Wonderfully intense flavour and texture. ", "We all ended up having burgers for mains. The quality of the meat was compatible to a supermarket and the truffle flavour I was so looking forward to was absent. I\u2019ve had better at GBK for a fraction of the cost. Chips were average too. ", "They do offer a good cheese selection and their wines are really good too. ", "Overall, this was a highly overpriced experience for what it is. \u00a3250 for 3 people seems excessive. Average service. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r644835122", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Night!!", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "9 January 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Tonylucyfrankie", "reviewer_origin": ["Castries, St. Lucia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r644835122-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Just had a meal and seen Rebecca Ferguson perform. Outstanding voice! The food was not too bad quite ok actually. Highly recommend"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r642028820", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "No faults at all", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "28 December 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Y7225QWmatthewf", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r642028820-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Came here yesterday evening for the Frank and Dean Vegas show and honestly couldn't fault it at all. Excellent food, excellent cocktails, superb food, great service and some really fun entertainment. A great evening out."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r645294679", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Rebecca Ferguson Boisdale Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "12 January 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "IngDS", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r645294679-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Loved it, great evening. Never been to that venue before and it\u2019s pleasantly different. Relaxing & luxurious. Polite & attentive staff . Would go again , and have meal next time as the food looked good . We went for the show, and enjoyed a bottle of wine. ", "Adore Rebecca, massive fan . This venue good for her as it\u2019s intimate & welcoming. Thank you , good work."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r639842247", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "No atmosphere", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "16 December 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Karen D", "reviewer_origin": ["Longfield, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r639842247-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We attended this restaurant for a Christmas meal with business associates. We had a private room booked and the service for drinks was slow. The restaurant seemed half empty - it was a Wednesday and during the Frank and Dean show there was no audience interaction. We visited the same restaurant for the same show last year and the atmosphere was amazing with dancing and a party feeling. The food is ok, I had shell in my crab starter but did not want to offend our host by making a fuss. I would advise if you are booking a show night for a party atmosphere, don\u2019t book midweek."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r632766024", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Boisdales is a MUST -- Add a touch of Fleur East & the night was brilliant", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "12 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "dont1947", "reviewer_origin": ["Epsom, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "37"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r632766024-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["An absolutely fabulous steak meal accompanied by an equally fabulous performance by Fleur East and both coupled with truly professional & obviously well trained team made our night very very enjoyable."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r632834657", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Nice spacious restaurant with live jazz", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "12 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SimonW4366", "reviewer_origin": ["Cardiff, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "87"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "96"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r632834657-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This was a lunchtime visit. Nice spacious restaurant with live jazz played while you eat. We were shown to our table which was good except a limited view of the stage where the live band played, a column was in the way. Otherwise the live jazz made a nice atmosphere with a good view over Cabot square. We chose from the 3 course set lunch which is \u00a337.50. For the first course I chose the Dunkeld Scottish oak smoked salmon. This was well presented and tasted nice. For the main course I chose the Roast rib of aged Tee Valley Charolais beef,Yorkshire pudding and horseradish. All roasts are served with duck fat roast potatoes, bunch carrots, wilted greens & red wine gravy. This was well presented and the meat was nice and the Yorkshire was massive taking up most of the plate. Unfortunately the roast potatoes were rock hard and tasted like they had definetly been reheated and not freshly done which spoilt the dish. Don't think this is good enough as it's not cheap here. For desert I chose the Dark chocolate & cherry torte", "70% Valrhona chocolate mousse, poached cherries, honeycomb. This was well presented and tasted very nice. We chose a bottle of the Navaldar Joven 2016/17 \u00a323.00", "Rioja, Spain. This young Rioja has very intense aromas of licorice & ripe forest fruits. Long & intense wine, with red & dark fruit on the palate & spices on the finish. This compliment ed the meal nicely. When we asked for the bill a 12.5% service charge is automatically added. The service on this occasion was good but feel that tipping should be discretionary."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r636669262", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What a drinks", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "30 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "E8985RDfoodlover", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r636669262-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Well.. for my first time we have been to this place and from the welcoming to the end was actually really good.", "But what made us super happy was the taste and the quality of their drinks. We had few from the menu, and WOW."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r632869662", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Sunday Lunch with Live jazz", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "12 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Robin S", "reviewer_origin": ["Wickford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "623"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "217"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r632869662-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["First time visit to Boisdale, Canary Wharf for sunday lunch accompanied by a live,3 piece jazz band, playing all the classics. Be warned this is not a low cost experience, but where in London is? (Wetherspoons. maybe!) This scottish restaurant is well designed and we were seated one table back from the stage. There are other tables away from the stage in the huge windows, with fab views over Canary Wharf. The set menu is \u00a347.50 each with 3/4 bottle of spanish house wine. I must say the Dunkeld Scottish Oak smoked salmon starter was outstanding with a simple creme fresh and horseradish dressing sprinkled in grated lemon zest! My main of rib of charolais beef was sadly cold where it had been on the pass too long but the accompanying veggies were fine. With buttermilk pancakes and ice cream to finish the whole experience was excellent."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r634006784", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "17 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "E8185IUamandar", "reviewer_origin": ["Queenborough, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r634006784-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My husband booked this venue as we had been to the one in belgravia so he thought we would try this one too, and it was such a good night just as the belgravia one can't wait to book again the service is second to none very attentive staff in all areas of the evening"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r634110769", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "No service and plenty of attitude! ", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "18 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "trueandhonestholiday", "reviewer_origin": ["Stock, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "27"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "38"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r634110769-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We arrived at the Resturant and were shown our table. Then after waiting sometime we had to try a get a waiters attention, finally someone came over. Drink orders were taken then we waited a while then waited some more only to then figure out our waiter had disappeared. Finally got someone else to collect our drinks only to then spot the first waiter coming back into the Resturant we asked where he had been and just laugh, we think he had gone for a break or call his girlfriend. Went to order food and a number of items on the menu was not available? Food arrives but only 3 main dishes turn up, mines not there, I ask the waiter as by then he busy talking to his mate that I have not got my food and he says ( I KNOW!) with gritted teeth. Order second round of drinks , doesn\u2019t turn up, by this point we ask to speak to the manger who\u2019s comes over and say I\u2019m sorry I\u2019ll keep an eye on your table. I think what he meant was he wanted to have a argument. Plates getting slammed down and constant eye rolling. By this time we chose to ignore and started getting up and pouring our own wine as was quicker. We had also noticed that the two tables either side of us were waiting for food and drinks, seemed like there was just not enough staff and apart from one none of them gave a crap and thought it was funny. A little while later the manager came over and kneeled down next to my wife and started whispering in her ear I thought he was saying sorry but in fact he decided to come over and start on her saying what is your problem, if I had known I would have told him to do one. The cocky waiter started being nice when the bill arrived obviously sniffing around for a tip - jog on. We paid the bill minus the service charge as we had no service. On a positive note the Jersey Boys were really good. Shame about the aggressive staff! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r634451243", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "impressive show & dinner", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "19 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "BunchOfLilies", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "517"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "181"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r634451243-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My boyfriend and I had a lovely evening at the Boisdale for a Michael Jackson tribute. It\u2019s a beautiful large, grand room and the lighting is quite dim. I was impressed by the 800 whiskies and there was a good wine selection too. Staff were knowledgeable and attentive. We paid \u00a360 each for dinner and the show. Dinner was excellent, everything was delicious and great quality. I was especially pleased with my haggis, neeps and tatties! Such a lovely way for a couple to spend an evening with dinner and a show at Boisdale. I do enjoy the atmosphere around Canary Wharf on a Saturday evening and I highly recommend!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r635250596", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Beautiful end to a stressful day!", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "23 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "prishat98", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r635250596-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Came here on my anniversary with my partner after having an awful experience with doubletree Hilton hotel. We originally missed our dinner reservations elsewhere because of the awful hotel we were at and ended up at Boisdale. This place is nothing short of amazing! My partner bought a cigar from their huge collection whilst we had some wine and then of course...dinner. I had a steak with the amazing triple cooked chips (honestly I will be coming back here just for the chips ) wanted to order another portion but unfortunately the kitchen had closed and my partner had a burger which he was thoroughly happy with. If you\u2019re looking for a restaurant with a chill but lively atmosphere with AMAZING food...you need to come here! Thank you to the staff at Boisdale for an amazing ending to an awful day!! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r636299827", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Dine out.", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "28 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "jonky2016", "reviewer_origin": ["Basildon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r636299827-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great food! Great staff! A bit pricey and extremely slow service considering the place was almost empty! Maybe because it was middle of the day."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r636532171", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Overpriced and overcooked", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "29 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "martz238", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "40", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r636532171-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Have been a few times and the food has always been ok. Last night the meal was disappointing and the more I think about it we should not have paid for it. Starters were ok main courses should all have been sent back - it was an evening out (8 of us) to enjoy the lovely Orli Nyles who was as always excellent. It spoils the evening if you have to keep complaining - we did complain but with hindsight not enough! Two of us ordered the Hamburger (I\u2019ve had this before and it was very nice) last night it was half the thickness of previous burger shrivelled up burnt and dry - I couldn\u2019t eat it - the mushroom and bread was ok but \u00a318.75 is a lot to pay for a burger bun a mushroom and a few chips - the message I received was that the Chef agreed it was burnt !! The steaks (ordered 3 rib eyes with a \u00a39 supplement) were thin, very tough difficult to cut and I noticed watching the two men opposite me eating them rather chewy! My other friend sent hers back as she just gave up trying to cut it . After complaining they said they would cancel the supplement and gave us some cheese and biscuits! Desserts eventually arrived - myself and a friend decided on the chocolate brownie, was looking forward to this - well it was not a brownie it was chocolate (sickly) mousse on a layer of chocolate sponge which was about 7mm thick neither of us ate it. I would also add we waited a very long time in between courses, when the \u2018complimentary cheese\u2019 arrived our dessert menus were taken from us but our dessert order wasn\u2019t taken? Eventually we had to ask for the menus to be returned so we could order our dessert? The red wine Vina Amate Rioja not recommended - I have never tasted a bad Rioja until I tasted this one. The venue was quite packed - it seemed they couldn\u2019t cope."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r627028892", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Dinner and music at Boisdales", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "21 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "rangerover2", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r627028892-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited Boisdale on Friday evening, for a VIP dinner and show. I had visited Boisdale several times before and always enjoyed it. I expected the musical entertainment to be good, and the soul band were fantastic. But we found the service at the table really wasn\u2019t on top of it. I had to ask three times for more water , and there was an overriding feeling that the restaurant was struggling to keep up on a busy night. Given the cost, very disappointing. The steaks were ok but not particularly tender."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r627533581", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Birthday ", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "23 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "philipt428", "reviewer_origin": ["Romford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r627533581-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great night great table right on the stage Aleksandar Oneill\u2019 was very good considering he been around the block. Only complaint was the service 30 mins on arrival before we got a drink waited so long for our meal I had the crab bit disappointed very dry we ended up eating wile the show was on and we did arrive in plenty of time they wanted a \u00a380 service charge bit cheeky they put the service charge on the ticket price as well they advertise meet and greet when we ask when was this happening we were told that was and extra \u00a3150 ffs good night tho "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r627433572", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Birthday present to see Alexander O\u2019niel and dinner", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "23 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "michellehen2017", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r627433572-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The show was really good, food was very nice, 3 courses, starter, main meal, dessert, this was at Canary Wharf, the wine per bottle started around \u00a323 ", "We had the 12oz ribeye steak, but watch out, they slap a \u00a39 supplement on each steak meal and the steak burger. This is not stated on the menu, so make sure you ask about any extra charges."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r632611504", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Shambles! Save your money.", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "11 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Claire H", "reviewer_origin": ["Diss, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "31"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "40"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r632611504-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Having visited one of their sister restaurants, decided to give Boisdale Canary Wharf a try, just for a change. Never had any problems with the restaurant near Victoria station, over many years, so expected the same. How wrong was I. ", "Don't know where to start really. Travelled down from Suffolk. Arrived at Canary Wharf tube station. Took us 15 minutes to find. My husband actually called the restaurant only to be told they didn't know how we should get to them. Won't go into what happened next, but Canary Wharf nobody seems to know where anything is.", "Hooray, arrived at 12.45pm. Our pre dinner drinks arrived 35mins later and wrong. Had to call a waiter over to place our order. Got our starters wrong. Had to call another waiter over who then went to find someone else it went on and on. Eventually the right starter arrived think they must have run out of Burrata mozzarella, 3 slithers is what I got. This took over half an hour. It is now 2.10pm. We have to leave at 3pm. This was meant to be a relaxing catch up with dear friends all we seemed to talk about was the service. We were given free wine, but the whole experience was horrendous and they lost out on \u00a3150. Service! There isn't any. 2 hours for 2 courses?Didn't have time for desert. They did have a large party come into the restaurant around 1pm. This was not our problem. You should get the staff. Cannot believe Jools Holland is part of this establishment. A shambles. Will not be going back or recommending."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r627629224", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great evening in a fantastic venue", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "24 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "AnitaS279", "reviewer_origin": ["Upminster, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "33"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "32"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r627629224-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Entertained by talented Jermain Jackman and a brilliant band. Food and service excellent.", "Looking forward to our next visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r630570094", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Birthday", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "3 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "harryc640", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "43"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r630570094-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Nice atmosphere. Friendly staff. Food is overpriced and very, very average at best. Expected more for the amount of money spent. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r630101646", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Lovely atmosphere ", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "1 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Leo86L", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r630101646-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We came here on a Thursday afternoon for a drink ,..and the Bar on 1st floor was appealing! Lovely terrace where you can have a cigar, jazz music and the drinks menu with a large selection of whiskey made our night ! ", "Definitely recommend !!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r632561582", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Redemption ", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "11 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SimonBP", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "54"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "45"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r632561582-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We\u2019ve been to Boisdale a couple of times before - once excellent the other not so, in fact the last time was so disappointing that this visit took a lot of convincing for me to go.", "However this time we had a voucher for a Chateaubriand experience, which made the price point substantially lower.", "The staff were very attentive, the food exceedingly enjoyable, and live music itself was reason to return.", "Despite the voucher it was still an expensive evening, however one that I would happily repeat in the future maybe after some time for the bank balance to recover.", "Would I return? Yes, however as I have learnt before, I would not return on Burns night but any other time of the year could potentially be an excellent evening.", "One question though does still remain - how does one pronounce Boisdale? We say it using the French pronunciation on Bois (bwah) but the staff use an anglicised form of \u201cboys\u201d sounding like something from New Jersey."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r631747938", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Excellent venue for business until the music starts", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "7 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Ray P", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "26"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r631747938-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a great business dinner here, good food, drink, ambience and attentive service.", "would highly recommend, however, don't forget there is live music which isn't necessarily conducive to having a conversation at a normal sound level. Just bear that in mind. However, on the whole a great experience and would return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r632525356", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Really Rude staff, they don\u2019t keep your booked table", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "11 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "12stanislavad", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r632525356-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I live in CW, and always planned to visit this place. We booked it for the last night in London for some guests, and all day planned towards this. Arrived in the evening where they told us how they don\u2019t cooperate with Openable app since that very morning and they didn\u2019t keep a table for us. In the most rude manner, they literary didnt care even though it was a mistake from their end that they didnt make sure to pick up all the reservations on time. At least they should have helped us in this situation not just let us go.", "Definitely dont recommend this place, if you want a good view with amazing food in CW just stop by down the street to the main square or even go to Bokan on 38th floor near by. They never disrespect and disappoint their guests that is 100% guaranteed."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r622874648", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great evening ", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "7 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Steppin-owt", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "583"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "203"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r622874648-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We came to celebrate my partner's birthday and use the opportunity to see the wonderful Si Cranston, who I first saw singing on the streets 12 years before, so all credit to him for a fabulous show. We came for the early show, where you are immediately advised you only have the dinner \u00a0table for two hours! On further investigation you find they basically only mean for the first show, I will add however we were never rushed. We had seats overlooking Cabot Sq., on the website it would be beneficial to say you'll have a limited view of the stage area. Whilst a TV is fitted, our view was blocked by a column and decorative plants for a clear view of the stage area, perhaps it's written in the small print?", "As for the decor of the restaurant it is both spectacular and extremely comfortable too, the restaurant has a wonderful ambiance from the moment you arrive. The staff were exceptional and could not have done more to make our visit feel special. On finding it was my partner's birthday, after our meal they brought a small birthday greeting cake, this was a lovely touch. There is a wide selection of choices for all tastes on the menu and an immense wine list too. The food was of ample portions and well cooked and presented, again I add you are made to feel important and that as an individual the occasion is for you, fantastic friendly and attentive service.", "I will add & it's not just here, adding the service charge (12.5%) in advance is a pet peeve. I only hope it's only the staff that receive it! It does subconsciously make you consider that every penny spent is added to the impending service charge.", "Overall, we very much enjoyed our visit, the staff lift the restaurant to another level, well worth a visit but before booking your table ensure you can find where your location will be relative to how you want the evening to be for you."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r622798532", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Carol", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "7 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "carol883", "reviewer_origin": ["london"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r622798532-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Considering how much it costs for cocktails and ", "Food it was actually very mediocre. The burgers were quite dry and the toilets had no toilet paper. You pay all that money then go to the toilet and there\u2019s no toilet paper !! MacDonalds is better and costs a fiver. At least check your toilets during the evening!!! ", "Very Poor"]}
