{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r620390987", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Amy Winehouse Tribute Night", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "29 September 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "JanP888", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "549"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "279"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r620390987-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Let me first start by saying the music and the band were fantastic!!", "We have been here several times and always had a good meal, but what the heck happened last night!! Food was awful, and very expensive awful come to that.", "Wait staff seemed rushed off their feet (not enough staff, especially as I over heard one saying on the way out that they had not had a break the whole time they worked, and never do when they work a shift there.) A waiter delivered our main course to a side table next to us and stood next to it, telling us he wasn't allowed to serve and had to wait for a main waiter, who took at least 5 minutes to appear (busy serving other tables) whilst our food slowly congealed and went cold, we then saw the same waiter who wasn't allowed to actually allowed to put the food on our table, putting someone else food down in front of them!!! It was a complete shambles, and for a supper club that has music nights on a more than regular basis this is simply not acceptable.", "We paid a lot of hard earned money for this, and believe me we were not the only ones complaining last night!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r626765639", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Disappointing", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "20 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Alison F", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r626765639-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Came here for drinks after work, had one of those Time Out vouchers. None of the staff seemed to know what to do with it. Booked a table for 5pm but apparently they don\u2019t open until 6pm (even though the voucher said valid 5pm - 7pm) so waited at the bar. Cocktails were nice but they didn\u2019t have all the ones listed on the Time Out menu so limited choice. Terrible service - they were more interested in people ordering food. Nice place but wouldn\u2019t go back for drinks."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r623427010", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Birthday lunch", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "9 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LisaKalugin", "reviewer_origin": ["Milton Keynes, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "62"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r623427010-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were seated by the window and enjoyed lovely views over Cabot Square. The atmosphere was warm and friendly and the live jazz band were a treat (and not too loud!). We had the 3 course Sunday lunch chosen from a set menu which came with a glass of prosecco and we opted to have the 3/4 bottle of wine too. Very generous portions but the food itself was average with roast potatoes that were so rock hard they were inedible. That said the atmosphere and surroundings were so enchanting we'll definitely return!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r624609901", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Morag C", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "14 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "momocameron14", "reviewer_origin": ["Glasgow, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "124"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r624609901-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Wonderful time at Lulu show and meal on Friday night 4 of us travelled down from Glasgow all good friends great night ...food was incredible scallops amazing show fabulous loved loved loved it we will be back at another venue staff were friendly too would highly recommend beautiful club "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r623791680", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Very nice", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "10 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Suzy x", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r623791680-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Only stayed for a little but loved the live music and atmosphere. Drinks were really good too. Staff were pleasant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r625319686", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday Lunch!", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "16 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ToniMurphy", "reviewer_origin": ["Milton Keynes, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "128"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "39"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r625319686-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited Boisdale with my Dad, his girlfriend and my boyfriend for my birthday lunch on Sunday. It was absolutely fabulous. Great service by the waitresses and glorious decor in the restaurant itself. The jazz band was playing and it was just a beautiful atmosphere. The food was incredible. We had the three courses. For starters i had the chilli squid, my boyfriend had the smoked salmon and my dad and his girlfriend had the avocado and poached egg on toast. All superb. For mains, i went for the salmon, my boyfriend had the aubergine parmigiana burger, my dad had the smokehouse burger and his girlfriend opted for the pork roast which was that huge her veg and potatoes came seperately. Portions were sized generously and were so tasty. For desserts my boyfriend had the buttermilk pancakes and my dad and his girlfriend had the chocolate tortes. For me they brought out my cheesecake with candles and \u201cHappy Birthday\u201d written in chocolate sauce. Really lovely and such a thoughtful touch! Wine was flowing and I had a wonderful \u201cSummer Rose\u201d cocktail which was to die for. Thank you for making it so special, we will be back. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r619933655", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good Food - relaxing atmosphere", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "27 September 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "559tobiasr", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "267"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "485"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r619933655-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had lunch there on a Sunday. There was Jazz Music included which was quite nice I must admit. Not to loud and easy listening. The views are quite nice from that restaurant. Unfortunately the Bar on the first floor was closed. They seemed to be a bit understaffed but the staff members who were there have been very friendly. We chose the lunch menu with wine included. It included a glass of sparkling wine for the start plus 3/4 of a bottle of white and red wine depending on your food per person. Price wise absolutely alright. I had Salmon for a starter which was really nice. The beef and the pie for the main course was alright and desert was good again (cheese cake). All in all a very good lunch with entertainment and not too pricey. Unfortunately a certain wow factor was missing to vote for 5 stars."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r606428433", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Sunday Lunch", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "14 August 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Ashsaw", "reviewer_origin": ["Surrey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "537"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "221"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r606428433-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very nice setting, very friendly and helpful service.", "The Sunday Lunch is a set menu with choices that isn't the best value I've ever had but this is the City - although they won't get their regular clients on a Sunday - and it makes a nice change.", "The food was good and we all enjoyed the experience."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r611431367", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fantastic Restaurant, one of the best in London", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "28 August 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LondonReview247", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "31"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "50"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r611431367-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Fantastic place to have a meal and enjoy a show if you fancy.", "Have been twice in the part, one to see a Santana tribute and another time to see The Stones. Both times have been equally enjoyable, steak was cooked to perfection, waiters and bar staff were courteous and friendly.", "Would most certainly recommend. Careful when booking a table for a show as you may get a table right up the front and be slightly deafened :)"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r603079946", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Music excellent, food bit boring", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "5 August 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Lula927", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r603079946-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited with 3 friends on Sat 4th Aug. Canary Wharf shopping mall is a bit of a maze so it took a while to find it, especially exiting the tube from the Jubilee line. It's apparently easier to find if you use the DLR. ", "Once you get to the elevators that take you up to the restaurant, it takes a while to figure out that not all of the 4 lifts actually take you up to that floor. ", "Once inside, staff very welcoming and friendly. On this occasion there was an old school reggae sound system Saxon on the bill, which is what we were really looking forward to. They didn't disappoint - which is more that I can say for the menu. We booked a ticket online for \u00a319.95 which was a 2-course meal and the dance to follow.", " An eclectic mix of dishes on the menu ranging from haggis to jerk chicken (not 'jerked' very well, ie not much taste and non-fish tasting fishcakes. I also had the spicy jerk chicken wings for my starter - again, where is the jerk?? Many people ordered the platter for their main as we did, and the corn wraps that came with it (naan bread which I presume was made with corn somewhere in the recipe) were dry.", "We later learnt that during the week the restaurant served as a scottish based one and the organiser of this particular event - lovely Paula who introduced herself to everyone table by table - has taken it over for the summer on weekends. Hence the scottish-west indian combination of meals on the menu.", "We luckily met happy hour 2 for 1 cocktails between 6-7pm (usual price would have been \u00a39.95 per drink). ", "We joined the dancers in the long balcony-like area outside once we had finished eating. The area where the music was playing was very narrow and not really conducive to too many people dancing to be honest, it got very crowded and you couldn't move, so we stayed inside but the vibe wasn't the same.", "An ok place but I wouldn't run back in too much of a hurry for the food. Just go early for the dance so you can grab your spot before it gets too busy!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r612984464", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Groupon deal - \u00e7hateaubriand", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "1 September 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Mart247", "reviewer_origin": ["Nuevo Vallarta, Mexico"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r612984464-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Just returned from a fantastic meal at Boisdale. A great experience , food was really good, staff attentive and service excellent. Thoroughly recommend the deal and the place."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r613557102", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "How wonderful", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "3 September 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Zac C", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r613557102-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had the most amazing time. Great location, wonderful staff and fantastic food. We will definitely be returning and it\u2019s all thanks to the service we received from Roland. He was attentive, polite and honest about the reason our food was slightly delayed. Needless to say the extra wait was definitely worth it and we could not be happier."]}
