{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r596299730", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "BBQ LUNCH SATURDAY", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "15 July 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MartiniGold", "reviewer_origin": ["London -East"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "150"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "66"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r596299730-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited here with a group of friends", " Lovely terrace area. Staff were welcoming. ", "The set up for the BBQ could have been a bit better. ", "The salads breads along with chicken skewers,lamb - didnt really like but worth the \u00a315.95 I guess. ", "Also,I must point out not everyone eats Pork so this does need to be separated from Chicken and Lamb in consideration.", "The chef did go out his way to grill fresh chicken which my friend was happy with.", "I must say a fruit salad or something of a sort light dessert could have been added to the buffet that would have been nice. ", "Will return maybe try the Cajun BBQ too .", "Thanks for a great service."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r593066825", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Ignorant staff", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "4 July 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LondonJimTraveller", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r593066825-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited the venue for a few quiet drinks. Some colleagues joined us who kindly offered to pick up the tab. The waitress proceeded to shout at us insisting that the balance had not been paid.", "When it transpired that this was a mistake, the waitress offered no apology."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r598776601", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Wedding anniversary ", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "23 July 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Petchi", "reviewer_origin": ["Luton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "73"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r598776601-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Picked this place out some weeks before the visit, because we liked the look of it. Surroundings and live music all good. However food doesn\u2019t offer best value for money and is only average. Service was poor waiter not smiling once through out the meal. Had to wait an about an hour for the bill and when it arrived they had the cheek to charge us the \u00a322 service charge. I got the impression that they weren\u2019t bothered if we had any intentions of revisiting as we left. (Not very friendly. )And the place was hardly at capacity, not that surprising really if this is the way they treat customers."]}
