{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r602290622", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "One petulant person spoilt it for all", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "3 August 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "WorkNPlayHomeNAway", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "108"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "62"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r602290622-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were booked to for a table at Canary Wharf on Monday 30th July ", "I had visitors from overseas and thought it would be a great experience to see a great British Restaurant.", "I\u2019ve attended Boisdale City and Mayfair on several occasions and had drinks in The Wharf - always a great experience. ", "Unfortunately the gentleman who was serving downstairs at 9:00pm on Monday was unnecessarily rude.", "1) It was clear from the start that we were not welcome. His meet and greet highlighted that we had 9 people not six - this was not acceptable. When we went up to the lovely lady on the 2nd floor - she had no issues and simply changed the booking. She informed that downstairs was empty. Upstairs was going to be loud with a rock band. So we decided to sit down stairs. ", "2) One person in group was diabetic and needed a quick snack. When one of the group picked up a bowl of nuts, the same gentleman snapped at him - stating that people spit into these. Not necessary to be that graphic regardless of the hygiene implications.", "3) Even after we complained to the manager, he continued with unnecessary curtness such as stating at 920pm that we must order immediately as kitchen shut at 10pm. ", "We settled the UKP70 bar bill and moved on somewhere else for dinner. ", "This is in contrast to the two barmen who were exemplary and in contrast to what I have experienced and expect from Boisdale."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r592570443", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Lovely lunch with a great atmosphere ", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "2 July 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "georgieboy1655", "reviewer_origin": ["Horsham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "59"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "44"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r592570443-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited Boisdale for the first time a couple of weeks ago. ", "Food was really excellent and the staff and service were professional, friendly and on the ball during a busy lunchtime. Was a very nice atmosphere in the restaurant and I look forward to going back to try out the dinner menu. It also has a lovely terrace bar below the main restaurant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r588705098", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Late meal and music", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "19 June 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jeff L", "reviewer_origin": ["Edinburgh"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "63"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r588705098-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We chose to combine a late (ish) meal with the live music offering. Have to say that both were very well done. The food was great, with a small but interesting menu, cocktails also v good. Will definitely be back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r589216068", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Stunning food, Atmosphere and Service", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "20 June 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Ruth H", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r589216068-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale is situated in a great location in Canary Wharf, with great views.", "The menu had a great choice for all of us, and was absolutely lovely.", "Venue also caters for all types people with a good mixture of Couples, Business, Solo and families, giving the place a great atmosphere.", "On leaving the restaurant there was music just starting to softly play, giving it the extra WOW.", "Great place fully recommend."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r587539958", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Love the food", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "15 June 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Pochums", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "58"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r587539958-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This was an impromptu visit after spotting a 50% off a la carte offer. I've lost count of the amount of times I have eaten here.", "On this occasion i felt compelled to review because the food was excellent. To be fair it's usually very good but this time i was very happy!", "I maintain their ribeye is the best I've had in London (and I've eaten A LOT). The triple cooked chips send me to heaven every time.", "On this occasion i tried going vegetarian. I must admit I wasn't exactly overwhelmed with options but what i ate was delicious. Started with the asparagus and egg which i did not expect to be impressed by; the flavours and quality of cooking were perfect. Then onto the pumpkin tortellini for main. Again excellent flavours and a touch on the stodgy side (which i like but may not be to everyone's taste). Sprinkled with some crispy cheesy seedy things which made it a 10/10 for me!", "We got one of the great tables by the window (go early) with the lovely view of cabot square fountain. ", "Only disappointment was service is slow (which has been the case every time) and on this occasion just not very pleasant from our main waiter e.g. \"what do you want?\" were the first words we got and the tone was much the same thereafter.", "It's also not cheap and without the offer it would not have been my first choice but after that meal I'm hooked! I'd definitely recommend it if you are not in a hurry, not starving (the wait will seem longer) and not a delicate flower."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r587899090", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Exceptionally disappointing", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "16 June 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Laura M", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r587899090-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went here for Christmas lunch, wine was off, staff unhelpful, additional candle for dark table proved to be a real problem for them. Food nothing special and overpriced. Bill was totally inaccurate, charged twice for all food. Enormous service charge added automatically to bill. On the plus side the music was good. Won\u2019t be returning and don\u2019t recommend."]}
