{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r590338747", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic night, entertainment was amazing. ", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "24 June 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Lesley_AnneD_12", "reviewer_origin": ["Aberdeen, Scotland, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "21"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r590338747-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We wanted to experience a little bit of the London Jazz scene and were not disappointed, we combined dinner and a live show and loved every minute of it. As it was a once off we didn\u2019t mind the extra money spent on drinks and desserts. The staff were fantastic, very attentive and service was quick. As for the show, Nicole Emmanuelle: The Ella Fitzgerald Songbook was simply breathtaking and the closest I have seen that sounds like the First Lady of jazz herself. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r591410307", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing food and service", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "28 June 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "dm82277", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r591410307-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I visited this bar and restaurant for a work social evening and I can't recommend it highly enough.", "With only a small party of four we had a few drinks in the bar before heading upstairs for a meal. The food was amazing and we could not fault the service.Each of us had a starter, main and dessert and no one was disappointed. ", "There was a good selection of dishes on the menu, with standard options covered but also some more unusual dishes, which we tried.", "The food was matched by the service. from the bar staff downstairs to the waiter upstairs everyone was friendly, polite and professional.", "Definitely recommend it for almost any occasion as the environment is lovely and can cater for everyone."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r592143445", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "A Special Experience", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "1 July 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Klaus C", "reviewer_origin": ["Greenhithe, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "331"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "165"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r592143445-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We want there last Saturday evening, having booked a 8.15pm table on level 2 to enjoy the second part of the stage entertainment in the restaurant. This was booked some months before and changes once although, I was told, they do not normally change appointments. Paid \u00a3190 for 4 people which included the given menu.", "Wine list relatively affordable but other drink are expensive.", "On the 1st floor bar area there is however nowhere to sit outside, one either has to pre-book a terrace table or be a member to sit in that area. Otherwise it is very limited outside and the bar inside can get very busy.", "Restaurant menu and service was great and I can strongly recommend the haggis (although maybe as starter only) as very strong and spicy but brilliant (irrespective what it is made out of!). ", "I would go again but for a special event only as can get expensive."]}
