{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r572588357", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday Treat", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "11 April 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "aitchjayes", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, UK"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "59"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "103"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r572588357-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went with my daughter last night, early dinner and the restaurant was fairly empty but was quite busy by the time we left. Used a Groupon voucher - \u00a355 for 2 Chateaubriand and glass of champagne very good value. Our server - Krzystof Toda (had to copy that from our bill) was very knowledgeable with his wines and recommendation and attentive. Had a table by the window overlooking the square and fountain. ", "Was here at Christmas for a Sinatra tribute which was excellent and am about to book for an Ella Fitzgerald tribute in June."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r573101935", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Food good, but....", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "13 April 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "mrgbarnes", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r573101935-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went on a Groupon Chateaubriand meal deal on a Wednesday April 11th for 6pm. Had a great table with a nice view. However they had to be reminded about the champagne that was included in the deal. And they plain forgot our \"unlimited\" fries. And we had a long wait for our meal, and it had only just opened. Not once we're we asked about our food during the main. In their defence they knocked the starters and tip off the bill, but I will sadly not be returning. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r575061013", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Could Do Better...", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "23 April 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Nidgehammer", "reviewer_origin": ["Stevenage, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1453"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "859"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r575061013-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Despite indifferent service, I would have been prepared to award more stars had the food been up to the high standards we expect when paying these prices. ", "The prawn cocktail starters were good quality but the mains of roast chicken no better than we would get at a local pub. Not bad but decidedly average and really not worth the price paid despite the attractive surroundings. I\u2019m also becoming increasingly annoyed at the number of restaurants that insist that you have (or at least pay for) dessert. I wouldn\u2019t choose to have dessert, indeed none of our party did but there was only a three course option which I find odd. There\u2019s a sugar tax for a good reason and we\u2019re trying to cut back so why not offer two course options - well I think we all know why..", "Despite being a little underwhelmed I would probably have given this restaurant another try but my wife has spoken and we won\u2019t return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r579979248", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Safe choice ", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "13 May 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "KittyTrigger77", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "63"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r579979248-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a table in the bar and terrace area rather than the main restaurant because we weren\u2019t staying long enough for the jazz (starts at 915 on a weekday and you had to pay extra to buy \u2018tickets\u2019). Food was as expected - good quality if a little over priced. The smoked salmon starter is my favourite as it comes with a number of options to \u2018dress\u2019. The calamari and sausage tapas starters are smaller portions but still good. For mains we had the chicken mushroom pie (creamy, good) and two fillet steaks (7oz right size). Wouldn\u2019t recommend the Bloody Mary Sauce but the peppercorn was fine. All in all a safe choice for a meal. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r574999049", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good food, bad experience", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "22 April 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "dieterd808", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r574999049-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["It was my girlfriend's birthday and I'd booked a table at Gaucho in Piccadilly for us to have a nice meal in a rather swanky restaurant. ", "I met up with a friend that day and he convinced me to go to Boisdale as the steak is supposedly amazing, with that in mind I took his advice and booked a table. ", "When I called the restaurant I was told there weren't any tables available at 20.00 however there was a table available 45 minutes later, i was also informed that there would be an additional \u00a312.50 per person added to the bill if we are still at the restaurant after 21.45 as their entertainment starts. I found this a tad annoying as I wasn't interested in seeing the entertainment but I agreed as it was a special occasion.", "When we arrived we were seated at a rather small square table and I asked if we could move to the larger circular tables. The waiter was very helpful and dresed the new table and after 10 minutes we were seated.", "The waiter gave us our menus, took our drink orders, house wine & a tonic water, then went about his business. Another couple arrived five or so minutes later and sat at the table infront of ours. They wait five minutes and also ordered their drinks. We waited another 10 minutes before we started thinking the wait was exorbitant when we saw the couple that can after us get their drinks, all in all we waited about 20 minutes from our to receipt of our drinks", "The starter was good, we had peppered squid and for main we had the large steak which was amazing. However our waiter forgot our drinks order, we had to ask him twice, we asked for water and that too was forgotten. When paying for a meal for two which is due to cost between \u00a3100-\u00a3200 You expect good service.", "By the time we asked for the bill (\u00a3143) I was ready to go home and decided to pay \u00a3150 instead of the \u00a3163 which included the service. I thought rather than pay no service at all I'll pay some.", "I was not ready for the waiter's response when I told him what I was paying. ", "He abruptly and in a very curt manner asked me why u was was not paying the service and that the meal costs \u00a3163 And that's what I should pay.", "This left an extremely bitter taste in my mouth. You see, I'm happy to pay a service charge even when the service isn't the best but when I'm paying such a large sum of money for a meal i expect a good level of service and don't expect to be barked at by a waiter because I decided to pay less. ", "The restaurant states if you aren't happy with the service in any way don't pay. I didn't expect that reaction and won't be going back there regardless of how good the food is."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r568284443", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Important business lunch which lacked services", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "23 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "194joelb", "reviewer_origin": ["New Malden, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "45"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r568284443-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Took clients out for lunch, there were 7 of us and we were located slightly away from all the other diners (upon request) however we didn\u2019t received ANY service. We had to ask for drinks, then to order food and then finally the bill (I don\u2019t think I\u2019ve ever had such poor service - as it\u2019s not as if these people haven\u2019t been trained)", "We all went for a famous burger.", "Half the burgers appeared to be fine, but some of them were over cook (nuked) and the buns were burnt) again no-one bothered to ask how our food was until collecting the plates ... and even upon providing feedback, no attempt to rectify the problem.", "However I enjoyed my diverted g&t but the rest of the experience / meal was poor. Left disappointed and will not go back or recommend to anyone I like.", "Unfortunately too many places in London providing poor service / food and very high prices, of which this place appears to be one of them."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r566710552", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Country House in town", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "15 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "stephengrange", "reviewer_origin": ["La Herradura, Spain"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r566710552-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A delightful oasis of country house charm with jazz, blues and live music often tinkling in the background. Reasonably varied Menu coupled with sure footed cooking makes for a pleasant experience. Lovers of a dram will be in whisky heaven. Attentive but not intrusive staff. Well worth the visit but do book ahead."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r571853670", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday celebration", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "8 April 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "488jilll", "reviewer_origin": ["Blackmore, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r571853670-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great way to spend a Saturday night! I initially had a problem with my booking as I thought I had booked the set menu deal inc Jazz via Open table but it turned out to be the First floor grill . However once the maitre'd ( Kate ) realised we were celebrating birthdays she very kindly arranged for us to be moved upstairs. The food was lovely , the music was excellent and the service delivered by Kate and our waiter made the night very special. Thank you for a really memorable night!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r568259650", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "St Patrick's Day fun", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "23 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Shirley F", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "66"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "50"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r568259650-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a fabulous afternoon at Boisdale Canary Wharf . I haven't been here before but will defiantly be going again .", "I brought tickets on line for Guinness and a burger for St Patrick's day , not knowing what to expect , but was very pleasantly surprised. On arrival we were shown to our table and had fantastic waiter service all afternoon . The burgers were delicious . ", "The staff here were so nice , we stayed for the evening entertainment which was a lovely little Irish band . ", "Highly recommended"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r578202746", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Brunch with Friends", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "6 May 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "julie b", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "165"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "55"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r578202746-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Atmosphere dark and mysterious a little bit disappointing", "I would say stepping back into time. we were showed to our seats and the view was pleasant. The food was ok. I had the full English without the black pudding. There was a older gentleman playing the piano which was nice and the only lively thing. Not one of my best but for meeting friends it was ok"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r577032033", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Horrible Staff", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "1 May 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "talkingmongoose", "reviewer_origin": ["Loughborough, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r577032033-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Food was nice, but there were two staff members who were particularly unpleasant. I spoke to a couple of other visitors on the dancefloor and they spoke about how one waiter had shoved them out of the way and stood on their toes!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r568687064", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good dinner and evening but poor service", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "25 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "BDelapre", "reviewer_origin": ["Paris, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "62"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "43"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r568687064-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I recently went here for dinner, booking a deal from another website. The venue is very elegant and beautiful and we got offered a great table near the stage where the band would play later on.", "We waited quite a bit before ordering and did not receive the glass of bubbly that was part of the offer we booked. It was later rectified and arranged for the desert, so no big deal. But later on, the service was just very long between each dish and we had to remind the waiter of the glass of bubbly.", "The show was great, the food was good but we had to wait again a long time to get our bill. When we paid, the waiter did not even thank us or said goodbye. So it did not feel as special as we would have liked, such a pity!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r576575095", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "No dancing!!!!", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "29 April 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ctid22", "reviewer_origin": ["Jersey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r576575095-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Food was ok, music brilliant, completely spoiled by over zealous staff who tried to stop dancing (at a Motown night! Lol). Appalling lack of judgement, they did all they could to ruin atmosphere which seems bizarre. Take care spending your money here."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r570051898", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Birthday celebration", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "1 April 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LightPacker522851", "reviewer_origin": ["Paphos, Cyprus"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r570051898-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited Boisdale for the second time last night to see Legend, the Bob Marley tribute band. The band were faultless, the food was great and the service improved since my last visit. Best gin n tonic ever! Atmosphere fabulous with the whole place on their feet dancing, wonderful night, will return soon.", "Honor W."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r569698117", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Atmospheric and delicious", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "30 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "stubbsea", "reviewer_origin": ["Hilton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r569698117-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to Boisdale with another couple for dinner on a week night, and this place was buzzing! The restaurant itself is charming - cosy, subtly lit, and well furnished. We had delicious scallop and prawn starters, followed by on the bone steaks, all recommended by our wonderfully attentive waiter, Trevor. ", "One of the attractions of the restaurant was the live music which started during dinner. We enjoyed the music very much, but our only criticism would be that it was a fraction too loud. ", "I would very much recommend this restaurant to those that enjoy live music and lovely in lively surroundings. If you're a whisky lover, I would imagine it's a must as it has the biggest whisky bar I've ever seen - around 300 bottles we were told! All in all a very positive experience, and we wouldn't hesitate to return. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r570522940", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Pleasant atmosphere", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "2 April 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Lola363", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r570522940-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["It was quite difficult to get to venue due to train closures but we we're looking forward to Sunday Lunch and Jazz. Warm welcome,great table for two. Waiter was lovely but the food was not good. Masses of beef but not of good quality and everything else was rather amateur. Jazz hardly featured. In hindsight I wouldn't have made the effort ."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r571172899", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday meal", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "5 April 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Aiden H", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r571172899-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This place was amazing. Live music was great and the food was excellent. The waiter service was on point couldn\u2019t fault them either. Has an indoor cigar shop where not only can you purchase a cigar but also smoke it. Great night 10 out of 10"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r571087003", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely afternoon", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "4 April 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "rosiemarch", "reviewer_origin": ["Buckingham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r571087003-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went for the Easter Sunday roast and jazz experience. They sat us by a window table as requested and there was no trouble with the telephone booking as people have complained. They answered first ring and I received a confirmation email before the call ended!", "We had the 3 course set menu. The food was generous, good options and more importantly tasted fantastic.", "The jazz music was really good too and we weren\u2019t rushed to leave.", "The only negative is that we had to keep asking for our water to be refilled when other diner had this done without asking. We felt a bit excluded."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r562552260", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Food\u2018n Jazz", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "24 February 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MikQuadrat", "reviewer_origin": ["Konigstein im Taunus, Germany"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r562552260-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Scottish style, nice location in the heart of Canary Wharf, huge Whiskey bar, live Jazz music and good food make this place a nice experience. However, pricing is at the higher end."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r566129569", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Anniversary Lunch", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "12 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "chloejos", "reviewer_origin": ["Hertfordshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "51"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r566129569-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My husband surprised me for an anniversary lunch! We have been to the Boisdale before with friends so i was excited! We were seated by the circular window which was a great view of the whole restaurant. Our waiter i believe was called Jos\u00e9 and he was great, he explained the menu perfectly(this was also Mothers day -so was a little different), he knew all about the dishes and helped us choose! The starters, my husband had the squid and i had the egg Benedict, both starters were incredible, such great quality. This was followed by the amazing roast beef and i had the roast chicken this was amazing, great size portions accompanied by carrots, greens and potatoes! Both white and red wine and prosecco we had were lovely too. We had the Pineapple carpaccio dessert and the Dark chocolate marquise, honeycomb", "& salted caramel, both were incredible but the marquise won! Rich, full of flavour and i recommend to anyone if it's on the normal menu! Both dessert plates had 'Happy Anniversary' written in chocolate on them which made our experience even more special.", "The live jazz band were good but unfortunately seemed pretty quiet! Jos\u00e9(waiter) really is a credit to Boisdale! We will recommend this to all our friends!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r562013035", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect !", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "21 February 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "AgneseV38", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r562013035-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["What a stunning place ! I can nearly admit it's kind of my one of the favourite places now ! Service ( by Alexandra / Alex ) - our waitress was lovely . Her knowledge was very good , done some good recommendations . Spot on service ! Always was there for us ! ", "Food was amazing ! We are returning guests ! ", "Ambiance , live music , views - perfect !"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r563642738", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Scottish Beef in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "2 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "OzoneSpin", "reviewer_origin": ["London, UK"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "50"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r563642738-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale is one of my favourite eating places in the Wharf area - in the summer there is a veranda - narrow but with table and chairs overlooking Cabot Square below. I\u2019ve always had great food and service and regularly meet friends for evening drinks and dinner. Access is from within the main concourse down from the DLR towards Cabot Sq and up in a lift."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r563085932", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Food & Jazz", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "27 February 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "blueval", "reviewer_origin": ["Portugal"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "707"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "201"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r563085932-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Came here for the Sunday lunch & jazz, very good value for money. Took a while to book, no one took any notice of the emails I sent for a while and I got a lot of help from the Mayfair restaurant, so thanks to them, but on the day everything was perfect, massive food portions, and really nice staff, particularly ours who was Meli."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r560850258", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Overrated and expensive.", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "16 February 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "jumpingjohn", "reviewer_origin": ["Ongar, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "140"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "66"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r560850258-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very disappointed. Paid \u00a342.50 per person for a night out plus entertainment and found out I had wasted my money. The band was very good but that is the best I can say about the place. The food was mundane to say the least. I ordered the smoked salmon for starter and got a plate with smoked salmon covering it and a small wedge of lemon. I, at least, expected some sales to accompany it. For the main course I ordered the special burger but would have been better off in Burger King. My wife ordered the steak and it was so small it was untrue, plus it came it\u2019s chips and nothing else. All very were extra outside the Prince we paid. The drinks cost a fortune."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r563962449", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good food, good views", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "3 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "tregarvon21", "reviewer_origin": ["Chingford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r563962449-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Always great food and the views are pretty decent. Have only been for business lunches beat it's a lot better when full....not much atmosphere at lunchtime."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r565381179", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great night", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "9 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "tallbloke1", "reviewer_origin": ["Surrey"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "38"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r565381179-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife made a late booking based on hotel recommendation. No problem getting in on a Thursday. We had starter and main plus bottle of wine and a couple of single malts. Music starts at 2115 each night and if you are still at table there is a small service charge if you are still at the table. Steak was perfect and my wife had cod which was excellent. Wine list is extensive as is the whisky list. Would recommend. Cost \u00a3175"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r564813589", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Fumador, Dinner,Dance and Tartan!", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "6 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Dee_Dee_Soup", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "50"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r564813589-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Not a Kilt in Sight Unfortunatley.", "This is a small chain made popular by ", "It's Live Jazz music and cover artists,Wedding Singer Standard.", "They have a fumador which is fun and a good selection of Whiskey, Bit like a Hotel feel Lodged in a Time Zone of its own.", "The Walled gallery make the Place look Clutered with already Tartan every where:)", "2 floors for Diners and More casual diners lower floor, with lots of Oysters! Yuuum.", "Some interesting characters about the place, every area has a Story, so you will fit in.", "The Menu is really good with Basic Steak,Chips,Mushrooms,Yeay", "I've been in with friends and had a Fab time!", "The Staff are always changing and still never smile, which is a shame really because the tips and service charge for waiters is quite generous.", "There is No TGI feel here or T.V Screen although it maybe a cool idea for the Bar on lower level.", "It's a Sort of Prohibition meets Tartan with Cigar Smoking Number Crunchers and Friends in a Surreal Tardis Dr Who Scene, With everyone piling in and having a Fab time.", "Where people are dressed Smart Casual.", "The Food is Incomplicated and Simple British.", "The Wines aren't anything Special as they get their Suppliers from same as Their Competitors???", "So as a Serious Foodie I would go for a Selection of Beers, Ask if they have a Taster Menu for Beers/Food and stock any beers from Scotland???", "For sure the Whiskey is a Must try!!", "Advanced Bookings for upstairs restaurant Advised as it gets Busy when Music is On!", "I think they should put on an Open Mic night!! It would be Fab!", "Best Part of the Restaurant is the Terrace!", "Enjoy:)"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r566104004", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Great whiskies...that\u2019s about it \ud83d\ude15", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "12 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "kegmar", "reviewer_origin": ["Stoke-on-Trent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "82"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "38"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r566104004-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Really Really looked forward to this... ", "Lover of fine whiskies... one of the widest range of whiskies I\u2019ve come across. However, quite heavily priced! ", "But what really upsets me, is the service. Bartender was in no way knowledgeable, brought me the WRONG whiskey twice before pouring. And when I asked again for the right one, I was huffed / puffed at, before he walked away looking for it... ", "Only eye contact was to roll eyes away... quite upsetting really...", "At nearly \u00a330 for two whiskeys, I frankly expect more from the staff who are essentially the flagship and front of house for their product...", "BUT.... best choice of whiskey if that\u2019s your thing "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r556248669", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent, knowledgeable service by Filipe at the cigar library!", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "25 January 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "KarenRT18", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r556248669-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I was purchasing a box of cigars for my partner and Filipe provided excellent customer service. He is extremely knowledgeable, trustworthy and helpful."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r560604125", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Legendary Place", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "15 February 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "twentysomething_x", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r560604125-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I have been to Boisdale on several occasions, with friends. my other half and for family meals. Yes it is pricey but the food is exquisite and the menu has something for everyone. I'm usually not a huge fan of haggis but the haggis they serve is delicious. ", "The staff are very good and attentive, the shows they put on are definitely worth seeing! so far we have seen a Ray Charles Tribute and also the rat pack! both excellent. ", "I look forward to my next visit!"]}
