{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r558336750", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Highly recommended", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "4 February 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "g0ldiebf", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r558336750-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale is welcoming and relaxed. My family and I went for Sunday lunch today for my parent\u2019s 50th anniversary. The food was excellent, and the service is friendly and attentive. They made my parents feel very special and I am grateful for the extra effort that the staff went to, to make their visit memorable. ", "As mentioned, the food was really lovely, and they give you a very good portion. I can't bare it when you are presented with a plate with hardly anything on it, which doesn\u2019t happen here. We were all pleasantly full after the 3 course lunch, and I would not hesitate to recommend it to everyone."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r558358724", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Super Sunday lunch", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "4 February 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jacqui b", "reviewer_origin": ["Shrivenham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "189"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "58"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r558358724-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We came here in November for my husbands birthday and returned with friends for Sunday Jazz lunch. Both visits were equally good- very good service, well presented tasty food - roast was excellent, crispy potatoes and well cooked vegetables. We upgraded to the half bottle of wine each and both times our glasses were refilled above and beyond the said half bottle!! Relaxing atmosphere and great to have the music playing throughout lunch."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r558817892", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Expensive meal", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "6 February 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jeff M", "reviewer_origin": ["Auckland, New Zealand"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "308"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "74"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r558817892-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I came here with a group of friends. Firstly, the band were great. Very entertaining and had many people from the audience up and dancing. The food was good though very overpriced. The service was alright although I had to fill my water myself as the waiters avoided the table."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r558822169", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic restaurant with live music", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "6 February 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "seaniem_13", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r558822169-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I dined here on Saturday night with friends. The service was impeccable. We had the 3 courses and glass of bubbly offer for \u00a327 and it was well worth it. We also ordered a lovely bottle of Portuguese wine that was value for money. The food was delicious and piping hot. Great menu choices. The staff were very professional and friendly. The live jazz started around 10 and the jive aces were brilliant. There are not many venues in London with live music so this added to a special evening. I would highly recommend and go back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r559618525", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Bottomless prosecco brunch heaven", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "10 February 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "kayceequeue", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r559618525-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were lucky enough to be given a voucher by relatives for a bottomless brunch here and we had a wonderful experience!", "Though initial booking proved a little tricky (had to be done by email but it took several emails and phone calls to actually get booked in), the lovely lady I eventually spoke with who made our booking was extremely friendly and even recommended a later brunch so as to benefit from the live music.", "On the day we were wowed by the venue itself, it felt strangely surreal to have the huge restaurant and bar on one side of us and a fab view of Cabot square and the river beyond on the other. ", "The menu was an interesting mix, not entirely what I was expecting from a brunch menu but some delicious sounding dishes nonetheless, I chose the squid and it was delicious. I forget now what my other half had, the dangers of not writing a review straight away, but I seem to think it involved roast beef.", "Most importantly, the waiters were not stingy with the prosecco! Bottomless is a slight misnomer, as with so many venues offering this there is a time limit so I was on a slight mission to ensure I benefited from my fair share before time was called (hic!) but our glasses were never empty which was great.", "It was fairly quiet when we arrived, with more people arriving as we approached lunchtime. I can imagine when that dining room is full and the music is playing the atmosphere must be incredible. ", "We both thoroughly enjoyed it and would like to go back for dinner."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r559973023", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great night , lovely food , excellent entertainment", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "12 February 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Michelle H", "reviewer_origin": ["Thurso, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "83"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "56"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r559973023-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked a night here when Rebecca Ferguson was singing for my husbands birthday . It was the best birthday hes ever had ! Rebecca was fantastic , the food was beautiful and the atmosphere was great . We would definately go again . They even upgraded our table and wrote happy birthday with a candle in my husbands cheesecake . "]}
