{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r553706900", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Unexpectedly Disappointing ", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "14 January 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Steve G", "reviewer_origin": ["Tadworth, England, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r553706900-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Having been a regular visitor at Boisdales in Belgravia we thought we would try their restaurant at Canary Wharf. ", "Having arrived early we had a couple of cocktails in the bar and they were superb. We made are way upstairs and were shown to our table and from here is where it all went wrong. There were 3 table for two persons and you could barely walk between then. ", "Next we were given the wrong menus!", "We ordered some wine and sparkling water The wine arrived promptly but we had to ask a further 3 times for the water!!", "The starters arrived as ordered and were both very good indeed. ", "We both chose rib eye steak for main and we ordered two extra side dishes. The steak arrived and were very good, but no side dishes. We just kept being told they were coming!! They did eventually arrive once I had finished my steak so we refused them. The waitress then arrived and asked my wife why we had refused something that we ordered!!!", "We had coffee that was Luke warm and a liquor whilst watching the band. ", "I asked to see the Manager but he never showed his face. Over all a terrible experience and one I will not be repeating."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r553414281", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Rebecca Ferguson Sings The Blues In E14", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "12 January 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "steve b", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "42"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r553414281-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["What a great night!", "To celebrate the growth of our business with a couple of our business partners in 2017 we all decieded to take the two teams out and celebrate in style in an evening of good food and drink with the added bonus of the soulfull, husky voice of Rebecca Ferguson singing to us.", "Rebecca was amazing, she sung a repoitoir of some popular Blues covers and some tracks from her recent 3rd Album \u201cThe Lady Sings The Blues\u201d. She sang for about 90 mins. ", "After the show, I thought it was a nice touch that Rebecca came down through the audience and was happy to have photo\u2019s taken chat and interact with us. I think she hung around for at least 30-45 mins after the show. ", "Amazing.", "I have concentrated in my review on the many positive sides of the evening as I didnt want the terrible service we recieved from our table waiter to cloud what was an excellent show.", "We have visited Biosdales Canary Wharf loads of times before and I want to make it known the service here has been very good.If are served by a waiter called Trevor- please ask for someone else as this will seriously improve your chances of being served promptly. I will be taking this issue up futher with Biosdales to enable them to look into this.", "Trevor was all over the place.", "Thank you Biosdales and Rebecca for a great evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r555663307", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic Evening", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "22 January 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "karenluch", "reviewer_origin": ["Sandwich, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r555663307-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great evening spent at Boisdale on Friday 19th January. Rebecca Ferguson has the most amazing voice and her choice of songs and the brilliant backing group just made the whole evening special. ", "Food and service was first class. Will definitely be back again."]}
