{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r547528898", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Birthday treat", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "16 December 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jan2412", "reviewer_origin": ["Orpington, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "112"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "80"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r547528898-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Service - poor", "Food - poor", "Entertainment brilliant", "Great location, brilliant jazz music, 2 people in our group of 10 sent back their starter and then their main the main was inedible for some not being able to put your fork in a Potatoe is extremely bad, we waited over and hour for drinks and then only half the table got drinks our server told us to send an email as there was no managers available, we ended up get the services and 3 bottles of wine knocked off the bill, I would have rather had great food and better service."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r547511016", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "ATROCIOUS!!", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "16 December 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "10chris02", "reviewer_origin": ["Sorede, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "467"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "153"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r547511016-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We have visited two of the other Boisdale venues before and did really enjoy them so was basically really looking forward to visiting this one.", "IT TURNED OUT TO BE MAJOR DISAPPOINTMENT!", "We had booked a VIP table and sat down at 8.20 and this is when the ongoing wait started and which then kept on happening. ", "We waited about 20 minutes for the menus to arrive, a further 20 odd minutes for some one to ask if we wanted drinks which then took a further 20 mins. At this time, no one had asked if we were ready to order or whether we wanted the wine list so we had to ask for both. Once this was done and the wine had been ordered and delivered, we then faced another 30 minutes or so wait for the starters, then at least another 30 odd minutes for the main course by which time our patience was wearing thin so we demanded why there was so much delay. The answer was ambiguous at best and the apology muted. ", "By the time the main course arrived, our wine had been drunk so I requested a glass of the same wine to accompany the dinner. What arrived was 'plonk' at which time I asked to see the head waiter. He apologised and arranged for a replacement glass of wine which did arrive and which was correct this time.", "On finishing our dinner, believe it or not, there was yet another wait with the cheese platters arriving past 11pm by which time our appetite and patience had disappeared. ", "It also meant that due to our depressed mood, given the wait, we did not enjoy the music as much as we would have hoped especially given this was part of the reason we went.", "That was it, I demanded to see the manager to whom I relayed our thoughts on the whole evening and stated that we would seek compensation and that we would never return to the venue. We also expressed that the experience had clouded our overall impression of the Boisdale group.", "OK, all drinks were wiped from the bill but in our minds, this did not make up for what was by far the worst dining experience we have ever had.", "AVOID!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r547793572", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "London club style decor looking as tired as the food and the entertainment", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "18 December 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "J_dubbs7", "reviewer_origin": ["Croydon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "148"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r547793572-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The title gives you an indication that I was not impressed. Maybe it's a personal thing but giving a poor review is unusual for me so when I mean it I mean it. ", "Everyone and the tables are so packed in that there is little space to move but possibly this is to maximise business in December. To be fair the food was mass catering quality, poor school dinners at best. The table service was excellent at ensuring wine bottles were emptied so that more could be opened and charged for, definitely good for business. The entertainment was shades of grey literally! I am unsure if the band actually wanted to play and even waited until 9.30 to start - I'm just not sure if that was such a great idea.", "I know that I am being generous giving a 'poor' rating but it is the season of good will and giving less than that would be just terrible!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r551505919", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fabulous New Years Eve", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "4 January 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Mac097", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "175"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "57"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r551505919-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Absolutely fabulous New Years Eve with the west end Jersey Boys. Great table (premium, by the bar), excellent food and service. Entertainment was the best we have seen here (having seen Soul sisters last year, and numerous Frank & dean tributes). Disappointed with management decision not to allow dancing at the front, as cramped dancing was always a feature. Someone complained, and not entering into the spirit of the occasion. Jersey boys was so good, really lovely evening in an intimate location. Only negative for us was to have 12.5% service charge added to already expensive (pre paid) dinner and music ticket. A bit strong."]}
