{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r551092516", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "New Years Eve", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "3 January 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Kevin L", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r551092516-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited for New Years Eve and as expected it was a great evening. Good food, good service and fabulous entertainment.", "The only disappointing thing was the managers decision to stop us dancing in front of the stage because of one woman\u2019s complaint she could not see the stage properly. ", "Anyone who has been to Boisdale previously knows that is the place to dance, the squashed packed dance floor just adds to the atmosphere.", "It was just such a shame one person could be so selfish."]}
