{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r542141097", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great venue, good music and food, awful bar service.", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "20 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "JezzaC35", "reviewer_origin": ["Verona, Italy"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r542141097-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Third time we've been and we love the place, Food id good for what it is and our waitress was supper on a busy Friday night. The bar service downstairs is slow and the tree guys on duty were almost surly. Sort it out please Boisdale!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r538566474", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Very overpriced", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "5 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "sanaltos", "reviewer_origin": ["kent"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "30", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r538566474-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Just recently visited for the Friday music night. We have been to one of these evenings before so thought that we knew what to expect. However, as good as the music was the food on the set menu was very over priced as there were supplements on most of it and the main course did not come with any side dishes. The food choices were limited and food was very disappointing. The music finished much earlier than expected which was again disappointing. Sad to say we will not be returning which is a shame as the venue is lovely and music brilliant but food lets it down."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r539278789", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Blinking costly extras Boisdale", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "8 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jay3025", "reviewer_origin": ["Barry, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "126"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "36"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r539278789-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Four of us went here for a Friday night two course Travel Zoo offer costing \u00a380 for 2 courses and a glass of Fizz. The place looks amazing and the singer was great though he did come on a bit late for me and I suspect does multiple gigs in a night as he was off a bit early. Service and food great but the itemised bill was not presented to me and I ended up paying \u00a3200 in extras. I was a bit tiddly and had guests so did not query it. I hounded Boisdale on email and challenged the bill via Amex. All my money has been refunded but it's such a shame this place is plastered all over discount sites and has some of the adverse comments below. Just reprice so as not to try and rip off unsuspecting tourist and City types/sort out your consistency and you have a winner Boisdale."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r538838316", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Cracking place to have fun!", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "6 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "RobDebenham1", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "286"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "121"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r538838316-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Attended a private event at The Boisdale in Canary Wharfe during a trade event at Excel (6th November) and although I\u2019d previously really enjoyed the Belgravia restuarant I was uncertain as to what I\u2019d find..", "I needn\u2019t have been, it was a fantastic evening, great decor (full of conversation starting images), really friendly staff, great drinks and a stage to rival any decent club...", " The night I attended was a \u2018Cuban night\u2019 with great starters and a cracking buffet of delicacies reminiscent of our previous trip to Havana and Cuba....", "The whole evening was a huge success and I will certainly be going back..."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r541995573", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Second visit won't be my last", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "19 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "rosebug", "reviewer_origin": ["beds"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "669"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "307"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r541995573-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Love this place. Feels classy. And Friday night is soul night! The dinner and show ticket is very good value. We had a table with a great view of the stage. Food was good. Service was great even though it was an exceptionally busy evening. We saw The Black Hat Band who were excellent and got everyone up dancing really early. They were fronted by a charismatic talented singer. We had a wonderful night out. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r539616675", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Decent lunch", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "9 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "7RAC", "reviewer_origin": ["York, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "493"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "427"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r539616675-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["+ scotch egg was lovely.", "+ Service is professional and our young waitress was really on the ball.", "+ the burgers are really good here and the atmosphere and quality of food is worth the price. ", "- it was really quiet service and on entering downstairs we were sent upstairs only to be sent back downstairs again. I was with a pregnant lady so that wasn\u2019t well handled. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r540973552", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Mixed feelings", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "14 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "jaynedevine", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "39"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r540973552-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went as group of 8, booked in advance for Frank Sinatra tribute plus 2 course meal \u00a345 ..... ", "The menu was good but 2 out of the 4 choices per course had a supplement. Most of us went for the squid (extra \u00a33) and the steak (extra \u00a38) ..... must point out the food was very good but we had to wait over 2 hours for our main course.....", "The place closed at 12 and we where served our main at 11.10. ....", "We complained and the manager was very apologetic and discounted our drinks bill..... even before that the waiter... (who was excellent) had bought us a bottle of wine on the house for the delay in our food.", "We did have a good time ... but it was expensive and felt a bit ripped off....why bother with a set meal if you are then going to charge so much for supplements...", "I did want to give this a 4 star mark but because of the delay in food and the supplements I felt I couldnt.", "Great venue , food very good, friendly waiters, packed out but they could do much better."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r538140026", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "This place infuriates me ", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "3 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "629BPL", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r538140026-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great venue, great location but boy does the bar, restaurant and service disappoint ", "Been to this place for lunch, drinks, dinner for business and social occasions for years now but finally decided I really can\u2019t say I care if it\u2019s there or not", "Bar service on a busy day / night is always poor, especially if you\u2019re smaller than average build person - there was a time I waited for over 10 minutes the bar man didn\u2019t even acknowledge my existence until another customer he signalled to serve shouted at him to say hey this customer was here before me. This happened not just once - quite a few times", "Food - hit and miss. Did like the miniature Scotch eggs but standard not consistent - sometimes soggy, sometime salty, sometime spot on. Recent visit (not my choice) for lunch- I\u2019d rather forget and never return . The fish cake - apart from being too salty and couldn\u2019t really taste much else, didn\u2019t find much fish there either. The steak was ok but for the surcharge on top of the set lunch price ... day light robbery "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r528190358", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "New Orleans themed night, shocking service", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "29 September 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "cwharfcouple", "reviewer_origin": ["East London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "51"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "20", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r528190358-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We reserved a table for 4 for 28/09/17, 2 of us arrived a bit early and were shown to the bar. The bar staff was VERY busy and not once in the 15 minutes we stood there did anyone even acknowledge our presence despite me actually staring them down. This is basic customer service. We decided out of desperation to sit at our table as we waited for the other two to arrive. Funnily got our drink order taken and drinks in less time than we stood at the bar, made by the very bar tenders that were ignoring us. Go figure...", "The special New Orleans menu was good and I can't complain about the food quality. The prices were breathtaking, but sadly the service one would expect with breathtaking prices was lacking. Again, BASIC customer service skills lacking. Never once did our waitress check back to see that everything was ok. I had to hunt down a fork is it was not replaced after the starter. I literally could no find a waiter or waitress to flag down so I walked to an empty table to get a fork. It seemed the restaurant was understaffed for a Thursday night and everyone seemed rushed off their feet, however this is not an excuse to not get the basics right. Had we not been with special guests I would have asked for the service to be removed from the bill.", "This was our first time at Boisdale and most certainly our last. The whole approach to service was not customer lead and quite frankly if I am paying \u00a380 a head I could have easily had a fine dining experience in London with the service to match.", "You brought NOLA to London but you forgot the key ingredient!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r530682822", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Two out of three is bad", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "7 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "866NickC", "reviewer_origin": ["Norwich, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r530682822-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I have been to Boisdale many times over the last two years but on my last 3 visits 2 have been very poor. The food is generally great but the last two times I have been in a group of 5 people. Two guests on both occasions have not received what they expected, Lamb shank that was pure fat and over cooked steak. The restaraunt were good and swapped them over but it means that you end up eating in two groups which isn't great.", "To top it off this week we were presented with the bill that we paid including the service charge. 10 minutes later we were leaving and a lady came over saying we hadn't paid the bill presenting us with a new \u00a3100 higher bill as they had forgotten some wine on the previous bill. We paid as its the right thing to do but no apology was offered.", "I found the lady who could have been the manager to be transactional with no interest in her customers. It felt like an expensive canteen and we were just part of the process.", "I guess we all learn, my feedback is that it can be a lottery at Boisdale and if something does go wrong the service isn't great."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r531422626", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fabulous food!", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "9 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Pitstop51", "reviewer_origin": ["Taunton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "27"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "44"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r531422626-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked a table there to have a nice meal on a recent visit to London after seeing it on Celebrity Masterchef. Originally planned to have the set meal but ended up choosing from the main menu. It was all fabulous! There was live music too which was an added bonus and the jazz was right up our street. Overall quite expensive but worth every penny. My husband had the lamb and said it was the best he\u2019d ever tasted! Would definitely go back as we usually stay in Docklands and it is just across the river."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r534684463", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fabulous food", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "20 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Surreygirl23", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "31"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r534684463-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["First visit to this restaurant and highly recommend. Great menu choice. Food was fantastic and first class service. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r533108867", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice and calm", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "15 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "tweeniess", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "30"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r533108867-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A friend booked a table for 3 at Boisdale on Saturday night, and we had a fantabulous evening. The meal was very delicious and enjoyable, lovely potion too. Very highly recommended, oh let\u2019s not forget the jazz band, the lead singer was very entertaining. 8/10 if you ask me "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r533395310", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Very disappointed and very sad, I was really looking forward to take my best friend there as a treat.", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "16 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Smillena", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r533395310-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very disappointed and very sad, I was really looking forward to take my best friend there as a treat. The waiters did not seem to know what was going on but that's neither here or there in the scheme of things. The royal seafood platter was a horror of frozen clapped out prawns and some sad old half lobster. But wait for this, the shallot and vinegar to accompany oysters was awful, shallots and vinegar? How can you get that wrong? The steak to follow was tougher than shoe soles, I could not even cut it with a steak knife, let alone chew it. There is something wrong there, they cut corners for profit. And we won't notice?"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r537862878", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sunday jazz was a real treat", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "2 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Emma P", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r537862878-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I took my parents and husband for lunch while my parents were over from Australia. It was a set menu with three courses for an acceptable price (around \u00a337) considering the live music. It was fantastic from start to finish and the experience was made even better by our fantastic waiter, Jose. He ensured absolutely no detail was missed and should be commended for making our time there so memorable. My husband and I will definitely be coming back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r527510733", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic Evening", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "26 September 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "karenpEdinburgh", "reviewer_origin": ["Edinburgh, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "172"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "102"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r527510733-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited Boisdale on Friday night and used a Travelzoo Voucher. It was very easy to book via email. When we arrived we had a lovely table for two quite near the front and were greeted with our glass of prosecco. Jeremy Sassoon was playing with his band and the music was absolutely first rate, very professional and polished. Service was very friendly and we had enough time between courses to really enjoy the wonderful ambiance and the music. Food was good and I would definitely recommend this place if you fancy something romantic and just a bit different - I will definitely be back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r532016953", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday gift", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "11 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "medmonduk", "reviewer_origin": ["Hayes, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r532016953-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went here for a birthday treat to my husband as he likes jazz, blues soul. Great place, the decor was in a tartan theme, and the show we went to see was a Cuban show. The 2course meal that came with the show was fantastic.,and it wasn\u2019t expensive either. The only downfall was the prices of the drinks, atmosphere was alive, and the waiters were very polite"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r536886802", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent Lunch, Excellent Service - a great afternoon", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "29 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "hayes_12", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r536886802-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Having just made a purchase at David M Robinson and wanting to complete our visit to Canary Wharf with lunch the sales person at DMR, Mel highly recommended this restaurant and was kind enough to phone ahead on I and my elderly mothers behalf.", "How glad I was I took her advise. The set lunch menu is excellent with the main course dish of the beef being exceptional. The staff are attentive without being over bearing and made the visit a real treat for my mother. I would without doubt recommend this restaurant for Sunday lunch with the staff and food being absolute top draw."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r524102031", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Always exceeding expectations ", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "13 September 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Meander585321", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r524102031-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went in with no reservation and got a table immediately. Great restaurant with amazing cocktails. Service is great and wine selection top notch. This is the 5th time we're having dinner at this place and service , food qualityMr ambiance absolutely amazing. Highly recommended! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r525035829", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Loonnnggg lunch", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "17 September 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Dave C", "reviewer_origin": ["Camberley, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "98"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r525035829-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Came here for the three course, fixed price, lunch menu. Half of the menu options required a supplement to be paid. Food was lovely, though the steak looked a bit lost and naked on the plate with only a cup of chips for company.", "Service was slow, seats were well wobbly and interior looked shabby. We could see wine splatters on the backs of other seats.", "I expected better of the place.", "But do remember - the food was good."]}
