{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r512400296", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great venue, food, service and music", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "13 August 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "San S", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r512400296-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["All 11 of us girls had a fabulous night at the Boisdale Canary Wharf on Friday. We had a 2 course set menu for only \u00a319.95 with a glass of Pressco via opentable.com. A much varied choice of food on the set menu than our previous visit which was nice. Food was delicious and hot and service was good. A special thank you to Agne for assisting us with the group booking and giving us a great table near the dance floor, as we had requested. We danced non stop to a fanatstic soul live band and had a another great night. For some of us it was a third visit and once again we were not disappointed. Will definitely be returning again soon . Thank you to the Boisdale team"]}
