{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r504971684", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Mother-in-law Birthday ", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "24 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello Samantha B, ", "Thank you for taking the time to write your recent review. I am keen to get some more detail on why you found the food offering to be disappointing. ", "Please contact me directly on gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk as I would like the opportunity to speak to you directly. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Samantha B", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r504971684-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The venue is very nice, the whole ambiance. They had a live band which played lovely music but the food was disappointing. Not worth the money. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r503831200", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Wonderful Family Visit - Jamaica 55 Excellent Event", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "20 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Sue M, ", "Thank you so much for letting us know of your recent visit, and enjoyment. I am glad you eventually found us and were able to take advantage of our Jerk wrap 'Happy Hour' - it is a fantastic offer and, I agree, delicious! Paired with an ice cold Red Stripe or refreshing Appleton Cocktail it is the perfect snack on a summers evening. ", "There are areas of the terrace that are less exposed to the music as we do try and cater for all needs. However, should you join us again on a Tuesday, Wednesday or Saturday you can request to be close to the music and we can point you in the right direction....where I am sure you can make some musical requests!", "We look forward to seeing you soon, ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sue M", "reviewer_origin": ["Negril, Jamaica"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "75"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "44"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r503831200-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Read about this place in the Jamaica Gleaner before I left Jamaica to visit family in Liverpool. My son and I had been to the amazing Pink Floyd Exhibition at The V & A museum that afternoon as he is a big fan. ", "Our links with Jamaica made us choose the Boisdale, Canary Wharf, plus we always enjoy the 'after work' vibes at CF. We had a little trouble findingthe venue it but well worth the effort, as when we arrived staff were so friendly, helpful and fun! ", "Beautiful ambience with Bird of Paradise Flowers and other Jamaican Decorations. Began with their recommended great Appleton or Red Stripe drink and a free Jerk Chicken Wrap special which was the best I ever tasted. Tradition Red Stripe in a bottle! Appleton Special Fruit punches were delicious.The Jerk Chicken was the best, almost equal to 'Scotchies' in Jamaica. We ordered the great Chef's Jerk Platter, again amazing followed with a few more cocktails and finished with Coffee Martini's. It was great night and my only disappointment was in waiting for Saxon Sound to start playing I asked the Waiter if they were on Jamaica time? He said they had begun at 6pm but we couldn't hear them from where we were sitting outside in the centre of the terrace. They upped the volume later but it was mostly Soca and we would have liked to hear some good oldies, plus feel like the Sound was actually playing (sounded like a background recorded tape playing and not really Jamaica music vibes). Having said that I am taking my sister back there on Friday when we visit London again for her to take part in the 100mile cycle race on Sunday! One Love"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r505017828", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best of Scotland Showcase", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "24 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi helenmiller2016,", "Thank you so much for your feedback and it is great to know you would recommend us! ", "We hope to see you soon, ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "helenmiller2016", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r505017828-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Best of Scotland showcase for PAs/EAs who also book business travel. Brilliant evening, Boisdale staff were very attentive, fantastic venue in Canary Wharf, with roof terrace.", "Would recommend this lovely venue."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r505392306", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best for a Business Dinner in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "25 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Snowball71,", "It was a real pleasure to read the review of your recent visit. Thank you so much for taking the time to provide us with your feedback. ", "You will need to come back soon so you can enjoy our fantastic live music - it really does add that extra special touch to the evening.", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Snowball71", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "43"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r505392306-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We recently had a team leaving dinner there and the menu was extensive, the wine list was awesome and the atmosphere was brilliant. Such a shame there was no Jazz on the night we booked but I just love this restaurant and they have never failed"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r507662397", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Interesting but Expensive", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "1 August 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Arnold L", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "171"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "92"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r507662397-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Location is excellent. 5 minutes from Canary Wharf Station which has Jubilee Line and DLR connections so really well accessible from both east and west London. Reception was fine, great table overlooking the square and the service was excellent. Not too swift but relaxed enough to have reasonable conversation but at the same time efficient. The atmosphere livens up around 2000 so I would not book for dinner before then unless you simply want dinner and then leave. If you overstay into the music session you will be charged a cover charge which is not cheap at around 25 pounds a head. We booked dinner and a show, it was UKL 44.75 per head excluding drinks. We had a two course meal which was included. We both had the squid deep fried which could have come out of a bag of frozen squid and a steak which was cooked well and along with fries was good. I had a portion of steamed broccolli which was ok. A gin and tonic is 11 pounds and water is 4.20 for 75 cl. A Treacle pudding which looked like it was out of a bag was 7.50. So as you can see this is not a cheap place to be. The total bill as above and service charge added ( its also added to the show price so beware ) was 152.10. I think that is expensive. We could have had a meal and show at Ronnie Scotts for less. The room itself is a good size and sound is good so this is a good venue. Its pub food at fine restaurant prices but if you are happy with that in order to see some live jazz on a Saturday night then I guess it is worth it. We probably would not visit again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r507494877", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Birthday meal ruined!", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "31 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Theresa666,", "I was given the feedback from my team and as my duty manager promised you on the day I have subsequently sent you a personal e-mail to go into a bit more depth with regards to your recent visit. ", "I look forward to your reply,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Theresa6666", "reviewer_origin": ["Waltham Abbey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "27"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r507494877-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked a table of 4, to celebrate my birthday, with my best friends.", "Table was booked for 13.45", "It appeared that there was a shortage of staff. ", "We did wait some time before our drinks orders were taken.", "And no explanation of how the menu options worked.", "My friend asked what of the two meat roast options the ma\u00eetre d recommended and he suggested the Pork. She was very happy with this as she said she loved the crackling, as per the menu.", "And then a further long wait for our starters.", "We had to request more than once, to have our glasses re-filled..after sitting with empties for some time.", "Eventually the food came...haggis option was hard, overcooked.", "The rest of the starters were good.", "Then we waited and waited and waited for the main course!", "1 hour 45 minutes later, we called the ma\u00eetre d and waiter over to enquire where our main courses were, bearing in mind that it was now 15.30 and the place closed at 16.00?", "As we were speaking to him, the plates arrived.", "The meat was almost cold.", "1 little pot with a few VERY small roast potatoes for me. The others were presented with CHIPS. And there was no crackling for my friend!!!", "We each had a small bowl of soggy looking sliced carrots YUK", "No apologies ", "No explanation ", "Nothing except excuses...", "They went to check in the kitchen and returned to say they had run out of crackling AND roast potatoes! ", "Had we not of raised this, we were just expected to accept it...not even the courtesy of an advance warning or apology or explanation.", "By now I was in bits. Birthday meal ruined. ", "And still no satisfactory explanation.", "We ended up walking out and refusing to pay a penny for the few drinks and a starter each.", "Disappointing service, food and lack of people skills.", "We won't be returning!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r509149372", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great night out", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "5 August 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "rosebug", "reviewer_origin": ["beds"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "669"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "307"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r509149372-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked dinner and live music tickets for a Friday Soul Night. Tickets were \u00a339.50 and included a 2 course meal plus a glass of prosecco. We booked our table for 8.15pm and the show started at 9.45pm. I loved the decor and atmosphere and we were given a nice candlelit table near to the front. There are nice views from the window side and you can go downstairs onto the terrace. Food was good and so was the service. But the highlight of the evening was the band - Andy Mitchell and his Big Funk Corporation, an eleven piece band - they were great! They played a really good set with many current songs as well as standards, which was nice. The set lasted 90 minutes and many of us were up and dancing. Do be aware that some of the options on the set dinner menu incur a supplement (e.g. \u00a36 for steak). With desserts, a bottle of wine, a beer and service charge we spent a further \u00a378 which I didn't mind as we were celebrating a special occasion but I wouldn't want to do that every time. Apparently you can also book tickets just for the show and a cocktail at \u00a319.50 each. Would certainly go again. We thoroughly enjoyed the evening. ", " "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r509426883", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Time to leave boisdale", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "6 August 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "robertpuncher1", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r509426883-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["It pains me to say this will be the last time we visit Boisdale. We've been going to boisdale twice a year for the last six years (summer and Christmas) in the last 18mtns we've seen a significant decline in food, entertainment, beverages and overall standards. We went to see ELVIS on the 5th August which being a massive Elvis fan I was really looking forward to. (Drinks) For a beer drinker like me you usually have at least one run of the mill beers (fosters ,carling,heiniekn) no, only two beers which I've never heard of. (Starters) We used to have a varied choice of starters and if you didn't like what was on offer there was always the good old prawn cocktail which was absolutely superb. (Main course) A fair choice but nothing like it used to be. The menus come on a piece of card, yet in the last five or so years it would have been a leather bound founder with a wider choice of food. The food they do serve is nice and hot and the service is excellent and I wouldn't criticise this at all. (Deserts) Standard deserts but excellent just what we want. (Show) We have seen earth wind and fire, Elvis, rat pack and have always walked away feeling we have been entertained and had a superb night of dining and dancing. (Toilets) Years ago it was always good quality hand wash and paper towels, now we have pound shop hand wash and you rub your hands under the dyson. A clear sign to me it's all about the profits. (Show) As a big elvis fan I thought he was a good singer but the actual show was poor. In the past five years all shows finished between 2345-midnight this night it was 2310, a long time to sit and wait for our cab. (Overall) We have always had a great night at boisdale, it's not a cheap place to go and it can also be a real expensive place if you've had to many beers. We always have the same table close to the stage (table for four at the top of the stairs) which we pay \u00a3140 for which on top of the \u00a3395 bill is a fair old bill for a night out. At the end of the day you know when the time has come to quit and move on. Thank you BOISDALE for some great nights but goodbye."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r484960227", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Food left a bit to be desired", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "17 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi porkynagger, ", "I am so glad to hear that you enjoyed the atmosphere and music at your recent Sunday lunch with us. ", "I have spoken to the chef about your comments on the seasoning of the sides and this is something that we both are monitoring closely. I am confident that should you join us again this is not an issue you will face again. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "porkynagger", "reviewer_origin": ["Croydon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "40", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r484960227-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Atmosphere, music and drinks were great. We were a party of six for Sunday lunch. The menu only had one item marked as vegetarian although there were a couple of other options. Everyone enjoyed their starters, although mine was tepid. All the vegetables served with the main meal were very salty. We asked for some carrots that were not as salty and we were given spinach, but that wasn't much better. Even the roast potatoes had too much salt. Desserts were ok."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r484950399", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Dinner", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "17 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Stuart O, ", "Good food, music and service pretty much sums up what we work hard each day to achieve. Thank you for recognising this and posting your findings!", "We look forward to seeing you soon, ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Stuart O", "reviewer_origin": ["Great Dunmow, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r484950399-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great place for dinner and a bit of Jazz. Very good service and good food right in the middle od Canary wharf."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r487486174", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food and service and atmosphere!", "diner_date": " August 2016", "rating_date": "24 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi jmrich29,", "This was a lovely review to receive and thank you for taking the time to provide your short and very sweet feedback! ", "Looking forward to seeing you again soon, ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Joanna R", "reviewer_origin": ["Bromley, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r487486174-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Love this place, steak always amazing, atmosphere buzzing and the staff are really friendly, will return again"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r490947812", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Let Us Celebrate", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "6 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi 127anthony01,", "It was an absolute delight to read your recent review of your Sunday lunch celebrations with us! I am so glad that we were able to make this a special and memorable experience, we work very hard to try and do just that for all of our guests. ", "I have passed your kind words on to Siobhan who was more than happy to help and is on hand should you have any other special occasions needing organised! ", "Hopefully we will see you in the near future,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "127anthony01", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r490947812-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["It is always a wonderful feeling to share an amazing experience with family and friends on special occasions.", "Needless, to say these gathering are never easy to organised \u2013 However, with the help of Boisdale \u2013 Events Manager Siobhan Brewer we were able to planed a wonderful memorable Sunday luncheon accommodating 17 guests in order to celebrate a family member 50th Birthday. ", "The private room which we hired overlooking the square in Canary Wharf was spacious with a view of the live Jazz band performing in the main restaurant. The music permeated the room adding to the wonderful setting \u2013 The menu was accommodating \u2013 The Salmon, Chicken which comprises the Main Course was a generous portion, it was absolutely delicious with the house wine complementing the excellent three course meal. The staff were magnificent. All the diners were made to feel special with their dietary requirements catered for. All this led to a wonderful 50th birthday celebration - one which those who attended will never forget for many years."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r491727183", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Disappointed", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "9 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi igloolondon, ", "Thank you for your review of your recent visit with us. ", "I am sorry to hear that there was a slight delay with you being seated due to the fact that you had come upstairs from the 1st floor into the main restaurant, our reception is at the other end of the restaurant at the entrance by the lifts so this is where the confusion was. If no one was available to seat you then you should, of course, have been pointed in the direction of the reception by a member of our floor team. This is something I have briefed everyone on and not something that is usually an issue for us. ", "The lemon mayo should have been served with your Langoustines - again, please rest assured that this is something that has already been addressed and is no longer something that is served separately in case anyone else faces the slight delay you had. ", "The chips for your main courses came on a separate tray from the kitchen and followed directly behind your main meal, which I served and it was myself you spoke to. ", "I am glad you enjoyed the food and music,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "igloolondon", "reviewer_origin": ["london"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r491727183-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We book a table for my daughters birthday 8/6/17. ", "We arrived early so went to the bar for a drink. Once the rest of our party arrived we went to the restaurant to be seated. I should have known the evening was not going to go well when we were completely ignored by every member of staff and no one wanted to seat us. I had to grab a member of staff and inset that we were seated. No apology at all.", "We let this go as we all wanted to have a good time as we were celebrating.", "The waiter came and took our order. So far so good. The starters came (sort of!) The majority of the group order langoustine and lemon mayo. The langoustine arrive on a bed of ice and that were it stopped. No plates no mayo no finger bowls. We waited for about 5 minutes nothing. I asked the waiter, he said someone else was bringing the plates and mayo. By 10 minutes I was betting a bit upset. I had to ask again before the plates and the rest of the order came. We finished the staters and waited for the main course. What could go wrong this time? you guessed it................not all of the food turned up. Again we waited again I had to ask. I was told its coming. Shouldn't the whole order come together!!!! still two guest did not have their whole meal. Chased again and was told the kitchen is very busy it will come. By this time the foods going cold so I ask for the manager. A waitress arrives with the 2 missing sides and I ask for the manager again. Im the manager she tells me. I explain the situation and that it is not acceptable. Her attitude was not the best. Leaving me with the feeling that she was angry with me for complaining and not with the terrible service her staff have given us. Begrudgingly she say I will look at the bill and see if I can do something for you after your meal. The waiter comes back to take the desert order and guess what ?????? again we didn't get the whole order. We only ordered 3 deserts and 3 coffees and a coffee was missing. The bill come and the waiter presents it say that they had reduced the bill by 20 % and taken off the service charge.", "All in all the food was very good the music was very good the service was absolutely horrible. Boisdale please take note if you want repeat customers please treat them better.", "Would I come here again? maybe for the music"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r485803262", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Avoid the Steak but amazing haggis ", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "20 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello zigtravel, ", "Thank you for taking the time to provide us with feedback of your recent visit. Feedback is a really important tool for us to measure where we are and how we can evolve as a business and improve. ", " I am saddened to hear that you did not enjoy our steak. It is our most popular item on the menu and we rarely receive negative feedback. I have shared your comments with our chef and we will both be keeping a close eye on the cooking of our steaks moving forward. ", "To hear the service described as 'stunning' gives me great pride and is a comment that really made the team smile. We all work very hard at providing a 1st class service and to know that we are doing well makes it all worthwhile. ", "Hopefully we will see you soon for some Haggis and a wee dram! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "zigtravel", "reviewer_origin": ["Norfolk, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "194"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "70"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r485803262-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["For such a supposed high class establishment in such a moneyed area of London the steak was overcooked. I knew I should have stuck to gauchos for steak. If you come here stick to what Scotland does well. Argentina does steak, no-one else does. Have the haggis as a main not as a starter as I did. Avoid the steak. If you like whiskey you're in for a treat. The service was stunning and made us forgive the steak. The steak was rescued by the delicious accompaniments of sweet potato chips and the stunning sauces which rescued the night, bar of course the great conversation I had with my friend at a place with superb views over the area and great atmosphere. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r501088200", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great night", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "12 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello michelle s,", "I am delighted to hear that you have been able to come and enjoy our Jamaica Garden Terrace as well as all of our tasty Jamaican offerings to accompany the beautiful surroundings. ", "Thank you for your review and we are looking forward to welcoming you back soon, ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "K827EOmichelles", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "48"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r501088200-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Love boisdale nice cocktails great night with friends have a great selection of cocktail sometimes do themed evenings we went for the Jamaica themed night well it's on for the month of July the rum punch was very nice so was the BBQ. They had jerk pork and chicken on the terrace we just had a good drink and and bite to eat on terrace but you can also go upstairs to the restaurant would certainly be returning"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r499743768", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "A real disappointment", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "8 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello charlotte4112017,", "Although I am disappointed to read a number of the points you have raised in this review I would like to thank you for taking the time to give us your feedback. It is an important tool that we use constructively to ensure we are moving forward in the right direction. ", "Apart from wanting to delve a little deeper into the concerning points raised I would be grateful if we could speak as there are also some details that I am confused by - we have not had steak tartar on the menu for over 3 months.", "Please contact me directly on gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk so that I can have the opportunity to deal with this personally and better understand how we fell short on this occasion. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "charlotte4112017", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r499743768-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to Boisdale Canary Wharf for the first time for my daughters 22nd birthday. I paid \u00a360 in advance to reserve a table in the premier area close to the band. I booked the table at 8.15 because the band came on at 9.15 and, my thinking was, that we would be approaching desserts then, and be in the mood for some live jazz. The service was terrible, We waited and we waited and, eventually, we were served. The drinks that eventually came (cocktails) were all wrong. The starters finally arrived at around 9pm and, before our main meal had arrived, the band came on and it was far too loud to have our dinner at the same time. Even though I had paid \u00a360 for this spot we asked to be moved to another table in the main part of the restaurant so we could talk while we ate our main meal. My steak tartar was, to be honest, awful. The rest of the food was average. Due to the slow service, I had asked for red wine to accompany the main meal well in advance but it never arrived. More cocktails were ordered but they were wrong again. The bill was over \u00a3300 (plus \u00a360 for the premier table) making the total bill for our evening frantically over \u00a3400. An expensive night for a less than average evening - I would not go back and I certainly wouldn't recommend this venue."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r492351287", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Business as usual ", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "12 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Oliver, ", "You have made some deeply concerning points in this review that I am sorry to hear as your opinion. Of course, all opinions are subjective and it seems that this is very much the case with this review. ", "We have some fantastic feedback on our food offering here. As well as diversity and flexibility when it comes to prix fix menu's and larger parties. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Oliver G", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "136"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "149"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r492351287-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This is a typical corporate hang out in Canary Wharf.", "Nobody, including ourselves, comes here for the food. Unfortunately, that shows. This is fast food at a higher level. Pre-selected menus are engineered to cater for the lowest common denominator. The preparation of the food is industrialised and again engineered to maximise profitability. Everything is just about edible.", "One of our guests summed it up well \"...that steak was awful...\".", "But I guess, food and venue play less of a role when you decide to come here. Most likely you will be part of some form of corporate event and as the restaurant is organising these rather effectively."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r497712296", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Empty restaurant", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "1 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Dauban M,", "I am sorry to hear that you were unable to enjoy our live music when you joined us recently. We have no music on a Monday, Tues-Sat in the evening and on a Sunday afternoon. ", "Generally we have a great atmosphere in the restaurant so it is a shame that you were unable to see this. I fed back your comments on the food to our chef and I will keep a close eye on the Salmon dish moving forward. I am glad to hear that you enjoyed our service. ", "Thank you for taking the time to provide your feedback, ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "daubanm2016", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "69"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r497712296-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Live music but not during this visit. Very large place, but almost all tables empty. Food is nothing special, overcooked salmon. Service is good"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r477980275", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Tapas...mmmm....lots of deep fried stuff", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "22 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "jacob123", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "144"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "92"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r477980275-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Although I work at Canary Wharf I have never eaten here until this month. Note we ate in the lower area and not the upstairs restaurant. The service was perfect - a very charming young Spanish guy. However, the food was really pretty poor. Maybe we should have known better than to order the tapas - it's just a selection of ready made items, or deep fried items. Nice decor although getting a bit worn in parts. Would be happy to try the main restaurant upstairs however."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r477608052", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wonderful Dining Experience", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "21 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MikeG2153", "reviewer_origin": ["Baulkham Hills, Australia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "68"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r477608052-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Taken to Boisdale by business colleagues last night and enjoyed a fabulous meal - superb mini haggis with obligatory Glenfiddich for starters, and a succulent rib eye for mains, all washed down with a quaffable Malbec from Argentina. A great experience - highly recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r478135180", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great party venue", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "23 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Robert M", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "471"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "139"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r478135180-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great atmosphere with Friendly staff who are all well trained. The live group Payback were sensational and it was pleasing they did not stop for a break after 30mins but played on continuously until about 11.15pm lots of dancing and party atmosphere something you always can expect Boisdale to deliver."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r484485295", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Complete fail", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "15 May 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Davidcm555", "reviewer_origin": ["Norwich, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r484485295-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I have just returned from a night at Boisdale Canary Wharf and usually do not revue restaurants, but tonight was very poor, so I feel I need to warn others.", "I booked a dinner and show to see Kerry Ellis and phoned to confirm my booking of a few weeks ago. Strangely they could not find my booking, I gave the the confirmation number but after a few minutes they said they could not find the booking and would phone back. They phoned back and said they had found it and all was OK, although I could only have 8.15 or 7.45. I explained that my booking had been confirmed for 8pm many weeks ago, but they said thats the only table they had available. ", "I had booked a standard seating table with 2 course meal for \u00a350, when I arrived i was shown to a table that had no view of Kerry Ellis, which was in a \"restricted view area\". I went back to the reception area and complained and they said they would inform the manager. Needless to say the manager did not show up and I had a good meal listening to a good sound coming for a structural pillar. ", "I thin it is obvious they had lost the booking and tried to assume i would accept a v. poor viewing area. It is a shame they didn't own up when i phoned to confirm, as I would have cancelled if they didn't have a seat where you could see the artist.", "I like the Boisdale ethos, but today they dropped the ball and did not even have the courtesy to come and talk to e about it. Shame in you Boisdale."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r482021757", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Canary Wharf stalwart", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "6 May 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "richmou", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "381"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "115"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r482021757-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale has been in the wharf a longtime but it isn't one of my go to places. I think it could be because it is tucked away at the far end of the shopping mall and you have to use elevators to get to it and they are a bit tucked away. The place itself is a bit tired and dated now and probably could do with a refurb but it's an okay average sort of place! We had finger food at a drinks party this week and it was really pedestrian and all tasted and looked over fried. Definitely put me off eating in the restaurant. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r478199812", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wonderful night out", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "23 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "479grahaml", "reviewer_origin": ["Rhoose, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "25"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r478199812-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Food was outstanding, service attentive, cocktails superb and loved the entertainment. We went on \"Swing night\". Loved every second"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r479815892", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Not worth the visit ", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "28 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "406jolenem", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r479815892-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went here for a drink at the bar, waited 25 minutes, I asked to be served and NOTHING! Not sure if it's a staffing issue or if they only prioritise their service to eating customers only. ", "Just don't bother."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r479128653", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Nice location, bad food", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "26 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "GlenM465", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "38"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "34"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r479128653-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great location and lovely views of the fountain, but the food was dreadful. The chicken breast was rubbery - I initially worried that it was under cooked, but it wasn't pink so all I can assume is that it was cooked ahead of time and warmed up. The burger was OK, but for >\u00a320 I expected much better. Overall; I'd recommend avoiding the restaurant if they can't even cook chicken and a burger well."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r482158316", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Bankers \u2026", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "6 May 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ABK1959", "reviewer_origin": ["Stowmarket, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "40"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r482158316-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale is a terrifically stocked bar in Canary Wharf, catering for the downtrodden sins and daughters of toil who lurk there. High grade booze, great bar food and an on-site cigar outlet of which two (female) friends availed themselves. Great evening. Bring money. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r484418433", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sunday lunch", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "15 May 2017", "answer_text": ["hi 53lesley2016,", "This is exactly the kind of review that puts a huge smile on the faces of all of our team!", "I am so glad that we were able to make your trip to London memorable and we cant wait to host you next time. ", "Thank you for your kind words,", "Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "53lesley2016", "reviewer_origin": ["Sheffield, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r484418433-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Wow.. wow..wow what can I say. We took our daughter and son in law for Sunday lunch and it was amazing. The food was fabulous.. we had a 3 course lunch.... the staff were so attentive and there was a wonderful jazz band playing. We can't recommend this enough. Would go every time we visit London..."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r477521802", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best Place to relax", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "20 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "DenisOCallaghan", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r477521802-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["By far my favourite place to relax in London. Great staff all round and you will never be disappointed. If you like a drop of whisky or a nice cigar, speak with Filipe. His knowledge and customer service skills are exceptional. Would highly recommend."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r469489269", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "SIMPLY AWESOME, TENDER, SUCCULENT STEAK", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "22 March 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "sevdah_11", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "70"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "70"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r469489269-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I dined here several times with my husband. Steaks are extremely tender, melt in the mouth sort of taste, like no other I have tasted. We dined here on 50% of meals deals sent to me via an email. Otherwise it is a rather expensive restaurant. We have also dined at their Bishopsgate branch, serving equally quality steaks. The sides are rather small and not quite enough. At \u00a34.95 per side is rather a lot for approx. 10 pieces of chunky chips, but nevertheless tasty and well cooked. We ordered mushrooms and broccoli and chips on the side which all come as separate items all at \u00a34.95 a portion, which are all very small but beautifully cooked and served hot and perfect for consumption immediately. Would go again and again as a treat on special occasions and also when sent emails with promotions. They always send me special offers and dates of special quests attending the restaurant and special occasions of Jazz Events. If you stay to dine after 9.30 in the evening you have to purchase a live music ticket or vacate your table. We don't stay for the live music so I can't comment on this. I would definitely recommend this place for quality steak lovers and for celebrating special occasions. Scottish theme throughout, owned by a Scottsman. Menu also Scottish themed. Not suitable/ designed for children, young children anyway, we have yet to see any children there each time we have been there its more catered for Canary Wharf office staff and the older/more mature generation with city pay packets. Drinks are also very expensive, a very extensive wine selection. Soft drinks are also very expensive. They do offer tap water to guests and sliced up sour bread with butter on sitting at the table, which are served fresh and are rather mooorish. We ordered salt and pepper calamari for starters which were \u00a39 for approx. 8 pieces. The steaks were on average \u00a335 with sides extra. All in all a rather expensive evening but well worth it. If you want quality steak, this is the place to visit. Give it a go and enjoy. They also add 12.5% or so tips. If you order the 42 day mature steak you will not regret it. They also do the steak to share for around \u00a370 but again its matured for 42 days and it melts in your mouth. Delish, enjoy."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r472057791", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great food and entertainment ", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "2 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SimonC14SRD", "reviewer_origin": ["Windlesham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "178"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "146"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r472057791-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We dined and watched suspiciously Elvis on a Saturday night. The setting is like going back in time, old fashioned dinner dance. Elvis was 5 stars, the food was traditional British Fayre and not over priced at all. The only negative was the service which lacked attentiveness and follow up (a bit functional). I would definitely do it again and Elvis is a must! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r471892377", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing place!", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "1 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Georgi A", "reviewer_origin": ["Strasbourg, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "78"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "49"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r471892377-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to the Boisdale restaurant for my anniversary and we were very happy of our choise.", "An excellent and spacious restaurant, perfect service, nice atmoshpere, very good food, high standard wine and drinks.", "On the top of it, Mud Morganfield, the eldest son of Muddy Wateers, made a great show with his band.", "To recommend!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r471594614", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Always good", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "31 March 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LS_85123", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "82"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "41"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r471594614-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Have been here a few times and it's always good. The food is consistently of a high standard; the environment's nice and a bit different; the service is excellent and they're really helpful; and the price is pretty reasonable - especially with the set menu and the deals they tend to run. Recommend!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r470833034", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Mothering Sunday lunch.", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "28 March 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "theclarkes3inspain", "reviewer_origin": ["North Yorkshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "63"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "68"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r470833034-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife, 19 year old son and I took the trip down from Yorkshire to experience Sunday lunch at the Boisdale. We hadn't appreciated at the time of booking that it was mothers day, so an added bonus for us. We arrived at 12 noon and were shown to our table next to the floor to ceiling windows with nice views of the surrounding area and within a decent proximity of the stage. My wife and I had visited before but never for Sunday lunch.", "We opted to include the wine option and upgraded to the finer wine. Great choice, the Rioja was superb as was the Chablis that my son decided on. We explained to the staff that we didn't want to rush the afternoon and they said we could take thing at our own pace and call in our food as and when.", "My wife and I chose the roast beef for mains whilst my son had the burger. All was fine, beef nicely cooked however like a previous reviewer the roast potatoes were desperately salty (just had to drink more Rioja!). Deserts very nice and overall no complaints about the food. The jazz was discrete and not like the shows they put on in the evenings, just background sort of music but very pleasant none the less.", "We managed to hold out until 4pm and agreed that the value for money was exceptional taking into account having enjoyed a good meal and some very good wine.", "The staff who took care of us were very professional and friendly and we enjoyed some great conversations with them. Special thanks to Jean-Claude who kept us topped up with table water, Kevin Anderson who provided the bread and Christophe our lead waiter who made sure our afternoon was perfect and kept the glasses filled.", "We are already planning our return and look forward to seeing the team again soon. Thanks for a great Mothers Day afternoon."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r473308294", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great steak and music", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "7 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Lafite64", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r473308294-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Slightly hard to find the first time, it's upstairs adjactent to Cabot square, with its own lift off the main mall. Staff are very welcoming, and the selection on the menu is good. While you're waiting, you can admire the amazing whisky bar, which must be the biggest in London.", "Large stage for the music performance, which started (for us) a little later on after 9, so we didn't see much of it.", "The food is great, unfortunately one of our main courses was wrong - they simply served up the wrong dish - but it was well handled by the manageress.", "Good place and we booked to go back there and then."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r472173386", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Really enjoyable lunch", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "2 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "margaretw597", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "145"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "32"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r472173386-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I had not come here for lunch before so was pleasantly surprised at how bright, airy and Scottish the main dining room is. We had a table by the window. Very well priced 2 course menu although we ate a la carte. Fish and steak were delicious and service prompt and friendly. Would definitely come back. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r472328367", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Nice place except on the day it was exceptionally poor", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "3 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "sarabjits2014", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "25"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r472328367-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The venue is excellent. We arrived on time and were met by a happy receptionist. Got to our table and the service was absolutely terrible. This is no reflection of the staff who were short staffed. The manager on the day was the most useless person on the floor. The quality of staff was below what I would expect. The staff should visit Zedel or Fischers and just see the difference. The fault lies with the management.", "The wine we ordered was great, the starter was above average but the main ( chicken) plus vegetables was awful. The chef really needs to go back to basic or needs to find a new job. The chicken was over- done, the potatoes were served in large chucks in a terrible bowl and the green were full of oil. These are simple basic steps the chef should be fully aware.", "The bill came along which was wrong and got corrected after three attempt. ", "Terrible place,", "Happy to discuss with mgt my comments."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r476522908", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "2nd floor drinks in the wharf", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "17 April 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Marius G", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "32"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r476522908-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["There is a nice balcony and a cigar room in the rear. Can usually be quieter than the other bars in the wharf so a good place to check in if everywhere else is standing room only. The balcony offer a good view of the fountain and a good place for some summer beers."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r467916986", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The Boisdale Experience", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "16 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Scott M, ", "Thank you so much for taking the time to feedback your experience of Boisdale of Canary Wharf. Having 'all our bases covered' is really what we strive for from every aspect of the 'customer journey'. ", "Reviews like this make all of the hard work worthwhile and I will take great pleasure in feeding this back to the team!", "We hope to see you soon, ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Scott M", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r467916986-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["As a regular customer of Boisdale Canary Wharf, I have to say this is a place everyone who knows Canary Wharf must visit at least once. ", "You have all your bases covered for an amazing experience that will have you returning for more. ", "You can dine in style in the amazing Scottish Restaurant where you can be whisked away on an amazing culinary experience that will excite your tastebuds and melt your heart at the same time. The food is simply divine and the service is top class. The staff make you feel warm and welcome from start to finish. This space also hosts live performances and you can sign up for the privilege of being able to meet the stars too. ", "If drinking whisky or smoking a cigar is your thing, you've only got one choice. Boisdale. From the amazing assortment of Scotches, the top class cocktails, to the collection of fine wines, you've got anything you could want to drink. If you fancy a wonderful cigar to compliment it you only need to ask the cigar specialist Filip. His knowledge of cigars and exemplary customer service have me returning time and time again with a smile and a bounce in my step. There is no better returning welcome than his. Once you know it you'll understand. ", "So what else do you need to hear? If you need more, god help you...."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r468212970", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "5 star music, 3 star food", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "18 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello Andrew H, ", "Thank you for taking the time to leave a review of your recent visit. Feedback is very important to allow us to ensure we are delivering on our customer's expectations. ", "Although you have raised some negative points re; the vegetables on the whole I am glad that you enjoyed both the ambiance and the food. Please rest assured that our Head Chef and I will be paying closer attention to the details you mentioned. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "W6327VDandrewh", "reviewer_origin": ["Hornchurch, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "32"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r468212970-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We opted for the 3 course Sunday lunch menu, at \u00a347.50 per head with 3/4 bottle of wine per person. ", "Let's start with the good, the ambience. It's a beautiful venue with some good Celtic decor and a fantastic bar display what I guessed displays nearly 400 bottles of whisky. The live jazz music was melodic and soothing and a lovely accompaniment to what was a decent meal. ", "A starter of haggis was well received, hearty, generally well seasoned apart from a tad too much pepper. A traditional roast it rib of beef was very good in some aspects, less so in others. The good? Well cooked flavoursome meat, tender to the bite too. The not so good? Salty roast potatoes, although they were lovely and crispy and very generous with their portions. Next up, over cooked flabby and tasteless carrots. The broccoli was OK, but a smattering of butter on it would have been welcomed. ", "A dessert of pear and apple crumble with ice cream was of a good pub standard. I must say that the nice piquant apple complemented the sweet pear. The crumble topping needed something extra though, perhaps some honey roasted oats and more nuts. ", "The wine (you get 3/4 of a bottle per person) was good for the price and was free flowing. Big thanks to the waiting staff. ", "The lead waiter who took the order, although nice didn't feel like he had a good understanding of the day's menu. He wasn't even sure what the fish of the day was. However he was very polite and always kept us topped up. I must add this place welcomes children and they gave our daughter a nice activity pack (colouring book, pens) to keep her busy. Also the 'distorted' mirrors near the toilets kept her entertained for ages. ", "All in all a good experience but had better roast dinners at places like the Gun. Thing is the Gun doesn't boast the great music, whisky selection or cool decor. ", "Give Boisdales a try, you won't be disappointed, just as long as you go in with realistic expectations regarding the food. Decent but not great. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r468897426", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic Sunday lunch with Jazz Music bonus", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "20 March 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Tracy S", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "56"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r468897426-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went here for Sunday Lunch as a pre-mothers day treat", "Mothers day is always so busy so bought a Sunday lunch voucher for 2 from Travelzoo and went a week early.", "The whole experience was fantastic - the atmosphere was great from the moment we arrived and although the place was busy we didn't feel hemmed in.", "Three courses of delicious food.", "The roast beef was plentiful and the roast potatoes, carrots, wilted greens & Yorkshire pud were all tasty and completed the main course.", "The dessert was also very well presented and tasted wonderful - looked quite a small portion when it arrived but it was just right.", "We only had the house white which was the cheapest bottle but to be honest I am no wine buff and we enjoyed every last drop.", "Even asked to take home my left over beef for two very happy dogs as a sunday treat ! - staff were more than happy to wrap it up and brought if back in a paperbag for me to take away - no problem", "Thoroughly enjoyed lunch and would definitely go again"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r468402443", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Not good value for money !", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "18 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi ipek2208,", "Thank you for taking to provide us feedback of your recent visit. ", "I am glad you enjoyed the atmosphere however was disappointed to hear that you are not as positive about the food. We generally receive fantastic reviews on our steak so I was surprised to learn you found it to be 'ordinary'. I have shared these views with our Chef. ", "It is a shame that you did not think the acoustic was right, we are very much a live music venue and as such have spent a significant amount ensuring that our sound system is correct for the venue. Above this we have a highly qualified sound technician to ensure that the levels etc are correct. The Dukes of Mayfair are quite a lively band and do put on quite a show, perhaps there will be another act coming up soon that is less so and you can give us another shot! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "ipek2208", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "30", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r468402443-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were at the Boisdale Canary Wharf yesterday. The atmosphere was really nice. However I cannot say the same thing for the food. We had steak which was ordinary. The cheesecake was so so. The band was Dukes of Mayfair . The lady singer has an amazing voice. Unfortunately, the acoustic was awful. Secondly the sound level was extremely high, it was at some point unbearable. In summary, not a good value for money !"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r468447341", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "What a let down ", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "19 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Adrian S, ", "You have raised some concerning issues in this review that I would like the opportunity to speak with you about in more detail. ", "Please contact me directly on GM@boisdale-cw.co.uk", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "adrians273", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "161"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "59"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r468447341-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I went here to celebrate my birthday with a friend. I was so looking forward to it, as I had wanted to go there for some time. ", "The table we were put at was best described as the naughty table, on its own in an odd position. We asked to move and the way it was handled could of been much better, there were only about 75 people in the place and lots of empty tables. Anyhow, we got moved and ordered. The waiter was useless, he kept saying that he had forgotten what drinks we had ordered and that he should of written it down. The food was OK, nothing special, part of the order was missing, he said because he had not written it down. ", "At about 9:30, the jazz band kicked in and it all just went down hill from there. We paid and left, without even getting my surprise birthday cake that had been pre arranged. ", "The food and staff at the Big Easy are a lot better than this overpriced restaurant that is trying to be something it is not. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r468573852", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice atmosphere", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "19 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello Louise t, ", "Thank you for your review and apologies for the delay in my reply. ", "I am glad that you enjoyed your offer with us and didn't leave hungry!! Sunday's are a day to feast. ", "Hopefully we will see you soon, we also have live music every Tues-Sat in the evening which is something you may enjoy. ", "Kind regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "louise t", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r468573852-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We got a deal on a travelzoo, otherwise may have felt it was overpriced. Portion sizes were enormous, but go early as they were sold out on some things when we arrived. Sadly the jazz seemed to end at 3pm. Staff were very friendly. Nice ambience and decor, can't have enough dead animals on the wall for my liking. The plates were warmed which we appreciated! Small point but tables were far enough apart to feel like you had some privacy and not be annoyed by other diners. It was also child friendly from what we saw."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r468533481", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Disappointed ", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "19 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello Snoopyandfrenchie,", "Thank you for taking the time to provide us with feedback of your recent visit. We use such reviews as an important tool and constructively as a way to evolve and improve. ", "I have shared your concerns re; the food with our Head Chef who was very disappointed to hear your comments on the food.", "Being regular guests I would appreciate if you could drop me an e-mail before your next visit so I can ensure I am here to catch up with you personally to discuss further on GM@boisdale-cw.co.uk", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Frenchie_xox", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "60"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "83"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r468533481-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went to the suspiciously Elvis show last night. Had pre-drinks in the downstairs bar first which has a lovely view. Bar was busy. Went up for dinner before show started, orders were taken quickly and food arrived promptly. I have to say as frequent visitors of Boisdale the last two times we have been we have been disappointed with the food. Over priced and if I'm honest wasn't great last night. The menu has been changed since our last visit, I ordered fillet steak to be cooked well done, and specifically said no red. My husband and friend asked for medium. Husband and friends steak arrived rare and had to be sent back. Mine was ok but wasn't as well done as I would of liked. Small in size and didn't taste as good as previous steaks I have had there. Elvis was good. Lots of people were up dancing. Good atmosphere. Had a good night overall but think food standards are slipping which is a shame as we really like it here. Good for couples or groups of friends/family. Would recommend, only disappointed as we here been many times before and know how good it can be!!! Staff polite and helpful. If food was fantastic wouldn't mind paying the prices but when mediocre not good value for money. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r468896202", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Saturday Night, Steak and Elvis", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "20 March 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Charles E", "reviewer_origin": ["Guernsey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r468896202-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Dinner and an Elvis tribute band. Good food, although a little pricey, with attentive service and a great ambience. A fun evening in a cross between a Scottish hunting lodge and a jazz club."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r468632475", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fab night", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "19 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi MapBoy,", "Thank you for your very short but very sweet review - It was a pleasure to read and I'm sorry for the delay in coming back to you.", "We have lots of other really exciting acts coming up and amazing steaks are always in abundance so don't wait too long before you visit again!", "Kind regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "MapBoy", "reviewer_origin": ["England"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r468632475-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Food great (amazing steaks), alcohol flowed and music was outstanding. We were treated to The Dukes of Mayfair for entertainment and what a fun group. Really good night, highly recommend."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r468734887", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Poor service, terrible music band. Tried to overcharge twice.", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "20 March 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "apsoni", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "53"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "44"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "20", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r468734887-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Tried this place mainly for music and food. The bar on 1st floor is excellent, enjoyed the drinks. Initial reception at the restaurant was good. However, the service by our waitress was poor. Cold not break a smile. The food was average to good. Vegetarian choice was limited. ", "When the live band started at 9.45, we were shocked! Poor music, singing was awful. Doubt if the drums were tuned in last 12 months. We decided to leave and have deserts elsewhere. When the bill arrived, it was almost thrown onto our table. Bill included several items we never ordered including deserts. Revised bill arrived, again almost thrown on to the table. Over charged on the wines again. When they saw us checking prices on menu. they quickly brought a third bill with correct pricing. This time bill was literally thrown onto our table. ", "One wonders!! I do not recommend this restaurant. ", "IF you do eat there, check your bill in details."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r467645656", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great lobster", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "15 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Danny M, ", "Thank you for your review of our downstairs bar area. I am pleased to hear that you enjoyed our more than reasonably priced lobster! As well as the wine and cigars.", "You should come again to experience our 2nd floor when you get the chance - where we have fantastic 2 4 1 cocktails and live music! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Danny M", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r467645656-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great live music and lobster dinners. Lively bar on the lower level with great wines by the glass. Humidor and smoking terrace great for cigar fans. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r464877425", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Frank and Dean night", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "5 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi jackfamily17,", "So glad to hear that you managed an impromptu visit and managed to catch some of the music! ", "Lots of more fantastic acts coming up so please don't wait too long until you come again. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "jackfamily17", "reviewer_origin": ["Rochester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "42"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r464877425-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We popped in to catch the last hour of the show and have a drink. Were not disappointed. Have previously visited and enjoyed dinner. Shows are excellent and would recommend. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r465147360", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Date Night", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "6 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Karen H,", "Reading you recent review really brought a smile to my face. You touched on all aspects that we work really hard on to ensure are well received for a memorable experience! Thank you. ", "Keep the romance alive and come back soon.....", "Kind regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "karenhU8470KQ", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "137"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "83"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r465147360-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to Boisdale for a romantic dinner and really enjoyed the evening. The cocktails were unusual with whisky being a main component. The fish starter with Oysters - Mussels and Prawns was delicious. Our main courses and desserts were great - the menu is extensive' Quirky but super service. A big choice of whiskeys and live music."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r465768347", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Love it but room for improvement", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "9 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello minimemo,", "Thank you for your constructive feedback on your recent visit. Also being a Scot it saddens me to hear that you did not enjoy the Haggis. We do use an extremely high quality supplier and I agree that the texture is a little smoother than what many are familiar with. ", "Of course I am pleased that our staff are able to advise on what the 'recommendation' of cooking temperature should be for steak but if this was delivered in any way other than 'advice' then I will of course address this. ", "Please drop me an e-mail on gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk to let me know when you are coming back in for your celebration - rest assured we will not disappoint!! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "minimemo", "reviewer_origin": ["England"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r465768347-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Been once before for a date night and loved it so much, came back with friends for a birthday celebration. I'm Scottish so kind of have an idea of what I'm talking about here...the haggis?? was like a spicy smooth pate and not in a good way! If this had been my first time eating haggis, I'd never want to eat it again. Haggis has texture but not here :( such a shame....then 3 steaks ordered with the waiter 'telling' us how to have our steaks cooked but two of them had to go back 3 times each and in the end couldn't eat them! In fairness to Boisdale, they knocked the price off the bill but would rather have had all being well in the first place. There needs to be a bit more on the side dishes of vegetables too. Cutting corners, cuts customers. We live five hours away from London so when we go to Boisdales, that is our sole purpose of travelling and take it on the chin the cost of the hotel for the night! We are planning on going back again prior to daughter and her fiance's wedding and them emigrating immediately after the wedding, as they have never been before and because we big it up!! Lets make it a night for them to remember...for all the RIGHT reasons Boisdale!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r465643173", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely atmosphere, friendly staff, great music", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "8 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Nikkibains78,", "I am delighted to hear that you enjoyed the atmosphere! I am slightly confused by the comment on limited food menu as we do have an extensive and diverse A La carte menu upstairs and a similarly extensive British Tapas and Bar menu downstairs. ", "We do have a number of set menus however anyone booked on a set menu offer is more than welcome to take a look at our larger menu's too. ", "Please come back soon so you can take full advantage! ", "Kind regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Nikkibains78", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "21"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r465643173-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This place has a great atmosphere and is great for a romantic drink for jazz lovers. The only thing that lets this place down is the limited food menu and the quality of the food, but I would still visit again for the music and atmosphere. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r465984866", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Celebrating a birthday", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "10 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi franchaines,", "I was pleased to hear that - overall - you enjoyed your recent visit to Boisdale Of Canary Wharf. Thank you for taking the time to feed this back. ", "Please rest assured that I have taken your comments on Burgers and bill timings constructively and will be paying extra attention to these points moving forward.", "We have lots of great live music acts coming up, perhaps you will find something that suits and be able to find something else to celebrate! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "franchaines", "reviewer_origin": ["Margate, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r465984866-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited this restaurant on Saturday night when a Fleetwood Mac tribute band was there. ", "My food was superb, (langoustines, salmon, mussels and saffron rice, followed by an incredible choice of British cheese and biscuits), although the rest of my group chose hamburgers or steak and were all very disappointed as they were over cooked. The haggis and squid are also recommended by our group. The one thing we didn't like was that vegetables are charged separately for a lot of the main courses.", "The service was very good apart from getting the bill at the end of the evening - it was unfortunate that everyone wanted their bills at the same time.", "The tribute band was excellent, more space could of been made for dancing though. ", "I would recommend this restaurant for a special evening out if you are prepared to splash out. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r465860905", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Food", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "9 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Berni54,", "I am really disappointed to hear that you found the quality of the steak and burgers to be below par. As I am sure you can imagine both of these dishes are high volume sales items for us and we generally receive very positive feedback. ", "That said, I will of course bring this up with our Head Chef and endeavour to monitor these dishes more closely in the coming weeks. With this in mind, I am confident that should you be willing to give us another chance we will not disappoint! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Berni54", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "30", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r465860905-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I asked for medium rare steak and got well done. They did change it but very tough. Four of our group had the burgers which were so well done that they were dried out. This is the fourth time I have been here and disappointed that the quality of the food has gone downhill! The music was good and the service was fine. Definitely think twice about returning."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r466444595", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great location, terrible food!", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "12 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello Richard s, ", "Thank you for taking the time to provide us feedback of your recent visit. Although I appreciate that when there is live music people do feel inclined to dance it is worth mentioning that we are a restaurant with live music and so have revisited the 'dance floor' space which is no longer advertised. ", "Unfortunately, due to the size of the restaurant, as soon as even a few people get up to dance it ruins the show for the vast majority - the view of the stage becomes totally obscured. This is unfair given that people pay for music tickets. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "richard s", "reviewer_origin": ["Bromley, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "21"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r466444595-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Six of us went there last Friday to see the Black Hat Band. Bar upstairs was good, reception was great, table in the restaurant was excellent, music was brilliant! But.....the dance space was ridiculously small...surely they could have moved two tables away. Ok, we were on a group on deal, which just seemed too cheap, but the limited menu was all extras, and the food quality was uninspiring at best. so what did we get?...great value, but poor quality in a great venue. What an odd combination. Come on Boisedales...lets keep up the standards!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r466834505", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Poor Attention to Detail Can't Cook Steak as Requested", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "13 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello AllanC1960,", "Although you have raised some points that I will certainly be investigating and are far from the kind of feedback we enjoy hearing, thank you for taking the time to bring them to my attention.", "We use feedback as a very important training tool and I am confident that should you visit us again all of the points mentioned above will have subsequently been ironed out. ", "Thank you, ", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "AllanC1960", "reviewer_origin": ["Stockton-on-Tees, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "34"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r466834505-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale's is a restaurant which provides entertainment and food.", "Visited in December for a Frank and Dean show. The singers were good but both were Franks in my view but they were very good.", "The problems started with the ordering and service.", "Having ordered starters and mains and a bottle of red and white wines, the wine had not arrived by the time the starters arrived. When we pointed this out the waitress spoke to my wife and seemed to offer her a glass of white on the house. Nothing was said to me.", "It turned out that the wine was the wine we had ordered, but Boisdale's had the good grace not to charge us for that bottle. What was bizarre was the waitress placed the wine bottle in a cooler some 8 feet from our table, my wine arrived and was placed n the table.", "When the starters arrived I had ordered the Haggis which was supposed to be a mini \"roast\". The texture suggested that the only oven the haggis had seen was of the micro wave type. My wife had the Scallops which were good.", "For main I had ordered the \"guest steak\" at \u00a336, which I asked for medium rare. My wife ordered quail. ", "My steak arrived rare not medium rare.", "The quail came on a full plate which contained game chips. The waiter brought bread sauce which he served onto the plate covering the game chips making them soggy and unpalatable. The main issue though was that as the plate was full it was very difficult to eat the quail as there was no room to manoeuvre. ", "All in all, was not impressed with the service or food but the entertainment was good."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r459574283", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "great place, great music...but value for money?", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "14 February 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "dartfordchris", "reviewer_origin": ["dartford"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r459574283-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Have been to the Boisdale on many occasion for live music. Great venue, great place. have previously eaten in the main restaurant as part of the dining/seating package at \u00a340.00 each. Always been good.", "Recently saw a Santana tribute who were excellent. Stay with me if you can here....paid \u00a340 for a seat and 2 course dinner. Normal price for a seat to watch the band \u00a310.00...meaning \u00a330 for a 2 course dinner consisting of 5 choices for starter/main...but 2 of these came with a supplement....so soup (which was lovely) and goujons of plaice/fries/dip for \u00a330.00...PLUS a service charge of \u00a38 bringing this to \u00a388.00. I reiterate....band great, place great, service great....food was fine...but not value for money.", "for future reference... 2 course fixed menu available from the bar at 12.95....and a non dining seat for the music weighs in at \u00a346.00...much better value!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r464594336", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely bar", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "4 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi snazzzle,", "Thank you for your kind comments - I will take great pleasure in sharing your compliments with our bar team. ", "To hear that you will definitely be coming back is exactly the kind of reaction we are looking for! ", "See you soon, ", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Snazzzle", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "42"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r464594336-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This is a lovely bar you can get table service, there is a smoking area with heated terrace, they have a restaurant upstairs prices are reasonable and there are also live jazz bands which you can watch while eating, the bar staff are all friendly and polite,I will definitely be going back here"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r459204239", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Jazz Lunch", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "13 February 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello Serica2015,", "To hear the venue being labelled as 'superb' is fantastic - I agree that it is quite an impressive site. ", "Above this, to leave such kind comments on the food, drinks and music really tops it off!", "Almost on your doorstep means there is no excuse for not coming back soon. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Serica2015", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "41"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r459204239-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Superb venue, spacious and light but an ambience for the great Jazz trio playing. Food was first class, the aged beef superb and of course the whisky list was mind blowing. Great to have this almost on our doorstep!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r460569678", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Borderline food, service poor", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "17 February 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Andrew P", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r460569678-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Using a travel Zoo voucher so the me he was limited. Our glass of champagne arrived after we ordered red wine (v strange...) I had soup, which was so salty. My partner had haggis which needed seasoning! The burger was good but the steak was a little too fatty (it was a rib eye but all the same it was just a bit too fatty...)", "The service was poor, our server didn't appear to be too busy but you just couldn't find him. When he was there he would just walk past quickly - he topped our wine up once! Love this place but really....! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r459248291", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great experience.....", "diner_date": " March 2016", "rating_date": "13 February 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Mitchell1960,", "To be labelled as 'Excellent' is absolutely the kind of accolade that we strive hard to achieve. Feedback is a very important part of our business and to read such positive words makes it all worthwhile! ", "Glad to hear that you will be joining us again and we look forward to maintaining such standards upon your return. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Mitchell1960", "reviewer_origin": ["Kingston upon Thames, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "21"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r459248291-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Okay, there's not much about this place that isn't all the way up there in the excellent category. Service superb - it really was - food same - wine quite expensive unless sticking to the house bottles.", "Entertainment excellent - a jazz night - great environment- sound and seating superb", "Will go again"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r466531641", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Always a great experience ", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "12 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Rositsa,", "Thank you for your very short yet very sweet review! ", "We hope to welcome you back soon for some jazz and Whisky and if you haven't already you should give the food a try too..", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "rosie3208", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r466531641-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The food is fantastic and the atmosphere is always great! If you love jazz and whiskey Boisdale is the perfect choice "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r463970441", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Trendy Place", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "2 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello vonnyDublin, ", "Thank you for taking the time to provide us feedback of your recent visit. I am sorry to hear that you found the price of the food to be on the higher end of the scale. We do use extremely good quality suppliers and as such our pricing reflects such quality. That said, we are still priced competitively for the market. ", "I am glad to hear that you enjoyed the service. It is unfortunate you were unable to enjoy the live music. It is advisable to book - especially at the weekends - as we do get extremely busy. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "vonnyDublin", "reviewer_origin": ["Dublin, Ireland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "51"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r463970441-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Ate here Friday evening with my daughter and Aunt. A nice open room with an outside balcony area where people can smoke. Food ok! Have eaten better elsewhere for much less. Thought \u00a318.50 sterling for a burger a bit over the top. I ordered the steak and this small sliced piece of meat arrived on a plate, chips and veg all at extra cost. Cocktails also steep at \u00a313.50 but I suppose they are catering to a business and finiancial clientel who can afford these prices..", "The service was good and there was a nice atmosphere to the place.Unfortunately we couldn't get in to hear the music as it was booked out and we ate on the first floor. Had a lovely evening but found the place expensive."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r461380906", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great venue and food 4th time here for a music night", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "20 February 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi hoenesm.", "Thank you so much for your fantastic feedback on your recent visit! Feedback of any kind is very much appreciated and obviously even better when as positive as yours. ", "We would love to have you and your family back again so please do not wait too long!", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "hoenesm", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r461380906-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["As always, it has lived up to its feel and look and ambience.... I booked a table of 14 and was told we would have to be on 2 tables. We visited the day before our booking to ask if they could try to sit us together as my 2 families were coming a long way and i didnt want to split them up...., it was no trouble for the staff and had a call the next morning to say they had re organized tables so we could sit together. Unfortunately i then had a call to say 4 could not make it due to family member ending up in hospital. I called Boisdales back and apologised that it would now be 10... When we arrived we had a superb table for the 10 of us...great credit to them for accomodating us again in such circumstances.", "My family that did come all made a comment about how amazing the Rib eye steaks were... and to be honest evertime we have been here we have never been disappointed in the quality... you may have to pay a supplement and add side dishes, but we have always found it to be excellent. Oh... and the Haggis is amazing.... The entertainment on that night for us was not as spectacular as other nights we have been, but we knew that may be the case anyway.... My family loved the whole feel and ambience of the venue.... we have all been to expensive restaurants and plush places, and we are very picky and fussy and have no problem pointing out to staff any failings we feel are justified....At Boisdale Canary Wharf we have never had reason to say anything....and i have always been amazed at how reasonable the final bill has been at the end... My family all want to come back again.. !!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r461426260", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Friendly atmosphere, tasty food, great music!", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "20 February 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi b9scottuk,", "To be highly recommended is exactly the kind of feedback that we are looking for - thank you for taking the time to provide us with your feedback! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "b9scottuk", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r461426260-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were here for our friend's birthday on Friday night. The food was delicious and very reasonable (a special deal: 2 courses, a glass of bubbly for \u00a320) the entertainment was fantastic and the staff were wonderful. I highly recommend this place for friends, dates, or business"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r463834238", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wow - what a venue", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "1 March 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi John L,", "Words like 'impressed', 'attentive', 'fantastic' and 'stunning' in relation to Boisdale of Canary Wharf really do make us feel very proud as a team here! ", "Thank you so much for sharing your views and we hope to welcome you back in the near future!", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "537JohnL537", "reviewer_origin": ["Ramsbottom, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "189"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "96"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r463834238-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited on a Saturday evening and was so impressed with the attentive service, the fantastic food and the stunning live band. ", "This is a must visit venue and the management and team should be rightly proud of their efforts - well done!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r461523939", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Nice Music.....", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "20 February 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello Nigel T,", "You have raised some concerning points re; the quality and timings of the food. I have raised these with our chef and we will both be paying close attention in the coming weeks! ", "On a positive note I am glad that you enjoyed both the music and the service. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "44nigelt", "reviewer_origin": ["Farnham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "25"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r461523939-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["On our visit the food took far too much time to arrive at the table and when it did, it was cold. Upon complaining the staff were very attentive but the replacement food again too far too long to arrive. The music was fabulous, but being a large open room it was very difficult top hear the artist due to the noise of people talking etc.."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r455353902", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Our booking was cancelled 1,5 h before we were supposed to dine", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "28 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Anna70_13", "Needless to say I am both shocked and disappointed after reading you review. We have various different offers running at the moment as well as using third party Booking agents and I can assure you that no booking takes priority over another. ", "Please contact me directly at gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk to discuss this further.", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Anna70_13", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r455353902-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Me and my friend booked one of Boisdale Canary Wharf's special offers on opentable as we thought it would be a nice ending to the evening after attending the Winter Lights Festival. I arrived in Canary Wharf at 6 pm and noticed that I had a missed call from the restaurant telling me that they could not fit us in (we had booked for 7.30 pm). I booked the table the night before and they had 20 hours to figure out if there were space for us or not (there were several free slots when I booked)! This makes us suspect they got a booking request from people not using an offer and they were more \"attractive\" guest. This lead to that we were out of a place to dine and since I refuse to eat in big restaurant chains with bland food we ended up walking around for ages trying to find something. I will never try and book this place again as it is far too unreliable.", "I have used opentable for years and I have never experienced this kind of behavior before."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r454830458", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Poor wee thing...", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "25 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello OnehandEconomist,", "It was a great shame to hear that you did not enjoy the Haggis, many of our customers come specifically for this and - being a Scot myself - I must say I am proud to serve. We buy our Haggis from a seriously reputable supplier who is renowned for their quality. ", "That said, I have had a conversation with our head chef and we will both be ensuring we pay extra attention to the preparation moving forward to ensure the correct consistency. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "OnehandEconomist", "reviewer_origin": ["Edinburgh, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "53"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r454830458-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Pleasant enough evening but for the haggis starter. It was billed as wee, so no inaccuracies there. But was it haggis? Is haggis a smooth, sticky, tasteless paste? Where was the grain? The pepper? And was that really bashit neeps? Or just an English turnip? I was reminded of the great Burns' alternatives to his master o' the pudding race. And of his reaction to such junior members of the pudding race - especially ragout. For a Scottish restaurant, this is poor. The Saltire deserves better. C'mon, you can represent us better than this! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r454439392", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Liked it", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "24 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi WilcoBraintree,", "Thank you for taking the time to provide the review of your recent visit. We have just introduced a new menu and if you are looking for a bit more of a buzz then you should join us on a Thursday, Friday or Saturday evening. We also have live music which I am sure you would enjoy!", "Hope to see you soon,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "WilcoBraintree", "reviewer_origin": ["Braintree"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "166"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "87"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r454439392-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A pleasant surprise, large, plush and nice staff. We were there early so it was quiet. Had haggis as a starter followed by cod. Nothing special but good enough"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r455808072", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Sunday Jazz lunch with not enough Jazz", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "30 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi cazw0406,", "Thank you for taking the time to write your review of your recent visit. To hear that the food and atmosphere was \"lovely\" is fantastic! ", "I am surprised that you only managed to enjoy 20-30 minutes of the Jazz as the musicians play for 1.5 hours. I will ensure that the timings are clearer moving forward. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "cazw0406", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r455808072-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We really enjoyed our visit here, the food was lovely as was the atmosphere. My only negative is we booked as we love live jazz and we were at lunch for just over 2 hours and there was only 20-30 minutes of music which i think was not enough considering its sold as a sunday Jazz lunch!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r455134794", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Lovely location, not bad food, slow service", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "27 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello Kohan R,", "Thank you for taking the time to provide us with feedback of your recent visit. I was surprised to hear that you found the burger to be average as we have won awards in the past and generally receive very positive feedback on that dish. That said, I will ensure I speak to our head chef and we keep a close eye on the burgers moving forward. ", "I am confident that you will not be late getting back to work on your next visit, alternatively you should join us in the evening as we have just launched a fantastic new cocktail menu - perhaps you would like to sample!?", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "kohanr", "reviewer_origin": ["Purley, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "133"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "65"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r455134794-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went to Boisdale for lunch and had the spicy burger. Was nice but very average. You're paying for the location as it is stunning inside and has a really good ambiance. Service was really good but so slow. Took 45 mins for our burgers to arrive and we were late getting back to work.", "Overall good, but nothing to write home about."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r455840411", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lots of Positives Spoiled By Speed of Service", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "30 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Bignickandlittleted,", "Although I was disappointed with some of the points raised in your review I would like to thank you for taking the time to provide feedback. I am glad you felt the dinner and entertainment to be 'Excellent'. ", "I was unaware of any delays with food on the evening and would have certainly addressed this at the time had I known so apologies that this was not the case. ", "Please rest assured that the configuration of the restaurant had not been altered in anyway however it is not usual to have two larger tables book in the VIP section - it is usually smaller tables of 2 or 4. ", "We have some fantastic acts coming to join us over the course of the next few months. I am confident that should you wish to enjoy any of these there will be no problems re; speed of service. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Bignickandlittleted", "reviewer_origin": ["High Wycombe, England"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "195"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "112"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r455840411-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for a Saturday night entertainment and dinner (Jersey Boys), both of which were excellent. However, it's not cheap and the speed of service was poor - 90 minutes between starter and main. The waiter (who was very good also) said the kitchen was under pressure, but nothing they didn't know about in advance and is presumably a regular thing, so unless they were people down this isn't really an excuse or explanation. It looked like they'd squeezed two extra tables onto the dance floor too, which was a shame as it made the whole place look like an untidy village hall event rather than classy."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r458012929", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fab night out!", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "8 February 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Carol B,", "Reviews don't really get any better than this so thank you so much for taking the time! I am so glad to hear that we exceeded your expectations. ", "We have various different offers running at the moment, perhaps one of them would suit you and you can use as an excuse to visit again!", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Carol B", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "142"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "68"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r458012929-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited with group of friends on a travelzoo deal following matin\u00e9e theatre show. Bit of a trek from the westend but definitely worth the effort! Fairly easy to find and magical location overlooking Canary Wharf. Great vibe on arrival; welcoming and efficient staff. Food and service good but the unexpected highlight of the evening was the cabaret entertainment NY the outstanding Westend Jersey's; a Jersey boys tribute band who were simply amazing!! Definitely of Westend standard. Wow, what a night!!", "Highly recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r456787093", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good location, but had better food in less expensive restaurants", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "2 February 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello LGladders, ", "Thank you for taking the time to provide your feedback of your visit to Boisdale Canary Wharf. ", "I am glad to hear that you found the room to be enjoyable and the waiter to be good. I am, however, disappointed to hear of the issues you faced with regards to the timing on the evening. I would like to assure you that this is not the 'norm' and would like you to rest assured that if you decided to dine with us again I am confident that you would find the speed of service to be more in line with expectation. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "LGladders", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r456787093-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I had a belated works Christmas meal so we had one of the private rooms as there was 10 of us. The room was well laid out with a good size square table so that you could talk to everyone easily. ", "We had a good waiter, but as with other reviews, the service was very slow. It's good not to be rushed but 5 of the diners missed their last train home as there was such a big gap between courses! The wine wasn't left on the table but on a table at the side of the room and due to the slow service, it wasn't easy to keep your glass topped up!", "The starter was lovely, but I had the steak for my main, which was OK, but I have had better at less expensive restaurants. One of my party is a vegetarian and they only had the choice of one main, which wasn't very good. ", "The view from the room was lovely, but I think that's what you are paying for, location, location, location.", "The restaurant closes at 12am, but by the time we had paid for the bill it was 12.40am and the receptionist who deals with the costs, was all packed up with her own coat on! As one of my party was in the toilet when the majority of us picked up our coats, the receptionist had left before she could get her coat, so we had to go and find someone.", "I think if I returned I would go for drinks only and sit in the main room listening to the live music."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r457266314", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "A must have for all jazz lovers", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "5 February 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello Giusi F,", "It was a real pleasure to read your recent review - thank you for taking the time to provide feedback. ", "We work hard to ensure that we deliver a well rounded experience from all aspects and it seems like we managed to deliver just that! I will take great pleasure in feeding your kind comments back to the team. ", "We hope to see you soon!", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "669giusif", "reviewer_origin": ["Ibiza, Spain"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r457266314-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I've heard and read lots of positive feedback about this restaurant and finally I've had the chance to dine at this lovely place; the venue itself is stunning with a baroque style decor and split in two floors; the restaurant is upstairs where diners can enjoy a fantastic view overlooking Cabot Place; as for the food we tried all the Scottish dishes which were absolutely delicious- a particular mention goes to haggis and the black truffle mayonnaise! On the top of that our dining was accompanied by live jazz music which made it really pleasant and unique! Staff very attentive and polite. I definitely recommend it especially for romantic people or simply jazz lovers!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r456674445", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "The danger of second visits", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "2 February 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SimonBP", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "54"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "45"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r456674445-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I first visited Boisdale a year ago - as part of two couples celebrating two birthdays. That visit was tremendous, the food was excellent, the service impeccable and whilst expensive - we all felt that it was worth it. However that was then...", "Late January 2017, to celebrate a birthday - my wife and I decided to enjoy Boisdale once again, believing that the anticipated expense would be worth it as it was a celebration. Unfortunately, the night soundly failed to deliver... There was obviously a private function going on that evening (the night before Burns night?), so the main restaurant never got more than 40% full, however it seemed that the staff wanted to sit all couples next to each other (more on this later).", "Perhaps it was due to this function that the focus of both front of house and kitchen staff - were focussed elsewhere.", "The choice of starters was somewhat limited (seemingly a lot of fish - we don't eat), so opted to share a game terrine with foes gras. Unfortunately the fatty fois gras which masked all other flavours except the gingerbread melba toast, so the experience was that of fois gras and not terrine. But it was only the starter - so we weren't overly worried.", "We followed with two steaks, a medium and a rare fillet on the bone. Unfortunately the medium was rarer than fillet. After some time, we managed to actively attract a member of staff's attention - who took the steak away to be cooked some more. Unfortunately when it had returned, it was evident that it had been now cooked in a pan that had just cooked either heart or haggis from its strong metallic taste, ruining this meat for both diners. The fillet on the bone was unremarkable (so damned by faint praise), the highlight of this course was the sauce diane (and that is not a reason to go to a restaurant).", "The desserts were quite nice - a chocolate torte, tasted good but looked fussy. The salted caramel ice-cream was tasty and smooth. However the diners now sitting at the freshly turned neighbouring table had just started on their very smelly fish starter (when they could have been sat anywhere else in the 60% empty restaurant). I am sure that no-one could enjoy a dessert with an all encompassing smell of fish and lemon.", "Throughout the evening the service was conspicuous by its absence. The staff had no knowledge or joy of the dishes, we had to chase for the steak to be cooked correctly, at no point were we asked if everything was alright, indeed no-one checked if the recooked steak was satisfactory.", "At the end, we queried the service charge (a restaurant set 12.5%) which was deducted without hesitation. Speaking with the manager, he said the couple were seated next to us as they had decided they didn't want to sit by the stage - surely they could have been sat anywhere else instead (this shows lazy planning and lack of consideration for other diners). ", "I mentioned that we had returned as part of a celebration, to which the manager told me that I should have told him. Does this mean that Boisdale only gives good experiences to those whom they are know are celebrating a special night. In summary Boisdale charge prices for which one expects (\u00a3200 for 2) an excellent experience, one should not need to actively ask for it or justify it. For this price, Boisdale should be delivery a consistent experience to all of the appropriate standard - this evening, Boisdale failed.", "Can I recommend Boisdale? In all sincerity, I can not - for the price paid, there is no guarantee of consistency. Ultimately, it appears that Boisdale is relying upon the price charged persuading its patrons that it must be good and hoping that others won't complain too much."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r451217798", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Something a bit different", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "11 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi sandra f,", "Thank you for taking the time to provide us with feedback from your recent visit. I look forward to sharing your kind comments with the team. ", "We have various different musicians who play here in Boisdale Canary Wharf, you can find the music listings on our website. ", "We hope to see you soon,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "sandra f", "reviewer_origin": ["Southampton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "24"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r451217798-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I went to Boisdales on Saturday with my husband and had a lovely time. The service was very good and the jazz music excellent. The food was choices from a set meal, and was quite good if not a bit on the basic side. The venue itself is great if you like something a bit different from the usual run of the mill eating places."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r453946229", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Worst most expensive burger EVER", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "22 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello Tony M, ", "Thank you for providing us with your interpretation of your recent visit. I appreciate you taking the time. After a bit of investigation with regards to this booking I would like to clarify some points. ", "Your table had been booked with us on the 20th of January with our new receptionist who was unaware that the 50% offer was not available on the 1st floor - only on the 2nd floor. Needless to say, all staff are now fully aware of all offers and the T&C's attached to them. As soon as this was recognised we made several attempts to contact you to explain and left a voicemail to ask you to confirm if you would like to go ahead with the booking but this would be on the second floor. We received no reply and so cancelled the table, assuming you did not want to proceed. ", "When you arrived, we did accommodate you and also - as a gesture of goodwill for the mix up - extended the 50% discount for you on the 1st floor. With regards to you waiting for hours, this is not quite correct. Your bill was opened at 20.39pm and closed at 22.10pm. A 1.5 hour time slot for starters, mains and a bottle of wine and a further 2 glasses would be a reasonable time scale from our side. ", "It is a shame that you did not enjoy the food, our burgers and chips are extremely high volume items and we had no other complaints on the evening. Not to mention having won various awards for our burgers. At the end of your meal our Manager downstairs enquired as to whether or not everything was alright, as there was food left on the plate, to which you replied 'fine'. Had you mentioned any of the points raised here we could have endeavoured to rectify things for you on the night.", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Tony M", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r453946229-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Dont touch this place with a barge pole. We booked a table with a 50 % off coupon when we arrived we were informed that our table had been cancled and therefore our coupon was not valid. We decided to take a table anyway. The bar menu is very limited so we ordered a sharing platter to start, which was very nice. Then we waited and waited and waited for our burgers. 1 hour 20 mins after finishing our starter i asked where our burger was. It arrived 10 mins later. What a massive disappointment. The chips were cooked in dirty oil which gave them a unusual taste. The onion rings were stale, yes stale iv never had stale onion rings befor and dont particularly want them again. The burger its self was dry very dissapointing. \u00a390 for a bottle of wine a starter and 2 burgers is more than a rip off, i feel as thou iv been mugged. Only eat here if you like paying well over the odds for crap food and you dont mind waiting for hours. Wont be going back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r449877412", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Lunch", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "6 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello John F,", "Thank you so much for taking the time to share your kind words. A really important part of our business is to build relationships with our guests and so to be able to recognise what you drink is exactly the level of service we are striving for. ", "You really should have a look online at our music calendar as I am sure you will find an act that is appealing and I can guarantee you will enjoy, the performances really do add something special to any visit. ", "Hope to see you soon! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "John F", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "37"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r449877412-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I am slightly loathe to write this report. ", "By far the best bar in Canary Wharf for service and surroundings. ", "Lunchtimes are quiet in the bar area, which means you get served a lot quicker than other (much poorer) pubs. It's nice to walk into a bar where they remember your drink and you. ", "It's also not the most expensive bar in the wharf. ", "I go there once a week usually and chill on my own or with colleagues. I enjoy trying to spot the celebs in the photos. ", "It's the best kept secret in the wharf but deserves the recognition. ", "I have sadly never been able to attend the gigs at night although one day that will happen. ", "Come and enjoy it but please don't tell anyone."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r451321031", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great night out", "diner_date": " November 2016", "rating_date": "11 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Denisehuckett,", "Thank you for letting us know of your recent visit and providing us with much valued feedback. ", "I was surprised to hear that you felt the sound was not great, we have invested a lot of money in a extremely high quality sound system and this is not feedback that I have come across to date. I will ensure that I pay extra attention to this moving forward so that if the sound quality is not as it should be we can rectify the situation. ", "Kind Regards, ", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Denisehuckett", "reviewer_origin": ["London "], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "65"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r451321031-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great atmosphere buzzing restaurant which made it quite difficult to hear Kai Hoffman the jazz singer who was singing Etta James and Dana Washington songs. ", "We paid \u00a330 each for VIP tickets but couldn't hardly hear her and this was being quite near the stage. ", "The food was delicious but quite pricey after paying \u00a330 each to sit close to the stage it made it an expensive week night out. ", "I would return but would not pay for VIP tickets."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r449822727", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Very nice food and great atmosphere", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "6 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi David_985,", "To get feedback like this makes all of the hard work the team put in here worthwhile. I will take great pleasure in feeding this back to them! ", "We do hope to see you again soon. If you enjoy cocktails then you should come and check out our new cocktail menu which will go live on Monday - very impressive, even if I do say so myself. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Dav1d_985", "reviewer_origin": ["Surrey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r449822727-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I ate at the Boisdale Canary Wharf for a Christmas night out with work collegues. The service was excellent and the food was very nice. Live music added a great atmosphere to the restuarant and made the whole evening more special. ", "I would highly recommend paying this place a visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r449478786", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food and great value ", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "5 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi paul s,", "Reading your recent review brought a smile to my face - thank you for taking the time to share. ", "To hear that you were impressed with the terrace, food and service is fantastic! If you are a Whisky fan you are certain to be impressed with our Whisky collection - make time to nosy through our extensive list next time.", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "213pauls", "reviewer_origin": ["Gerrards Cross, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "207"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "110"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r449478786-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great venue with a rather impressive terrace.", "Steaks are consistently good but the lobster is excellent value at around \u00a322. Worth going back again just for that. ", "Very busy as it was pre-Christmas but the service was excellent "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r448055507", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice view, good music, excellent service, average food", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "31 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi UD K,", "Thank you for taking the time to review your recent visit. All feedback is very much appreciated so thank you for taking the time. ", "I have to agree - the view is quite spectacular and one that I will never tire of. I was so pleased that you found your service from Ashley to be 'Excellent'. The team work very hard and so to get a bit of recognition is always very well received. ", "I was sorry to hear that you were let down by the food and I have highlighted these comments to the chef. We will both endeavour to keep an eye on these dishes over the next few weeks. Our Burgers are extremely popular so this is surprising. ", "I am confident that if/when you join us again it will be the full package and the food will be of the same standard as the rest of your experience. All of our staff are well equipped to offer any advice on the menu too - should you so wish! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "UD K", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "355"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "111"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r448055507-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We came for dinner and a jazz performance. The view of the canals and the lit skyscrapers all around you is very nice and romantic. The service was excellent-- our waiter (Ashley) was polite, cheerful and efficient. The music was very good-- a 4 piece band played well jazz of various flavours. The main disappointment was the food, which was average. I had a hamburger which was just OK, and my wife had a chicken curry dish she did not care for. But overall it was a good experience that we might repeat for the view, service and music."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r453263694", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "VIP Music", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "19 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello michealE4102AH,", "Although I was disappointed with some of the points you have raised I would like to thank you for taking the time to feed them back to me. ", "I feel the 'minimal efforts made' is an unfair statement. I was myself working that evening and although could not position myself personally in front of the stage all evening I went to great lengths to politely ask those who were dancing to move to the side and did successfully manage to do this. Please rest assured that we have, subsequently, contact our musicians to ask them to refrain from inviting everyone up to dance as obviously this does cause some problems. ", "I am glad to hear that you enjoyed the food and service.", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "michaelE4102AH", "reviewer_origin": ["Blandford Forum, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r453263694-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Be careful what you pay for::We booked a VIP table for 4 to watch and listen to Ben Walters Boogie evening> Whilst food and service were good the show was not: the staff allowed dancers to block the stage: minimal efforts were made to clear them unsuccessfully> the dancers ( it was like watching you're Grandad at a bad wedding with two particular men from the rear of the restaurant jigging around for the whole evening, but more importantly changing the music to dance style by request and only missing was the \" birdie Song\" > An expensive evening spoilt by poor management and misrepresentation of dinner cabarat"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r452918104", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Always great food and great atmosphere", "diner_date": " January 2017", "rating_date": "18 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Hudstefer,", "This type of feedback is exactly what we are striving so hard to achieve - from the service, to food quality as well as the live music element which is a bit of a unique selling point. Thank you so much for taking the time to share your thoughts! ", "I will take great pleasure in feeding this back to the team and we all look forwarding to welcoming you back soon.", "Kind regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Buckoh1", "reviewer_origin": ["Leeds, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "44"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r452918104-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A confession, I love this restaurant and have been a number of times with family and for business. It never lets you down and I felt compelled to say thanks via this site. ", "Great staff. Really professional and hard working. The food is always top quality. And the music nights can be really incredible, whether it's the Jazz themed Sunday lunch or a live band at night. ", "This place deserves all the plaudits it gets."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r453423614", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice restaurant ", "diner_date": " March 2016", "rating_date": "19 January 2017", "answer_text": ["Hello Madalina M,", "To hear that we were able to positively contribute to such a special evening is fantastic! Thank you for your feedback. ", "I hope that we will be able to host you again in the future for another special occasion.", "Kind regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "335madalinam", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r453423614-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Was a great night out of the bridesmaids team. Nice atmosphere, music, food and staff! Pleasant surprise at the end of our dinner, the waitress came with a different cakes on the house, cause she figured out that we were celebrating the wedding that was about to come."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r447895181", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great ambience, with live music", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "30 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi Claudia A,", "To receive such a lovely review is a fantastic way for us to start the new year. Thank you!", "To hear that you visit us often is great - I do hope that means we will see you soon.", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Claudia A", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r447895181-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Food is lovely, staff friendly, good music, good wine. Would highly recommend. We often go here with family or friends and each time we have not been disappointed. The food is always up to standard. And you can have a little dance if you feel up to it after or in-between meals. Be careful as when you book there is a surcharge if you go into the live music slot which is added to your food bill."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r444873020", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Xmas show", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "17 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi Keith! ", "I appreciate that having joined us so frequently you may have felt that providing some feedback would be unnecessary,however it gave me great pleasure to read your kind words!", "It has been an absolute pleasure hosting you and your company and there is lots more Claret to be had so don't wait too long before your next visit. ", "Look forward to seeing you then,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Keith E", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r444873020-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Attended the Xmas show on the 3rd, 10th, & 17th with various friends and family. Boisdale Belgravia and Canary remain my favourite restaurants & the Frank & Dean Xmas show at Canary Wharf truly was exceptional. The food is great and the team headed by the new general manager Jenny are fabulous, nothing is too much trouble even with the restaurant packed to the gunnels. ", "Great food, service, entertainment and a Cigar terrace to boot!!!! What more could you want!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r444907805", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Place is nice, food is awful", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "17 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi Marshall B,", "It was with mixed feelings I read your recent review. Thank you for taking the time to provide us with your feedback. ", "Although I was glad to hear of the positives it is concerning to hear your comments on our food offering. We do have a rather varied music calendar and do not only play Jazz music, a lot of the artist who perform here have quite a following too so - for the moment - we are happy with the musical aspect of things. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "MarshallB429", "reviewer_origin": ["Isle of Wight, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "58"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r444907805-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Firstly, the great things: excellent cigar terrace for members, with personable service, good choice of wines at reasonable prices, often some good blues or reggae bands playing. Good sports bar/pub atmosphere on lower level for watching rugby with a beer and a burger. ", "However, the food in the main restaurant ranges from passable (at best) to God-awful, and this is after having eaten there for business or with friends over a dozen times in five years. Not once have I left there saying \"wow that was good - let's go back soon\" and most often I go there for a beer or a cigar and eat elsewhere. ", "The food is simply too bad or inconsistent to make it worth the effort. ", "Also, do people really like jazz? I mean, really? Get more upbeat bands playing and fill the place. Just a view..."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r445094184", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Sunday Jazz Lunch", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "18 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello Brightredangel,", "Your short but very sweet review has been very well received by myself and the team. Thank you. ", "Don't wait too long before your next visit!", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Brightredangel", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "65"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "40"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r445094184-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Thanks for another lovely Boisdales meal, service good, food lovely, generous portions and quality food."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r446028951", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great music", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "22 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi N D, ", "Thank you for your recent review, I was delighted to hear that you enjoyed the music and the atmosphere of the restaurant. ", "I have to agree, the window tables with the view of the skyline are quite special! ", "We do hope to see you soon, ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "318nd", "reviewer_origin": ["Lincolnshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "761"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "677"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r446028951-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Having visited the Belgravia venue, we thought we would try Canary Wharf. The music and atmosphere were excellent. We would ask for a table near the window another time as the view were fabulous. The food is overpriced and nothing special. We found the same in Bekgravia. Having said that, we'll go again because the music made up for it."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r445791462", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Loved it here", "diner_date": " September 2016", "rating_date": "21 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi paul m, ", "I was really pleased to hear that you enjoyed your evening with us recently, thank you for offering your feedback. ", "Although people do tend to get carried away with the festivities please rest assured that Canary Wharf Security do a fantastic job to ensure a safe environment and are always only moments away should any situations get out of hand. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "paul m", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "160"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "103"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r445791462-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Spent a great evening here with Friends ", "food was very good ", "Music great ", "service also very good", "Will visit again", "Only downside to it all we went on a friday evening and on leaving so many drunks about at canary wharf and was a bit nervy ( never police around just the security officers ) but dont let this put yu off of going"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r445969538", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Regular Customer Getting Fed Up With Experience - Xmas Dinner", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "21 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello Oliver R, ", "It was a great shame to read your feedback of Boisdale of Canary Wharf, although I would like to thank you for taking the time to provide it regardless. ", "You have highlighted some seriously concerning issues from different aspects of the evening which have saddened me. I would have to say, genuinely, that I don't feel that this is a true reflection on the level of standards and service that we usually pride ourselves on. ", "Please contact me personally on gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk as I would like the opportunity to discuss in more detail. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Oliver R", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r445969538-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Have to be honest, we live nearby and have been to the Canary Wharf Boisdale numerous times and have had mixed results. I have just been for my Xmas dinner with my partner and we have reached the conclusion that we wont be going back in the near future. ", "Being completely honest we never go to Boisdale for the food, in our opinion there are better places to go if you want a choice of good food. What we go for is the overall experience and after a few bad experiences we have had enough. ", "The overall experience tonight was poor and not worth the money at all. We have experienced poor service on previous visits (including 1 incident in which family members were rudely moaned at by a waiter for dancing near to stage, I did complain). On tonights visit our drinks didn't arrive until half way through the main meal (we did have starters), I did feel slightly sorry for the waitress who went to the bar numerous times to tell the waiter to check for the drinks. After that we were not offered drinks again throughout the entire meal.", "My partner was particularly disappointed because she booked because of the band that was performing. When we arrived we discovered that the lead singer wasn't there (she was replaced by someone not in the band!) and they would only perform until 10:30pm (closes at 12:00am). ", "To sum up.", "Poor choice of food, very poor table service, service charge is automatically added to bill, entertainment sub standard and finished early.", "The cost of the experience tonight with 1 drink each was \u00a3130+ and in our opinion not worth the money at all. We said, if we were ever persuaded to go back we would start off by only going for a drink and the music and skipping out the meal experience. ", "First time reviewing a restaurant but it needed to be said."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r446735987", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Great live music & food but very poor service", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "26 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi Saintfreethrow,", "It was a real shame to read your negative comments on the service you received on your recent visit. I do not feel that this is representative of the level of service that the team here at Boisdale Canary Wharf usually pride themselves on. ", "I will of course ensure that I pay extra attention to this moving forward. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Saintfreethrow", "reviewer_origin": ["Gettysburg, Pennsylvania"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r446735987-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked tickets and table for live band and dinner for 8. Service was very poor - floor staff ignore when called. Really frustrating. Having said that the band was great and good good. But at more that approx \u00a3140 per head, the service was abysmal & ruined the evening. Not recommended. There are far better choices at this price range. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r446450254", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Steak", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "24 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello 629berniev,", "To read your positive feedback on the various different elements of our offering here at Boisdale Canary Wharf was a real pleasure - thank you for your kind words. The team all work very hard to try and ensure that everyone has this type of experience. ", "I am glad that you kick started your festive period on a high and hope that you had a lovely Christmas thereafter. ", "Kind regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "BV1958", "reviewer_origin": ["Buckhurst Hill, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "48"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r446450254-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My mate and I attended Boisdale Canary Wharf for our annual pre Christmas 'feed', our waiter was excellent his service friendly and helpful. we had a very excellent relaxed lunch, which included one of the Chefs special's a Rib Eye Steak on the bone cooked to perfection, finished off with a couple of single malts.So in conclusion, although very expensive (we could have chosen cheaper mains!!) it was a once a year treat and very enjoyable, good service , good atmosphere, wonderful single malts and of course Great steak."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r447203949", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Cigar tasting service by Philip", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "28 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello misamae2016,", "It was a real pleasure to read your recent review of our Cigar library and the service you received from Filipe. Thank you for taking the time. ", "His Cigar knowledge is such a huge benefit to the business and this paired with his perfect understanding of the needs of each individual customer second to none. ", "We look forward to seeing you the next time you need to relax...", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "misamae2016", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r447203949-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["If you are looking for a relaxing enviroment for a cigar, the room at biosdale is a perfect choice. The humidor is kept under perfect supervision and cigars are in perfect condition. In case you are not sure what suites your taste Philip can give good advice on the Cigar. And all this comes with great service provided during the cigar tasting as well. ", "So this place is highly recommened."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r444771360", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Very Average", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "17 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello tinker186338,", "I was disappointed to read the review of your recent visit but would like to thank you for taking the time to provide it. ", "It is a real shame to hear that you will not visit us again as what you experienced is not a true reflection of what we offer here. The team work very hard to provide a personable and memorable customer experience and I am saddened to learn that this is not the level of service you received on your visit. ", "I am confident that this would not happen a second time and so, should you wish to change your mind, please contact me on gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk and I can make the reservation for you. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "tinker186338", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r444771360-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Food was average at best, service was poor - everything seemed too much trouble for our waiter and requests were met with an irritable \"yes I was going to get that\" but he would then forget and you would have to ask again 10 minutes later. Very disappointing and I definitely would not visit again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r440414826", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Visit to Canary Wharf And Overnight.", "diner_date": " November 2016", "rating_date": "27 November 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello Chairman1010,", "Thank you for the feedback of your recent visit. ", "It is fantastic to hear that you enjoyed the atmosphere here and that the prices were a pleasant surprise. You should try and come back to see our live music soon as it really does make the offering here quite special. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Chairman1010", "reviewer_origin": ["Hereford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "122"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "62"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r440414826-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Enjoyed this place for a couple of early evening drinks only. Very busy but great atmosphere. I was expecting heavy prices but turned out not much different from any where else. A lot of people were eating and it looked ok. There is a supplement for later evening entertainment but we were on a tight schedule to be somewhere else. Good to go though.."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r439736593", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "We were lucky we got food at all", "diner_date": " September 2016", "rating_date": "24 November 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello Sharon C,", "Thank you for taking the time to give us your feedback. ", "I am sorry to hear that your visit did not live up to expectation. I am confident that any issues you faced have since been ironed out.", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sharon C", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r439736593-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["8 of us went for Sunday Lunch in Septmber. The restaurant is very nice and spacious with great views. Unfortunately they were very busy that day and really couldn't cope. The service was frankly appalling and the food wasn't up too much either.... was disappointed as had heard good things about it."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r440738364", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice food.......have the Oysters ", "diner_date": " November 2016", "rating_date": "28 November 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello ClearSkyReviews,", "Thank you for giving us a review of your recent visit. ", "The kitchen team were very pleased to hear that you enjoyed the Oysters and Risotto! There is lots more on our menu for you to sample so do join us again soon...", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "ClearSkyReviews", "reviewer_origin": ["Bromley, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "94"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r440738364-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Lovely food, great venue and the food was great as well, try 6 oysters!!! Very nice and the risotto is great too"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r443071947", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Lovely night with parents, who remember 'rock 'n roll', dance and love GOOD FOOD.", "diner_date": " November 2016", "rating_date": "9 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello 42Gary42,", "It was an absolute pleasure to read your recent review of Boisdale Canary Wharf, thank you for taking the time to provide us with this. ", "To hear that your parents were up dancing and enjoying the atmosphere and offering to the full puts a huge smile on my face! ", "The team are thrilled with your comments and we look forward to welcoming you back in the near future - perhaps your Ma and Pa can teach me a thing or two on the dance floor!", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "42Gary42", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r443071947-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went to Boisdale (again) to celebrate the 80th Birthday of Buddy Holly. I love Boisdale (all venues) for first rate service, super food, a wonderful wine and spirit list and great MUSIC.", "Today we dined at 7.30pm on the set menu; 'dinner and a show for forty five pounds'. Great choices; the chef's salad of rocket, pear poached in red wine, stilton and walnuts was perfect. To follow a perfect flat iron steak, with extras such as broccoli with toasted almonds and sweet potato fries, a table favourite. The extra course taken was the ten cheeses plate, with crackers taken before desert, of something chocolatey. ", "Coffee and a super show followed, with Ma and Pa (in their seventies) cutting a rug and showing two sons how to jive! ", "We drank the reasonably priced Taittinger champagne, by the bottle and selected house reds by the glass.", "The 12.5% service was included in the set-price experience price.", "The night was around four hundred pounds for four persons; that's dinner, a show, dancing and champagne - a bargain! We will return soon."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r440643324", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday trip to the cigar lounge", "diner_date": " November 2016", "rating_date": "28 November 2016", "answer_text": ["Good afternoon Sara N,", "It was an absolute pleasure to read your recent review of Boisdale Of Canary Wharf. I have taken great pleasure in feeding this back to the team! ", "You are right - we have some fantastic live music, you should try and join us one evening to experience the offering we have upstairs in the restaurant. You can find our music listings on the website. ", "We hope to see you soon,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "saran868", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r440643324-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I took my boyfriend here for his birthday as he loves cigars and whiskey and it has a cigar lounge. I booked the terrace because we particularly wanted to go to the cigar lounge, however when we go again we will book the restaurant and the show because the music coming from the restaurant was so good!", "The terrace is informal - people in jeans and a tapas menu. As we were celebrating we were dressed up but they kindly let us order from the full restaurant menu. ", "The food was delicious, the cocktails were great, the service brilliant, we thoroughly enjoyed the whole experience. It was a little pricey but that was ok as it was a special occasion. Highly recommend."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r443098702", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great dinner and whisky", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "9 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello Giacomo A,", "Thank you for your positive feedback on your recent visit. I was surprised to hear that you felt the restaurant to be dark as almost a full wall is floor to ceiling window however was glad to hear that you enjoyed the atmosphere regardless. ", "Do join us again soon to enjoy some more tasty food and Whisky,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "jacksolo19", "reviewer_origin": ["Sofia, Bulgaria"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r443098702-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This place is a bit dark and may turn you off in terms of decor if you don't like the slightly seedy atmosphere - I personally really enjoyed it! Great starters and steak, had a nice whisky, everything was very tasty and enjoyable."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r444171371", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Average service, average food and eye watering bill!!!", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "14 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello Steve J, ", "Although I was disappointed to read your feedback I would like to thank you for taking the time to let me know of your recent visit. ", "It is clear that your experience is not a true reflection on our usual standards of both service and quality. Unfortunately throughout December we do need to give last orders for lunch time earlier than the rest of the year as we need to re-set the restaurant for dinner service however this certainly should not have been happening while you were still seated. ", "Please contact me at gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk as I would like the chance to discuss this with you further. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Steve J", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r444171371-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Came for lunch to find our booked table was added as an afterthought, more in the entrance hall than the actual restaurant. It also became clear that we didn't have a waitress assigned as we waited ages for menus, wine list, drinks etc etc. Service very average, we took to filling our own glasses.", "Food ok, though nothing special. Bill eye watering!! \u00a316.50 for a small bit of average smoked salmon starter!! The 4 of us had steaks, again ok, but not very special. Not too pricey this time, thats saved for the sides, but I've had nicer meals in a gastro pub for 25% of the price.", "None of us will be rushing to go back, which is a shame as we have just moved offices to Canary Wharf.", "We had a late lunch booking and expected to relax over a couple of glasses of wine, but the bar closed at 3:45pm and they started re-arranging the tables around us. Not very relaxing!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r444475522", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "It was okay", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "15 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi Shanni C,", "Although there are some issues in your review that I will need to address with the Chef I was delighted to hear that you could not fault the service.", "All feedback we receive is taken constructively, so thank you for taking the time to let us know of the difficulties you experienced with the food.", "I do hope that these issues will not prevent you coming back to join us in the future as I am confident that you will have nothing but praise for the food next time round!", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Shanni C", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r444475522-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Canary wharf - great view. Xmas Party. ", "Guess I expected a bit too much. My soup was great really creamy and flavoursome. My turkey - it's looked okay in terms of presentation. Nothing too fancy... it was also dry, very dry. I found it hard to swallow at time and the cranberry sauce came whilst we were half way through the meal - too late to even really try it out. Having said that I dont feel they could have redeemed that turkey. The dessert was nice... really chocolatey... so much so in fact it was a little bitter... not really to my taste personally but it went down well with my friends. I felt that it would have probably done nicely with some ice-cream or something. Can't fault the service thought the staff were brilliant. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r444378965", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Xmas Dinner", "diner_date": " December 2016", "rating_date": "15 December 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi John_Dareth_Evans,", "I was sincerely saddened to read your review of your recent visit. ", "Needless to say I would like to get a bit more detail from you as you have raised some issues that need to be addressed. you can reach me on gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk,", "I hope to hear from you soon,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "John_Dareth_Evans", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r444378965-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Works Christmas Do -- Food was cold and inedible. Barman was so slwo I could have made the beer myself in the time it took to get my order in.... Men's toilets were filthy and even when I told the manager, he didn't seem to care. Service was rubbish.... What the hell are people paying for???"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r433277199", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Avoid Sunday lunch", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "31 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello JASPA333, ", "I was sorry to read your recent review and discover that the food fell short of your expectations. Please rest assured that I have discussed this in detail with our Head Chef and we are seriously looking at what went wrong here and how we can improve moving forward. ", "Above this I will also be paying close attention to service and the wait time for drinks coming from the bar as obviously these were other areas of concern on your visit. ", "All in all you did not experience our usual level of standards, which is a real shame. I do hope you will return in the future as I am confident that we will be able to deliver on these. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "JASPA333", "reviewer_origin": ["Romford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "64"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "46"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r433277199-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went here with family for Sunday lunch ant to be fair the starters mushroom soup and the smoked salmon were very good but that's where it ended!", "4 of us had roast beef 1 pork and 1 chicken , the beef was tough full of fat and tasteless, the pork pretty much the same but the chicken was good as were the roast potatoes the veg of carrots and kale was bland with the kale tasting watery the desert was very average as well and for \u00a337.50 a head we was expecting something special and it wasn't!", "Service was average and drinks were very slow coming", "The venue is very nice inside a bit like a New York steakhouse and the jazz music in background was nice.", "Overall not a good day!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r433325690", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fun!", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "31 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi GiaKoutra,", "What a wonderful review! Thank you for your short and very sweet feedback. ", "We look forward to seeing you again soon,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "GiaKoutra", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r433325690-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a fantastic night at boisdale. Awesome jazz band playing live, exquisit malt wiskey from the jawdropping old bar, great art and oyster bar on the terrace. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r437708220", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Scots Food & Entertainment", "diner_date": " November 2016", "rating_date": "16 November 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi KiwiFlyng,", "Thank you for your feedback.", "There is always more food, drinks and music to sample so don't wait too long before you visit us again! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "KiwiFlyng", "reviewer_origin": ["Bangkok, Thailand"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "96"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "53"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r437708220-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Good noisy Scottish restaurant with band and soul singer. Wide selection of meats, fish and salads together with wines and of course whiskey."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r433372954", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fabulous, can't wait for next time.", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "31 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello slimbeau,", "Thank you so much for the review of your recent visit. Feedback is very important for us to keep our finger on the pulse and ensure we do not become complacent. ", "You definitely must make sure you spare some time for our fantastic Cigar Library the next time - it really is something special! Edita or Filipe, our cigar experts, will be on hand to offer any advice should you need it.", "We look forward to seeing you then,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "slimbeau", "reviewer_origin": ["Corby, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "127"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "46"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r433372954-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Hubby and I went there on a Saturday evening. We booked premium package . Show started at 9.45pm. The band was awesome, it was an American lady. Songs were mellow, then upbeat and then mellow. We ate and enjoyed the show at the same time. The food was very good . Unfortunately hubby didn't have time to have a cigar. That will be for our next visit. Most of the crowd were couples, late 30's and above. Loved it, loved it. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r434149033", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing service at the cigar library by Filipe! ", "diner_date": " November 2016", "rating_date": "2 November 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello Anush B,", "I cannot say I am surprised to read such a wonderful review of Filipe. He is a huge asset to the business and his customer service is second to none - I will take great pleasure in sharing your feedback with him. ", "Don't wait too long before your next visit! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Anush B", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r434149033-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Filipe at cigar library makes my visit worth while every time. He is not only extremely knowledgable in cigars and very welcoming but also very attentive to individual needs of his guests. Always a pleasure to unwind in peace after work. Highly recommend if you are into cigars. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r433614592", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Might be a good restaurant but bar doesn't really work", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "1 November 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi TraxTrax,", "Feedback of any kind is important for us to move forward positively. Thank you for taking the time to offer this. ", "It is a shame to hear that you feel our terrace to be nondescript. We spent a lot of time sourcing some beautiful trees/plants to try and make it feel like a tranquil garden in such a bustling city. ", "Hopefully you will give us another go and enjoy one of the various offers we have on at the moment, including two for one cocktails on the second floor bar which boasts one of Europe's best Whisky collections. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "TraxTrax", "reviewer_origin": ["Oxshott, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "144"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "43"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r433614592-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Ok first thing I didn't eat here", "So I'm only commenting it as a bar", "Now if you are a smoker it's ok - sort of nondescript outside seating area - nothing special", "The actual bar is ok but the room is an awkward shape around the bars so don't really feel it works on either floor", " ", "There are better bars in the area imo"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r434327668", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Exeptional", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "3 November 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi smk101,", "In a word it doesn't get much better than 'Exceptional' - thank you for your review. Although, you have raised a point about the music that you can rest assured I will look into. It is very unusual for any of our musicians to seem like their heart is not in it. It is usually quite the opposite!", "That aside, to hear that both the food and service you experienced were excellent is fantastic. Tim does a great job and I will make sure he is aware of your kind words. It makes all of our hard work worthwhile! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "smk101", "reviewer_origin": ["Bristol, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "39"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r434327668-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Beautiful d\u00e9cor ...Jazz a little subdued but it was a Sunday lots of gaps between tunes seemed rather like a practice than a polished set ..bit so a bit lazy..I came esp. for the Jazz so although the band were fantastic players and the singer a great crooner I felt their heart was not in the Sunday session. Food was amazing ....the best roast potatoes ever and the beef fantastic. The best part of our visit though and the reason we will return was the excellent service. Tim you were so attentive and friendly...you worked that room like the true professional you obviously are . You are a credit to the restaurant Thank you ..."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r437175111", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Oysters and ok service", "diner_date": " November 2016", "rating_date": "14 November 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi Michelle F,", "Thank you for giving us feedback of your recent visit. I have taken on board what you have said about the service being unwelcoming, this is not feedback we receive regularly and the welcome/departure of guests is something I will be paying close attention to in the coming weeks. ", "I do hope to see you soon so that you can enjoy a more all-rounded experience.", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "michellef577", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r437175111-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went to boisdale for oysters and wine with the intentions of staying for a meal. Service was poor not very welcoming and when we left just got stared at with no thank you or goodbyes. Oysters were good despite service."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r436768535", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "great venue ..average food", "diner_date": " November 2016", "rating_date": "13 November 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello tony h,", "Thank you for taking the time to give us the feedback of your recent visit. Elvis is always extremely well received so I am glad to hear that you enjoyed. ", "I am disappointed to hear you feedback on the food and service. Please rest assured that I am looking into the areas you have mentioned and am confident we can use your comments constructively to ensure we do not fall short moving forward.", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny "], "reviewer_pseudo": "tony h", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "73"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "33"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r436768535-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["we attended on saturday 12th november for a 60th birthday, we had the private room just to the left of the stage. Elvis performed that night and he was truly brilliant. The food we ordered was served luke warm and some of the salmon not cooked correctly. We only had 1 poor girl who was trying to serve us all with drinks etc and she was very very good but desperately needed some help{there was 28 in our party} Hard to score boisdle as we had a great evening of entertainment which i would score 9 out of 10. The food and price of the drinks would only score around 3 out of 10. Overall you;ll have a god evening if the entertainment is good but certainly do not expect a nice meal."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r436885031", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Big place with potential but precious", "diner_date": " November 2016", "rating_date": "13 November 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi Kenny p,", "I was sorry to hear that you did not have a fun evening when you recently joined us. We do try and be as flexible as possible with the menu however business levels can dictate this somewhat at times. ", "You are correct on the house wine, we did have a supplier issue which has subsequently been rectified and is not something that happens frequently. ", "It is a shame that both of these points impacted your evening. Thank you for providing your feedback and should you wish to join us in the future I am confident that you will have a more positive experience. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "777kennyp", "reviewer_origin": ["Glasgow, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "63"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r436885031-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a sales gathering dinner here on Thursday night and Boisdale is quite an impressive restaurant which looks like it could be great fun - except it just wasn't. Problem 1 and one of the team sismply just didnt like the menu and asked for a simple green salad with simply grilled chicken and all these ingredients were on the menu in other dishes. No! our chef is like Gordon Ramsey, I can't ask him for anything non standard????. Gordon Ramsey this place ain't. Then they run out of their own house red wine? Pretentious and precious and food was good but not anything other than 'nice\". "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r433134704", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Waste of money ", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "31 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello Jaine D,", "Thank you for taking the time to give us feedback of your recent visit. I am concerned about many of the points you have raised. What you seem to have experienced falls extremely short of the mark with regards to both the quality and standards that we pride ourselves on. ", "If you would like to contact me at gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk I would like the opportunity to discuss this with you in more detail. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "362jained", "reviewer_origin": ["East Sussex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r433134704-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I was disappointed from the minute I got there . I had emailed to ask for a nice table as it was our first time there . The email was never acknowledged . When we got there we was sat at a table along a curved window looking out at building works . The stage was blocked out by a big pillar . As it was a jazz lunch that was booked you would of thought that you would of been by the stage to actually see or even hear the music . What then was not meant to of been just a Sunday lunch out then became one , which is not why we travelled all the way to London for . ", "We opted for the dearest choice on the menu , which was a three course , 1/3 bottle of wine and a glass of prosecco @ \u00a347.50 a head .", "We waited ages for the prosecco , and soon realised that the 1/3 of a bottle of wine wasn't given to you , in a carafe , say , but you had to keep waiting for a drink throughout your meal as they came round and gave you a small glass of wine here and there . I'm not sure we drank a bottle and a half between us and surely this is a trading standard issue as you are sold one thing and that's not actually what you get . In fact also a licensing issue as you then are not aware of what you have actually had , which is then a breach of weights and measures . Quite Cleary an issue that needs resolving .Anyway moving on , the food ! My partner had a prawn cocktail that was served in a martini glass , lots of lettuce with a very skimpy amount of prawns on top , I had the haggis which was fine .", "He then had pork which he said was nice and the beef I had was also nice , a yorkshire,luke warm roast potatoes and the veg , really boisdales ? Who do you have in your kitchens , a very small dish of wafer thin sliced carrots and a spoonful each of kale and that was the roast .", "Desserts then even became more laughable , my partner ordered the baked elderflower cream with strawberry and then was told they didn't have it . We was in at the first sitting and it wasn't busy so not sure why they didn't have it . He then asked if they had sorbet which wasn't on the menu , they said yes and went to check flavours , he was told the flavours and chose the lemon . They then can back and said the chef was crazy and no they didn't have the lemon they told him they had so he chose strawberry . They then came out with two strawberry and another scoop of something else mixed ! Then had to take it back and bring one strawberry only ! Phew ! What a palaver ! I ordered the cheese board , I got a few cheeses and on another board the crackers , with ....", "Sliced pear and a dish of honey ?? ", "I asked if this was a poor mans quince ? Laughable really ! ", "Would I go back ...... No ", "I could of gone up the road from my house to a nice gastro pub and actually had a nice roast dinner . ", "Very poor food and awful experience ."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r430149982", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Okay, not as good as experience", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "20 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello mgdfit,", "Thank you for providing me with feedback of your recent visit. You have raised some points here that I would like you to rest assured I have dealt with - particularly when it comes to the service side of things. ", "I do hope that you will visit again as I am confident that the negatives you mentioned have been addressed and rectified, it would be nice for you to see this. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "mgdfit", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "99"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "56"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r430149982-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Nice decor, good choice of wines. Okay service, the waitress was a bit hyper and I didn't like that she didn't listen to me and instead proceeded to advise my boyfriend on wines I didn't want and obviously we wouldn't get. Nicely cooked steak but sweet potatoe chips and spinach were born tasteless. Tasty gluten free bread, but my boyfriend got his bread served with no butter and the butter arrived for both of us later with my gluten free bread. Nice place but overpriced for what it is and staff needs better training."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r430425641", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Surprisingly good food", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "21 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello Peter H,", "It was with great pleasure that I read your recent feedback - thank you! ", "The chef was over the moon with your comments about the dishes you enjoyed. Don't wait too long until you pay us another visit!", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "peterhC3689ZV", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "100"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r430425641-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This was our first visit and it didn't disappoint. Haggis to start was full of flavour. The burger to follow was succulent and nicely garnished. The mushroom side was one of the best I've had for a long time. And the Scottish rarebit was excellent value. Service good. Went there before the live music - worth it for the food. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r430194087", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Business Lunch ", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "21 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Good evening B D,", "I was disappointed to read your recent review however feedback is very important as it allows us to recognize our short comings and rectify any negatives. ", "These are certainly not our usual Boisdale standards that you experienced. ", "With this in mind please contact me on gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk so I can discuss this in more depth with you. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "bd863", "reviewer_origin": ["Leatherhead, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r430194087-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Whilst the food was good the service was lukewarm and the atmosphere was also cold. ", "The icing on the cake was when the waiter brought us the bill when we hadn't called for it, to suggest that we might like to finish at the table! Then about a dozen staff came out of the kitchen carrying their own meals and went and sat down in the reception area to eat!! Basically they give you the impression that you are an inconvenience to their afternoon. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r431383484", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Date nite", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "25 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi Nicky,", "To hear that we proved to be a suitable date night destination is fantastic (I know how important these nights are). Thank you for letting us know about your experience. ", "Don's wait too long before your next date night - we will be waiting! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Nicky M H", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r431383484-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This was a great find. My husband and I were out for date nite and wasn't sure where we wanted to go. With the help of trip advisor we stumbled upon this amazing restaurant. The lovely lady that greeted us on arrival explained that there would be a \u00a35pp cover charge as the evening entertainment had only just started. Our table was great overlooking the fountain outside. The restaurant staff were great taking our order and making good recommendations to us. All the food served was stunning. This is s great place for romantic dinners and good ambiance, it is a pricey place but worth it. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r431256686", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Friday night lobster treat", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "24 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi Riki747,", "I am glad to hear that you took advantage of our recent Lobster offer and enjoyed to kick start your weekend. ", "I am sorry to hear you felt the service dropped off towards the end of your visit, this is not something that you have to worry about upon your return. ", "We look forward to seeing you again soon,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Riki747", "reviewer_origin": ["Wilmslow, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "252"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "176"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r431256686-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I was passing through Canary Wharf shopping centre and was given a leaflet for a Whole Lobster 1LB for \u00a320 so thought why not, it is Friday so that's fish night anyway....", "Made my way to the restaurant and as it was only 6pm there was no problem getting a table and as a consequence service was quick and efficient.", "The lobster tuned up after a short wait -it was enjoyable and washed down with some suitable wine by which time the place had started to fill up and the service was slow after that. Not sure if they are short staffed? That's not to say it was bad, just noticeably slower than when I arrived....", "All in all an enjoyable meal, I would return, maybe at the earlier time just in case the service suffers later on as I had experienced."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r431273289", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing night! 5*", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "24 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Good evening Tasha, ", "Wow! We couldn't really ask for a better review than that, 5*s. Thank you so much for taking the time to share your experience.", "We have lots of fantastic musicians coming up over the course of the next few months, you should join us again if any of them are up your street. ", "Kind regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Natasha E", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r431273289-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I had an absolutely amazing time! Let's start with the great live music (Bob Marley tribute band) the band has me rocking all night.", "Food was scrumptious! I enjoyed a lovely fresh seafood platter with mussels, shrimp and oysters.", "Followed by a mouth watering Scottish salmon.", "I then could not resist going to the cigar library to enjoy a Cuban cigar to close the night."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r432043927", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "great value set menu", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "27 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello joanie_x,", "I would have to agree, the set menu we have is fantastic value and I am glad that you decided to take advantage of it.", "Please accept my sincere apologies for the confusion with regards to the dishes that were/were not available - I will ensure that this is something we pay extra attention to in future. I am glad that it did not impact your night too negatively. ", "Kind regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "skyeclayton", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "186"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "106"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r432043927-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["great value set menu for dinner. on the day we visited, the soup and one of the mains on the set menu were not available. They didn't tell us that the soup we ordered was unavailable until after an alternative was served and consumed but it was probably just a slight oversight. otherwise, service was good. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r432458565", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Nice but expensive", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "28 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello Wim V, ", "Thank you for your recent review. I am glad to hear that you enjoyed the flavours of the food and sorry to hear that you felt the price point unjustified. We do source all of our produce from high quality suppliers.", "I hope we have the opportunity to welcome you back again soon to enjoy both the atmosphere and music again! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "WimV1941", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r432458565-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I had the iron flat steak with broccoli and an ice Cream as dessert. The food was really tastefull but not mutch! It was rather expensive (+-50\u00a3) for what you'll get. The atmosphere was fantastic though with live music and candle light. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r432785325", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Seriously underwhelming", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "29 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Good evening Stylin2308,", "Needless to say you have raised some seriously concerning points in your review that I would be extremely keen to discuss with you in more detail. ", "Please contact me directly on gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk and I can give you my number so I can better understand what went wrong here. Obviously, from your previous reviews, you did not experience what our usual standards of both quality and service are. ", "I hope to hear from you soon,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Adrien P", "reviewer_origin": ["Chertsey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "96"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "52"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r432785325-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["As you will see from previous reviews, I have been to Boisdale on a number of occasions (for business and pleasure)! It used to be my favourite restaurant in London! sadly today, for my wife's birthday- it was below par!! ", "My waitress was far to busy focusing on a High roller table to worry about the plebs at my table!!", "Food was below average, the menu had changed & no more cheese trolley!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r426009996", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Cigar heaven.... Jazz heaven", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "8 October 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LittlePrincessJack", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "21"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r426009996-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I come to this place simply so i can smoke outside in the cigar area with my dear friends. It's warm with heaters and Philippe will give you blankets and he is always attentive to his customers. He knows his cigars! The food has always been good. Only downside if you are drinking at the bar the service is a little slow for my liking. Table service is much better. To top it off you get to listen to some great music and it sets the mood of a classy ambience. I will keep going back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r428359685", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Overpriced - mediochre", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "16 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello Tim R,", "Thank you for taking the time to give us your feedback - we really do value this information. ", "I am sorry to hear that your dining experience did not live up to expectation. Please rest assured I have discussed the points you have raised with our chef and will keep a close eye on our seasoning moving forward. ", "Should you wish to give us another go I am confident that we will be able to showcase our usual standard of quality. ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Tim R", "reviewer_origin": ["Luxembourg City, Luxembourg"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "74"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r428359685-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went on a Friday eve, in the bar/grill. Ordered from set menu, Gravalax, Fillet steak. The steak arrived cooked ok but over seasoned m, so much salt and pepper couldn't taste meat. Sent back next one came , but a little dry."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r428466919", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "I don't like Mondays", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "16 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello KMgibbs,", "I am glad to hear that you managed to take advantage of one of our offers, it is a real shame to hear that you joined us on an evening where the levels of business had a negative impact on the atmosphere as when we are busy there is a fantastic buzz both upstairs in the restaurant and downstairs in the bar area.", "I have shared your feedback re; food with the chef and I will ensure that we monitor the cooking of the chips going forward. ", "I would love for you to give us a chance as a leisure destination as well as business as we showcase some magnificent musicians upstairs in the restaurant. You can find out who is playing on our website. If there is an act that you fancy and we have availability I would be happy to book this for you. ", "gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk is where you can reach me, should you wish to take me up on this.", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "KMgibbs", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "97"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "78"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r428466919-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I visited on an early evening for a short business meeting. I had booked via a table booking app and therefore got a meal deal at \u00a317.95 per head, including a glass of fizz. This was a great price and looked a good deal.", "The negatives were really down to it being really quite. It is a barn of a place with tables on two floors. We went to the wrong one and then had to insist they checked when referred back to where we had just came from. The lack of dinners, meant that the atmosphere was a bit thin. The last thing that I think was poor, was that my chips weren't cooked! How can you mess that up! ", "The positives were the staff, who were friendly and attentive. The starters were excellent. I had Haggis, beautiful. Finally, the steaks were small but of very high quality. They cook to English standards, so my medium was really well done, but my guest who wanted well done, had it well over in my view but, he was really happy with his, so I guess they cook to that standard. ", "Overall, it was ok. I will be back for a business stop off but not a leisure venue on a week night. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r426196533", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Birthday Sunday roast", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "8 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Thank you for taking the time to post a review from your Sunday lunch experience at Boisdale of Canary Wharf. I was very sad to read that the food did not meet your expectations. If possible please can you contact me at your earliest convenience so that I might get a better understanding of where we went wrong. You can reach me either via my email gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk alternatively you can call on 202 7715 5818.", "I look forward to hearing from you in due course.", "Kind regards", "James Hardesty"], "reviewer_pseudo": "13mayc", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "37"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r426196533-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My friend booked the restaurant for her birthday. It was a special offer 3 course sunday roast. The starters were good, the the main was very dissappointing. Half the pork was still pink. The roast pototoes were rock hard and difficult to cut or chew. The dessert was good, but i don't think i will come back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r428370609", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Robin andrew", "diner_date": " September 2016", "rating_date": "16 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello Robin, ", "Firstly I would like to thank you for taking the time to provide us with your feedback. Secondly I would like to apologize that obviously our usual standards of service and quality were seriously lacking on your visit. ", "I would like the opportunity to discuss this with you in more detail, if you would be so kind. ", "Please drop me an e-mail on gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk", "I look forward to hearing from you,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Robin J", "reviewer_origin": ["Biggin Hill, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "33"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r428370609-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very poor, disappointed , no attention to detail as the restraunt standards are very disappointing , it needs a revamp in the cold light of day, food cold over priced, service was exceptable, but severs have their work cut out as they have little or no support, the senior manager needs to improve his standards "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r430141220", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great music and great food! ", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "20 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi markandandrew,", "This is a lovely review to read and I am so happy to hear that you enjoyed your evening with us. ", "To hear that you will be coming is music to my ears and we look forward to welcoming you upon your return! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Andrew P", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r430141220-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Travelzoo voucher visit so expensive once you add wine however food despite thee supplements was great. Wine excellent and entertainment fabulous. What a great setting too! We'll be back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r428664936", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Seafood and Steak!!!! :D", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "17 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hi Zuben, ", "It is always a real pleasure to get such positive feedback so thank you for taking the time to let us know about your recent visit. ", "Fantastic to hear that we will be seeing you again soon!", "Until then, take care.", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Zuben M", "reviewer_origin": ["Manchester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r428664936-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Checked this place out on the weekend ... have to say the food was great but the service really made our night. Big thank you to Mary for helping us out, your suggestions hit the nail on the head! Will be back for sure!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r428929835", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic restaurant with a relaxed Scottish vibe", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "17 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Good afternoon,", "It was with great pleasure that I read your review of your recent visit to Boisdale Canary Wharf. Thank you for sharing. ", "To hear that we ticked all of the boxes from food to service, drinks and atmosphere is absolutely great. We work very hard to provide exactly the experience you described and to hear you would come back again is the icing on the cake. We look forward to seeing you then! ", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "louise E", "reviewer_origin": ["Cumbria, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r428929835-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Thoroughly enjoyed our visit. Oysters were amazingly fresh, delicious haggis with tatties and neeps for starter, for main tender pink grouse with bread sauce, redcurrant jelly, grouse crisps and wild field mushrooms- unbelievable. Wrapped up with a dark chocolate fondant cooked perfectly :) a bottle of two of champagne then into the cigar lounge to enjoy an espresso martini or 3 while the other half enjoyed a cohiba - perfect evening. Staff were great, live music gave a good relaxed atmosphere too. Would go again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r429797810", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good and not so good", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "19 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello teslart,", "Thank you for providing your feedback of your recent visit. You have raised some concerning points that I would like the opportunity to discuss with you in more depth. ", "Please contact me on gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk to do so. ", "I hope to hear from you soon,", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "teslart", "reviewer_origin": ["Gothenburg, Sweden"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r429797810-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very mixed feelings here - this is very much a chain restaurants that aims pretty high and falls short of its ambitions.", "The food is definitely tasty but there's always something to dampen the enthusiasm - I had a venison carpaccio as a starter: tasted great but was on the small side, and the decoration was downright uninspired - some lettuce leaves and stripes of average parmesan. Mains was the fillet steak - excellent flavours, served as ordered (rare) but rather stringy and definitely on the smaller end of the 10-12oz range at best. Finished with a cheese platter, for which I was not \"happily\" shown the tray by \"dedicated staff\" but was rather presented with a rather boring and conservative choice. The fresh pear turned out to be just two super thin slices.", "Service had difficulties getting their act together with food turning up before the wine for both the starter and the cheese (for whom the accompaniments also took a significant time to turn up). Can't blame the staff for this since they are clearly competent but overloaded - never seen waiters just constantly on the verge of actually running through the restaurant to keep up. This also ruins the cosiness of the place. Perhaps things are nicer on a quiet night.", "Overall, the food stands out for flavour of the main component (except the cheese I ended up with), but in every other respect, there is a lot of room for improvement. Worth the money? If you're dead set on staying in the neighbourhood, it's a tough call - in any other case, you can do better."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r428789663", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Brilliant experience ", "diner_date": " October 2016", "rating_date": "17 October 2016", "answer_text": ["Hello Dionne, ", "To read feedback like this makes all of the hard work really worthwhile. Thank you for sharing it with us. ", "Hopefully we will be welcoming you back soon, you should join us for dinner as there is fantastic atmosphere in the restaurant with live music.", "Kind Regards,", "Jenny Hughes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "dionnep1208", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r428789663-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Loved the Sunday roast! Food was just lovely, brilliant service and cracking wine list. Would definitely recommend to anyone looking for a restaurant in Canary Wharf and surrounding areas! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r425544509", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Tres chique Tres Expensive", "diner_date": " September 2016", "rating_date": "6 October 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "patrick b", "reviewer_origin": ["The Hague, The Netherlands"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "269"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "62"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r425544509-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went here for lunch with the team, set menu as we with quite a big party but nice options and variety across the courses. The decor isn't my style as it does scream class & old world money all over. At any rate the food was good, the service certainly not as bad as some other reviews suggest yet the bill was probably a bit over what would have been justified by the overall package."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r418240987", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Just great", "diner_date": " September 2016", "rating_date": "13 September 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "skip2564", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "107"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "44"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r418240987-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I love this place. Its all about great food, music and just enjoying yourself.", "We went recently for a Motown music evening. The live music was fantastic with the only issue the dance floor being slightly too small. This is one of the best restaurants for steaks. Remember to avoid adding too many extras. Ribeye, fries and mustard or Horseradish is all that is required.", "There are hundreds of whisky and an excellent wine selection.", "You can take a break from the music and sit out on one of the balconies with a drink and cigar.", "Big thanks to James, Glen and all staff for making this a great evening, as usual"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r418635028", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "What a miserable experience", "diner_date": " September 2016", "rating_date": "14 September 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "craigsj75", "reviewer_origin": ["Chorleywood, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r418635028-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This place touts itself as a steal restaurant in Canary Wharf and has one steal on the the menu - Flat Iron so I was forced to eat a burger and I don't eat burgers. We asked for thick cut chips/fries and they only arrived after a 3rd request once we were half way through our meal. The 2015 Cab/Merlot we got, advertised as 2013 on the menu, smelled and tasted corked even though it wasn't and the Irish Coffee was luke warm. The service was what you would expect in a busy coffee shop in Oxford street and for this they charged us a poultry \u00a395!!! We would have been better off braving the Jubilee line into the City at 35 degrees! They couldn't have done much worse! Avoid this place like the plague!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r419041532", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Sunday lunch", "diner_date": " September 2016", "rating_date": "16 September 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "RCML", "reviewer_origin": ["Pinner, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "82"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r419041532-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Took me a while to decide what to say about Boisdale. I think our problem was that we arrived late on Sunday only about 15 mins before last orders for lunch. However if they take your order they should deliver their best. I ordered the beef and my wife the cod, well the beef was not the greatest, the roast potatoes a bit solid not the best roast. My wife's cod came with mussels which were not on the menu and my wife cannot eat shell fish. They were going to remove them but they were part of the sauce and as that was the last cod she had to settle for the risotto which she did enjoy. The service was good and the staff were friendly and efficient, we may go back again but earlier and book next time."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r424689500", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Over rated, Over Priced, Poor service.", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "3 October 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Donesomemiles", "reviewer_origin": ["Chester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "82"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "67"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r424689500-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Sadly took some customers to this recommended restaurant, the service was so poor it it has become a standing joke with my customers, we booked for a table 7.15-7.30 pm actually got food 9.37 pm, and when it actually arrived, it was at best average.", "I was so embarrassed, we would have gone somewhere else but we where intrigued to find something good about this place, and it was poring down!, but sadly the only good thing was the music."]}
