{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r406483089", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "great venue, great service, poor food", "diner_date": " August 2016", "rating_date": "17 August 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "david j", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "66"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r406483089-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We have visited Canary Wharf Boisdale several times but not of late, there are three reasons to visit a dinner and dance venue, these are great atmosphere, great service and great food 2 out of three is not good enough, why, i will tell you:", "On arrival we were greeted and shown to the lower bar a great area for pre drinks i love the place! onward to our table some 60 mins later, after a few cold ones. Our service was excellent the atmosphere was superb, then came the most horrific excuse for food. I started with a sweaty Carpaccio of Venison, it was straight from a packet placed on a plate and served, it was dressed well on the menu but the execution lacked skill and imagination, appalling, then came the Chef Salad for my main meal, the menu stated it changed daily,wow, it needs changing immediately, soggy rocket leaves covered in oil with lentils and pine nuts can not be saved with a mere shaving of dry truffle powder.", "Canary Wharf is a vibrant gastronomic powder house with restaurants surrounding Boisdale, Toms Kitchen, Plateau, Roka, One Canada Square, The Parlour and Hazev. I understand you cannot dance in these 6 restaurants but my advice, eat elsewhere, then enjoy a drink and dance at Boisdale at least until the chef is able to look after large events? ", "My rating below is based on an overall package 2 out of 3 sections very good the other not worth turning up for.", "If you disagree let me know"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r396265411", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "In a world of sameness, Boisdale has personality and good food", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "24 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ObjectiveGp", "reviewer_origin": ["New York"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r396265411-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Time I commented about the Boisdale in Canary Wharf, since different is often god, and this is GOOD. Chains are so . . . damn boring, and although there are now three Boisdale's in London, give them a go, music, food, understanding and patient staff, and a lot of fun.", "Great wine, food, including the steak, that is generally excellent, well thought out interesting.", "Go for the music - damn fine!", "Go for the food - brilliant!", "Go because its a great place to meet and have fun with friends, perfect!", "Really, give it a go, and be happy that there are still places that are not just over-designed factories."]}
