{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r413586091", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A place to come back to again", "diner_date": " August 2016", "rating_date": "1 September 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Rosanna W", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r413586091-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went on a Thursday night for my birthday, and it was quiet which was great.", "The service and food was outstanding! There was a slight mishap, but it was forgotten.", "Atmosphere was amazing also.", "There is only 1 tiny bit of constructive criticism - I found majority of the waiting staff was rushing around like flies - I don't know whether this was due to having a private big table, but at times I felt on edge when they came round to top up the wine or take plates away."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r415120041", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "So good we went back a week later!", "diner_date": " August 2016", "rating_date": "5 September 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Rastnim", "reviewer_origin": ["Singapore, Singapore"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "162"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "158"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r415120041-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A friend bought us a Groupon deal at Boisdale as a thank you for 2 Wagyu Beef Burgers and a prosecco. As I am a veggie, I called ahead and asked if I could have an alternative and asked if I could have the mushroom and black truffle risotto, which they allowed. We were seated on the balcony that looks our over a leafy square in Canary Wharf on a lovely warm day - it was excellent! I enjoyed my risotto, it was very flavoursome, and my boyfriend said his burger had been good but not exceptional. He did have the truffle fries though and I stole a couple, they were divine!! We had a cheeseboard additional to the deal to finish and that was amazing, it is bespoke so you can choose 6 or 10 cheeses from a selection of hard, soft, blue and smelly! ", "We enjoyed the meal so much that the next week when we had cause for celebration when I got a new job we immediately decided on going back to Boisdale. This time we could choose more freely and had a few of the tapas sides. I had the truffle and mushroom rarebit which was really yummy and we shared a variety of the small plates and a plank with cheeses and cured meats (for him of course!). We were very impressed once again, and have said should either of our parents come visit we would definitely take them back there!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r403699495", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "IN LONDON - THEN THIS IS AN ABSOLUTE MUST", "diner_date": " August 2016", "rating_date": "10 August 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Verna K", "reviewer_origin": ["Wellingborough, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "85"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "38"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r403699495-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Been here umpteen times since November 2015 and can't praise it enough.", "We own Vista - a stretch limousine and events company in Wellingborough, Northamptonshire and regularly recommend and take our clients to Boisdales of Canary Wharf (and Belgravia.) ", "Great venue for Stag or Hen party, or those clients looking for a first class night out in London with fantastic music (great cross section), dancing, fine dining and great atmosphere. ", "Well run and managed, great and helpful staff who work together as a fab team, excellent customer service. ", "Ambience second to none, food is 5 star +, check out their amazing whisky selection. Prices extremely reasonable for London and great value. Menu superb and something for all tastes.", "Boisdales ..... what's not to like. Try it once .. guarantee you will want to return. So do yourself and your friends and family a huge favour ... go check it out."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r399295822", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wonderful experience", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "30 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "travelbb2010", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r399295822-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for an after work dinner. Firstly we had cocktails at the bar which were superbly made and then onto the terrace for dinner. We opted for the set menu and had the whitebait and steak. Perfection. The waiting staff, cigar expert and bar tender were superb. Boisdales Canary Wharf is a hidden gem and an example of to how to provide a wonderful bar and dinner experience. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r402889138", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "So disappointed", "diner_date": " August 2016", "rating_date": "8 August 2016", "answer_text": ["Dear Kate", "Thank you for taking the time to respond to your experience at Boisdale Canary wharf on Trip adviser. I was disappointed to read your comments in light of the email that I sent to you detailing the information relating to our music listings. Please see below.", "\"I understand that you dined with us through the Group on forum, that will indicate only that you had a dinner and show package, and does not communicate the specific act. All our music acts are listed on our website which includes video footage of each act, so that our guests can get an appreciation of the music that will be performing on each night.\"", "This clearly states that there is no \"small print\" and that our website provides substantial details of each act, so that our guests can make an informed decision as to which show they would like to attend. The act in question was Cream, which has a very specific guitar based blues sound, and was generally well received by our audience. ", "All of our guests who purchase tickets via the Groupon forum have a choice as to which show they would like to attend, and we will make every effort to provide the best experience for dining as well as a memorable music show. ", "On the Groupon website we are referred to as a Jazz and Blues venue, although it does go on to detail that we have tribute acts such as David Bowie and Queen, which is an indication of the variety of shows that we host at the restaurant.", "You clearly stated in your email to me that you enjoyed your meal and the service very much, and that the show was not to your liking. I am sorry that the music was not to your taste, although we believe that a variety of acts is essential to ensure we have a broad and consistent appeal to all.", "Please do not hesitate on contacting me in the future should you require any information relating to future acts. ", "Kind regards", "James Hardesty"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Tallulah21", "reviewer_origin": ["Upminster Essex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "25"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r402889138-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited with a groupon voucher and had never visited the restaurant before. The food was lovely and we looked forward to the evening of jazz and blues that was described on the groupon and Boisdale website. What a shocker the music was loud rock, so loud we couldn't hear ourselves speak and not the sort of music any of us would have chosen to listen to. ", "The manageress agreed it was dreadful and we left our table and took our drinks to the bar downstairs. ", "I emailed Boisdale to say how disappointed we had been but they responded saying that although they advertise as a jazz and blues restaurant they have a more eclectic mix on a Saturday. ", "No apology just suggested we might have looked into the very small print on their website. ", "Customer service sadly lacking. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r400427743", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Brilliant night, with delicious food and great music", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "2 August 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "GBH63", "reviewer_origin": ["Wokingham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "121"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "59"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r400427743-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Fabulous night from start to finish. Professional, friendly, experienced staff, with great service , delicious food and an amazing band.", "We danced the night away once we had finished dinner, which was outstanding and we drank a variety of cocktails. This is a must visit place if you are after a special day or night out, we loved the whole experience and we will be back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r401396934", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Professional and prompt ", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "4 August 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "T8949OPandyg", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r401396934-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Really refreshing lunch with few glasses of champagne and bellinis for the girls as well as single malt for the boys.", "Crystal clean glassware and proper serving temperature.", "A little confusion with timing with one of the dishes but hey good attitude works miracles.", "Very good Rib-eyes cooked as requested med-rare with all the trimmings.", "Very good crowd and fine ambience, very friendly stuff and interesting decor.", "I like the place."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r403838675", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food, Great music in one lovely venue.", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "10 August 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "FRIENDLYDINER", "reviewer_origin": ["MANCHESTER"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r403838675-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked a meal and an evening of great Jazz music through Groupon at a discounted price. The evening was fantastic from the minute we walked in the service was first class as well as the table near the stage, the food and the singer performing. Would highly recommend this venue to couples especially as it's a great place if you want a romantic venue with lovely food and great music."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r404217022", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fun evening", "diner_date": " August 2016", "rating_date": "11 August 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Annette H", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "63"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r404217022-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great location. One tube journey from Waterloo then off at Canary Wharf through the luxury shops directly into Boisdales. Could see the shard and the gherkin from our table as the sunset. Boisdales has a loose Scottish theme and a very pricey menu. Definately overpriced for what it was. Service a bit sporadic over the top at one point and then disappeared the next. Over \u00a3400.00 for 6 with no starters or deserts although we did have a few bottles of wine. However we really came for the entertainment which on this particular night was a sort of Vegas themed . Could do with making the dance floor a bit bigger as everyone wanted to dance even the staff were getting into the spirit. Would have been nice to have 2 halves as it all seemed to be over quite quickly but great fun."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r396123066", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Lovely food and wonderful music", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "24 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "siannyr87", "reviewer_origin": ["Porthcawl, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r396123066-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited here last night for dinner and a show. First time visiting and will definitely come again. We enjoyed 2 courses and 1 dessert between us. Mostly couples but a few groups too. The staff were all friendly and helpful. Great evening. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r392981951", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best Place In Canary Wife", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "15 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MissMonique2000zw", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r392981951-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Amazing food , beautiful atmosphere, top notch service and if you are a jazz lover then this is the place to be. Hidden away on the 2nd floor it makes it exclusive and a brilliant dining."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r392037894", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Soul night with Zalon", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "13 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SOHOTRAVELLER1", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "89"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "53"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r392037894-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A group of 6 of us went down to see Zalons Soul Show! What a great night music and performance was amazing with lots of people dancing all night and great customer interaction from Zalon who is an amazing singer! ", "We started the night with drinks on the beautiful terrace on the 1st floor overlooking the square. Great friendly service too.", "We then went up to the restaurant on the 2nd floor for dinner. We had a great table with a good view of the stage. We were greeted by a very friendly host chap who showed us to the table.", "Starters were spot on ( mini haggis, scallops, smoked salmon and a crab) crab was very disappointing sliver with mostly unnecessary garnish. Mains were great, lobster, steak, calves liver, and fish. All tasted great and had a few extra side dishes (rather small).", "We had some lovely wine (well priced). Didn't have room for puddings. We then danced the night away until way past 11.30 to great sounds of soul!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r392762871", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Opulent bar experience.", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "15 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "TheOExpress", "reviewer_origin": ["Hong Kong, China"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1917"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1428"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r392762871-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I don't even like whisky and only (begrudgingly) smoke cigars at weddings but this bar is something else. The selection of different whiskies downstairs is impressive but upstairs it's breathtaking, covering a huge wall behind the bar. And if expensive cigars are your thing, the smoking room looked like a great spot to spend a lot. We were only drinking beer, like peasants, but it wasn't as expensive as I'd expected: north of \u00a35 a pint is standard round there anywhere you go. The legions of staff were very friendly and they have a smoking balcony with a decent view as well, with blankets for when it gets chilly. I full intend to return soon and fully live out a Gordon Gecko-style evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r391093162", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good place for small groups", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "10 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Birchy74", "reviewer_origin": ["West Byfleet, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "24"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r391093162-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Good place for small groups to meet in the week, large groups can get a bit difficult as large crowds at the end of a week. Great menu, good food, excellent wine list and cigar lounge. Jazz and full menu upstairs but for most of us the terrace downstairs is great. Members terrace good value for a quiet place to catch up. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r393470320", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Probably one of the best beefburgers I've tasted!", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "17 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Bryan W", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "173"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "68"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r393470320-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were here with a Groupon voucher which made it decidely cheaper as it included a glass of pro seco. We added on a small haggis to share for our starter - it was good and quite enough for the two of us. Then the beefburger! The bun it is in is way above what I have experienced in other restaurants. The beef is wagyu and the taste is splendid. A couple of lettuce leaves on the base and on top of the burger some mushrooms and a large fried egg, cooked to perfection i.e. white well set and the yolk very liquid. The chips were good. Interestingly they charge \u00a31.50 for mayonnaise but it is homemade with a touch of mustard in it - added a nice flavour to the chips. My companion is Italian and felt the pro seco was of a good quality. The decor is outstanding - lots of tartan around. Live music too, later in the evening - we had a few minutes of a taster as the musicians did a 10 or so minute rehearsal. Then canned music - much of it from the 1930's and 40's - so enjoyed it. We will certainly be returning here to taste other items on their menu. Note that the restaurant does not open for lunch on a Saturday."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r393668562", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Terrific Travel zoo deal ", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "17 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "christine l", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "310"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "123"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r393668562-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked this offer for two courses and show for something a bit different. On arrival seated at a perfect table at the front. Menu was great really unusual to be honest I hadn't realised it was a Scottish restaurant which went down well with my Scottish husband. Haggis for starters was apparently delicious. I had goat cheese salad also lovely. Onto the main poached salmon and lamb chops both amazing. Food was really excellent we paid extra for the cheese board a selection of 5 British cheeses WOW. service food and entertainment were superb special mention to our waitress Rody. Would highly recommend and will return "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r394386680", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantatic Sunday Roast", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "19 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Robert M", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "471"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "139"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r394386680-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["If you enjoy good Scottish Roast Beef The Boisdale is the place for you. Excellent service with wine included , live jazz music to boot you cannot go wrong "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r394942084", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Food was very good", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "21 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "teemay2016", "reviewer_origin": ["Coventry, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r394942084-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to this restaurant on a voucher deal, on arrival staff were welcoming and we were shown to our seat.it took a while before we placed our order as our waitress seemed distant and distracted as if her mind wasn't on the job! However the food was excellent and the live music was top standard."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r388142844", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Heavy evening", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "1 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SJZone", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r388142844-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["If you want like hearty British food, whiskey and low lighting with a sprinkle of jazz music this place is for you. The food is good and plentiful, you won't come away hungry. Staff are friendly and pricing reasonable, but the whole thing doesn't blow me away and makes for a very heavy evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r391062272", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great celebratory evening with excellent band", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "10 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "DiPont", "reviewer_origin": ["Canterbury, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "27"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r391062272-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were treated by friends to an evening at Boisdale as part of special birthday celebrations and could not fault it. As we walked thought the entrance I was concerned as to where we were going but as soon as we walked through the door to club was really impressed by the interior which is beautiful with rows upon rows of whisky bottles in a grand display cabinet make a great backdrop. Not only did we all enjoy our meal which included amongst other dishes Haggis, Chilli Squid and Steak, but the band that were on that evening were fantastic. It is not often that everyone in our group of 50 somethings rush to the dance floor. It was made particularly memorable by the fabulous waiter who was attentive but discreet. I wish I had made a note of his name."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r394547197", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Ok", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "20 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Chris_Rob8rts", "reviewer_origin": ["UK"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r394547197-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A colleague booked. It wasn't on my list. ", "Pleasantly surprised by the food - good steak, and a lovely Chianti, but for a business dinner, the others were commenting on the decor which just feels a bit like an strange Scottish nightclub in places. ", "And half empty where other places booked out which given the size of the place left you with a feeling that you got a table there easily for a reason. ", "Hosting customers and the last feeling you want is a slightly apologetic one. ", "Staff were lovely but it's the ambiance... "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r388490999", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Boisdale -Canary Wharf, Eat at home first!", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "2 July 2016", "answer_text": ["Dear Celia,", "Thank you for taking the time to write some valuable feedback regarding your visit to Boisdale Canary Wharf. I was very disappointed to read that the experience did not match your expectations. Please can you contact me at your earliest convenience so that I can discuss the issues you encountered in more depth. You can either contact me via email gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk or on 020 7715 5818. I look forward to hearing from you in due course.", "Kind regards", "James Hardesty"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Celia918", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r388490999-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I've been wanting to visit this place for a long time, but it was to my disappointment. We were sat quite a distance from the live band plying that night, but we asked to be moved closer, the manager told us it was a VIP area costing an addional \u00a345 just to sit there, Yikes. ", "The food was not top notch as I expected, the starters had 2 slivers of ery bitter cougettes and about 4 bits of cheese, it was bad so complained. The manager said we got into this club using a voucher but after my challenge of suc a strange comment fro him, he couldnt explain why a voucher had anthing to do with the quality food since all diners were eating the same foods. He did offer another starter but the first was enough to put me right off.", "The service was excellent, very prompt and polite, and decor was really nicely done, but the fact that we not even allowed to around the bar, which could easily have had 20 plus more, i find it too contolling for a good night out.And thank the good ", "Lord i didnt pay full price for the bits i got.tears at bedtime comes to mind. Sort it Boisdale"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r388951553", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Zalon! ", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "4 July 2016", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your valuable feedback on your visit to Boisdale Canary Wharf. I would like to discuss in more detail some of the issues that you raised. Please contact me at your earliest convenience either via email gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk or on 020 7715 5818.", "Kind regards", "James Hardesty"], "reviewer_pseudo": "saintlysinner", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1932"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2116"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r388951553-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Show ", "My friends and I were here to see Zalon who used to be a backing singer for Amy Winehouse. I'll start my review with the positives. The show was absolutely fantastic, zalon and his band were great and had most people on the dance floor wanting more. So definitely worth going there for the show. ", "Food ", "We paid \u00a345 each for a two course set meal and tickets to the show, the only reason we opted for this was because we wanted to be seated. What a mistake! First of all we were seated so far from the stage so we had to get up anyway! I was annoyed when I looked at the menu, most of the items on eBay set menu had supplements, so you ended up having to pay at least \u00a310 extra per person excluding service and drinks. This would have been fine if the food was good! I had the scallops ceviche my friend had the squid and her husband had the salmon... All extremely average. For mains my friend and I had the burger and her husband had the steak. I asked for my burger to be medium rare and it came completely charred! Sent it back and got another one which was medium well. But I couldn't be bothered to send this back as everyone else was finishing their meal. The food is nothing to write home about and for those prices I rather go elsewhere. ", "Service ", "The service is really hit and miss, the staff here seem like they think that they are too good to be working in this place. Some of them were bordering on rude! Even when we asked for bread it was just plonked on the table! ", "Overall. ", "In my humble opinion I would suggest that this place is good for a drink and show, the venue is lovely. But save yourself the money and eat elsewhere. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r388996584", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Enjoyable Canary Wharf Restaurant but watch show ticket price", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "4 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Y7028XFstevenm", "reviewer_origin": ["Leicester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "38"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r388996584-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Friendly service, nice Scottish menu, food was very good, great choice of whiskies and all in all a very pleasant meal. We took in the show, normally jazz but on this occasion an excellent Elvis impersonator. Only complaint - when you buy the ticket for the show it suggests there is a table d'hote meal included yet we only got the a la carte menu and there was no allowance made on the bill. This needs to be much clearer on the website. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r390714233", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "3 is harsh but deserved", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "9 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "RichardOldfield", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "399"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "184"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r390714233-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited when there was live jazz, \u00a330 per person for two courses (and the music), but over 50% of the menu choices had a hefty supplement of at least \u00a34-8.00 - the choices on the menu without a supplement were the choices you'd probably overlook and were just basic dishes. This applied to both starters and main courses. ", "It's a shame because the food is good (but we paid the supplement as there was nothing on the menu we fancied without a supplement), the wine list is good, and the music was very good too, as was the service. But the \u00a330 pp is not the actual price, we paid an additional c.\u00a310 each in supplements. On the one hand, perhaps we don't mind, but I believe that a higher price should be the advertised price! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r389678616", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "One of the better places in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "6 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "EmiliaS", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "145"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "82"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r389678616-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Not great value for money, but good selection of food. Decent place in Canary Wharf for dinner or lunch. Also has a terrace."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r389783618", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Yummy food but big price tag attached", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "6 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "miamara", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r389783618-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We bought a dinner and show ticket and treated us to a special night. I was a bit disappointed knowing the Victoria branch by the overall flair, it lacked a bit of soul. Food was delicious, although the set menue has many extra charged supplements ( for a burger an extra \u00a3 4,95 and so on and they charged us for the truffle mayonnaise an extra \u00a33 ! This supposed to be on the burger but we couldn t taste any. So Overall WE Ended up with a Bill of \u00a3 125! , having had a bottle of wine for \u00a325. The band was great and it felt like being back in 1959. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r390530950", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great evening - but \u00a3\u00a3's can creep up", "diner_date": " July 2016", "rating_date": "8 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "bluehat64", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "278"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "84"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r390530950-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited on a Thursday for a special occasion. Set menu and jazz. Scottish theme steak whisky etc and many staff had kilts..Mixed reviews on food.. starters excellent but steak ok..Most items seemed to be extra \u00a3 Drinks very good - great selection of cocktails especially those whisky based. Wall of whisky was impressive and loved the vibe feel with attentive service. Jazz was very good and overall a very enjoyable evening and definitely will return. Why not 5 stars ? On leaving the bill felt bit high but a great evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r390334412", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Steak & Cigars", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "8 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "JonnersB", "reviewer_origin": ["Bray-on-Thames, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "428"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "453"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r390334412-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A great bar, very decent restaurant and cigar emporium. I enjoyed oysters and steak washed down with a very palatable red. Staff were efficient and pleasant. It did shut a little early but that's Canary Wharf for you. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r388138216", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Favourite bar", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "1 July 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Carol o", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "85"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r388138216-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Excellent bar and also very good food. I have been many times both for drinks and dinner. If you can get a night when they have a band play its well worth it. Usually quite jazzy. There is a balcony off the bar which is great when the sun is shining. For whiskey lovers there is a huge selection."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r383510685", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Very good meal, warm atmosphere and great whisky selection!", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "17 June 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "GiEspoo", "reviewer_origin": ["Espoo"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "83"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r383510685-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I was at this restaurant for a business dinner and I thoroughly enjoyed it.", "I have a 2 course meal and both dishes were very good and well presented. Service was good and attentive.", "Very good selection of wines and excellent selection of whiskies.", "Highly recommended"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r386381023", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Boisdale", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "27 June 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Brian M", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "111"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "84"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r386381023-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited Boisdale Restaurant at Canary Wharf for our Anniversary which was our first time there after a recommendation from friends. I must say we were not disappointed and in honesty, we could not fault any of it at all. Not only was the food mouth watering tasty and well presented, the service was such a high standard and probably the best we have ever experienced. It was quite a pleasure to watch the staff on occasion going about their business, serving tables as well as our own almost being unnoticed at times. But as soon as you needed something, they were there and a credit to the management. Sometimes I do contest \"service charge\" when applied to our bill but not this occasion. The entertainment (Viva Santana Tribute Band) was also really good which made it a very enjoyable evening indeed. We would have absolutely no hesitation in going there again or recommending to friends and family. Just excellent."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r384810232", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Father's Day Treat", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "22 June 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MrsScottCroydon", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "21"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r384810232-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We took my dad here for lunch on Father's Day - I had heard it was good but it surpassed my expectations. We opted for the lunch without the recommended wines and it was excellent value for money, the atmosphere is warm and welcoming and the staff friendly and helpful. I had haggis scotch egg which was wonderful followed by roast pork and baked cheesecake. The wine list is reasonable and covers all tastes as you would expect. Afterwards we had coffee and whisky on open terrace which was wonderful.. My dad really enjoyed the afternoon and i would recommend Boisdales for a special occasion - good man food!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r386635416", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Jazzy Ambience, a great steak, and some fine scotch", "diner_date": " February 2016", "rating_date": "27 June 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jules M", "reviewer_origin": ["Oklahoma City, Oklahoma"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r386635416-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very enjoyable evening here in February, top notch plates served up, most excellent steak in London. Selection of scotch and whiskey is superb, practically unmatched. Don't forget the desserts. Just be sure to bring your am ex."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r385403270", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Classic", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "23 June 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "bambamm1", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r385403270-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very good meat, very good seafood and classic service! Special mention to our host, Gianluca, and the guy who brought us the food, Kevin, impressed about him, he is very attentive and assisted us when rest were busy! Whiskey menu massive!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r385726831", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Not good, not good at all", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "25 June 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Kevster100", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "148"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "180"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r385726831-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had lunch here with friends and as much as like what Boisdake is about they just don't deliver. Small portions, cold and over priced food for what is is. Service depends on who you get. We had three different waiters to who we explained the menu and constantly chased for service. If you like Boisdale I would try the Bishopsgate branch but alas we will not be going back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r386842461", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Reassuringly proper business restaurant with Jazz, Oysters & Cigars for afters", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "28 June 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Juvejon", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "46"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r386842461-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Coming out the lift up from the busy, bustling shopping mall, you find yourself in a quiet, dark, draped & boarded corridor as if in a fine, London gentleman's club leading to an tartan art-deco curved dining room. The staff were professional and attentive (though a lil' under-resourced this particular lunch). The a la carte menu is half Scottish/Italian classics and half full Grill room standards. Plumped for Air-dried Wagyu beef, asparagus & egg for a starter, then an excessive order of rose veal & aged Parmesan pappardelle with sides of bone marrow, herb crumb & horseradish and truffled seared foie gras - all absolutely delicious! No time for dessert or coffee this day but a lovely meal nonetheless"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r388127021", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Cannot see what anyone sees in this restaurant!", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "1 July 2016", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your feedback regarding your meal at Canary Wharf Boisdale. I was very disappointed to read that the experience fell short of your expectations. Please can you contact me at your earliest convenience so that may get a better understanding of the issues that you encountered. ", "You can contact me by mail gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk or on 020 7715 5818.", "I look forward to hearing from you in due course.", "Kind regards", "James"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Michelle R", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "55"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "38"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "20", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r388127021-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I have been here before for a tribute Earth Wind and Fire Band a couple of years ago - great atmosphere but very very expensive. I took a friend here for a birthday on Tuesday this week - it was an early dinner so restaurant was quiet as expected and service was very good. However, the food was dreadful. I ordered a goats cheese salad which came with one crouton and two square pieces of goats cheese! I was in total shock and thought they were joking!! I then ordered a steak and chips which was an additional \u00a38 on top - steak was lovely however the size of a small orange! aND I had about 15-20 chips. I asked for mayonaise and had to pay another \u00a31.50 for that although the tomato sauce my friend ordered was free.????? Definatley not value for money at all! The service was good however, the bill for drinks first time round for a gin and tonic and a bottle of beer was completely different then the second time. Why was the first one more expensive?? They sold doubles without even asking if I wanted doubles or singles so be careful.... Very disappointing visit and would not reconmend this place to anyone... if you go bring plenty of cash.."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r387778944", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Consistently excellent", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "30 June 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Boris X", "reviewer_origin": ["Pembroke, Malta"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "30"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r387778944-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This restaurant is the place where one can get out of his/her comfort zone - my suggestion is that one should just infer his/her preference to the waiting or bar personnel and just see what they recommend. ", "The ambiance is very nice, the food is excellent and the service second to none - definitely one of my favourite restaurants in London."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r375728765", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Jazz Night with Fine Food", "diner_date": " May 2016", "rating_date": "23 May 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "StewartK_13", "reviewer_origin": ["Aberdeen, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r375728765-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Did the fixed menu and show package and have to tell you - it was great. We were seated right up by the stage, the food was great, the music fantastic (Mississippi - spelling alert - Swamp stylee with plenty of really great musicianship), the wind most enjoyable - just a fantastic night out.", "Fixed menu had something for everyone - even our picky vegetarian daughter - and all very high quality.", "Highly highly recommended. Great waiter too but sadly can't remember his name."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r374477605", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great birthday night out", "diner_date": " May 2016", "rating_date": "19 May 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "353jand", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r374477605-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked for 5 of us with Groupon for my sons birthday. Having been to Bishopsgate we knew the food would be excellent. ", "I told the receptionists on arrival that we were celebrating a birthday, they took his name, asked if we had a cake. I said no, they then said he would arrange for a candle to put on his desert with happy birthday inscribed on the plate. Also they would mention it to the band for the to announce, They could not have been more helpful. The manager James came to introduce himself, and was delightful and helpful, shoeing us to our seats and asking who the birthday boy was. Ashley our waiter was great, really friendly and attentive, helping out with choices for Whisky. ", "We had to pay supplements on the food that was not included in the voucher price, but it was well worth it, the steaks were delicious. As was all the food we had. ", "The band were very good if not a little loud so we had to shout, but that wasn't a problem.", "The two men especially like the cigar room and disappeared for 1/2 hour! ", "Overall i would highly recommend if"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r382261007", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Loved it .....", "diner_date": " June 2016", "rating_date": "13 June 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "CatherineBeaumont4", "reviewer_origin": ["Sidcup, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r382261007-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a great night, top class cocktails, fabulous oysters, can highly recommend the haggis. Well looked after by Martin Moran and his waiting team. Can't wait to go again. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r375547436", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good evening, but...", "diner_date": " May 2016", "rating_date": "22 May 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "susanv116", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r375547436-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went with friends on a travel zoo offer, \u00a320 per person per head for two courses. The menu offered a good choice, but almost all the dishes carried a supplement of up to \u00a38! Plus extra if you wanted sides. I chose for my starter Warm Vichyssoise with pickled St Georges mushrooms, new potatoes and garlic. The soup was fairly tasty with very thin slices of potato, but I really couldn't tell if there were any mushrooms in it at all - St George's or otherwise. I told the waiter and he said he'd tell the chef to put more in next time! There was no feedback from the kitchen though. Generally the food was pleasant but nothing special and the final bill was \u00a3170 plus the \u00a380 we'd already paid. So \u00a3250 for 4 people with very little alcohol seems a bit excessive, considering it was supposed to be a promotional price. The jazz band were entertaining and got people up dancing. Staff were friendly and efficient, and we enjoyed the evening very much. It was our third visit, and we'll probably go again, but really not good value for money."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r377929878", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Birthday dinner", "diner_date": " May 2016", "rating_date": "30 May 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Kitti T", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r377929878-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My partner and I went to celebrate my birthday with the Groupont deal.Everything was perfect except one thing.Due to the fact that it was my birthday I requested a nice table because it was a special occasion for us.Unfortunately we did get a farthest table from the stage...I understand Groupon voucher is Groupon voucher but at least they could try to satisfy us.Anyway the food,the service and show was excellent.We went to try some cigar as well...worth it."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r381132026", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely food", "diner_date": " July 2015", "rating_date": "9 June 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "karolina1424", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r381132026-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had some haggis and steak, which were really filling. First we were seated outside as it was quite sunny, however later it got windy, and the staff had no problem to move us inside. We went around 12 o'clock weekday and it was not busy at all. Would come back again"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r381231566", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Very disappointing ", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "9 June 2016", "answer_text": ["Dear Rini9", "Thank you for taking time to feedback with regard to your visit to Canary Wharf Boisdale. Please can you contact me at your earliest convenience, so that I can discuss your visit, and also your previous encounter at Boisdale on the 24th May 2015. ", "You can contact me via email gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk alternatively by phone 020 7715 5818.", "Kind regards", "James Hardesty"], "reviewer_pseudo": "rini9", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "46"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r381231566-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went on a night when the band was playing so had to pay a surcharge for that (which we didn't mind as they were lovely). The staff we dealt with were unfoundedly pretentious and not great at all. The food was a real disappointment- the 'chicken' pie I ordered had one tiny piece of chicken. How was that allowed to be served for the prices that they charge. Left feeling extremely underwhelmed. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r379767330", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great stake:) ", "diner_date": " October 2015", "rating_date": "4 June 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ilonam575", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "145"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "46"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r379767330-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["If you up to a nice properly cooked food, it is a place to enjoy it:) I always take their salmon as a starter as it is melting in my mouth. In regards to main, you do need to select it yourself - I do go for stake. The quality is very high and you can also go for the blue, if you do like raw meat:) "]}
