{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r374139543", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "I am confident the rating will be better next visit", "diner_date": " May 2016", "rating_date": "18 May 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ItsJustMyOpinion", "reviewer_origin": ["Huntingdon, Cambs"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "75"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "80"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r374139543-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Jazz can range from the sublime to the ordinary and I'm sure the level has a significant impact on the quality of the experience. For our visit, it was towards the lower end with too much emphasis on praising the musicians rather than relying on creating a special musical ambience. The venue is impressive although with some touches spoiling the grandeur. The food was good and service professional. My lasting impression is how good an event could be here - and probably is on many event days."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r368924372", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely Sunday Jazz lunch", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "30 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Londongirl_8", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "48"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r368924372-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went here for Sunday Jazz lunch and it was great experience. I ordered the smoked salmon as my starter and was very happy with the taste. My main meal was the roast beef and that was also very tasty with generous proportions.", "The overall dining experience was very enjoyable. We weren't rushed and the Jazz was an added bonus.", "I definitely recommend Boisdale for a Sunday lunch treat"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r369668875", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great steak and whiskey", "diner_date": " May 2016", "rating_date": "2 May 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Richard C", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r369668875-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a great dinner with colleagues, very comprehensive list of whiskeys, knowledgable staff and great steak."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r370233974", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A classy place for whisky and cigars", "diner_date": " May 2016", "rating_date": "4 May 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "FindingJLu", "reviewer_origin": ["Durban, South Africa"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r370233974-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["If you're looking to add a touch of class and have some money to burn then go here! It's really nice inside and the staff are helpful. With 600 whiskys to choose from you can find something rare. Perhaps, like me, you can't afford the whole bottle from a shop but you can taste it anyway and brag about how good it tasted later.", "The balcony is a great place to try their cigars. Luckily I was given one from a nice client!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r370121563", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic venue, fantastic food.", "diner_date": " May 2016", "rating_date": "4 May 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "M6127XQchrisd", "reviewer_origin": ["Hythe, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "45"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "41"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r370121563-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Really can't praise Boisdales enough. We went for an evening meal as the music was a Bowie tribute night. We had been told it was good but it was superb. The music was brilliant, the food was stunning and the staff were very attentive without being intrusive in any way. Really don't know how to praise this place enough, we will certainly return. The food was reasonably priced, the d\u00e9cor was very nice and the atmosphere made the evening perfect. Their website lists all the upcoming music nights so you can book when there is something on to suit your taste. A night to remember. Thank you Boisdales, we'll be back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r373378869", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Jazzy fabby night out", "diner_date": " May 2016", "rating_date": "16 May 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "FifiLasVegas", "reviewer_origin": ["London, England, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "50"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r373378869-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["8 of us turned up via a Groupon Voucher not knowing what to expect. We loved it all. The restaurant is stunning and very welcoming. The service was great and the waiter was very helpful. Our table was in an excellent position quite near the stage and we really enjoyed Ray Gelato and his band. It was a very entertaining night and I would definitely go again. The food was delicious, hot and well presented. The only reason for a 4 star and not 5 is that most of the dishes had supplements and the cocktails were very pricey. Our \u00a320 a head outing turned into a \u00a360 affair. However, it was such a fun night no one really cared."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r372829051", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Let down by the service ", "diner_date": " May 2016", "rating_date": "14 May 2016", "answer_text": ["Dear Sir,", "Thank you for taking time to write a review on Boisdale Canary Wharf. I was very saddened to read your comments regarding the service you received on your visit. Please can you contact me at your earliest convenience, so that I may get a better understanding of what happened. My details are gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk . ", "I look forward to hearing from you in due course. ", "Kind regards", "James Hardesty"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Bulla1983", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "100"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "43"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r372829051-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I have been to the Boisdale a number of times over the last few years. Every time I go it's the same story. Excellent food / great music / awful service ", "There is a reason why I am rating my combined recent visits as 2 stars", "When you spend this money you expect at least a average level of service, you don't expect to spend you entire evening with your hand in the air or trying to catch the eye of a waiter hurriedly rushing from table to table ", "You will feel more attended to in Nandos ", "After my two recent visits I don't think I will be returning again ", "5 star prices / 2 star service "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r372986058", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great night out!", "diner_date": " May 2016", "rating_date": "15 May 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LESLEY C", "reviewer_origin": ["Barcelona"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r372986058-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Bar on first floor quite loud and raucous, unsurprisingly for a Friday night, however on entering the restaurant on higher floor, the atmosphere was totally different. Warm and inviting, even though it is a huge area. Service was impeccable, friendly but not overbearing. My boyfriend went for the haggis starter, which he really enjoyed and I had the calamari, which was a bit 'chewy'. Both my partner and I went for the Steak, which was nice, but not the best I've ever had. Band came on at 9.45 (Black Hat Band)..great entertainment and had everyone up dancing. Waiter found out it was my birthday and produced a plate with my name on and happy birthday message, candle, plus after dinner treats...nice touch. We will be back as the overall experience was great!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r368704994", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great for a business lunch", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "29 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Mascot1", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "225"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "85"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r368704994-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Was meeting two business partners in Boisdale for a business lunch. The service was very good (and unobtrusive), the food is excellent (I had the venison with rigatoni pasta) and there is sufficient privacy for business conversation. I have previously eaten at Boisdale for evening meals and have never been disappointed - strongly recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r365600772", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Nice food service and setting", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "20 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "mrtwig", "reviewer_origin": ["Beckford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "138"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "110"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r365600772-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for business lunch on the second floor, really nice setting on the river, good selection of food and drinks, lovely decor and everyone had a great time. Not unreasonable costs either considering the location right in the heart of C Wharf."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r364886532", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best Sunday lunch", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "17 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Lily Travel P", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "72"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "32"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r364886532-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Convenient location for us. Excellent food. Lovely wines. Good value for money at \u00a350 p/h for three courses including drinks. Lovely ambience with lunchtime jazz. Good background buzz but quiet enough to talk gently with the people we were eating with. Fab staff and service. Cabs ordered for us afterwards with drivers waiting for us in the lobby. A thoroughly enjoyable afternoon. Will make this a regular. thanks Boisdsale."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r371012056", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Nothing to write home about.", "diner_date": " May 2016", "rating_date": "7 May 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "emjay1968", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "130"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "51"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r371012056-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My experience of booking a table for 6 on a weeknight was interesting, and not in a good way. I requested a table in the first floor bar for 6pm and was told I would have to give my credit card details. When I asked why I was told that it is their policy to charge a \u00a325 per person cancellation fee for no-shows. After refusing to provide my card details I was put through to the manager who held the same line. It was only when I explained that in my opinion this is an offensive and money-grabbing practice AND that as one of the most popular reviewers on Tripadvisor in London this is exactly what would be going in my review did she change her tune. I was told that this policy is aimed at corporate clients and because we were just a small, private group they could waive the policy. ", "On the night we enjoyed the cocktails but the food was very pedestrian. Five of us paid \u00a3260 for 8 cocktails, 3 steaks, 6 tapas plates, 3 desserts and a coffee. To me this was not value for money: the service was slow, atmosphere pretty bland as we were stuck in a far corner and the quality of the food really wasn't anything special. Such a shame as I had high hopes based on a lovely dinner here nearly 4yrs ago. I may give Boisdale one more try but if it doesn't live up to it's reputation AND provide good customer service, I won't bother to come back. London has lots of wonderful restaurants that are hungry for success and are keen to treat customers well. I'd rather spend money in those."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r368382777", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "pre dinner drinks in the gorgeous bar", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "28 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Susan E", "reviewer_origin": ["GRAYS, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "92"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r368382777-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We love Boisdale, it's just such a cool place to visit for any reason, whether you are having dinner in the upstairs restaurant with a show or just in the lower bar with the fantastic veranda (which has patio heaters and blankets supplied for the chillier evenings) or visiting the cigar lounge it's a must ! the staff are so friendly and service is fantastic - LOVE IT !!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r367063839", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Atmospheric ", "diner_date": " March 2016", "rating_date": "25 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "xxtigerxx", "reviewer_origin": ["New Delhi, India"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "88"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "51"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r367063839-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I've been here a few times and have always enjoyed it. The food is reasonable but I like the setting. Indoor and outdoor seating and jazz performances too. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r367327403", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Don't take my word for it - just go - you will NOT BE DISAPPOINTED :-) 10/10 ALL ROUND", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "25 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Verna K", "reviewer_origin": ["Wellingborough, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "85"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "38"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r367327403-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["WIned and dined here 5 times since December 2015 - yes we really love going. Staff are amazing, food superb, entertainment terrific. Ambience and overall atmosphere buzzing. Can't praise it enough ...... and cant wait to go back.", "Went with friends on Saturday 23.4.16 and saw \"Suspiciously Elvis\" great act, well worth going to see. Lots of fun. Whole evening was tremendous success (as were all the other visits!)", "The Best Place to Wine, Dine, be Entertained ...in London"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r366796876", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic Live Music - Great Food", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "24 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Rilla45", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "192"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "75"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r366796876-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a fabulous night at Boisdalebmin Canary Wharf. You can park underneath Canary Warf and just take the elevators straight into the restaurant. Split over two levels with terrace bar downstairs and Resturants upstairs. Sat by the window and had great night time views of the buildings around us. Food and service were great. Awesome wine list.mon the night we went we saw 'Suspicously Elvis' a tribute act to the King. They play at the restaurant every couple of months and are actually very good, entertaining and fun even if your not an Elvis fan. Lots of good acts scheduled over the months ahead so well worth checking out what's on via their website or Facebook page."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r368611291", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Rip off at music time", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "29 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "JerseyGaz", "reviewer_origin": ["Jersey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "64"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r368611291-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I, and my colleagues were fortunate enough to be hosted for a corporate dinner recently, and on arrival we were very nicely greeted, great table with view across to the City of London. The service, whilst prompt, was a little hit and miss and I must have been knocked at least 5 times by staff having to reach over. The food, whilst enjoyable was not wonderful with the main course cold. All the desserts that came out, plus cheeseboard were faultless. The drinks selection is great but unless you are buying vintage whisky the bar service, at the bar, very poor with 10min wait when nobody else at the bar apart from two pretentious people trying to look and act as they knew what whisky to buy! My biggest problem, and don't foget we were being hosted, our host had just settled probably a \u00a31000 bill for our smallish (10) group, was the fact a small proportion of the party stayed on to watch the jazz band (OK, not brill) and the restaurant slapped a \u00a330 music charge onto our additional,not the main party, drinks bill, OUTRAGEOUS, and if I were paying they would have received a few sharp words. When is my next vist, probably never"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r368452698", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Not quite bells and whistles...", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "28 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "347faithb", "reviewer_origin": ["Milton Keynes, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "126"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "47"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r368452698-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["OK so he wanted to try Boisdale as we are both jazz fans and love great food. ", "Booked a Groupon set menu for \u00a320/pp and went for it.", "Arrived and in the lift were a party of people sniffing with a 'Colombian cold' and quite frankly had just stepped off the set from TOWIE. We ventured on...", "The reception girl was quick to take out coats and assign us a table. However it was clear she was board due to the florescent pink highlighter doodles and block colouring on the guest list...", "Upon being seated we were asked by three waiters (two minutes between them) if we would like drinks. We ordered the usual double gin & tonic with a large bottle of sparkling water. ", "The decor is eccentric and warm but slightly shabby round the edges. ", "We order ( mostly EAL staff with some difficultly in translation) drink in the atmosphere. The young male waiter by the window was very keen and attentive, perhaps we were in the cheap seats due to our voucher?!", "Starters arrived and my haggis had clearly been microwaved as it was tough and scalding hot, yet the neeps and mash were tepid. His goats cheese salad was... skimpy but tasty. Two blobs of goats cheese puree with micro salad; we normally share but I did not want to deprive him of his 2x 2p diameter portions...", "A splendid looking espresso floated by which prompted my order.", "There was one server who was doing both serving and clearing (black lady with braids and such a warm smile) she clearly enjoyed her job. Although all of the servers do require a course in waiting on. ", "Steak arrives, \u00a35 supplement for the 28 day matured beef, I opted for the sweet spud fries with alioli (4.95 sup) but I was not given extra veg to compensate for my not having the original fries. And his arrives with no fries... they arrive 5 minutes later with his supplemented portion of mushrooms. The steak was epic!!!!", "Espresso martini arrives... and the jazz starts 9pm ish", "I visited the ladies room via the cloakroom to ask someone to clear our table as the plates were still sat there 20 minutes after we had finished eating. The young lady was finishing off her colouring in with gusto.", "\u00a365 bill. Plus the voucher... \u00a3105 for well, not very much."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r365701142", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "QUALITY BUSINESS DINING", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "20 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Richard G", "reviewer_origin": ["Ashford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "355"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "154"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r365701142-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This remains one of the best places to have a serious business lunch in Canary Wharf. OK, today we had a rather dopey waiter who forgot several things (water, mustard) and kept on interrupting, but the view, food and ambience are all great. Steak, fish and liver all great, and an excellent wine list."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r362699596", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Not quite sure what this is", "diner_date": " January 2016", "rating_date": "9 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "itsmissfitz", "reviewer_origin": ["Northampton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "360"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "256"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r362699596-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Interesting place that smelt a bit like an old people's home when we first walked in, juxtaposed by semi naked photos on the walls. The service was good and I think that the ambience here would be wonderful in the evening. Food was delicious and they make Scottish and British food in the most inventive way."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r360239184", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Evening Dinner", "diner_date": " March 2016", "rating_date": "31 March 2016", "answer_text": ["Dear Sunshinesoul", "I was very saddened to read your review. Please can you contact me at your earliest convenience so that I may discuss this with you in more detail. ", "I look forward to hearing from you in due course.", "Kind regards,", "James Hardesty", "gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk"], "reviewer_pseudo": "sunshinesoul2014", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "39"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r360239184-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The food was lovely but the service was awful!! I never take off service but had to. We had to literally shout down the waitress for every meal and she was incredibly odd in behaviour and rude. We made the manager aware of this but still they continued to ignore the tables. Not enough staff. No manners and just downright weird place. Shame because chef and singers on point! Let down. Not worth the money and def not worth service charge. Remove it till they prove it! Disappointed."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r361710398", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice attmosphere", "diner_date": " March 2016", "rating_date": "5 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "katyp1313", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r361710398-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Not enough choice on the Bar food menu. Drinks are quiet pricey but nice for special occasions. Caters for groups of people, nice view over the city of an evening. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r359967351", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Dinner and dancing for the older couple", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "30 March 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LynneB843", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r359967351-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I love that this is dinner and dancing and that I do not feel old. We went for my birthday celebration and I loved it. I started with the scallops and then had the braised lamb. The food was cooked perfectly and the presentation was so pretty. Loved the band and danced to 80's music all night. A very enjoyable evening out."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r360710200", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Poor customer service - and we never even made it!", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "1 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "princessbeccy", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r360710200-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I booked a fabulous treat for my husband's birthday, he's Scottish and loves whisky so where else is there to go? ", "I purchased our table tickets a while ago and noticed the non refundable policy. Unfortunately, my husband has been ill all week and so I phoned today on the off chance that if the table was able to be resold for tomorrow night then maybe I could transfer my payment to another night? I was told a flat no. Even if it was resold. I was then told if my husband (or any other family member) had died or was in hospital then I would have been able to transfer it! But as that wasn't the case I wasn't able to book another night. Helpful but then a policy is a policy.", "To top it off, after being told there was nothing they could do at all, the girl I spoke to was ending the conversation and I asked her whether she actually wanted to take note of my name so they could resell my spot, as she had not thought to ask!! She then took great pride in saying \"so I've cancelled all that for you\".... Not even a we look forward to seeing you soon, hope your husband feels better, look online for our great calendar of events etc etc etc. Customer services hasn't been their strong point so far! ", "So, all in all I'm a little disappointed and I've not even got there yet. Such a shame too as my husband had been given donations for his birthday so he could indulge in some of their rare whiskies. Once he's better we'll look to rebook but whether it'll be here or not is still to be decided!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r359524440", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Simply Amazing!! ", "diner_date": " March 2016", "rating_date": "28 March 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MrBSelfMade", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "46"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r359524440-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Service: Amazing ", "Food: Amazing (from starter through to desert) ", "Drinks: One of the best rum bars in town", "Entertainment: Live jazz as you dine . ", "Value for money: On the expensive side but well worth it. ", "If I had to find a negative is its not easy to find in the busy Canary Wharf "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r364767068", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Quite good but not worth a trip", "diner_date": " March 2016", "rating_date": "17 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "simplefruit", "reviewer_origin": ["Zurich, Switzerland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "137"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "77"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r364767068-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited as a group of four Saturday evening.", "Three of us had the gravlax to start and it was magnificent. Easily worthy of five blobs.", "For the main course I had a steak that was nicely cooked but came with a cold sauce in a little pot. Three blobs. My wife had Venison that was really a bowl of pasta with some sauce. Two blobs. We also ordered some side dishes that were ok but a bit small - not really enough to share.", "I'm not sure that it is worth a trip but if I lived locally then I would return. It's a pity that we had had a long day because it would have been nice to stay for the music."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r363038266", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Dining with Fab Friends!", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "10 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Deborah H", "reviewer_origin": ["Winchester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "134"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "78"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r363038266-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["never been here before but will definitely be going again and again! What a fantastic location, the view is amazing, the restaurant is unique, a built in Humidor for those cigar loving men ! Great ambience and very exclusive feel to it. The food is to die for, the staff are on their game and the entertainment kept us buzzing all night ! This is for romantic meals, family celebrations and a perfect place for a wedding buffet!! LOVE this place !"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r363099894", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great music from Kokomo, good service and good (but not cheap) food", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "10 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Alan J", "reviewer_origin": ["Marlow, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "76"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "32"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r363099894-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went on a Friday night, one of Boisdale's 'soul nights'. This featured 'Kokomo', a British soul band that started in the 70s. They were tremendous, massively funky, and filled the dance floor. Great to see that it's not just tribute bands that can succeed at this type of venue.", "We had a Premium dining table that was close to the stage. It was a little disappointing that one of our seats had a somewhat restricted view. This mattered less when we took to the dance floor.", "This being Canary Wharf, it wasn't cheap. \u00a318 (plus 12.5% service) for a burger and fries is a lot. However, it was very good. Desserts were better priced at \u00a37.50. My wife had a chocolate marquise, which was excellent.", "Service was very good, and more personable than I'd expected.", "All in all, I probably wouldn't return just to eat. But, with the right band, it's a fun night out, if you can afford it."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r363978024", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great food & music venue", "diner_date": " April 2016", "rating_date": "13 April 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Minty1971", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "66"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "41"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r363978024-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited this restaurant/bar for the first time 2 weeks ago. Amazing food, great service in a really stylish venue. However, I was greeted by a very rude receptionist, who didn't crack her face all night! All in all a really good place to eat, drink and watch live music but in need of some staff training!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r351922004", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sunday jazz", "diner_date": " February 2016", "rating_date": "29 February 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "WDSmith66", "reviewer_origin": ["Glasgow, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r351922004-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked this for Sunday lunch with some jazz. What better. Was slightly unsure as this seemed to be in a shopping mall. However once in the lift you realised you were entering a different space altogether.", "Great decor awaits you as you are transferred back in time to a place where jazz ruled.", "The staff were very helpful. A small trio were playing as you would except. The food was typical Sundagy roast. Don't let that put you off it was great food. We upgraded the wine selection and made a great choice. Just between you and me try the sticky toffee pudding, OMG! Shh", "We had a blast. We were surprised as the place was not full on a Sunday. But hey we would recommend the place . We will be back.."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r359438138", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Excellent food and service", "diner_date": " March 2016", "rating_date": "28 March 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Erin_leigh79", "reviewer_origin": ["Erin_leigh79"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "484"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "236"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r359438138-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for dinner on Thursday night with my friend after a work event. I wasn't sure how crowded it would be since it was St. Patricks Day. In the states, that night is a big \"AVOID\" if you don't want to dine in a pub or party location with a bunch of drunken savages. But, no one seems to care about that \"holiday\" here in London. Service near the bar (bar menu) was very good. We had a few apps (Welsh Rarebit - not great; Empanadas - very good; sweet potato fries - standard). I had a salad which was really good and my friend quite enjoyed her fish and chips. I'd definitely go back here if I needed a nice, affordable place to eat when in this area next time. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r349888496", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great food but a little pricey!", "diner_date": " February 2016", "rating_date": "22 February 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Longissimus", "reviewer_origin": ["Orpington, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "85"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r349888496-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went there for our son's birthday & had a great time. There was an excellent selection of food & I changed my mind several times plus an extensive wine list, or should I say expensive! We had a Beronia Reserva 2011 Rioja priced at \u00a347.50, which was very nice & suited our taste but you can buy this in Waitrose for \u00a313.49! I understand you have to pay 'corkage' but paying over three times as much, is too much. The drinks in general were expensive but we were in the restaurant & had live Jazz, although even then, we had to pay for tickets to be able to listen. Nevertheless, we had a great evening & if we went again, we would probably go to one of their bars instead of the main restaurant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r352446100", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Slightly Disappointed - just not the usual atmosphere and experience", "diner_date": " February 2016", "rating_date": "2 March 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "rwilli2", "reviewer_origin": ["Portloe, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r352446100-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I am luckily enough to visit Boisdale a few times a year, unfortunately we were both disappointed with the evening that usually promises so very much, especially as this was a birthday treat for me! The singer was over 40 minutes late with no official announcement to confirm this delay, we were just told this by a member of the Boisdale staff which for a restaurant of this high caliber I was surprised, it is nice to be updated of any delay. The mood of the restaurant was something that I had never experienced before, very flat and very surprising as I have had an excellent time every time I have been here previously. We left at 11pm, an hour early, which by looking around was something that a lot of other people were also doing. Food and drinks to the high standard that we have always been served, we just both left disappointed."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r353203092", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good food and an excellent cigar bar", "diner_date": " February 2016", "rating_date": "5 March 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Gaston M", "reviewer_origin": ["Managua, Nicaragua"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r353203092-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I got into London late and was staying in Canary Wharf. I went to Boisdale for dinner around 8, had a nice rib eye and went to the cigar bar. They have a good selection of Cuban cigars and a very knowledgeable person in the smoking room. The atmosphere is relaxed and friendly. There was a nice group of people in the room, everyone talking and enjoying themselves. I will go back for sure."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r354768966", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great evening", "diner_date": " March 2016", "rating_date": "12 March 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "makethemostolife", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "73"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r354768966-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Been a few times with live music and dance area. Meals, service and staff always very good. Music charge extra depending where you sit but starting at \u00a310 per person. Worth a trip. Also other branch at Belgravia which I have not been to."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r356601443", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best Sunday ever....!!", "diner_date": " February 2016", "rating_date": "18 March 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MissSunshineSally", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "84"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "74"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r356601443-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited Boisdale on Sunday 28 February... It was a very unplanned Sunday lunch after a big night out... We were feeling a little fragile to say the least. We settled on the three course set menu and upgraded to 3/4 of a bottle of wine each and a glass of pink fizz..... This proved to be a very good decision!! The food was amazing!!!!! Rib of beef cooked perfectly for me (very rare at my request) and pork shoulder with cracking plus HUGE Yorkshire puddings!!!!!! The wine flowed, the cheeseboard arrived and our amazing waiter Tim was kind enough to give me a small sample of some of the cheeses to help me with my choice. More wine flowed and we ended up with a two day hangover, missed a train stop and a lost phone!!! If Carlsberg did Sunday lunches this would be it!!! Many thanks to the wonderful Tim and his extensive knowledge and humour! We still can't believe one glass of vintage whisky is as much as \u00a32700!!!!! Sunday lunch..... Highly recommended, can't wait for the next time... Minus the lost phone xxxx "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r353119775", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Got the worlds largest Whiskey selection !", "diner_date": " February 2016", "rating_date": "5 March 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Richieperera", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "46"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r353119775-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great food amazing wine collection. If bankers make your stomach turn then this place may not be for you, however once you get past them pompous nobody's you will love this place if you enjoy a good cigar and a good whiskey! ", "Also they have a Jazz bar, the night i went there was Bob Marley tribute band, i had just got back form Jamaica so absolutely loved the night !"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r352949798", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "fantastic venue", "diner_date": " March 2016", "rating_date": "4 March 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "loubuddy", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "120"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "53"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r352949798-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["visited this restaurant for one of their entertainment evenings. upon arrival. we had to get the lift to the second floor for the jazz, soul and blues events. we had booked to see the SINATRA AND DEAN event. we booked a table to eat beforehand which was a good call because we were then able to sit back and just enjoy the show. this restaurant is very tastefully decorated, the atmosphere was buzzing and the ambiance was perfect. the staff were very pleasant and attentive even though it was very very busy this particular evening. I had the tournedos steak which is a fillet and it was probably one of the best i have ever tasted, cooked to perfection, so tender ", "and not at all dry which so makes a change. my partner had the sirloin which too was beautiful. would highly recommend the steak dishes. most of the food that passed by us looked very mouth watering so i would say go with anything really. The show started at 9.15pm and it was very entertaining, the guys sounded very much like the real deal and it was like being at a cabaret show in vegas. the band that accompanied Frank and Dean were brilliant too. we were all encouraged to get up ", "and dance which really made it that little bit more special and the whole show lasted for about 1 hr 20 mins. it truly was a fantastic fun evening with beautiful food, fantastic friendly staff and i would so recommend visiting this place. you will not be disappointed. thankyou to everybody at BOISDALE for a most entertaining evening. cant wait to visit again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r357542553", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best restaurant ever!", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "22 March 2016", "answer_text": ["Dear Christina,", "Having just been alerted to your review although you visited in November - I would like to Thank You on behalf of the team at Boisdale of Canary Wharf - we are so pleased your experiences have been so flawless, which is what we strive for. At the same time we wish to Congratulate you & your fianc\u00e9 & ask that you contact me when you next intend to visit: Katie@boisdale.co.uk", "Best,", "Katie"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Nekokama", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r357542553-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We've only had the opportunity to visit this restaurant twice but what can I say other than that it was flawless on both visits.", "The first visit consisted of a steak tartar starter and a porter house t-bone steak special for a sharing main. Both were suggested and came highly recommend from our extremely charming waiter and we're both dishes we didnt even consider on first glance. To be honest he sealed the deal when he displayed the cut of meat to us before I final decision.", "The next time we came was for a big band evening and once again I couldn't have asked for more. The food (a fillet steak main) was once again cooked to perfection and so tender that it took no effort to cut at all. The staff were exceptionally attentive and friendly.", "I also describe it to my friends as my lucky restaurant as during the first visit we received word that my sister-in-law had given birth to my godson and my boyfriend proposed the night of the second.", "We're coming back after the wedding and can't wait to show our family what all the fuss is about.", "Thank you Boisdale! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r344028710", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Crooning and great food - a joy!", "diner_date": " January 2016", "rating_date": "31 January 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Wooky61", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r344028710-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited Saturday night with husband and daughter. We had a VIP table near the stage. Service was attentive from start to finish. Food was first class with our menu choices of carpaccio and baby haggis to start and slow cooked lamb and calves liver for main. Cheese board selection extensive and delicious. Cabaret was very good with songbooks from Sinatra and Nat King Cole. Great atmosphere and although a large restaurant it didn't feel overwhelming. Will definitely visit again. Whisky selection amazing. Well worth a visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r345056971", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Could ask for better!", "diner_date": " January 2016", "rating_date": "4 February 2016", "answer_text": ["Dear 1221,", "Thank you so much, what a lovely review. I do hope you will keep coming and hope to meet with you next time you visit! Please do ask for me when you arrive. ", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt", "General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Laura G", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r345056971-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great food, amazing service.", "Went there many times and will always come back. Atmosphere is brilliant, very relaxed and the food is super delicious."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r345594266", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Get a table by the stage", "diner_date": " February 2016", "rating_date": "7 February 2016", "answer_text": ["Dear Maurice1808,", "Thank you for writing a review. I'm really pleased you enjoyed the act and apologise for any delays you experienced. We have some great acts coming up that you may like, keep an eye out on our website for the details. I look forward to welcoming you back soon.", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ruth F", "reviewer_origin": ["Chigwell, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "116"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "42"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r345594266-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This was our first visit to the Boisdale and we would certainly go again. We were lucky to see an Eagles tribute band who were quite entertaining. We had the set menu which was \u00a340 a head including the entertainment, but obviously the drinks were extra and due to the expensive cocktails we had quite a hefty bill. Service was slow, but we didn't mind as we were going to be there until the band finished anyway.", "One big pointer is get a table by the dance floor or you will feel \"out of it\"."]}
