{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r337683579", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "a Saturday night experience", "diner_date": " January 2016", "rating_date": "5 January 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Stone11M", "reviewer_origin": ["Stone, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r337683579-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A Saturday night supper in the Terrace restaurant chosen on the basis of past experience of staying at the Lamb at Hindon (sadly no longer part of the stable). I attended with both my wife an son and we have to say be were treated like' royalty'. Nothing was too much, with the Maitre de giving us a personal tour showing both the Cigar room and also the main dinning area with the whiskey collection(heaven). We can't wait to come again and experience the supper room."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r341143943", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice environment and great selection of Whisky!", "diner_date": " January 2016", "rating_date": "19 January 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "sihongtravel", "reviewer_origin": ["Shanghai, China"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r341143943-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The bar on the ground floor is nice, the restaurant is not bad. There is a great selection of Whisky! I would love to check the 1946 Macallan, but too costly!!! ", "Nice place for an afterwork drink or a romantic dinning."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r342643633", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Extremely rude service, never experienced anything like that!", "diner_date": " January 2016", "rating_date": "25 January 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Gabriel L", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r342643633-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went there last week with my colleagues for our end of year dinner and I experienced something I have never seen before in a restaurant of this category.", "The waiter arrived with several steaks and french fries but the portions of fries were clearly not enough. He distributed the plates in such a way that half the people in the table had their portions and the other half had nothing. I was over half of my steak and had already claimed my portion but had to claim it again so I could eat them with my steak. What he did left me speechless, he literally went to the other side of the table and without asking for permission he grabbed a plate from one of my colleagues to drop it by my plate. As I was finishing my steak he decided it was not enough to remove someone else's fries so he came to my side and attempted to take the plate out again and in the plate there were not more than 5 small fries!", "I had to ask him to keep the plate there as I hadn't finish my portion and told him I had never seen something like that and I didn't expect to see it in a restaurant like this one, but he didn't even apologized to me!", "Extremely rude service! I don't think I will ever go there again or recommend it to anyone else!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r342672396", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Christmas Party with Frankie & Dean - superb", "diner_date": " December 2015", "rating_date": "25 January 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "tresadla", "reviewer_origin": ["Zurich, Switzerland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "186"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "87"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r342672396-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This was our 3rd year celebrating our Christmas Party, its really such a laugh and great fun. Frankie & Dean are brilliant and everyone is up dancing after the 2nd song!! Food is expensive for the portion size, but its very good. Service is wonderful and attentive and I just love the whole atmosphere of the bar and restaurant. A lot of people here didnt realise that there is another bar underneath the main restaurant, which has a lovely outdoor area with view over Canary Wharf."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r334782544", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Over-priced but okay-ish!", "diner_date": " December 2015", "rating_date": "24 December 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear stf02,", "Thank you for your review. Our cocktail list is varied in price due to the premium sprits used, the starting point is \u00a39.50 ranging up to \u00a318.50. Please get in touch to arrange another visit to our bar, my email address is below. I hope to be able to show off our cocktails to you soon.", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth", "gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk"], "reviewer_pseudo": "stf02", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r334782544-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This is a good looking bar but the cocktails are around \u00a35 too expensive. The drinks average \u00a315 - \u00a317, they should be around the \u00a312 mark. 1 Canada Square serves better cocktails at a more friendly price range. I don't mind paying for what I get, they just aren't good enough to warrant the cost."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r342921035", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Impressive", "diner_date": " January 2016", "rating_date": "26 January 2016", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "293corinnef", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "101"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r342921035-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Although slightly intimidating at first the restaurant was lovely and the service very good. Reasonably priced even with the steak option!! Not too busy and very enjoyable. The food was absolutely lovely - everyone left full and raved about their option!! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r333231228", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Not worth the money", "diner_date": " December 2015", "rating_date": "16 December 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Lulamugs,", "My sincere apologies that your experience wasn't pleasant or to our standard. Please get in touch with me to discuss your meal at your earliest convenience. ", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt", "gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Lulamugs", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "20", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r333231228-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Dined at CW Boisdale last Thursday with a friend for an impromptu dinner.", "Ordered a Inferno Burger and a classic burger , had to order fries as they don't come with fries! And one glass of Chablis and a glass of Merlot. Bill came to \u00a340 each.", "I don't mind paying for good food- but the burger cam up cold- the bun was hard and the chips were soggy. More like pub food from weatherspoons. Normally I would complain and send it back - but the waiter looked like he couldn't be bothered to help and that we were lucky to get a table as walk ins during the Christmas period.", "Safe to say I wont be going back in a rush. Way over priced for poor food."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r334070323", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely! ", "diner_date": " December 2015", "rating_date": "20 December 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jane F", "reviewer_origin": ["Stone, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r334070323-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited here on Thursday night with my husband. The food was lovely and the atmosphere great, we didn't see the live music but the place was full. My husband had a cigar and whiskey in the Cigar lounge which he thoroughly enjoyed. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r334055268", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Yet again, perfect !!", "diner_date": " December 2015", "rating_date": "20 December 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "mattsW1168VQ", "reviewer_origin": ["Goring-on Thames, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "38"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r334055268-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This is the third time I have dined at boisdale Canary Wharf at it never stops giving. Staff were second to none, even when we asked to change the set menu for another menu just before ordering, they produced new and personalised menus within 10 minutes. Food was outstanding, entertainment fabulous and like I say, the staff are so accommodating, not to mention patient !! Can't wait to return in the not to distant future."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r334086000", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Price versus Quality", "diner_date": " December 2015", "rating_date": "20 December 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Craig1967", "reviewer_origin": ["Plymouth, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "42"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r334086000-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked at short notice & we're pleased to get a table for 2. It is a nice place & definetly has \"atmosphere\" in there, especially with live music on the top floor. The steak was very good but fries very \"McDonald's\". Also very basic for the price of \u00a322 for steak & chips with nothing else on the plate. The extras we ordered was mushrooms & they were v good although hugely expensive at \u00a39.50 a portion. Enjoyed our experience but could have got more value for money elsewhere. In short, only issue was price"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r334198022", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good food amazing band", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "21 December 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Boltac,", "Thank you for your review, I'm so pleased you enjoyed your meal! We have some great acts coming up including Burns celebrations at the end of the month, all the details are on our website. I look forward to welcoming you back soon. ", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Boltac", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "43"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r334198022-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": [" I went for a date and the band was a cameo of the blues brother", "The musician were amazing", "The food was good. ", "A big choice of wine and whiskey ", "Nice decor", "Slightly on the expensive side.", "Perfect to impress on a first date"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r334229581", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Hair in Soup, Dirty Old Cutlery, Scruffy Staff & definitely not worth a Visit", "diner_date": " December 2015", "rating_date": "21 December 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Ghaza A,", "Please get in touch to discuss your review with me. ", "I hope to hear from you soon,", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt", "gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk"], "reviewer_pseudo": "666ghazaa", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "34"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "47"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r334229581-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["It was a present for me and was served the starter soup which had a hair see the photo for it. I couldnt stop laughing being in a place like Boisdale and after a couple of spoons of the soup I find a surprise HAIR. HA HA HA. I got put off and it was quietly replaced with another starter but yet they carried on serving the same soup to other Customers which I found really strange. The tables were too small so small that there was not enough space to leave anything other than the meal you were having.", "The only good thing about the place was the view from where we were sitting. See photos.", "If you are going to get drunk, just eat whatever comes to your table as you have money to waste than visit Boisdale.", "Go Hair Soup only at Boisdale..."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r334372123", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fun venue .... but a little chaotic", "diner_date": " December 2015", "rating_date": "22 December 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Pick_E_Diner,", "Thank you very much for your review. As you mentioned December's run up to Christmas can be a very busy time for restaurants, this shouldn't have effected your experience,I am sorry the meal felt chaotic for you . Please do email me next time you are coming so I can make your reservation and return visit special for you.", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt", "gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Pick_E_Diner", "reviewer_origin": ["Aston Clinton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "138"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "80"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r334372123-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Venue great for an entertaining evening", "Pre dinner cocktails and G & T's poor.....", "Food a little disappointing, which may be down to the numbers dining (it is pre-christmas)", "Some side dishes lost into the ether......free ports to compensate.", "Service was for the most part attentive and helpful.", "Cheeseboard very good.", "Entertainment \"Frank & Dean\" ..... made for a very enjoyable evening, which lifted final points given."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r334750637", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Dinner , live music , cigar ......perfect", "diner_date": " December 2015", "rating_date": "24 December 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear dkwilli,", "Thank you very much for your review. I'm pleased you enjoyed the meal but sorry that the special offer on the website had finished and not been amended. We do try to keep our website as up to date as possible, I'm sorry that this side of the experience let you down. I do hope you'll visit us again and hope you will let me know when you are coming. ", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt", "gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk"], "reviewer_pseudo": "dkwilli", "reviewer_origin": ["Cirencester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "239"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "187"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r334750637-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Dinner with Dean and Frank , food was pretty good and so was the wine . bit dissapointed that online there was a half price XO brandy by the glass and when I enquired at my table it was full price so on principle I didn't order it . As other people have said watch the bill !", "also one waiter in particular has a bad habit of pouring wine at a stupid rate just to sell more wine , attentive staff fine but by commission waiters not ", "would go back I know there are more interesting themed evening's ahead. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r334682382", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Watch the bill", "diner_date": " December 2015", "rating_date": "23 December 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Mr Goodman,", "I am so sad to hear this error ruined your otherwise pleasant lunch at Boisdale of Canary Wharf. This was a simple mistake that should never have happened, your food should have been ordered via our inclusive pricing but instead was charged at full price which then appeared on your bill. I do hope you will come back and give us another chance. Please do let me know if you wish to return so I can make arrangements for you.", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt", "gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk"], "reviewer_pseudo": "653stepheng653", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "80"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r334682382-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Excellent food and ambeince.However when the bill arrived we found we had been overcharged \u00a3220 yes that's right \u00a3220 for a party of 10.they appologised and changed bill but \u00a3220 is no small amount so I don't think I will return,plenty of restaurants to spend my money in.", "Sent e-mail to restaurant but no response from management", "Stephen Goodman"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r329914188", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Private Dining", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "30 November 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Pete2boogie", "reviewer_origin": ["Stotfold, Beds"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r329914188-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Chose the Boisdale CW for my retirement luncheon, as I'd been there several times before for the music. Having made arrangements with Valerie before the event, I can't fault the service from the team. Great attention to detail, excellent food and a great location. All of my guests couldn't speak highly enough of their experience. Many thanks to all involved in my special day."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r329989436", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Don't bother ", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "30 November 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "412aland", "reviewer_origin": ["Croydon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "67"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "45"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r329989436-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["There was 8 of us that had pre booked and we thought this looks like a nice place but the service was so slow from the start and the restaurant was only half full at this point. The starters was all good. Then they brought out the main course and gave the wrong steak to the wrong person who had started it and then the waiter said I'm sorry that's not for you and gave the started meal to another friend on our table and then walked away. We asked to be shown to the cigar room and told 2 minutes but the waiter forgot for 30 minutes and then said its just down the stairs just go yourself. When we returned to our table its was slow to get a drink again. We paid the bill which was \u00a31800 and we left early and will not be returning in a hurry. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r329883619", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Never disappoints - 5* all round! Haggis is a must!", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "30 November 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Sian F", "reviewer_origin": ["Epping, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "176"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "86"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r329883619-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Fantastic food, fantastic wine, fantastic service! We are never disappointed in Boisdale and can't wait to visit again! ", "Highly recommend the Haggis and Rib Eye Steak!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r329314889", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "First time ever that I get charged for bad music", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "27 November 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Catpimimi,", "I'm sorry to hear you didn't enjoy your experience with us. May I kindly ask you to get in touch with me so we can discuss your evening further. My contact details are below.", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt", "General manager", "gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk", "02077155818"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Catpimimi", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r329314889-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Overall the food is ok, nothing exceptional. But the music charge is absolutely ridiculous. As I got home and realised that the table had been charged some 30-40 pounds for the terrible music (it was a relief when it finally stopped), I sent an email to the management to explain that I was not happy about that. Never got a response. Just poor."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r330639548", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Expensive but worth the money", "diner_date": " December 2015", "rating_date": "4 December 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "X4999BCalexm", "reviewer_origin": ["Maidstone, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "206"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "150"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r330639548-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A gem in Canary Wharf. This is a huge restaurant over two floors which is well known for its love of music and live shows. The menu is excellent if not a little overpriced. The food is of a good standard and the waiting staff are well trained and very polite. Worth a visit if you have deep pockets."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r332650694", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Surf 'n' turf", "diner_date": " December 2015", "rating_date": "14 December 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Kevin,", "Thank you for your lovely review. I am so pleased you enjoyed your experience with us. We have some fantastic acts coming in the New Year to watch out for. l hope to welcome you back soon.", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt"], "reviewer_pseudo": "719KevinM", "reviewer_origin": ["Borehamwood, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "381"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "124"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r332650694-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Once found, hard to find entrance. A great venue to enjoy good food and good music on the stage, making this a unique experience. The food and wines were reasonably priced. The staff were friendly. Great views over Cabot Square, a place to enjoy and relax. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r330091038", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fabulous Rib Eye Steak", "diner_date": " March 2015", "rating_date": "1 December 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "johndriscolluk", "reviewer_origin": ["Petts Wood, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "172"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "102"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r330091038-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Quite possibly, one of the finest rib eye steaks I have ever had the pleasure to eat!", "My fianc\u00e9e took me here for my birthday lunch and it certainly didn't disappoint. Both the rib eye and the fillet steak were excellent.", "Exceptional service. Cant go wrong with Boisdale.", "When booking a table, ask for one of the window seats!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r331445914", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great evening venue", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "8 December 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Nevleary,", "It is a pleasure to receive such a great review, thank you so much for talking the time. I hope to welcome you again in the near future, please do ask for me on your next visit, it would be a pleasure to thank you in person. ", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Stelvioman", "reviewer_origin": ["Canterbury, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "73"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r331445914-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great food, excellent service and avenue to impress. The venue caters for many needs and is excellent for entertaining after a business meeting. Great variety of beers followed by excellent choices in the menu. Highly recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r330827292", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Excellent atmosphere BUT...", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "5 December 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Fjoralba M,", "Thank you for your review. I am so pleased you enjoyed your meal. My apologies that your server offended you when it came to your payment, I assure you this was purely an avoidable mistake. ", "We have brought up in our daily briefings since reading your comments to ensure all our guests are treated equally and the host of the table, be it male or female is respected. I do hope to meet you next time you visit us, please ask for me or mention this when booking with our reception team.", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Fjoralba M", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r330827292-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My partner and I went to celebrate our first anniversary on 24th November, eating, drinking, dancing and enjoying the excellent singer. I even ordered a second bottle of wine. In the end, i asked for the bill. The waiter approached our table and i handed in my card. He took it, slipped it in and then offered it back to my partner for him to issue password and make the payment. Shocked by his gesture i very kindly offered \"pardon me, i think i was the one who gave the card, not my partner' and he then offered a very poor apology and left. It was a very offensive gesture, with no excuse. People still believe (wrongly) that it is the man who ought to pay. But, all signs were clear as to who is paying the bill on this specific occasion. And don't tell me i am an angry feminist! What i'm talking about is common sense. We need to teach people (women and men) that if we want to be treated equally, we have to be assertive and clear on our social behavior. Other than that, this is the most elegant restaurant i've ever been to. Excellent food, excellent atmosphere, the singer was marvelous. Definitely going back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r332507227", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Glorified Weatherspoons Pub", "diner_date": " December 2015", "rating_date": "13 December 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Dash T,", "I would like to discuss this review further with you. I also sent you an email to your personal address earlier today. ", "As a successful Sunday lunch venue our menu is varied and accessible to suit all tastes. It is also on our website for anybody to view before choosing to dine with us. ", "I hope to hear from you soon.", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Dash T", "reviewer_origin": ["Melbourne, Australia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r332507227-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This has to be the worst restaurant me and my wife have visited in our entirety!", "For the type of venue, food and drink it is over priced and disgusting. ", "Upon entry we surrendered our coats and were seated by the window and handed the Sunday lunch menu. When reading through the menu I realised (which is not mentioned on the web site) that no steak type meals were on offer and the waitress told us we had no access to the al a crate menu. We were given a sales pitch by an oriental waitress that Sunday lunch was what the public wanted so we cannot provide you with what you wish! ", "So we ordered our starters which were minimal.....mushroom soup worse than Heinz and salmon gravaldax which was three small thin strips of salmon at \u00a39.00!", "We did try and order some decent gin and tonics but were told sorry you only have a choice from three brands! ", "The mains were just awful! Fish chips.....fish soaked in oil and over cooked chips.......gnocchi with tempura cauliflower soaked in a disgusting watery white so called cream sauce. ", "In summary ladies and gentlemen if you want a selection of whiskey please visit here but do not prefer food as it is disgusting and the when you enter the venue it does smell of vomit mixed with alcohol. I'm definitely sure a Weatherspoons pub could do far better at this venue as the management has no idea please find pictures attached...to escape from this place we had to pay \u00a360 which was not warranted in any shape or form! Plus any form of accompanying vegetables were extra dry, tasteless and resembled leftovers! ", "PLEASE FOR HUMANITIES SAKE DO NOT VISIT THIS PLACE AT ALL!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r328298892", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Really good Sunday Lunch", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "22 November 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Nortsat46", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "101"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r328298892-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had the set menu Sunday lunch with wine pairings and thoroughly enjoyed it. A glass of sparkling rose wine to begin our meal, then haggis scotch eggs as starters - a new experience for me and very flavoursome. ", "The roast beef and Yorkshire puddings were lovely and the waiting team kept our glasses topped up as frequently as we wished. ", "The puddings were cheesecake with blackberry sorbet (delightful) and my partner had a chocolate confection which he pronounced delicious. We finished with good coffee.", "The service was very attentive and the jazz trio were really good. ", "So enjoyable ... we fell asleep on the sofa when we arrived home!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r323672916", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Sunday lunch!", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "1 November 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Angela R", "reviewer_origin": ["Chelmsford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "85"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "56"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r323672916-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked to have Sunday jazz lunch here with friends. Efficient and friendly staff, very professional in their service. We had a window seat which overlooked Cabot Square. All the food was excellent and great atmosphere in this beautiful restaurant. Only disappointment was the live music! It really didn't compliment the dining experience. We were looking forward to some great jazz music over lunch but sadly we didn't feel this was achieved. The only minor disappointment to a fabulous lunch experience!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r324384474", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Shame about the jazz", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "4 November 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "vieuxprout", "reviewer_origin": ["Cambridge, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r324384474-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Sunday reunion with friends over jazz. Lunch was generally excellent and at a reasonable price. Wine prices too, were acceptable for the City though the single malt prices are steep. Tim was our excellent waiter. The disappoinment was the live jazz, competent but uninspiring and not for long; unfortunate, as it was a major reason for our long journey to be there."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r326625097", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Enjoyable ", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "14 November 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Tapiwa V", "reviewer_origin": ["Chigwell, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r326625097-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We enjoyed our evening at this etablishment. There was live music and the food was good,The service left much to be desired though. The Cigar bar was my personal favourite spent a lot of time in there. I would recommend a visit. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r324717720", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Poor floor service", "diner_date": " October 2015", "rating_date": "5 November 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "B\u00e1lint H", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r324717720-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale Canary Wharf is a fantastic venue but the quality of the floor service in their restaurant is not matching the rest of of the experience. It is a problem and might be the reason they unable to fill the dining area on a Saturday night. This was our second visit in the last three months and we wont be returning in the foreseeable future."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r323274117", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What a surprise", "diner_date": " October 2015", "rating_date": "30 October 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Wilmapx", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "109"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "55"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r323274117-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["On the spur of the moment we decided to go to Boisdale, what a good decision. Although the restaurant was fully booked and had a live music act playing that evening they suggested we went to the bar. Although not as keen on this suggestion, we gave it a try. ", "Service was first class, the food outstanding. We ate from the fixed price menu - a very reasonable \u00a311.95 - but paid the supplement and both had fillet steak. It was sublime, perfectly cooked and accompanied with fries and a side order of broccoli. Boisdale is a Scottish restaurant, no doubt this is why the steak was so good, we both had \"haggis, neeps and tatties\" as a starter. Dessert was an apple and pear crumble. We thoroughly enjoyed our meal, the quality of the food was excellent and the staff were friendly and helpful We will be back soon."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r323480127", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A Return Visit", "diner_date": " October 2015", "rating_date": "31 October 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "9SueT", "reviewer_origin": ["Chislehurst, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "55"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r323480127-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["After a disappointing Sunday lunch at Boisdale\u2019s in September we returned for a midweek lunch earlier this month and the food was superb. Our starters were haggis and the mushroom & tarragon soup both of which were delicious. Our mains were truffle Aberdeenshire rib steak hamburger and lamb, again both were delicious. Our server recommended wines to go with our individual courses and they complimented the foods perfectly. We had no room for dessert but had coffees. Thank you Boisdale Canary Wharf, we had a superb lunch (back to your best) and will definitely return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r327008691", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great atmosphere, good(ish) food, service needs tweaking for better rating", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "15 November 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Irawo", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "34"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r327008691-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked a private room all in all it was a good experience, for most of the time. The booking was painless, though it might be best to have an online form process, emailing a PDF that has to be filled and sent back is a bit clunky. Our room was nice, and just the right size for our party of 8 I feel 10 would be a bit cramped, the food was lovely, haggis was especially good as was the soup, the cheese platter was a let down, great cheeses but servings were stingy, I would have liked to have seen a better menu given the prices, chicken and salmon aren't exciting, and we were restricted to an a la carte menu, shame as other menus looked more exciting. Note: sides do not come with the dishes and have a charge. Our waitress was really nice, friendly, and attentive but she was obviously dealing with several rooms or tables, and rushed off her feet. The whiskey, wines and champagnes are first rate, sadly we didn't get to sample the cigars. Note although the brochure mentions music docks in the rooms there aren't any, a major oversight in my opinion. all the staff we met were courteous I could possibly come back. ."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r327421519", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Not disaapointing", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "17 November 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "GardenerBuff", "reviewer_origin": ["UK"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "261"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "121"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r327421519-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Varied menu, well cooked and presented food. Good service, wine list. All things that you expect to get from a good restaurant but do not always get."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r327173980", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Sisters Birthday", "diner_date": " November 2015", "rating_date": "16 November 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Klarissa777", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r327173980-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The room we had was adequate wine was excellent . i cant say that for the salmon though the spinach was lovely, the lobster seasoning was bland was expecting a sweet / savory taste. The haggis was fab!", "I did love the atmosphere that night of the 14th nov. I would try this place out again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r319829219", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Bad on many levels", "diner_date": " October 2015", "rating_date": "18 October 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "D_Wapping", "reviewer_origin": ["Norwich, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r319829219-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We've just got back from Boisdale Canary Wharf, and are quite disappointed. We'd been a few years ago, and felt it was a bit 'all fur coat and no knickers' then. Nothing has changed.", "The starters were nice, but the mains arrived as we were finishing them, which meant things hung around for a while.", " ", "The beef rib was supposed to be medium rare, mine was very rare and barely tepid, so I sent it back. When it returned, the server disappeared without offering any condiments.", "It turned out that both others having beef, were served cold meet. We sent one back, and again had to wait for condiments.", "All three diners' beef were tough as old boots, and mainly fat and gristle, with all plates going back with around 50% of the meat remaining.", "Also, drinks orders were forgotten.", "The sticky toffee pudding was dry, and lacked sauce. I had to ask for extra clotted cream, and my dining partner left most of his.", "The manager, at a push, knocked 2 of the set menus off the bill, but slipped the desserts back in. I wasn't impressed, but was muzzled by my fellow diners.", "To be fair, the fish course was nice, as was one of the desserts. Also, the duck fat potatoes were nice, but had gone cold due to the problems and subsequent delays with the meat.", "This visit was just like the last, all style over substance, and we won't be rushing back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r319883335", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great night !", "diner_date": " October 2015", "rating_date": "18 October 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "dkwilli", "reviewer_origin": ["Cirencester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "239"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "187"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r319883335-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["met friends after a meal round the corner. great cigars purchased at a big cost by one of our party which you can smoke out on the terrace . ", "went up to our table to listen to the live jazz , great easy listening music , wine was reasonable and good price , the cost is \u00a310 ahead to listen to the jazz and we'll. worth it . will be back . "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r321938538", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Guys Meal", "diner_date": " October 2015", "rating_date": "26 October 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "lolaessex28", "reviewer_origin": ["London, England"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r321938538-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked their set menu for 20+ Gents on Saturday night. Great steak, broccoli was lovely. Our main gripe was they brought one dish of chips and said it was for three people! One between two would of been just about passable but one between three was ridiculous at \u00a345 per head so we had to order extra chips. Also watch out for the water bottles it cost us \u00a350 in water alone. ", "We had ordered five bottles of wine for the table as some of the guys wanted to get beers and were saving themselves for the whisky and some were driving but they brought out and opened ten bottles before we had realised and we ended up not drinking them all. All that said, we had a fantastic night and the service was well worth the \u00a3140 service charge added."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r320479930", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Elvis Tribute Night......It ain't no Viva Las Vegas", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "20 October 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "tripper12London", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "148"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "98"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r320479930-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["At \u00a350 a ticket just for the evening \"entertainment\" I think I was expecting a bit more from the tribute act and the Boisdale Rooms. The photographs of the Boisdale Rooms do not quite show up how shabby this place is, in dire need of a refurb. The set menu was ridiculously overpriced for what was put before me, nothing special, \"a good steak\". Service on the other hand is excellent and the waiters ensured your glass was never empty! Now the entertainment.....Elvis .... Or should I say Ivor Potter...not as great as the Boisdale advertise him to be.... Couldn't help thinking about the only fools and horses sketch.......The singer who couldn't pronounce his R's...Roy Orbison looky likely singing Crying...I don't think you are supposed to take this Elvis night serious and I think as long as you drink as much alcohol as you can it will be ok and soon be over. A very expensive night. Great money spinner for the Boisdale"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r319714178", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great evening", "diner_date": " October 2015", "rating_date": "18 October 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "mrkroft", "reviewer_origin": ["london"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "54"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "41"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r319714178-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Really enjoyed our night at boisdale. Delivered on the food all three courses were high quality. We had pre drinks in the bar and a cigar on the terrace. Service was outstanding."]}
