{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r321170198", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lunch", "diner_date": " October 2015", "rating_date": "23 October 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Mark_Elliott", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "322"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "143"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r321170198-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had the fixed price menu but the full a la carte looked quite interesting. ", "The choices we reasonable for the price and the portions adequate. The food was average to good, but the service and room were better than average hence the score. The wine list was very good.", "It just wasn't 'engaging' as restaurant, so whilst I'd go again it wasn't the kind of place you would call a destination, in fact I'm not sure I'd make the effort to cross the road to get there. I'm not sure why this is, and I know it's a personal thing, maybe a bit weird even.", "So, in summary, it isn't too expensive, the food is reasonable, the service is quite good, the decor is OK, the wine list is comprehensive, but I found lunch there dull. Sorry.", "Mark"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r321257925", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food and entertainment", "diner_date": " October 2015", "rating_date": "23 October 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Livefortravel80", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "27"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "55"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r321257925-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This place is amazing. Wonderful band playing and delicious food. Will def be visiting again! They were also very kind to give us a great table when I mentioned it was our 5 year anniversary."]}
