{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r312288990", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "1st Class", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "21 September 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Tina, ", "Thank you so much for your lovely review! The staff were so please when I showed them. ", "We look forward to welcoming you again very soon.", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Tina R", "reviewer_origin": ["Leicester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r312288990-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["First visit to Boisdale, and it exceeded expectations. Multitude of attentive friendly staff made the experience one to remember, food was great too!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r313503117", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fine food, wine and music", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "25 September 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Rita P,", "Thank you so much for writing such a lovely review. It is great to receive good feedback from new guests. I do hope you've since visited one of our other sites since coming to see us here. Belgravia is where it all started 27 years ago and well worth a visit!", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Rita P", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r313503117-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We discovered Boisdale while looking for a restaurant with live music and good food and it fitted the bill perfectly. The restaurant offers a range of fine wines and vintage whiskeys and boasts that it serves the best of Scottish food including wild duck, salmon, venison and high quality beef. Top musicians perform jazz, blues and soul. It even has a cigar library offering Havana cigars, a few dating back to pre-Castro days. The restaurant is vast with deep red and green walls so may not suit customers seeking intimacy. The artwork is distinctive with large paintings of nudes. We went to the Boisdale in Canary Wharf only to find out later that there are other branches which would have been less of a trek. Prices weren't prohibitively high, worth a visit for a special occasion. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r312433734", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic Sunday Lunch", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "21 September 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Dawn,", "Thank you so much for your great review! It really does give the team a spring in their step to receive such great feedback. There are some amazing evening acts coming up that you might also enjoy. We look forward to seeing you again on your next visit. ", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Dawn B", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "43"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "53"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r312433734-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went to Boisdales yesterday for the Sunday Lunch and it really was the best roast we've ever had. The rib of beef,cooked medium rare cut like butter and was so tasty. Yorkshire Pudding and goose fat roast potatoes were crisp and full of flavour, accompanied by spring greens and buttered carrots it really was an amazing lunch. The starters we choose were beautiful, looking around the restaurant also seemed the most popular, haggis scotch egg and potted mackerel, gorgeous. Desert's looked lovely but we chose a selection of cheese,all good quality and a lovely white port!.Service was good considering how busy the restaurant was. Lovely live jazz trio played throughout the meal. Altogether a great afternoon, will definitely be returning to Boisdales."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r313956373", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Suspiciously elvis", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "27 September 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear BrendaW1023,", "What a lovely review, thank you so very much. I'm pleased to hear your birthday celebrations were enjoyed and we look forward to seeing you in the near future. Do check out the website for more amazing live music listings and offers. ", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt"], "reviewer_pseudo": "BrendaW1023", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r313956373-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A party of 12, my family celebrating my 70 th birthday. We had a fantastic night, the food, service and entertainment was excellent. Would love to go there every weekend."]}
