{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r314352928", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great atmosphere", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "28 September 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Garylisap,", "Thank you for taking the time to review us. The band you mentioned are one of my favourites, I'm so pleased you enjoyed it!", "Keep an eye out for some amazing acts coming up, Dire Straits will be fabulous on 21st November! We now have a new ticket available for some of our shows that includes 2 courses and the music. I hope you will come and see us again soon.", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt"], "reviewer_pseudo": "garylisap", "reviewer_origin": ["Rainham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r314352928-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A little pricey but good food, wine and music.", "Serpentine Fire an Earth, Wind and Fire tribute band excellent!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r315020261", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Elvis Presley tribute act", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "30 September 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jean P", "reviewer_origin": ["Romford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r315020261-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Service was first class. Food was delicious - perfectly cooked and served.", "The entertainment was brilliant.", "A really thoroughly enjoyable evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r317008116", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Very enjoyable, would happy dine here again", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "8 October 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "redversjones", "reviewer_origin": ["Bexleyheath, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "38"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r317008116-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My fiance and I went for Sunday lunch and it really was very enjoyable indeed.", "The service was very pleasant (including not looking down their noses at an Amazon Local voucher which can sometimes happen) and staff attentive but not in-your-face about it.", "The venue and live jazz music was very much to my taste - background music so you didn't feel like you were eating during a show at all, and altogether rather enjoyable.", "As for the food. Well like any Brit live for a good Sunday Roast. Oh boy, this was good. Very good. Top top marks on the food front, really top marks - and I've been out for a lot of roast dinners!", "My only downside, and it really is a minor one, is the cutlery. This may sound silly but they were using very nice old cutlery, i think old silverware (though i'm not expert). The downside is that it was mightily blunt, making even the most tenderly-cooked of meats more of a pulling match than cutting. ", "Overally a highly enjoyable experience and I will definitely be returning."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r306587512", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Huge potential but falling short ", "diner_date": " July 2015", "rating_date": "3 September 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Toolbag", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "276"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "178"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r306587512-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Love the idea of this place, clubby, mixing good music with good music. Unfortunately this venue seems to fall short, food and drink while good ends up being a seriously expensive experience, from a number of visits our bill is always way more than we're expecting, and doesn't reflect in the quality of the food and service. The service in our experience is chaotic at best, they always seem to be short of numbers, hence 15 min+ waits not uncommon for service items. ", "The venue itself is very cool and well designed, although sound quality seems to be an issue, as Band noise drowns out conversation totally (this may be the Banks issue with poor venue speakers, or maybe the acoustics of the venue itself).", "Plenty of potential here, hopefully feedback will help sharpen this amazing potential venue. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r306944003", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Blues and Dinner - a great way to celebrate", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "4 September 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Duncan,", "Thank you very much for your great review! It is so lovely to hear positive feedback from our guests. Please see the link below to an act you might like. Do let me know if you'd like to come and I'll happily make the arrangements for you. I look forward to welcoming you back in the near future. ", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt,", "General manager", "http://tickets.boisdale.co.uk/pages/events/blues--boogie-woogie-and-beyond--errol-linton-and-his-band/12-11-2015/"], "reviewer_pseudo": "duncan s", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "115"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "32"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r306944003-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I was given dinner and concert tickets for my birthday. It was a great night. The food was excellent and Mike Vernon and his Mighty Combo put on a great show. The haggis starter was simply wonderful. One small disappointed was the lack of information about the timing of the show. It would have been helpful to have the details on the tickets. But this is a wonderful location and we will keep an eye out for future blues artiste so we can go back and sample more of the wonderful food."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r305995580", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "I'll swing with it...", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "1 September 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Sm4llb1ts", "reviewer_origin": ["London, England, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "97"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "53"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r305995580-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale's Canary Wharf is a stones throw from my place of work so I've been here on a few occasions for the odd social drink and a meal. It always seemed okay and so with an evening dinner with friends to organise I looked into booking a table for 8 people. At the time that I initially looked into this they had several large round tables available but sadly when I finally got confirmation to book they had already gone. What held me back was that certain table locations warrant a different entertainment price which depending on location and act can vary. Entertainment is optional though, but if you choose not to partake you'll be expected to vacate the floor which may mean a rushed meal. So getting to the point we ended up with a straight table for 8 people at a premium of \u00a320pp for a decent act. The table was half way down the restaurant which wasn't that bad, but I wouldn't say it was the most comfortable I've had, with it being slightly cramped.", "As for the meal itself, hmmm! Certain dishes were worth the money, others not, with cost outstripping what you actually got on the plate. I personally think a steak should come with at least some veg and not simply on it's own with veg at an additional cost, a venison curry dish was also met with raised eyebrows, the meat content meagre in our personal view. Other than that most other dishes seemed adequate in quantity, but I thought the presentation of my Haggis main was a little poor. For the overall monetary outlay the meal was simply average, it didn't wow you. Saying that I would go again only because the overall experience of meal, entertainment and service was okay. So as the title says i'll swing with it and give it another go at another time, but i'd recommend it to be a consideration for yourself.", "Just to add, there is no specific dress code, we were smart casual and relaxed formal, but there were also people dressed more glamourously as well as those in jeans and trainers, albeit smart ones. And once the entertainment is in full flow conversation becomes a bit of an issue if you're intent on chatting rather than listening to the music. Oh and they need to learn what a Floater Coffee is, I can't describe what I got."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r307543298", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Light Jazz and a hearty meal", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "6 September 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Keith,", "Thank you so much for your review. I am always delighted to receive positive feedback and congratulate the team on their hard work. I hope you will come and visit us again and that I will be able to thank you personally for your kind words. ", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Keith B", "reviewer_origin": ["Orange N.s.w"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "52"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r307543298-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for a Sunday lunch and enjoyed the afternoon immensely. 3 course lunch with drinks was not what you would call cheap but the ambiance, Live Jazz playing in the background, and the food was worth the \u00a3220 for 4 bill. Decor fitted the restaurant theme as well some of the menu options. Staff were excellent and helped with menu and drinks choices. A pleasant afternoon ."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r315082288", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Simply the best business dinner in the wharf", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "30 September 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ExtremeMountainsport", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r315082288-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I always go here with business for drinks before a sumptuous meal, whisky or rum, jazz and then cigars. Food, Alcohol, Wine selection ambiance and over all feeling is great here."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r312184456", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Disappointing", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "20 September 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Sue T,", "Thank you for your review. I am so sorry to hear we let you down on Sunday. I would very much like to hear more about your lunch. May I ask you to email me so we can discuss the meal. I hope to hear from you soon,", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt", "General manager", "gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk"], "reviewer_pseudo": "9SueT", "reviewer_origin": ["Chislehurst, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "55"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r312184456-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Having eaten at Boisdale before, I was looking forward to returning; meeting with a group of friends making us a party of 8. Today's visit was very disappointing. The food was little better than average - having ordered the roast beef and informed it was medium rare or well done, I went for the medium rare. When it arrived if was difficult to cut and very chewy! A pot of roast potatoes came separately with the meal and other vegetables were delivered to the table but without serving spoons. Waiting staff made lots of mistakes and seemed to be inexperienced. A great shame - the venue is lovely and my previous visit had left a completely different memory to that of today."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r310791762", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "I think you will enjoy your evening here!", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "15 September 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Jacqueline,", "Thank you very much for your lovely review! It is so nice to receive positive feedback from our guests. I do hope you will come and see us again very soon. I would like to welcome you back in person. ", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt"], "reviewer_pseudo": "263jacqueline", "reviewer_origin": ["Nottingham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r310791762-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["So cool! Great restaurant design, food, drinks and of course music. Perfect place for almost any occasion"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r307816664", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Food, Jazz, Cigars and the wall of Whiskey", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "7 September 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "It is a pleasure to receive such a great review, thank you. Our team work really hard to provide a great experience for our customers and it is always lovely get positive feedback. I do hope to meet you on your next visit and thank you in person. ", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt,", "General manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Adrien P", "reviewer_origin": ["Chertsey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "96"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "52"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r307816664-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["If you're looking for a great Oyster/Whiskey/Cigar bar, with a fantastic menu and amazing jazz repertoire - then look no further!", "Boisdale is an amazing gem, snuggled in the high rise buildings of Canary wharf.", "What's not to like about this place! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r308725628", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Worth a outing", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "9 September 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Libby,", "Thank you for taking the time to review us. I'm glad your overall experience was positive and sincerely apologise if our service let us down. Please do come back and enjoy our live music on the second floor. The menu you initially booked for is available on our second floor where you can enjoy the live music. Do let me know when you plan to return and I can make the booking for you and ensure you are well looked after. I hope to welcome you back soon,", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt", "General manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Libby436", "reviewer_origin": ["Bristol, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "89"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "45"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r308725628-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I have been wanting to get up to this place for last couple of weeks. I booked a deal on trip advisor and went to the first floor bar. ", "On arrival I was given a nice table. It is as lively and had a very casual easy going atmosphere. Some people were dining, some just for drinks, some even just popping in for pudding- so all sorts. ", "I decided not to pick from the open table menu but instead off their daily two course special. This was great value at \u00a312 - but remember service charge is automatically added. ", "I had the salmon/ gravelaxe starter, I asked for bread- which came immediately. For main I selected the sausage special of the day.the food was good, good portions- especially the main and proved excellent value for what I thought would be a very expensive place. ", "There was no jazz when I was there but I would try and return for a jazz night. ", "I thought the service is as a bit haphazard and certainly slow- at one point I think my main could have been forgotten! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r310957462", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Average Burger", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "16 September 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "essex1london", "reviewer_origin": ["london"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "103"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "52"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r310957462-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The food here was just ok service was again just ok feel it lacked atmosphere.My burger was very average my friend had one of the home made pies which she said was nice. Generally we found this place over priced especially the drinks"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r312082332", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Just Stunning", "diner_date": " September 2015", "rating_date": "20 September 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Mr ODonnell,", "What a lovely review, thank you so much! Have you thought about becoming a member of Boisdale? I'd be very happy to talk about it with you on your next visit. We look forward to welcoming you back soon.", "Kind regards,", "Elisabeth Rutt", "General manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ODonnell-Stephen", "reviewer_origin": ["Stratford City, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "200"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "91"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r312082332-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I love Boisdale - all three of them are fantastic. Canary Wharf has a great outside balcony for drinks on a long summer night and a huge bar area. The food is to die for, do not miss the Haggis, the Steaks or the Seafood. Great selection of wine and booze. Amazing waitresses all dressed up in lovely kilts."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r302921848", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Who knew a cigar library could excite me!", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "24 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Clara_Tamburrino", "reviewer_origin": ["Milton Keynes, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r302921848-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Spent the evening here after my partner proposed. I would usually find this overpriced environment a little poncey but i had a great night and really enjoyed sampling some of the cigars, whiskey and champagne on the terrace."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r305115594", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Lovely atmosphere but average food", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "30 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Gigixo", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "37"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r305115594-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Came here for a birthday dinner and drinks, the service was brilliant and music was great. However the food was so average we were all quite disappointed. The steak had no taste even smothered in peppercorn sauce it had no flavour! Really surprised as Ive always thought boisdale would have a high quality of food. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r302806556", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Such a fabulous ambience and great staff", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "24 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "590RebeccaM590", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "101"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "72"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r302806556-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I came here on a recommendation from a friend, who loves the idea of a Scottish menu. We ate in the restaurant upstairs and had such a fantastic time. As soon as you walk up into the dining room you're presented with a glittering bar, ambient candlelight, and fabulous decor - think tongue-in-cheek taxidermy and portraits dotted around the walls. The waiting staff are all incredibly knowledgable, very helpful, and we loved the kitsch tartan touches to the uniform. Big praise to our waitress Christina who was superb and managed to remember every single cheese on the trolley! (this latter feature is another reason it's a must visit place). We went for a birthday dinner, and got chatting to the table next to us, where a couple were celebrating their thirty year anniversary. When the live music starts it gets even better - definitely a quality place to visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r305819653", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic Food, Great Service", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "1 September 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Londoner1991", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "27"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r305819653-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited the Oyster Bar & Grill section of this restaurant and was pleasantly surprised. From the name of the place I was expecting an american diner type experience which was not the case at all. I had purchased the steak & lobster deal from Groupon and went with reasonably low expectations as I was told i would not be in the main restaurant section as this would cost an extra \u00a320. However when I arrived, the Bar & Grill was still great. The steak had fantastic flavour and the Lobster was cooked perfectly. Also, I would definitely recommend the sticky toffee pudding! Will be returning 100%"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r304003425", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Anniversary", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "27 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Naomi B", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r304003425-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great little gem in Canary Wharf. Food was fab- big steak couldn't finish it, the waiter gladly packed the rest for me to takeaway. Live jazz was great although if you sit right at the front of the stage you won't be able to have a decent convo.", "Romantic setting with candles and dimmed lights.", "Went for our wedding anniversary and was given a sticky toffee pudding on the house! ", "Very sweet of them. ", "Overall great night!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r305129025", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent food, music and atmosphere", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "30 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MrThomas1981", "reviewer_origin": ["Ipswich, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "533"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "225"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r305129025-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Was really sceptical about this to start with, having grown up in the 80's and learned at school how Canary Wharf was developed as a 'yuppie playground', I was really unsure that this ousted be anything other than a bit pretentious. I couldn't have been more wrong, the staff were attentive, the food superb and the Jazz band absolutely brilliant. If you are a whisky connoisseur, they have the largest collection of single malts in Europe according to our waiter but be warned that some can cost up to \u00a3500 a shot! A lovely way to spend an evening - particularly an anniversary or birthday."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r304497784", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great night out!", "diner_date": " June 2015", "rating_date": "28 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "restlessbums", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "117"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "77"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r304497784-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a great night out with live 80s music and awesome food! There is a charge for the music which i don't believe is optional. Would recommend this place when in london. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r305446966", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Disappointing service", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "31 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "CamelotKidLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "52"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "20", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r305446966-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale is my guilty secret. We try and go as much as we can because its pricey but I will pay for good food, good music and good service. I have been twice in the last couple of weeks and both times the service has been below par. I did not write a reveiw last time due to money being taken off the bill and all my other great night. I went again last Saturday and again we had to wait for 25 minutes just to order, our waiter was trying hard to make everyone happy running between tables but could not keep up. The table next to were waiting longer both of our tables he apoligised, the table to my left called the waiter over to say that his food had been left on a small table to go cold. We were so disapointed that we decided to go after we recieved our food and not stay for the whole of the show. The floor manager recognised us and asked if we were ok, we told her no and that we feel that they are about 3-4 members of staff short. A previous floor manager ( Glen) went around checking on tables, pouring drinks and making diners happy, now the floor managers serve to keep up with demand. We have decided to have a rest from Boisdales for a while."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r305437922", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good food, jazz, but noisey neighbours", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "31 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "WoodyFleet", "reviewer_origin": ["Hampshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "155"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "62"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r305437922-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Good atmosphere and entertainment with very good food (albeit a bit pricey) but do beware the waiter trying to push up the bill by encouraging you to buy high priced drinks", "We had a very enjoyable evening and would go again, the only downside being that we had a table near us with three very noisy drunken young guys with little respect for their fellow diners or the entertainers. ", "I can only put this down to it's proximity to the financial district bringing in a few noisy people with too much money and too little culture. I can't imagine them being tolerated at Ronnie Scotts, where they would have been shown the door. To be fair one waitress did ask them to quieten down but they still interfered with the first half"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r305483976", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Second floor is nicer than first floor", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "31 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "EeyoreTravel", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "109"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "80"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r305483976-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a Groupon voucher \u00a349, steak & lobster plus glass of prosecco each. Which is a good price. ", "We booked for a table at 6:30pm but arrived at 6pm, the waiter are more than happy for us to take a seat and let us choose our own table. ", "Good we were early, as looking at others surrounding us, their food took ages to come. The waiter did say there were 58 people that evening who were using the Groupon voucher for dinner service. ", "We ordered a side dish, bottle of water, desert and a glass of red which bill came to \u00a335 which we thought was a bit pricey. ", "Dinner was served on first floor, after dinner we went upstairs to get our parking ticket verified, and realised second floor atmosphere seemed much better than downstairs, might want to give this place a try instead, as looks even nicer. ", "Food was cooked nicely, but felt lobster had been over cooked. However with me asking for medium rare and my hubby requested medium, the steak was cooked to perfection :)", "All in all, food was good, but we had to wait for very long time for service, and you can so tell the staff a very new. ", "I would like to try dining upstairs on second floor next time."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r298971059", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Okay food...terrible service", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "13 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "579danielh", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r298971059-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We sat in the bar area and the first issue was that the music meant any conversation was impossible. The service was poor from the start. Ordering was slow and surly and the plates were collected before the whole group had finished. The food was okay at best (burgers were only available medium well or well done) but not worth the poor service. Boisdale feels as if it would be fine if you were a member, but if not don't expect them to treat you well. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r300262159", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fabulous", "diner_date": " July 2015", "rating_date": "17 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Maryrose2014", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r300262159-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Brought a voucher on groupon for this resturant because we wanted to go somewhere different. This place is very different, in a good way. Really nice decor, really nice staff. The food was superb& value for money. Would definatly go back. And recommend this resturant to anyone."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r297298063", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent!", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "9 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Sherbie25", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r297298063-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My boyfriend and myself ate here using a Groupon deal. We had a rib eye steak and half lobster each, with chips and a glass of prosecco. The service was excellent; attentive and efficient (compared to a restaurant I have recently reviewed). The medium steak was perfectly cooked and the lobster meaty and juicy. We ate outside on the terrace which was very pleasant. It would be expensive without a deal but you get what you pay for. Will definitely be booking here again. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r301936066", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Very good set lunch", "diner_date": " June 2015", "rating_date": "21 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Matt2525", "reviewer_origin": ["Chandler\u2019s Ford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "187"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "311"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r301936066-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Have been here a couple of times for lunch.", "Access is upstairs from the shopping centre using either the stairs of the lift.", "They have a good 2 course lunch menu and the food has always been really good. ", "Love the mini haggis!", "Reasonable prices too.", "Service always impeccable."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r300539271", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fantastic Food - At A Price...", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "18 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Patricia H", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r300539271-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We ate here for our wedding anniversary and the food was fantastic. The steak were exceptionally tender. The green salad had a trace of dill running through it which was fresh and tasty. Followed this with a small cheese platter between the 2 of us. There was a wide tasty choice of cheese.", "The prices, however, do leave a bitter taste in the mouth. Being charged extra because a jazz band was going to play, even though we had finished before they started was unacceptable. 2 x steak and chips, 1 salad, 1 small cheese platter and a mid-range bottle of wine...\u00a3180.", "Coffee with a port for me, a whisky (the cheapest on the menu) and a small cigar was another \u00a370. ", "While we had a fantastic evening, next year we'll go away for a weekend instead!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r298225500", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A lovely evening", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "12 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MsVictoria", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "193"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "185"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r298225500-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Having been disappointed on previous visits we were a little hesitant to return but we had a really lovely evening.", "The ma\u00eetre d' was from the Belgravia restaurant and what a great character.", "Service was good, our waiter was new but you wouldn't know it. He was very good and a credit to the restaurant.", "All our courses were spot on and very tasty. The drinks were all good and we loved the cocktails.", "The live band really made the evening, they were fabulous.", "I do hope the restaurant can keep us this high standard for our next visit as based on this evening we will return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r296896734", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Little Scotland ", "diner_date": " September 2014", "rating_date": "8 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "1894dnk", "reviewer_origin": ["Barcelona, Spain"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "76"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r296896734-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Took my mother a number of times to the Boisdale . Fantastic especially amongst all that London has to offer. Great Friday and Saturday night haunt. Whiskey and cigars as a digestif. Really enjoyed a great experience there will most certainly return....... Music and entertainment was really enjoyable couldn't have been happier ."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r301867533", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Wonderful evening ", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "21 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Lorraine F", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r301867533-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked for the deal with a glass of sparkling wine, steak & lobster with strawberries to finish and enjoyed the whole experience. Beautiful decor, attentive staff and a 5 piece band to entertain you. Would definitely return, great for couples or groups on a celebration."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r301924598", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely meal", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "21 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "hcb81", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "65"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r301924598-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We ate here a few nights ago, dining from the set menu. It was good value for money and the food was lovely. Enormous portions too. My steak was huge! They do music too but we dined early and were sleepy so didn't stay for that unfortunately. The service was also excellent, attentive but not over-bearing."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r300765746", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Pleasant atmosphere", "diner_date": " July 2015", "rating_date": "18 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "NERV10", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r300765746-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great place to dine while music is played live. Great quality of food and service is attentive. Not noisy and enough space to discuss business while appreciating the vibe. Plenty of selection of drinks of that's what you are after."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r292533032", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Go for the food, Go for the music, Go for the cigar bar", "diner_date": " July 2015", "rating_date": "26 July 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "aadamopoulos67", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "234"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "156"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r292533032-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Just go - we love Boisdale in Canary Wharf. The food is just basic yet satisfying. The top floor dining experience is something we enjoy each time - great cocktails, wine and whiskey selection. They bring in very talented musicians and the service is attentive. We also love to go after dinner elsewhere to have a drink and cigar. They offer a covered outdoor balcony terrace and it is a great way to end an evening with friends. They also have an indoor cigar bar with a decent selection."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r291022972", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "An Amazing Night", "diner_date": " July 2015", "rating_date": "21 July 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Salamander1986", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "66"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "46"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r291022972-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked tickets at the Boisdale specifically to see Si Cranstoun perform. We paid \u00a350 each for the ticket/table reservation (including a goodie bag). I wouldn't pay the premium rate in the future (this was for a special occasion) as the band can be seen and heard well from further back - tickets were from \u00a320, and you could probably just book a table for dinner and enjoy the music, as there were a couple of spare tables.", "Anyhow, we had an amazing time. Si Cranstoun and the band were amazing and had half the restaurant up dancing by the end. The music started just before 10pm, and finished around midnight with a 20 minute interval.", "The service was excellent - our waiter Jon-Luca deserves a special mention for being very polite, friendly and attentive throughout the night.", "The food was very nice - I can highly recommend the haggis starter (despite not having tried haggis before...) and the steaks are melt in the mouth. The drinks were also lovely, although the cocktails are certainly on the strong side! However, the place is not cheap - we spent almost \u00a3200 on a three course meal and drinks (not including the cost of the tickets).", "The dress code wasn't as formal as we expected. Some men were wearing suits, but many were just in open necked shirts and trousers. Similarly, women don't need formal evening dress, just to look reasonably smart. We were a little apprehensive about the evening (not being accustomed to fine dining in Canary Wharf!), but were made to feel at ease and very much enjoyed the experience. Thoroughly recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r291633428", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "tres Bon. Service lent.", "diner_date": " July 2015", "rating_date": "23 July 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "cathsteve2002", "reviewer_origin": ["Tampa, Florida"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r291633428-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very nice restaurant. Good food. The service was quite slow. They have a nice terrace, so it is a great place to spend time with friends."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r287055387", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Beautiful evening", "diner_date": " July 2015", "rating_date": "9 July 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "wiggyv", "reviewer_origin": ["London, UK"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r287055387-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked for a Bob Marley Tribute & was a little dubious but shouldn't have worried. An amazing class act form 'The Legends'.", "Food was really delicious. Perfect size portions if enjoying a 3 course meal. Starters- Scallops were divine and potted shrimp was plentiful. Mains- My husband said the truffle burger was a bit too thick and not all flavours came through but he still enjoyed it. Pasta with pecorino, broad beans and pea shoots was beautiful light and more than enough. Dessert- Sticky toffee pudding had the lightest touch but would have been better with ice cream and not clotted cream. Cheesecake with strawberries and basil was small, perfectly formed, but the right amount. Very flavourful. Great price too. 3 courses, 1 side, water, mocktail & one alcohol drink all just under \u00a3100 inc 12.5%. Nice service.", "Slight negative....we were completely forgotten at the beginning of our meal for 25 minutes while more 'favourable' customers, who arrived after us, were fully served before us!!! Was later kindly offered a table with better stage view but we stayed at our lovely table. I think at least a free drink could've been taken off the bill considering they still included their service charge! Overall we had a lovely evening and will definitely return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r292685126", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Poor experience and would not return anytime soon", "diner_date": " July 2015", "rating_date": "26 July 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "RJB1000", "reviewer_origin": ["UK"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "211"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "170"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r292685126-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I came here with a colleague and a client a couple of weeks ago.", "I'd had been to the Bishopsgate restaurant and here for lunch previously. This time I visited for dinner and it wasn't good. The restraurant was very quiet and my colleague was first to arrive, what was nice though is they served him some lovely canapes at the bar as he was waiting. I wish I had ordered a platter of them as they tasted far better than the food I had.", "Ordered haggis as a starter, it was terrible; dry overcooked and tasted terrible I told the waitress as I left most of it. Then came the seafood gratin one of the most ill conceived dishes a chef can create, suffice to say it was poor. Then around 10 the jazz started which for a couple of musicians it was just too loud for a 25% full room. ", "The next day I could still feel the food lying on me, I won't be coming back here anytime soon and it taught me a valuable lesson, don't bother trying to have a decent meal in Canary Wharf. I've been a few times and yet to find somewhere any good."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r296606855", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "What's not to like !", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "7 August 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "67mccann", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r296606855-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Love this place, have lunch and drinks regularly on the 1st floor, the food is great and really reasonably priced, the set menu changes weekly. The best thing about Boisdale is the staff, always efficient and friendly even when the place is packed in the evening. The outside Terrace is an added bonus not to mention the cigar shop....... What's not to like! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r285703914", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Food, Jazz and fine Cigars", "diner_date": " April 2015", "rating_date": "5 July 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Phiri_Piri", "reviewer_origin": ["Surrey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "54"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "29"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r285703914-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A nice place to meet with friends and enjoy fine dining and music, No to mention fine cigars to add to the experience. Offers outside seating on the Terrace and a nice drinks list."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r293701672", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Nice enough but nothing special", "diner_date": " July 2015", "rating_date": "29 July 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Essextraveller52", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "94"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "65"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r293701672-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["If you like very noisy restaurants with average food and overpriced drinks this is the place for you. Even allowing for London prices the cocktails were very small for the inflated price.", "We certainly won't hurry back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r293042018", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Peacepics ", "diner_date": " July 2015", "rating_date": "27 July 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "peacepics", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r293042018-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This place is absolutely great. ", "The service the food and the entertainment spot on. ", "The cigars and whisky are very good I would recommend visiting this place for a great night out. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r296200196", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Very disappointing - Terrible service, would not return", "diner_date": " August 2015", "rating_date": "6 August 2015", "answer_text": ["Please email me to discuss your dining experience further Katie@boisdale.co.uk"], "reviewer_pseudo": "fo165", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r296200196-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I went to Boisdale yesterday with a colleague and friend for dinner. Firstly, the carpets from the entrance and stairs leading into the restaurant on the second floor had a stale smell. At the entrance, a lady promptly informed us that there would be a \u00a34.50 charge added to our bill to cover the cost of listening to the jazz musician. She then told us to walk in and pick our own table?! - at a restaurant? ", "We walked into the restaurant and sat at a table at 7.47pm. About two-thirds of the tables were empty and we observed 4 different waiters rushing around in a hurry. After waiting for 15 minutes, We tried to catch the attention of a waiter with no success. ", "The atmosphere was very odd. We then saw 4 people at one of the tables get up from their table (at the restaurant), and leave, carrying their glasses and bottles of wine out of the restaurant. Probably fed up waiting for service. ", "At 8.15pm, we still had not been approached by any of the waiters or given menus, so we got up and left after waiting for almost half an hour. ", "This restaurant has the worst service or should I just say \"no service\", and appears to be really short staffed. All the staff we observed yesterday, just looked so stressed and exhausted.. including the lady at the door. ", "I would not go back again or recommend to anyone. If I could, I would give 0 stars on the basis of zero service in half an hour."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r281595869", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Terrific", "diner_date": " June 2015", "rating_date": "20 June 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "PatrickH284", "reviewer_origin": ["Hong Kong, China"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "850"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "267"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r281595869-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Missed my flight and had a couple of hours to kill. The outside terrace is wonderful as were the selection of oysters, wine and a cigar. Latvian lady who served me, believe her name was Eva, was excellent. Will return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r283647990", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Perfect when you need to impress!", "diner_date": " June 2015", "rating_date": "28 June 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Midoriya", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "186"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "117"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r283647990-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited here for combined birthdays as a group of 10. From the start separate lift to go up to the restaurant, walking to reception area full of leather seats and art work to have your drink before lunch. Once everyone is ready walking to your table looking up to the impressive bar full of Scottish wiskeies crowned with a head of wild pig. Waiting staff were all very professional in friendly way. From the bread from the beginning to birthday cake at the end, all the food was very good! If I have to mention something, it is warm coffee I thought was less than avarage compared to good, strong tea in a pot. Also there were 5-6 birthdays, making it bit like \"yes, today we dug deep and came to celebrate!\" stated all round, but what can I say? Yes, if you have your family visitors to impress in London looking over all the new buildings such as cheese grater, etc, to the background jazz, it's a perfect place, but you need a budget of about \u00a350/person for three course, which may not be too bad in London."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r281338513", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Outstanding lunch -now I have been to all three Boisdales and loved them all", "diner_date": " June 2015", "rating_date": "19 June 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "GroundedKiwi", "reviewer_origin": ["High Wycombe, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "176"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "116"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r281338513-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I had a business lunch with an old colleague. Boisdales Canary Wharf has the design and charm of the other two, more old school, sites...although I did find having a view over Canary Wharf a little different - the sunlight came as a shock.", "The menu is the same wonderful listing of a modern twist on traditional greatness. I had the lamb...which was off the charts great. My guest had the seafood linguini which also went down well. The service was just the right side of close.", "I have always found Canary Wharf to be a hard place to find a great meal - no more."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r285459767", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Scottish interior with latin terrace.", "diner_date": " July 2015", "rating_date": "4 July 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Albanthiery", "reviewer_origin": ["Manchester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "135"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "44"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r285459767-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went there with some colleagues to celebrate the end of the year. The place has an impressive wine list. However, we opted for cocktails and a bottle of ros\u00e9 Champagne. The atmosphere is really good and the service a bit slow at first, but as soon as we ordered the Champagne, we had all their attention!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r280411193", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fabulous night! ", "diner_date": " June 2015", "rating_date": "15 June 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Deborah S", "reviewer_origin": ["Hartlepool, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r280411193-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited on Saturday evening after booking in March. Having read a few negative reviews I'm wondering if those people actually ate here or are only happy when finding fault with something. We arrived to a friendly welcome and were shown directly to our table. Actually couldn't have been happier with where we sat, third table from the stage with plenty of room around us. We enjoyed G&T's while we chose our food and wine. I had the dressed crab which was light and delicious, and hubby had the Haggis with a noggin of whisky. Igor, our amazing waiter, popping up every now and then to refill our wine glasses. For main course I had the salmon with squid and chorizo risotto. It was cooked to perfection and incredibly tasty. I ordered buttered baby potatoes to go with it but needn't have bothered as the dish was beautiful enough on its own. Phil had ribeye steak which tasted amazing, was cooked exactly how he'd asked and just melted in his mouth. We finished our main courses just in time for the band to start playing. Iain Mackenzie and Swing City, a Sinatra and friends tribute band. They were brilliant! We ordered a selection of cheeses and more drinks which we enjoyed listening to the band. We had the BEST night!! The food was great, the band was great, the drinks were great, the bill was a pleasant surprise and Igor was better than great :)) It's lovely to go somewhere and not have to think about whether you fancy another drink because your waiter pre-empted you! ", "To eat in a lovely restaurant while listening/dancing to a live Swing band is something that is on my bucket list, and now I can tick it off. Pleased to say I don't think we could have chosen a better place and have to say that Igor made it even better. Thank you Boisdale, two very happy customers! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r283546849", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Another great visit", "diner_date": " June 2015", "rating_date": "28 June 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Duane1965", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r283546849-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Another great time at this venue. Cannot fault the service you receive, the waiters and waitress are so well trained. food was great too. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r281005571", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Eximious place", "diner_date": " June 2015", "rating_date": "17 June 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Almajaris", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r281005571-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Absolutly amazing place to have dinner or some drinks while enjoying yourself with a live show. My girlfriend and I bought an offert on the Internet to have some cocktails at the restaurant while we enjoyed some live music. They knew we were going to have some drinks with a couple of vouchers and the staff treatment was absoulutly nice, as if we were going to spend as much money as the guys from the nearest table.", "We had four cocktails each, really good flavour. We enjoyed the live show, a band playing some soul music. The stuff looked after us the whole time, really polite and with excellent manners. Even the manager came to ask if everything was alright with us, and for sure it was. ", "We didn't go to the restaurant to have dinner but after that we regretted after seeing the menu and the food. It was not as expensive as we thought, you can get good food for a really nice price. And have a nice time with your couple or with your friends. ", "In short, tasty drinks, good location, and the most important thing, excellent staff."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r284853950", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great night spent catching up with friends", "diner_date": " June 2015", "rating_date": "1 July 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Triggle", "reviewer_origin": ["Luddesdown, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "27"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r284853950-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["decided to go somewhere we could actually here each other speak, nice menu, starters were plentiful a we shared they were so big ", "Mains lived up to expectations and there was a very reasonable wine list ", "All in all a really lovely evening would recommend it"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r284774044", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great location and theme", "diner_date": " July 2015", "rating_date": "1 July 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Charisma5", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "74"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r284774044-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Food was ok, probably just above average for the price. The steak was a nice piece of meat and well cooked. ", "Cheese board was extensive but it depends on what you choose. ", "Overall cost was a little expensive and results in a lower star rating. Outlook over the Wharf is a big plus point"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r284509302", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Sunday Carvery", "diner_date": " May 2015", "rating_date": "30 June 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Stuart C", "reviewer_origin": ["Piedmont, California"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r284509302-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["One of the great things to do in the UK on a Sunday is have a carver lunch. Roast beef, Yorkshire pudding, roasted potatoes, and gravy. If it is done well it is spectacular -- done poorly, you will have so suffer through dense Yorkshire pudding, lumpy gravy, tough meat, and greasy potatoes.", "The problem is to know where to go because nearly every pub will throw something together to attract the tourists and, like I said, it can be miserable.", "The Sunday Carvery at Boisdale Canary Wharf is fantastic! Everything about it is great but the enormous, light and fluffy Yorkshire pudding steals the show. If you can manage it, you can get a second slice of roast beef.", "I had a martini to start which was very nice. The service is fantastic and it is easy to get to via the tube."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r278951909", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Friday night burger", "diner_date": " May 2015", "rating_date": "9 June 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Sophonthemove", "reviewer_origin": ["Berkhamsted, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "304"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "99"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r278951909-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Ate in here on a Friday evening with friends. There is I understand a more formal restaurant and menu upstairs and a brasserie style in the bar area.", "I had the inferno hamburger with a spicy scotch egg and both were excellent. I had a couple of glasses of the Merlot and this made for a great accompaniment.", "The service was nice, I don't remember it being too attentive or lacking. I thought the menu was good value and it is available on their website with the prices.", "I would certainly dine in the Brasserie section again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r272787186", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Late night drinks", "diner_date": " May 2015", "rating_date": "18 May 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "S17London", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "143"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r272787186-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We ended up in here in search for late drink after an evening out with friends. We weren't dining so skipped the restaurant which had tables laid for meals facing toward a a small stage. We went downstairs to the bar and enjoyed cocktails, beer and wine - all well received by their recipients. The music upstairs was loud enough for us to decide that we weren't feeling we were missing out - not to my taste. Nuff said.", "The bar is ok but the decor on the whole is bizarre - very loud tartan carpet! I'm not personally in a rush to return here. I think I would explore some of the neighbouring area and find an alternative venue."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r273045283", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Nice food and Wine/Atmosphere..but why the hurry?", "diner_date": " May 2015", "rating_date": "19 May 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "sandfordpj", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r273045283-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Recently visited this restaurant on Saturday 9th,first visit as it was a special occasion and had booked early in the week.", "The menu wasn't extensive,but there was a good variety,we had a Crab starter which was very small(\u00a315) and Carpaccio of Venison(\u00a310),main was Lamb(\u00a327) and Chicken Pie(\u00a316) which was again small with additional portions of veg..the wine was ok and desserts lovely..cocktails to begin with weren't the best,biggest gripe about the night was the service,upon entry we were told to see the band would have been an additional charge which we didn't know when booked(\u00a310),the waitress wasn't sure on what the specials were and the waiters seemed to be very new as they looked like they were being shadowed,the whole service was hurried,courses arrived literally as soon as the previous one had finished,no breathing space in between,once courses had been eaten table seemed to be invisible,trying to pay took a while,the venue itself was really relaxing and could easily have spent more time there and stayed to see the act(Frank Sinartra Tribute) if had known in advance,did have a cocktail downstairs in the lounge which was nice.Cost \u00a3180 for 2 which as a special treat was expensive and probably would go again but there are better options in the area."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r274224793", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The Perfect Saturday Night", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "24 May 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LaraE14", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "99"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "47"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r274224793-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My Boyfriend and I visited the restaurant last evening, he is obsessed with the offer. On line, Amazon, groupon etc... I am not because generally the restaurant give you a 3rd class service when you are visiting with that deal! But yesterday it didn't happen at all!", "Since the first minute that we walked into the venue we felt really welcome from the staff. They offered us a really nice table overlooking the fountains in Cabot Square, and they were very attentive to our needs.", "In Particular an Italian girl, Elisa.", "She also suggested us to visit the Jazz ", "Venue upstairs and she offered to book a table ! We were too tired but we will definitely coming back!", "Thank you for the amazing evening! Also the food was exceeding our expectations !", "Lara and Abbey"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r277264484", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Special place", "diner_date": " April 2015", "rating_date": "2 June 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Natan53", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "162"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "50"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r277264484-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I've never been in a place like this. The restaurant can hold approximately 300 people, but the costumer is served at the table as if he/she is the only one in the main hall.", "We enjoyed a really special service, we drank Champagne (reccommended By my niece, a sommelier), Two great wines (one from Argentina and another from Germany) and at the end we chose a whisky from the biggest wall composed of high quality bottles, that I ever seen!!", "The men\u00f9 was interesting and various, I can remember a great risotto and a great selection of cheeses with Passito... It was just perfect.", "The Price is quite high (70 per person), but it worth every pound."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r273935551", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic quality of food, wished we'd found this place before!", "diner_date": " May 2015", "rating_date": "23 May 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "JCshenfield", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "73"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "51"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r273935551-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were a party of 6 celebrating a couple of birthdays, we arrived at 7pm and the place was fairly empty which meant we were given a great table for the entertainment (later). Cocktails were very good. Didn't know what to expect food wise, however the food was fantastic, the quality and taste/texture of the beef was amazing, a huge surprise. After a couple of bottles of excellent Malbec the entertainment (soul band) started which was great also, which culminated with most people dancing up by the band, we left about midnight, a great night. Bill for 2 approx GBP 220"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r274219726", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Snobbish staff and poor quality meals", "diner_date": " May 2015", "rating_date": "24 May 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "rini9", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "46"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r274219726-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for dinner as a walk-in on a Thursday night. Our waiter was very pretentious and talked down to me (I'm not sure if this is because we didn't book or because we had come straight from work whilst it looked like some others had dressed up especially for dinner?)- either way it was unacceptable and put a massive dampener on the evening. ", "I ordered the chicken and mushroom pie which literally had only 2 tiny pieces of chicken in it- the rest was mushroom and dry pastry. Not great for \u00a320. There was a surcharge of \u00a330 for the 4 of us for the live jazz that stated at 9.15pm which was ok given we were told when we entered. ", "Will definitely not be returning which is a shame given we live a 5 minute walk away and the actual restaurant looks very nice."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r278207907", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good place for a upmarket business meeting", "diner_date": " June 2015", "rating_date": "6 June 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "E H", "reviewer_origin": ["Tunbridge Wells, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r278207907-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A vendor took me to Boisdale for dinner.", "The greeting was a bit pompous, but when we got to the table the atmosphere was very good and the table staff excellent.", "The menu, especially the starters where very fish orientated. There are some vegetarian options but it appeared tome the restaurant is focused on fish then meat with a few vegetarian options thrown in.", "The puddings where excellent."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r278306946", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect lunch with loads of space and super quality service", "diner_date": " May 2015", "rating_date": "6 June 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "BrianG574", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "41"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r278306946-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A wonderful long lunch (the way they should be) with luscious wine, great steaks and warm surroundings. Service was just the best - much better than other restaurants in Canary Wharf I've also visited.Great private rooms and a fabulous long bar with more whisky than I've ever seen in my life in one bar."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r278936090", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great food and service, BUT.......", "diner_date": " June 2015", "rating_date": "9 June 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "joyful93", "reviewer_origin": ["Abington, Massachusetts"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "361"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "156"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r278936090-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a very enjoyable evening last night at Boisdale. Delicious food, attentive service and lovely wine. My husband and son and I had been to Boisdale, always on a Monday evening. This was now our 3rd time. The first 2 times we simply booked our table online, there were no \"tickets\" to buy. We had lovely seats and enjoyed the music However, this time, we were required to buy a ticket for a table. We chose the 14.50 GBP per ticket price for a guaranteed seat. The other 2 Monday nights when Eric Ranzoni played, we did not have to buy any tickets. So we asked the manager to clarify, as the artist last night was no better than Eric - it wasn't a \"special\" concert that would warrant an extra 14.50 per person. He basically said he would never pay 14.50 on a Monday night as it is quiet, and we should have just \"turned up to get the best seat.\" I believe we should have been credited that 58.00 GBP's - especially with spending over 335.00 GBP's for dinner! Not good customer service at all from the manager!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r272468697", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "so disappointed", "diner_date": " May 2015", "rating_date": "17 May 2015", "answer_text": ["Hi RickyTracey", "\u00a0", "Thank you for taking the time out to give us your feedback following your recent visit.", "Regarding to your\u00a0dinner with us I am obviously very concerned and I have spoken with our team \u00a0to ensure that this does not occur again. We are proud of the reputation we have created and so it hurts when we hear of the kind of\u00a0mistakes\u00a0that occurred\u00a0at your\u00a0table.", "\u00a0", "Please contact us directly to gm@boisdale-cw.co.uk if you wish to discuss your experience further. ", "\u00a0", "If I can be of any further assistance, please do not hesitate to contact me.\u2028\u00a0\u2028I look forward to welcoming you to our restaurant.", "Warm regards,", "Sergei Gubars", "General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "RickyTracey", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "124"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "118"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r272468697-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I am a great advocate of Boisdales, we booked for 7 for Fleetwood Bac and were looking forward to it (8th time we have visited). The food was good but served so quickly we didn't draw breath, it felt as though they just wanted to get it done rather than we could enjoy the experience, our desert turned up before our table had been reset and it was all rather amateurish. Following our meal our service stopped. we served our own wine and if we wanted a drink tried to order from a passing waiter which meant it did not turn up. My Brother ordered a whisky 4 times before a young girl slammed a glass down on the table in front of him. I discussed our experience with the manager who was pleasant enough and removed the service charge. It really wasn't about the cost it was about our evening being ruined. To sum up I am so disappointed because this was my favourite place and it isn't any more."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r265514963", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Brilliant", "diner_date": " April 2015", "rating_date": "13 April 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "fiona M", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r265514963-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went for the 2 course sharing menu on a Friday night. The oysters were to die for and the steak was PERFECTION. The view over the fountain and the band turned this into one of the best night ever! Small hicup with desert order was rectified quickly and very efficiently. VERY HAPPY CUSTOMER will be back soon."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r265412566", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Could be so much better", "diner_date": " April 2015", "rating_date": "13 April 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Peta M", "reviewer_origin": ["Singapore, Singapore"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "354"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "139"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r265412566-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went here for a evening of music and food. The music was very good and the tables/atmosphere was excellent.", "Unfortunately for the price, this place lets itself down. Although our main were great, we ordered a side of mashed potato that was just warm with no taste - it had the texture and taste that is was cooked some hours earlier and left in an oven to stay warm.", "Wine - we ordered a second bottle of wine and the waitress topped up our glasses - mixing the previous wine with the second (different) bottle. This may not bother some people - but when you buying expensive wine, you want to be able to taste the wine.", "The place needs to look at the details and it could be an absolute gem."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r265717348", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Not good", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "14 April 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SouthsiderGlasgow", "reviewer_origin": ["Glasgow, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "103"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "75"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r265717348-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went in for dinner. Starter was very good (quails scotch eggs). But serving seared fillet of Scottish salmon that is raw in the middle (and Luke warm) with cold mash? Terrible. Sent it back and had a classic burger with fries. Burger tasteless - but I wanted fish! Not good "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r266666640", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Enjoyable experience", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "19 April 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "KempoQueen", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "85"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "51"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r266666640-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I have been there three times. They have theme nights with live band. We have done soul night, Bob Marley night and Luther night. All very fun nights with dancing. We Loved it each time. The food and service was good too. Lovely rib eye steak and the sticky toffee pudding is delicious. Cocktails nice too. I recommend this place as a fun night out. It's not cheap but is good quality and definitely entertaining with lively food."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r266991093", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "dissapointing", "diner_date": " April 2015", "rating_date": "21 April 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Robin-j-bream", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r266991093-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Wandering around after a long day I fancied dinner and was recommended this restaurant by canary wharf mall employees.", "Upon arrival I had a look at their menu (lovely appetising range of food locally sourced) they had an offer clipped onto the main menu with a Set Menu. Which unfortunately offered only starters and mains as an option and Not mains and desserts. That was a little disappointing, but I fancied just the steak which I was told I could have alone for \u00a329!(?)", "Considering that the two course set menu was \u00a320, including the \u00a38 supplement for the meat, it was a little insulting to have to pay more for not having a starter! I asked if I could swap the starter for a dessert and I was told that the chef wanted the offer to be this one. Very unaccomodating for an empty venue on a Monday evening. I left to browse different options, ended up meeting an old friend that works locally and he suggested we try the set menu. I called the restaurant to make a reservation and was told the set menu had to be booked online! And online only..As they just serve the a la carte menu to the public, obviously untrue as I had just been there a moment ago. I was truly taken back by this.", "Discouraged by being bullied into booking via a website when they have a piece of paper with the offer attached to their menu and being just 5minutes away, I gave up and went elsewhere instead.", "Not the experience I was told I would have. A shame as the venue was beautiful and the menu enticing."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r264825997", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fabulous!", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "10 April 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Amanda C", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r264825997-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I love this place. I'm a Scot so was dubious about how good it would be but I was most certainly pleasantly surprised. Had the oysters and the haggis! Great service , great food!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r270609783", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Reasonable compromise", "diner_date": " May 2015", "rating_date": "7 May 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Eleanor_Sug", "reviewer_origin": ["Wetherby, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "100"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r270609783-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["While looking around Canary Wharf one Saturday evening, we came across this place which looked really nice.", "We went up to the second floor (where the food is accompanied by live music) to be told the tables were all booked so we were escorted downstairs and handed over to the other Maitre d' (who looks like Piers Morgan). ", "The bar menu (which we were given to choose from) was a little confusing and appeared to have more beetroot than any other menu I have seen, but a quick chat with the lovely Elisa clarified things for us.", "With her assistance, we chose the Charcuterie sharing board, with a Scotch Hens Egg with haggis, and a spicy scotch quail egg each along with the olives. The olives weren't fantastic and we could have done without them, but the rest was extra special.", "For our mains, I had the Inferno burger and the green salad. The burger was indeed quite hot and tasty. I had the extra cheese and bacon, but it really didn't need the bacon. The salad was wonderful - lots of fresh herbs with a yummy dressing. My fiance had the chicken, which he enjoyed.", "To wash this down, we chose the Terra Milenaria Rioja and finished with two amaretto coffees. All in all, it was a very pleasant meal made all the better by Elisa's service."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r272142916", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The place to go!", "diner_date": " March 2015", "rating_date": "15 May 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Elvira Nikolova", "Thank you for your kind review. We sincerely hope that you will visit us in the future.", "Warmest regards,", "Sergei Gubars", "General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Elvira_Nikolova", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "71"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r272142916-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Words cannot describe the atmosphere in this jewel of the fine dining. From food, through interrior and views to staff everything is excellent. ", "The music will be loved and even from people that do not like jazz!", "Personally recommend the oysters! Looking forward to go back."]}
