{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r261105537", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Jazz", "diner_date": " January 2015", "rating_date": "22 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Brightredangel,", "Hopefully nothing will go wrong! I hope to welcome you back again soon & thank you for posting your comments. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Brightredangel", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "65"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "40"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r261105537-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Oh, jazz, great people, great food, a well stocked bar with an extensive wine and whisky list and music of top of all that, what could go wrong?"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r260997880", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent set menu", "diner_date": " March 2015", "rating_date": "22 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear JonathanRB,", "Thank you for your kind review. I am delighted you enjoyed our 2course set lunch for \u00a311.95 on the 1st floor Bar & Grill. The menu changes weekly, so be sure to revisit soon!", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JonathanRB", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "86"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "36"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r260997880-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had the set 2 course menu in the grill/bar area of this restaurant (the larger restaurant has live music and a more up-market menu). The set course menu was excellent value for money with a good selection. Between us we had most of the menu options and all my friends enjoyed the food. The deserts were not included in the set menu but are worth paying extra for (we had an amazing one). We will definately be going back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r262280061", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "average", "diner_date": " March 2015", "rating_date": "28 March 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "foxbat", "reviewer_origin": ["Ascot, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "364"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "245"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r262280061-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I have been at least 10 times to Boisdale in Canary Wharf and normally it is good enough. But on this occasion the restaurant was virtually empty at lunchtime and the food was simply far too expensive for what we got. The service was proficient and friendly but with starters at \u00a316 and mains in the high \u00a330s, it just felt a bit toppy. This Boisdales is nothing like as good as the one in Victoria which had a wonderful clubby atmosphere. Finally, I have mentioned this before but please will the restaurant sort out the really nasty smell that greets you on arrival at reception."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r263717178", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Fur coat, no nickers", "diner_date": " April 2015", "rating_date": "5 April 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "terryoo2015", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r263717178-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The 1st floor bar and 2nd floor restaurant look amazing, in an enviable spot overlooking the fountain at Canary Wharf, but it all ends there really. In the bar when we arrived there were 4 or 5 staff and none said hello or took our drinks order. When they eventually did the barman didnt seem to know how to mix a Cosmoplitan and took ages. Dirty glasses were not cleared away from where we were sitting even thugh we were the only people in there. In the restaurant, our order was taken by a stroppy waiter. Ten minutes later he returned to say they did not now have the dish my friend ordered. Twenty minutes after that they came to say they had run out of my dish as well. I complained and they gave me another main course for free. The steak was probably the worst i have ever had. All vegetables and even potatoes are extra cost. The singer was nice, A bit twee. Dont go."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r263203972", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Taste of home! ", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "2 April 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LouLonie", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r263203972-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This place was recommended to me by a work colleague so I thought I would check it out when my family came from Scotland to visit. We were all really impressed with the service and the general ambiance. My dad enjoyed a cigar on the terrace - quite the novelty! The steaks and the fish of the day in particular were a real hit! We enjoyed it while listening to really good live jazz music! Again...what a novelty! I don't think I know another place like it in London. All in all it is safe to say we will be back. A terrific night was had by all! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r263219094", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "One of my favorite in CW", "diner_date": " April 2015", "rating_date": "2 April 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ThePrinceFamily", "reviewer_origin": ["Paris"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "69"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "43"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r263219094-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I have several times here and never been disapointed.", "Food is very good and expensive, wine list the same.", "Service really warm and helpfull", "We were there on Saturday night with a Jazz concert, it was really enjoyable.", "Highly recommended if you have spare \u00a3 to spend"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r264292836", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "An absolute delight", "diner_date": " March 2015", "rating_date": "7 April 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "laurafromscotland514", "reviewer_origin": ["Troon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r264292836-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My husband took me on a date to Boisdale, as he had heard through a colleague, how good it was, so we thought we would try it out. We are so glad we did! The staff were just amazing and the food really spoke for itself. Stunning fish which was cooked to perfection.The choices amazing....The jazz was such a great touch and the atmosphere was right up our street..Just loved the whole experience...We will so be back... Thank you Boisdale, for making our night."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r263954999", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Decent food, weird atmosphere", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "6 April 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "cjg101", "reviewer_origin": ["LONDON"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r263954999-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["It's always a bit too empty to have an atmosphere, except on the terrace in summer. However the food, service, and views are excellent."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r263720615", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Just alright, poor value for money", "diner_date": " April 2015", "rating_date": "5 April 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Limlj10", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "82"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "32"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r263720615-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I came here with the 50% off ala carte menu but still felt it was not really worth what I paid for. I cannot comment on the other dishes other than mine since I did not really try the rest. However, for \u00a324 for a steak with nothing on the side is not worth it. The steak was average with a a big price tag, I've had better steak elsewhere for about the same price or cheaper but sure made me smile. I ordered blue but it came somewhere close to medium, maybe medium rare but more to the medium side. I would have asked to re-fire a steak but with the company I was with, I did not want to make a fuss. To be honest, how can a blue steak turn medium, if it was rare would have still been excusable. Chips tasted familiar too.", "All in all, just an OK experience, but I wouldn't come back for more."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r258568327", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "great", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "9 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear england201516,", "I am very pleased you had such a great time and the team were able to look after you so well. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "stephen e", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r258568327-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["hi its us from folkestone we really enjoyed our time in your restrant all the staff are so helpfull epecialy Gabor Gervis and you cant forget the great Elisa thank you all see you soon x for elisa"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r258946367", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good atmosphere, slow service", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "11 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Ryan B,", "Thank you for taking the time to write your thoughts. Am was sorry to hear that the service was slow on this occasion and that you had to wait for your drinks. We work hard to deliver excellent service, and I am disappointed to have not delivered. To clarify the music timings, the bands start at 7pm on Monday & Tuesday, 9pm on Wednesday & Thursday while Friday & Saturday the shows start at 9:45pm. Hopefully you will let us know under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk if you plan to return so we may restore your faith in us. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ryan B", "reviewer_origin": ["Atlanta, Georgia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "468"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "233"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "20", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r258946367-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I brought my team here for dinner one night while staying over in London for business. We arrived about 1900 and got a nice table overlooking the fountain with a view of the Thames in the distance and were told that a live jazz band would start around 2000. We ordered drinks, appetizers and a main and that took easily 2 hours. During this time there was no band. We ordered dessert which took another hour and finally the band showed up. The service was extremely slow as it was a busy night, but the food was very good (the mini haggis as an app was great). The wine and cocktail list was also extensive and we would have indulged more had we not had to wait 25 minutes for a drink. I also noticed while paying the bill they charged us each a cover charge for the band which didn\u2019t seem right after we only heard them for a few minutes as they were very late. Anyway, it was a nice place they just need to improve the speed of their service and keep their bands on time."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r259065852", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "It's fine, it's ok, really", "diner_date": " March 2015", "rating_date": "12 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear CosmicCarrot,", "Thank you for taking the time to write. As you find it difficult to put your finger on \u2018it\u2019 I also am sure you should visit us on a Tuesday or Wednesday evening when the atmosphere is most like the original? Let me know your thoughts\u2026", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "CosmicCarrot", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "113"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "73"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r259065852-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["It's the city-life atmosphere and the views that make this restaurant. The food and service are excellent, too. The question for me is, would I go back? In truth, I wouldn't go out of my way to go here, no. It was a 'nice' experience but I can't say there's anything outstanding or particularly enchanting about the visit. We had champagne, we had a variety of oysters. Everything arrived swiftly and looked fresh and tasty. It's pricey, yes, but I would expect no less of a traditional-like restaurant in the wharf. If I were going to to the city for a business meeting, this would be an excellent place to wine and dine a client, or to unwind after a busy day. The food and wine selection is impressive, and it was a generally positive experience. ", "So, what's wrong? It's hard to put my finger on it. I feel the place lacks soul. But maybe that's a wharf thing. On the other hand, I have been to a few places in the same neighbourhood that has the kind of energy that makes you know there is love in the food. Am I being overly sentimental? Sometimes there is a fine line between a deceptively good copy and the down-home real thing."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r259770470", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Decent enough for a business lunch", "diner_date": " April 2014", "rating_date": "16 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear FrequentFlyerEater89,", "Thank you for your review and for your comments. Perhaps I can persuade you to come and visit us for evening drinks in the whisky bar. The atmosphere of the room changes quite drastically in the evenings and we receive excellent feedback for the ambience and drinks we serve. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "FrequentFlyerEater89", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "104"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "100"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r259770470-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I came here for a business lunch, but I wouldn't come here for a social occasion. The restaurant has a slightly cold and impersonal feel, in my opinion, especially when you compare it with a more intimate steak venue such as Goodman. ", "We had the steak tartar, which was nice enough. The wine was very good, and the service efficient and friendly. ", "I would recommend the restaurant for a business lunch but I couldn't see myself coming here for anything else. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r259306210", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Poor", "diner_date": " March 2015", "rating_date": "13 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Mike O,", "Please contact us directly under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk if you wish to discuss your experience further. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Mike O", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "67"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "20", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r259306210-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Joined a party at Boisedale at Canary Wharf. Posted this review about Boisedale in Belgravia by mistake. Went to Canary Wharf on a Saturday night. Poor service, poor wine, starter of beetroot and goats cheese nearly all beetroot, desert of rhubarb crumble inedible. When complained about a bottle of wine that was clearly off I was told that French wine is variable! All this for \u00a3100 per person!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r259479314", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Back to its best - even Seb!!", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "14 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Steve B,", "I am delighted you had such a lovely evening and we all look forward to welcoming you again back soon! ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "S3489YOsteveb", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r259479314-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Having a great night tonight. Here I am live on a Saturday night in Boisdales in Canary Wharf and I'd like to say what a thoroughly enjoyable evening I'm having. In recent times the steaks haven't been great, but tonight they were perfect!!! Special mention to Igor our great waiter and an even more special mention to Seb, who has always irritated the hell out of me for his obnoxious behaviour in recent times but tonight he was exemplary. Thank you Seb and thank you to all the fantastic staff at Boisdales. Well done guys. I just hope my friend gets some special attention because it's her birthday ;-)"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r260975783", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Excellent", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "21 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear nwk84,", "Thank you for your comments I am delighted you enjoyed our fabulous Truffle Burger! I hope to welcome you again soon. ", "Warmest regards,"], "reviewer_pseudo": "nwk888", "reviewer_origin": ["Mumbai, India"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "346"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "135"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r260975783-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Excellent for business lunch. Hefty and very delicious burger. Nice Scottish setting and very good service"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r260847775", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Marvellous..must come again!", "diner_date": " March 2015", "rating_date": "21 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear VikingRider_10,", "I am delighted you had such a fabulous time with us. We all look forward to welcoming you again soon. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "VikingRaider_10", "reviewer_origin": ["Amble, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "201"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "129"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r260847775-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We spent a most enjoyable evening at Boisdales in Canary Wharf at a charity event. The main performer was Jools Holland, he was brilliant and the atmosphere in the restaurant was electric. The food offered was superb bearing in mind that they were catering for around 250 guests. The Scottish steaks simply melted in your mouth, they were cooked to perfection. The cheese board was sensational and the service all evening was second to none. Boisdale ...keep up those excellent standards, well done."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r260834881", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Query your table", "diner_date": " March 2015", "rating_date": "21 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear dave187,", "Thank you for reviewing us. I am pleased to hear that you were moved to another table but concerned that you were subsequently disturb by other customers. Having reviewed the evening we will ensure sufficient space between diners & drinking customers and have additionally highlighted on our website music performances that with generate a livelier atmosphere in the room. Hopefully we are able to welcome you again. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "dave187", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r260834881-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went there on the 20 march for a music night , paid for a standard view dining table got put on a table with a big pillar in front of it had to lean forward to see the stage, so I complained to the girls on reception as I said this was a restricted view table , I got moved to a better table but then had people at the bar behind us later on in the evening invading our space , couldn't move again as no tables left. Marks out of ten I'll give it 2"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r260953228", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Don't pay for a premium seats for a music show", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "21 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear plodsquad,", "Thank you for your review. I am disappointed to hear you did not enjoy your evening as much as hoped. We have since added further information regarding evenings where we anticipate a livelier atmosphere so you may make a more informed choice of tickets. Please contact us under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk should you wish to discuss further. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Tom S", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r260953228-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Wanted a romantic evening with the lady got a table at the front then had what seemed like people from a Yates wine lodge barging past us so they could dance. Spent \u00a380 on the table couldn't see the musicians and got agro from someone who tried to barge passed me. We left early if you're thinking of splashing out on a premium table don't it's a massive waste of money. I am not recommending this to anyone."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r258450346", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Atmosphere, food, music, brilliant!!!", "diner_date": " March 2015", "rating_date": "8 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Rancidrick,", "I am delighted you have had a great night with us. While it is entirely possible to go for the finer things in life, we try to cater for everybody so it is equally possible to dine for under \u00a350 per person and still have an excellent time, the choice is yours really. Until next time! ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Rancidrick", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r258450346-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked a premium seat next to the stage and had one of the best nights we have had in a very long time. The service was attentive and helpful, the food was without any exception excellent ( wife had crab, new york strip and a marquis. I had haggis, fillet on the bone and cheese board). Buddy whittington and his band were amazing. Boisdale definitely attract the best talent. The cocktails were made perfectly, the whisky and rum selections were delicious and so was the wine. The atmosphere was truly unique and took my to the live blues albums i have listened to over the years. Be warned..... This is not a cheap night (\u00a3300 plus.....). But for a special occasion if you are a foodie and music lover, very hard to top."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r257096918", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Again just fabulous", "diner_date": " March 2015", "rating_date": "1 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear RickyTracey,", "Thank you yet again for such a lovely review. I am delighted Neha and Marco were able to make you visit that little bit more special and hope to welcome you again! As you know the two will receive a little gift as a thank you for looking after you so well. Hopefully until very soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "RickyTracey", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "124"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "118"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r257096918-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The staff here know how to treat you. Customer service is fantastic, I made a booking blunder and Nia (spelling??) sorted it for us and we had a fab night. Bob Marley tribute was wonderful and Marco waited on us with a professionalism and friendliness which it would be hard to beat. six of us had the rib eye which was cooked to perfection, orders ranged from blue to well done !!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r256553949", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good place for evening drinks", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "26 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Steve M,", "Thank you for your review. Please contact me directly under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk. I would love extra information on the service you had received as this is not the standard we set ourselves.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "stevemX2248EY", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "83"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "48"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r256553949-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Only went to bar for a few drinks but this is a good venue by Canary Wharf standards. Good mix of clientele and a refreshing change from most of the bland venues there. They actually serve proper beer as well. Nice views at nighttime (by the wharfs standards). Only downer was bar service a bit poor - one guy was quite surly even though he wasn't busy. Definitely going back to try out restaurant "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r256918303", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic!", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "28 February 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SusannaKj", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r256918303-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I never get around to writing a review!, but on this occasion it's a must!", "From the minute I entered into the stunning restaurant I felt I had gone back in time to old school glamour!.", "We were shown to our table which was right by the stage. ", "We were shown the wine menu and also the cocktail menu.", "After choosing our wine and cocktails, we expected a wait as the resturant was extremely busy", "After only a few minutes our cocktails arrived and the wine which was placed in a wine stand/ ice bucket ", "I have been to many restaurants where unfortunately you have to ask for the wine cooler.", "Our waiter ( forgot his name!, was really attentive, but not overly)", "I love simple things like the wine / water being topped up. It's just the little things that makes you feel you are in a special environment. The waiter was lovely, very charming and attentive.", "Our starters arrived quickly ", "I chose the potted Mackrel p\u00e2t\u00e9, which was divine. ", "We chose different steaks and I have to say my steak was like velvet, just mouthwatering tender and full of flavour", "The side dishes were small, but flavoured really well.", "We didn't have desert as we were so full, but ordered another bottle of wine!", "The band/ singers came on after an hour of us dinning and it was the best two hours I have had in a long time ", "The singers were fabulous and all the restaurant were hooked on watching and almost immediately half the restaurant got up and danced!", "The venue is beautifully decorated and boasts a beautiful bar with 100's of whiskies on display ", "It was an amazing atmosphere and lovely seeing couples dancing together ( some were really good!)", "It's great to have a venue, where you can dine, watch a band/ singers and dance all under one roof!", "I am so happy to have found this gem.", "It's a place I would say for couples and you could go with a group of friends. ", "A fantastic venue for a special occasion .", "There were lots of different ages, it was nice to see people our age group 40's!", " ( just leave kids at home!) ", "I have read other reviews and some say its expensive ", "I think it's worth every penny and in line with most venues in London. ", "One more thing, you have to go take a look at the cigar room", "I ended up buying some and you can even smoke a cigar in the special room!", "I can't wait to go back again!", "( I work in the hospitality industry and I am always critical over venues, this one I can honestly say is amazing!)", "Lovely goodey bag we received too ", "Thank you we had a great night!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r256725394", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic Food, Great Bar and Excellent Entertainment", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "27 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Chrislovesitaly,", "I am delighted the team was able to look after you so well and make your present special. Please let us know when you plan on returning so we can say thank you personally for your lovely review.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ChrislovesItaly", "reviewer_origin": ["Cowfold, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r256725394-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were introduced to Boisdale by our (Grown up) sons who treated us to meal here as a joint Christmas Present. After research we decided to chose the Canary Wharf Boisdale as it had the best reviews and we thought that the venue would be the best for the entertainment as the other Boisdales looked smaller.", "We visited on Saturday 21st and saw the incredible Steven Triffitt and his incredible orchestra for which we paid extra for - it was SO worth it.", "The atmosphere of the club was sexy and romantic with red walls adorned with sexy photos and photographs of famous jazz people (although I didn't quite understand why there were pictures of Mao Tse Tung?). ", "We arrived early but were shown straight to our table with no problem and from then on were looked after so well. We chose a standard view table but had a perfect view, not too near the front, or too far back. Our waiter served us with excellent timing and we enjoyed excellent quality food. We thoroughly enjoyed our evening and would love to return for another special occasion. The whole evening was pretty costly for an everyday occurrence but we didn't feel ripped off...on the contrary the evening was good value for a great experience.", "The waiters work so hard ... they definitely deserve their tips at the end of the evening!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r257833898", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great concert, best whisky bar ever!", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "5 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear GaroKiwi,", "I am delighted you had such a great evening with us and hope to welcome you again soon!", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "GaroKiwi", "reviewer_origin": ["Villebon-sur-Yvette, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "48"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r257833898-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went for my birthday and we were nicely seated at the front. I was afraid it would be very noisy, but it was perfect. The staff was very attentive, the food was nice (nothing super special), but the wine and whisky lists are just unbelievable! We finished at the bar after the concert, and the barman was the best. Such a knowledge about whiskeys, it will blow your mind! Such a great place to discover new things, musically and spiritually ;)"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r256428903", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Mica Paris at Boisdale CW", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "25 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Ibadanboy,", "Thank you for another lovely review. I am delighted that you enjoyed the show. It was about time to have Mica back. Look out for more great night, like our upcoming evening with Jools Holland on the 19th March. Visit our website for more information.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ibadanboy", "reviewer_origin": ["Nairobi, Kenya"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2399"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1027"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r256428903-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Just got home after dinner at Boisdale. Mica brought the house down. An excellent performance. As always, the food and service at Boisdale were great. However, tonight, the star of the show was Mica. My friend & I had a most wonderful evening. Boisdale Canary Wharf is fast becoming one of the preferred jazz/ live music venues in London. Most highly recommended!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r257905576", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "A humidor, cigars and a tonne of alcohol", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "5 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear John V,", "Thank you for joining and for posting your thoughts. I am delighted you had a good time with your friends on our terrace. I was a irked to hear you thought our cigar sommelier impatient, I will speak to him regarding the incident, however I have so far only ever received positive feedback. Hopefully we will be able to welcome you again soon. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "John V", "reviewer_origin": ["Enfield, England, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r257905576-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited Boisdale with a group of friends to have a drink and smoke (unfortunately I haven't dined in the Scottish restaurant yet). ", "If you're seriously into alcohol or cigars, this is definitely the place to be! The list of both cigars and drinks are endless and range from all different prices. ", "They have a fairly sized humidor and someone is there to assist you in selecting your cigar(s). We had a couple at different price ranges, from \u00a325 - \u00a340 but you obviously pay for what you get! ", "The first floor is the terrace where you can smoke outdoors. We went in good weather so I'm not sure if heaters are available during the colder seasons. The view is not amazing, especially if you already work in canary wharf. It is located in Cabot square, overlooking a central water fountain and 2 large office buildings. ", "For smokers, you can ask for a free cutter, or the cigar staff will cut your cigars for you. They also provide free matches. ", "Overall I would say drinks are fairly priced for London and cigars a bit on the expensive side. You can always bring your own! Staff are lovely aside from the assistant working in the humidor. They can become impatient, especially if you're new to cigars and unsure what to try first. ", "I would definitely revisit and would recommend it to others - don't expect to have a good cigar experience on the cheap. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r258405855", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Very Good business lunch", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "8 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Nick W,", "I am delighted you have given us the opportunity to restore your faith in us and that we were able to deliver. I look forward to welcoming you again soon! ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "karapetsa", "reviewer_origin": ["Kingston upon Thames, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "101"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r258405855-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I have been here before and was disappointed but not this time _ we were invited for lunch which was served quickly and in a friendly fashion. I started with the dressed crab - well presented and tasty. My main of Shetland cod was excellent not so much for the cod but for the shrimp garnish - really fresh , small and tasty shrimps which set off the subtlety of the fish perfectly. We will return and start bringing our own clients here at this standard of delivery "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r256056339", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic night, a hugely pleasant surprise!", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "23 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Janetrngr,", "Thank you for taking the time to write a review. I am thrilled the team looked after you and made you feel so welcome.", "We look forward to seeing you again very soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Janetrngr", "reviewer_origin": ["Bedfordshire"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "63"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "44"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r256056339-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The entire evening was wonderful. The atmosphere, in both the bar and then the restaurant, was fantastic. Very warm and welcoming. The food was lovely, although a bit pricey. The entertainment was beyond our expectations. Highly recommended! Try it."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r253640402", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Worst service I've ever experienced", "diner_date": " March 2014", "rating_date": "11 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear artyrach22,", "I am saddened to read of your experience and would love to receive a little more detail. Please contact me directly under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk. I would like to investigate your evening further. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "artyrach22", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r253640402-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We waited half an hour to be asked for orders, it took an hour for the food to come and then it took nearly an hour for us to receive the bill. I mentioned the slowness of the service to our waiter and was met with a frosty reply. Other customers had come in, ordered, eaten paid and left by the time we receieved our food. I have no idea why we were treated with such snobbery but, quite frankly, this was the worst experience I have ever had in a restaurant. The food wasn't particularly special when we did get it and the atmosphere felt very fake."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r258425899", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Buddy Whittington and great food", "diner_date": " March 2015", "rating_date": "8 March 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear RealNeilH,", "I am delighted you enjoyed the Buddy Whittington show. I have had some great feedback form that night and I am sure he will be back to visit again. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Neil-Hawkins", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r258425899-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked a premium seat at Boisdale mainly to see Buddy Whittington, who was as ever brilliant.We were very pleased with the standard of food and of the service.All in all a great evening at an affordable price,we WILL be back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r253501024", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Style over Substance", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "10 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Jon L,", "I have passed your comments on to our head chef who has already taken remedial action. Any feedback is greatly appreciated and will help to improve us constantly. I was delighted to hear you enjoyed the service from the team. We did have a cancellation from the band hand contacted all reservations made beforehand to inform them of the change of entertainment offering them a refund of tickets or a transfer to another date should they not have wanted to join us on this occasion. The charge for the music is designed to only cover the acts cost. We have always been clear that music will be charged and you would have been informed of a music charge. If this was not the case I apologise profusely; a quick mention to the manager on duty could have resolved any issue on the night. Please contact me directly should you wish to visit again and help us restore your faith in us.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jon L", "reviewer_origin": ["Rhodes, Greece"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "38"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "50", "50", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r253501024-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I visited on a Friday evening with some friends, table booked at 7.30pm. As with previous visits to Boisdales the appearance of the restaurant cannot fail to impress \u2013 the table are beautifully set out and the range of glasses shine out like an array of crystals. The staff are very friendly and attentive, service was just at the right pace. My concern was really the quality of the food. I had the Haggis for starter which was tasty but the \u201cnoggin\u201d of whiskey for \u00a35 extra was frankly laughable \u2013 drink it quick before it evaporates! I chose the burger for main course, got to say disappointing \u2013 tasteless, tough mushroom and the hand cut chips looked more like your freezer chips over cooked. My Rhubarb and custard desert was I afraid uninspiring as well. Drinks are hugely expensive - \u00a330 for a \u00a37 bottle of supermarket white wine. The band came on about 9.45am and despite spending \u00a3140 per couple we incurred \u00a37.50 a head extra on the bill to listen to the band. Not the advertised band, very good in their own right but not a bit of Jazz in sight \u2013 more like band from a wedding bashing through family standards. Overall a lovely place to experience but don\u2019t except the food or drinks to be good value for money."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r253145762", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Expected better", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "8 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear MrRommie,", "I was disappointed to read that the service on this occasion did not live up to the standards we set ourselves. Our wine list is very extensive & while we aim have all items available at all times it may be possible that we have sold out on the night. As for the service I would be grateful for any additional information. Please contact me directly under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MrRommie", "reviewer_origin": ["Traiskirchen, Niederosterreich, Austria"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "114"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "42"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r253145762-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great venue in terms of internadesign. Fantastic whisky bar, with a lot to choose from. Unfortunately food was average and the fact that wine list contained items which were not available was what made my note lower. On top of that waiter told me that the wine I happened to choose was not very popular and that is why it was not available. Pricey. Live jazz music was good, improved atmosphere. Service slow and not attentive."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r255645234", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The most cosy atmosphere in Canary Wharf.", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "21 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Agniukas", "Thank you for taking the time to write your review. I am pleased that the team looked after you so well. Hopefully we will be able to welcome you back very soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Agniukas", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r255645234-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went there for couple drinks on bussy friday night and was amazed by the atmosphere and customer service at this place. Can not recommend the food since I have not tried but the drinks are good value buy."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r255740773", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Overpriced", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "22 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Boycee9876,", "Thank you for your review. We aim to have many varieties of food and drink available. There are many options on the menu and it is possible to have a three course meal for under \u00a335 pounds. Additionally our wine list offers 6 bottles under \u00a330. Naturally when opting for finer things in life as our dry-aged Aberdeen beef it will come at a dearer price point. I was sorry to hear about the confusion with the music ticket. We have some of the finest UK performers on our stage every evening of the week and much like going to a theatre you buy a ticket to see the performance. Hopefully this clarifies your concerns and I hope we will be able to welcome you back. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Boycee9876", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r255740773-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited the restaurant on Saturday for the Frank Sinatra evening. Music was excellant. There was an advanced charge for the performance then an overall menu charge for food & drinks. We expected the advanced charge to be deducted from our bill on the evening, but sadly wasn't, it was an extra charge for the performance only.", "This charge aside we felt the food bill was too high for quite a standard menu At \u00a3140.00 per head all in, we all thought it was overpriced and felt it's not a restaurant we would go back to. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r254724672", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Love life - love Boisdales!", "diner_date": " December 2014", "rating_date": "17 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear DiddyDoddyDave,", "Thank you for your fabulous review. I am delighted you had a great time. The tables in from of the stage are mostly taken by customers who want to be the first on the dance floor. During the week this should never affect viewing however on weekends the danceable music can result in plenty of dancing throughout the restaurant. Hopefully we will see you soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Dave B", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "133"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "66"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r254724672-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I love this place! I have been here on a few occasions and each time it's been a brilliant all consuming evening. Boisdales is set in Docklands and it has everything. There's a terrace with a fantastic view of Canary Wharf; a wonderful bar area on entrance; and a whiskey bar to die for, which is set into into the main dining area. The dining area itself is a truly stunning set up, full of buzz and atmosphere, with efficient waiters darting about. Then the food... absolute top quality... the Rib Eye Steak was divine. But to top it all, there's entertainment from 9.30 pm and an area in which to dance to set the evening off. Yes, it's expensive... But it's definitely worth it. An evening you won't forget. PS. Top tip... Get a table away from the stage, no one ever seems happy there, normally crushed by dancers!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r255839520", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "A very disappointing lunch", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "22 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Kay24762,", "Thank you for your review, even though it was made for all the wrong treasons on this occasion. I have already been in contact with one of your party and am investigating the incident. I was encouraged that the duty manager took your feedback and reacted. Hopefully we will be able to restore your faith in us.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Kay24762", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "40", "30", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r255839520-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I have just experienced a very disappointing lunch at boisdales , not only was the the menu misleading , the service staff who albeit tried there best was just about satisfactory , the food came out cold and the sides didn't even materialise . After complaining to the manager all the food was sent back and fresh food was then brought back to us . we were given 2 bottle of prosecco on the house , I definatly won't be going back ."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r254067663", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Old world decor, great service, quality food and so many whiskies!", "diner_date": " January 2015", "rating_date": "14 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear mikepaterson,", "Thank you for your review, I am delighted that you had such a great time with us. The cigar library has been very popular recently and I have spoken with the team there was an unusually high amount of customers exiting & entering the library resulting in more than usual seepage of smoke. This has been addressed and should not reoccur in future. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mikepaterson", "reviewer_origin": ["Benfleet, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "79"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "46"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r254067663-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We took business partners out for a meal to the Boisdale. Despite being In the heart of Canary Wharf, it looks as if it would have not been out of place on the Titanic. The service was very good, and the steak served on the bone was fantastic. The selection of whiskies filled a complete book. They also have a cigar room, and unfortunately the cigar smoke smell had rather pervaded the restaurant too. Great view out of the window too, and live jazz later in the evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r256003478", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A perfect valentines", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "23 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear SatEats,", "Thank you for your kind review. I am delighted you enjoyed your evening & the entertainment of the lovely Atlantic Soul Orchestra. Hopefully we are able to welcome you back very soon, so check our website for all the information on upcoming bands. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "SatEats", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r256003478-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I recently visited on Friday 13th Feb for an early valentines dinner. We enjoyed starters, mains and 2 cocktails each for \u00a389, which represented good value when considering the quality of what we were served. I would recommend the Daiquiris and the gnocchi in particular. Additionally, we had paid an initial \u00a325 each cover charge and the entertainment, provided by the smooth sounds of the Atlantic Soul Orchestra did not disappoint. Overall, a lovely ambience and although an expensive evening out, it was a memorable valentines for all the right reasons."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r253139747", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "GREAT! committed to accommodate and exceed expectations.", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "8 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Gil J,", "I am thrilled you had such an amazing time & the team were able to look after you so well. Gintare & Rocio will both be receiving a little present as a thank you; something we do when members of the team are mentioned in despatches. Hopefully we can welcome you again very soon. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Gil J", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r253139747-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale definitely does not disappoint! It exceeds expectations! ", "From the very efficient and informative booking process over the phone with Gintaria who was indeed very pleasant to deal with all the way until the end of the experience, I have nothing but great things to say. My guest being a vegan, I informed the restaurant when booking the table. I was reassured to hear that it wasn't a problem. On the night she was offered a choice of several starters, main courses and flavors of sorbet for dessert. We both thoroughly enjoyed our food which was spot on. Trying my friend's dish I was surprised to realise that vegan food can be so tasty! (A stew with lentils, truffles, broccoli and more...). The musical entertainment was also excellent with a tribute to Buena Vista Social Club by talented musicians and charismatic singer. Finally the overall experience was enhanced by a fantastic service and a lovely Spanish waitress (sorry forgot her name) who kept a close eye on our satisfaction and offered just the right amount of presence.", "Across the board a great experience with a very dedicated team from chef, reservation, reception and waiting staff who are no short of efforts to make your evening special.", "We will most definitely be back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r250060104", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Overpriced, tiny pieces of stake and bad service", "diner_date": " January 2015", "rating_date": "19 January 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear RinaAK,", "I was disappointed to read we did not live up to the standards we set ourselves this time & apologise sincerely. This is out of the ordinary and very unusual. Hopefully you will return once more and we can restore your faith in us. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "RinaAK", "reviewer_origin": ["Hong Kong, China"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "33"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r250060104-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I was really looking forward to this experience and took my client for lunch. Service was slow, snail paced. 30 minutes for green tea and coffee and after reminding them. Overpriced steaks particularly given portion size. Nothing special. Chips were burnt. superfood salad was not bad. Overall disappointing experience."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r250289454", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Very overpriced and not that good", "diner_date": " January 2015", "rating_date": "21 January 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear MsVictoria,", "I am disappointed to read that we have not lived up to the standards we set ourselves. Please contact me under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk if you wish to discuss a little further. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MsVictoria", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "193"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "185"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r250289454-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I've dined here a few times over the past couple of years and there's always been something that's been cold, overcooked, dry or had to be sent back but this time was the worst.", "The mark-up on the wines is hideous. Almost \u00a370 for a bottle of Cloudy Bay sauvignon blanc is daylight robbery. This is a \u00a320-\u00a325 bottle of wine.", "Again the burger was overcooked and so dry (\u00a317.50). Ordered the foie gras with truffle sauce and shaved black truffles as an accompaniment (12.50). The foie gras was miniscule and was literally the size of a large stamp, if there was a truffle sauce I couldn\u2019t see or taste it and the shaved truffle tasted like dirt. ", "We asked for a jug of ice tap water and got a luke warm glass of water. The waiter was too slow topping up the water and wine glasses.", "After all the previous issues with sending food back, being given the wrong order, overcooked food, cold burgers etc. I won\u2019t be returning again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r250902702", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What a lovely, luxurious place", "diner_date": " January 2015", "rating_date": "25 January 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear HDismorr,", "Thank you for your review. I am delighted you had a lovely time with us. We look forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "HDismorr", "reviewer_origin": ["Cirencester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "102"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "34"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r250902702-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My boyfriend booked an evening at the Boisdale for my Christmas present, and he certainly did well! The staff are friendly and extremely knowledgeable on the wines and food, and are all very professional. The food was superb, pricey however. (steak on its own \u00a327 without sauce or veg).", "I would certainly recommend for anyone wanting a great night with live jazz music."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r251323148", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Amazing Atmosphere", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "27 January 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Gerrie L,", "I am pleased that you enjoyed your Sunday lunch with us. We celebrated Burns Night the day before this year and continued into the morning hours hence Sunday maintained the traditional Sunday Roast. We are looking forward to seeing you again soon. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "188gerriel", "reviewer_origin": ["Kathmandu, Nepal"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "77"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r251323148-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went here for lunch on a Sunday. The jazz band is such a nice touch, very welcoming and relaxing. As it was a Sunday a roast was the obvious choice, but thought seeing that it was Burns Night there would have been something extra special, which was not the case. Will definitely go back as the menu and choices is very varied. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r252103696", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Slightly disappointed", "diner_date": " January 2015", "rating_date": "1 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear EssexHappywanderer,", "I was disappointed to read that we did not live up to our standards on this occasion. Please contact me directly under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk should you wish to discuss further. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "EssexHappywanderer", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r252103696-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Waited an hour for starters, another hour for dinner, food was disappointing, venue very nice, staff were helpful, although the waitress who served us English wasn't great, but her helpfulness more than compensated for this,maybe I will try a lunchtime next, wont be rushing back, "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r252224304", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing evening", "diner_date": " January 2015", "rating_date": "2 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear MrsMichy,", "Thank you for your review. While I was disappointed that there were delays in the service to you I am pleased that the team made you feel comfortable throughout. Please let us know when you plan to revisit, we would like to say thank you personally. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MrsMichy", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "185"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "130"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r252224304-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were fortunate enough to be guests on Saturday and didn\u2019t have to pick up the bill!! (A little pricey, but worth it!). ", "The main reason for going to Boisdale was to see the Bootleg Beatles in intimate surroundings. We were not disappointed \u2013 it was an awesome atmosphere.", "If I had to find fault, I would say the service was very slow \u2013 it was at least an hour before we were served with starters, and we were still waiting for our main course when the Bootleg Beatles arrived on stage at 9.45 p.m. (I wanted to get up and dance!! <smile>.) ", "Having said that, the restaurant was filled to capacity. The waiters/waitresses were at all times polite and helpful, and in no way did the delay between courses spoil the ambience of the evening.", "The food really was very very good. Hubby tried haggis for the first time and was pleasantly surprised! The fillet steak I ordered was cooked to perfection and melted in my mouth, and from the conversation around the table, the fillet steak on the bone was even better!", " ", "Would definitely recommend and hope I get the chance to re-visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r252124635", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fabuolous Food, Service and Views!", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "1 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Huggy27,", "Thank you very much for your beautiful review. We are delighted to have made your evening so enjoyable. Hopefully we will be able to welcome you back very soon. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Huggy27", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "94"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "60"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r252124635-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale is a fantastic find in the heart of London's Canary Wharf - Views when dining in the restaurant are amazing even more so when night falls and the towering buildings of Canary Wharf are lit up.", "Menu has a great range of choices and for a luxurious restaurant; prices were definitely reasonable for the great quality of food and setting.", "My partner and I shared Oysters to start; these were presented lovely with a selection of different accompaniments on offer too.", "For main I had a whole lobster which for Canary Wharf was a decent price; cooked to perfection and would recommend to any lobster lovers out there. My partner had the pork belly; which he enjoyed very much and said was a great portion size and the taste was fantastic.", "During the meal a jazz band started playing; really added to the romantic mood and setting overlooking Canary Wharf. ", "The staff were very polite and extremely knowledgeable on the wines and food, all very professional which when paying the prices of Boisdale's is much appreciated and added immensely to the evening.", "Would recommend to all looking for a romantic evening in London - and for those lovers of Jazz music too!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r252685250", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good bar on Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " February 2015", "rating_date": "5 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Dan L,", "Thank you for your review. I am delighted you enjoyed your time with us.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Danlmarsh", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "286"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "95"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r252685250-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I stopped in here with a few colleagues after meeting nearby. In addition to the standard beer and cocktails, they have good selection of wine and champagne to go with oysters which seems to be their specialty. This a modern on two levels a very lively room on the first floor and a jazz room upstairs with live music. This is good alternative if you are tired of the pubs and are look ok for something different."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r252424276", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "WOW !!", "diner_date": " January 2015", "rating_date": "3 February 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Matt S,", "Thank you so much for your review. I am delighted you enjoyed your evening to such an extent. We regularly have great special offers available online so do look for them and hopefully you will be able to visit many more times. ", "Warmest regards,"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mattsW1168VQ", "reviewer_origin": ["Goring-on Thames, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "38"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r252424276-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["After reading reviews on here I was a little apprehensive.....I am so pleased that I decided to make up my own mind. Staff, second to none, there when you needed them but not in your face. Food, literally some of the best food I have tasted, cooked to perfection. Entertainment ( The Black Hat Band ), lets just say that I will be tracking them down again, great mix of songs, knew how to get the crowd involved, pitch perfect. Venue, a beautiful buzz about it....only wish that I could afford to go there on a regular basis. All in all, just a fabulous night that I don't think could of been improved on in any way. Well done The Boisdale !!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r249916745", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Last minute surprise", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "18 January 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Alan J,", "Thank you for your kind review. I am pleased you had a great evening. I have passed your comments onto our Head Chef and he is obviously disappointed to read about your thoughts on the fries. Hopefully next time we can deliver even better!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "AlanJ353", "reviewer_origin": ["Wedmore, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r249916745-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Walked in last minute for a table around 6.30pm, welcomed by a great host and given a perfectly acceptable table. Service was excellent, I can highly recommend the beef carpaccio and fillet steak on the bone. B\u00e9arnaise was out of this world, one of the best I have ever had... As for French fries... Hmmm, average at best, without doubt were bought in and probably frozen... For 30 quid, I expect home made fries. Everything else was great, would totally recommend ", " "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r245085429", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great start to Christmas", "diner_date": " December 2014", "rating_date": "19 December 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear V P,", "I am delighted you stumbled upon us and we were able to look after you. Remember we are here all year round and hope to see you again soon. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "V P", "reviewer_origin": ["Wellingborough, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r245085429-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["All I knew was that we were going out to find some food - so what a treat this was! Delicious menu selection, attentive & charming staff, terrific music from the \"Rat Pack\". Tribute band.Table by the window looking out on a square filled with twinkling Christmas trees - a much-needed evening for two during the frantic run-up to Christmas."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r247340595", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice staff, food, music", "diner_date": " January 2015", "rating_date": "4 January 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear AinZweiDrei,", "The Christmas show is a live sensation so not necessarily ideal for a calm conversation as you rightly point out, however for the remainder of the year the music from Monday to Thursday is much more accommodating with Fridays & Saturdays again being full shows to replace the need of leaving to see a theatre play or musical. Hopefully we will see you again soon. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "AinZweiDrei", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r247340595-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very nice experience, first time I tried Haggis and it was delicious. Splendid selection of wines, professional and friendly service. A bit pricier than other restaurants around the corner that are also good. Live Jazz band could be somewhat problematic past 21:00 if you'd like to have a lively conversation, otherwise a good opportunity to enjoy jazz/blues and even dance by it. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r247748256", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great Place, but disappointing experience", "diner_date": " December 2014", "rating_date": "6 January 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear LataV,", "Thank you for taking the time to review us. I was sorry to hear we did not have your preferred tipple in stock. To put just a little perspective on it I wish we had as much whisky however it is more around the 680 mark, give or take, depending on the availability of some whiskies as well as our ability to lay our hands on vintage varietals. Our Bar manager works tirelessly to keep the bar stocked & we are looking into systems to always have an absolutely accurate list at hand, however it has happened very few times that a particular whisky has sold out on the night. Your comments regarding the team\u2019s attentiveness have been taken into consideration and we do consistently focus on customer service. If we did not live up to our own expectations on the evening I sincerely apologise. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LataV", "reviewer_origin": ["Dubai, United Arab Emirates"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "200"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "92"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r247748256-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This is a 2 storey venue with dining,whiskey rooms, cigar rooms and live music. We had visited the venue to experience the whiskey room and dine as well with family. We were very impressed with the ambience and whiskey collection, which they claim is over 3000 varieties and have every single one of the listed items. However very surprised when the very first one ordered i.e a 1999 edition of Knockando was not available and no suggestions were also provided for a alternative.Also the time taken for someone to take the order and the time between taking the order to getting it to the table is very long. We also observed the stewards discussing between them as to who will serve which table. In the process there seemed to be a delay in attending to guests."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r249395430", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good for a hearty lunch, but lacks character of the sister restaurant in Victoria ", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "15 January 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear DiscerningDiner77", "Thank you for your review. I was irked to hear you did not rate us as highly as hoped however hope you give us one more try, perhaps during the evenings when we do have plenty of character and atmosphere. We even have a few defectors from the Victoria site coming over to us\u2026", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "DiscerningDiner77", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "61"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r249395430-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Good solid restaurant for lunch in the middle of the Canary Wharf complex.", "The menu is sound, but uninspiring, with a Scottish flavour.... Lots of steaks, haggis (good with a noggin of whisky....), salmon etc..", "A little expensive for what you get though."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r247883456", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "If you appreciate great food, atmosphere and service and don't mind paying for it then look no further", "diner_date": " December 2014", "rating_date": "6 January 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Carlosthegreat1", "Thank you for your very kind review. I am pleased that you have enjoyed your evening with us and look forward to welcoming you again and again. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Carlosthegreat1", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r247883456-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Yes it's pricey, but like the old saying you get what you pay for! ", "The food is stunning, the wine is fantastic and the service is above and beyond! ", "I have visited numerous times and each time I have had the same fantastic experience. Our Latest was to watch the Frank Sinatra and rat pack experience.... Incredible! ", "Honestly give it a go you will not regret it. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r245723835", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Surprisingly good in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " December 2014", "rating_date": "24 December 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Barry B,", "I am delighted we were able to surprise you. We look forward to your return. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Barry B", "reviewer_origin": ["Hoddesdon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1227"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1577"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r245723835-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This is probably one of th best places to eat in the Wharf, more expensive than some but beats Plateau hands down.", "Good steaks, very quickly served, tastes sides which complemented the main course flowed by some great deserts ", "Fitting way to mark the leaving of a member of the team before he relocates to New York", "I will return"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r249878765", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good atmosphere, but...", "diner_date": " January 2015", "rating_date": "18 January 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Nigel P,", "I am irked reading your comments (there is nothing like a bit of healthy competition between us & a sister restaurant) and hope to welcoming you back next time and getting it right. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "nigelpaton", "reviewer_origin": ["Newcastle upon Tyne, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "172"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "93"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r249878765-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Having enjoyed Boisdale Belgravia I went along to the outpost in Canary Wharf with high hopes. And, to be fair, we had a good night out, excellent band and lively atmosphere. It's just that, well, it's not as classy as Belgravia, and both the food and service were down a notch on what you might expect, particularly given the price. I will probably give it another chance, but I wouldn't rush back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r249890047", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Most expensive restaurant night in years, but...", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "18 January 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear Tord E,", "I am delighted to hear you enjoyed the Si Cranstoun night, it really was amazing. We take great care in being competitively priced and monitor our prices very closely. It is entirely possible to dine with us for under \u00a330 per person, however dry-aged steaks are a little dearer, but I agree; totally worth it. We hope to welcome you again soon. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "torde583", "reviewer_origin": ["Sala, Sweden"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r249890047-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["So good!", "We went mainly to see Si Cranstoun. ", "But the dinner itself was a wonderful experience. ", "Very nice atmosphere, friendly and service minded staff. ", "And the steak was absolutely fantastic. ", "As someone said. ", "You get what you pay for. ", "And it was worth it!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r249850734", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great atmosphere", "diner_date": " January 2015", "rating_date": "18 January 2015", "answer_text": ["Dear mary b,", "I am thrilled by your review & the whole team is proud of your comments. Thank you! Ernest will also receive a little present, a tradition we have to reward the team for being mentioned in despatches.", "We all look forward to seeing you again soon. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mary b", "reviewer_origin": ["Liverpool, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "69"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "46"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r249850734-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The food, service and ambience were excellent. Yes it's expensive but a very good experience. Service was a little slow between courses but it didn't detract from the overall impression of a well run, professional enterprise.", "We enjoyed the act and noted in the programme the many more interesting acts coming up.", "Earnest who ran the whisky bar was very good and informative. and seems like a man who enjoys his job!", "Will return asap."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r242109297", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice venue", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "30 November 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Andy N,", "I was disappointed to hear you felt that both starter and dessert did not live up to standards we set ourselves, however all the more pleased you enjoyed everything else that evening. How good was Midge Ure? Hopefully we will see you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Andy N", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "61"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r242109297-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went there to see Midge Ure on a friday evening which was very good.The venue is very attractive and situated in Canary Wharf.The service was very good the only gripe was being dissapointed with the starters and deserts that we had,very bland and expensive for what they were.The saving grace was the main course which was excellant.Had a very good wine list and overall a very good evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r242367572", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Another great night - almost perfect", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "2 December 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Steve B,", "I was irked to read that we had not gotten you cooking temperature for the steak right and have passed on your comments to our Head Chef for him to keep and extra eye on! However I am comforted that the waitress took action to ensure your satisfaction on the evening and thank you for letting us know on the night! ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "S3489YOsteveb", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r242367572-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I've been here quite a few times now and it's always great. Last night was no exception. When the three of us arrived around 9.30pm the live band was slowing down and it there weren't too many people left so the atmosphere wasn't as buoyant as hoped. Typical Monday night. However, the waitress for our table was excellent (and I'm really sorry that I can't remember her name), and more than made up for it. She was bright, bubbly, fun, informative and professional. The only niggle I had (which normally would have been much more annoying) was that my steak was over cooked. I normally have rare but last time here rare was blue. So this time I went medium rare but it came out well over. Come on Chef, please sort it out - Goodman is proving more reliable for a well cooked steak (and the place was almost empty)! Luckily your dressed crab was superb and the mushroom sauce was delicious. I made a brief comment about the steak (and it really wasn't an issue) and the waitress offered free desert. This was very kind and more than expected. We didn't take it as we had to leave but thanks for the offer. I'll certainly be back - for a great night out Boisdales is very reliable!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r242900275", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Always excellent", "diner_date": " December 2014", "rating_date": "4 December 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear disco123,", "Thank you for your kind review. I am delighted you enjoy spending your time with us! ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "disco123", "reviewer_origin": ["Kingswear, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "43"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r242900275-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I had another good lunch here this week. I really like the venue , it is perfect for formal or informal business meetings , the food is good and bar & grill menu offers everything I need. I usually have steak but this time round the fish and chips were pretty good. The service is prompt and efficient. The Boisdale brand is one I like and the style and setting make for an above average working lunch."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r244985011", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Very good steak place", "diner_date": " December 2014", "rating_date": "18 December 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear stockdale83,", "Thank you for your review & I apologise once again that your steak took more than the usual time to arrive. We are constantly working on improving ourselves and look to minimise errors, so hopefully there will not be a recurrence. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "stockdale83", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "214"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "68"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r244985011-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went to Boisdale for lunch in Canary Wharf and the food was great. The rib eye was cooked to perfection, and the chunky chips were also of very good quality. Had the eight petit fours as dessert which ended a very nice lunch. Two negative points though: this restaurant is pretty expensive and my main took 45 minutes to arrive after ordering, which is extremely long."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r242691758", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A great evening out", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "3 December 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear TDMB,", "I am pleased you enjoyed your evening out with us and that you enjoyed yourself. I have spoken to the bar manager regarding your comments on the whisky list & he confirmed that we had difficulties sourcing a few tipples pre-Christmas, however this had now been thoroughly resolved & I am pleased the team took remedial action. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "TDMB", "reviewer_origin": ["Milton Keynes UK"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "77"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "91"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r242691758-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were invited here by friends who'd been before and it was an excellent night out. We ate upstairs and listened to the Jazz band on a Thursday evening and it was great - busy without being too crowded - though I'd be happy to go when it was a bit busier and people were dancing. Ambience in the Oyster Bar downstairs and in the restaurant upstairs both excellent. All wood panelling and tartan carpets. Very cosy - you feel like you've stepped into a Highland retreat. Great service and amazing food - though not at all cheap! One downside was that, despite their extensive whisky collection, they didn't have either of the ones that my partner asked for. When the second one failed they did upgrade him to the next level up for no extra cost, so it wasn't all bad - but just a bit surprising given it's one of their main features. All in all I'd definitely recommend for a nice evening out once in a while."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r243214541", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent ", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "6 December 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Will M,", "I was pleased to read that you have enjoyed your evening with us. I hope to welcome you again soon. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Will M", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r243214541-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited with my wife and son", "Great atmosphere live music upstairs", "Good good, not fancy but very nice", "Excellent service friendly a place for something nice to eat, but not over the top"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r243200002", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good Food and Ambiance", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "6 December 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Eugene1958,", "I was irked to read you did not thoroughly enjoy your meal with us. Since then we have invested in new table feet that level themselves. The bone marrow butter is served much like a garlic butter so it can slowly melt over the steak, however we have clarified this on the menu to avoid recurrence. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Eugene1958", "reviewer_origin": ["Dublin, Ireland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "150"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "70"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r243200002-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Decided to opt for a bit of a treat. Ordered the Rib Eye (MEDIUM) with mash and mushrooms and bone marrow sauce. I would suggest medium well in future for those who want medium. The bone marrow sauce was a lump on the steak so not quite sure about that. Service was attentive, take was a bit shaky and sawing through some of the meat caused the candle to fall over but it went out luckily. Music was very good and non intrusive. All in all a good night but not spectacular. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r244046898", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great atmosphere, good food and awesome entertainment", "diner_date": " December 2014", "rating_date": "11 December 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear GillMargo,", "Thank you for taking the time to review us. I am thrilled you had such a good time & even a tiny little bit pleased your concert was cancelled. Next time you visit please let us know so we can say thank you personally. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "GillMargo", "reviewer_origin": ["Cambridge, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "147"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "213"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r244046898-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My husband and I were due to go to the O2 to see Ennio Morricone however Ennio had to cancel and we had booked a non cancellation hotel room so still had to go to London! I searched the internet to see what was on that night in Canary Wharf and came across 'Christmas with Frank and Dean' at Boisdales - we are both huge Frank Sinatra and Dean Martin fans so thought we would give it a try, boy am I glad we did. As soon as you walk into Boisdales you feel special, the restaurant is amazing and we were lucky enough to have a table right next to the entertainment. We booked our meal for 7pm, I had the terrine with Foie Gras to start with, I must say I was not impressed with that, husband had oysters which were extremely good. For main course I had the chicken dish which was gorgeous and husband had the fillet steak which was one of the best he'd eaten. Service was outstanding, the waiter was so attentive even taking our wine down to the cigar lounge for us so hubby could relax with a nice cigar before the entertainment started, the cigar bar is fantastic. The entertainment was outstanding, brilliant entertainers and a lot of people ended up dancing! We are even talking about going again next year. If you want a really good night out, great food and entertainment this is certainly the place to go."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r244436626", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "I absolutely adore this place.", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "14 December 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Karolina K,", "Thank you so much for your review. I was delighted to have been able to welcome you so often and look to the next time you visit. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Karolina K", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r244436626-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I loved their lobster linguine that they had on the menu last year. I was a regular there, loved to go there and just sit, with a book or just watching people passing by. they have an amazing cigar room. As a woman I love cigars and I'm going to try the room soon ;-) the staff are great(management is always present on the floor, but not just standing and talking, they work like crazy) atmosphere is amazing (been on both floors and had a romantic dinner with my boyfriend on both floors) love, love , love boisdale. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r240926024", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Very nice evening", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "22 November 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Nortsat46,", "I was pleased to hear you enjoyed your evening with us. Hopefully we are able to welcome you back in the near future.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Nortsat46", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "101"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r240926024-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a very nice dinner here, mid week. Rabbit terrine and mackerel pate to start. We both had the grouse with a matched glass of Pinot Noir for main course. Nice puddings too. ", "Very nice wine list, with a range of prices. Good service.", "We had a table at the front (extra cost worthwhile if you want a good view of the musicians) and enjoyed the jazz.", "Efficient staff organised a cab home for us.", "It was a very nice evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r244332699", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic ", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "13 December 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear stephenmaull,", "I can only say thank you for your review & hope to welcome you again soon. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "darthmaull69", "reviewer_origin": ["Guildford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "167"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "71"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r244332699-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This place was fantastic the food is totally great can't find any falt and the Jazz band are terrific really top class evening "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r239157930", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "cocktails and snacks", "diner_date": " April 2014", "rating_date": "10 November 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear fashionbabee,", "Thank you for your review. I am delighted you enjoyed your evening. I hope to see you soon!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "fashionbabee", "reviewer_origin": ["glasgow"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "89"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "40"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r239157930-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Cocktails are amazing! Barstaff also take requests as I wanted a French Martini but that is not on the menu but they made me something comparable on request! Very accommodating! We only had bar snacks (calamari and a few other things) but they were really really good so will definitely try dinner! Great view of the fountain from the balcony!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r238918426", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great Atmosphere, Excellent Live Jazz, Service and Food Not so Great", "diner_date": " October 2014", "rating_date": "9 November 2014", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Roger N", "reviewer_origin": ["Houston, Texas"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "127"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "56"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "50", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r238918426-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This restaurant was listed as the top place to go in Canary Wharf on several of the local web sites. It is located immediately upon entry into the Cabot Place mall. The restaurant has two floors, the main floor is for casual dining, with primarily the same food, but in a more informal setting.", "The upper floor is what the service person called \"fine dining,\" and is where the Live Jazz stage is located. We wanted to relax and have a really good meal, so opted for the upper floor. We did not have reservations, but they seated us promptly with a great view of the stage. It all started out very positively.", "Our server came to take our order, we ordered a Shrimp Cocktail appetizer for each of us and the 7 oz. Filet Steak. We settled in for our perfect meal. The upper floor has great atmosphere and was very busy with what looked to be mostly business men and women. The Jazz was outstanding and they have a different group every night with a brochure of who is coming in the weeks ahead.", "We got our Shrimp and finished it off, but it appeared that our server once he took the order decided that we were no longer important enough to check back with us, so was left alone for the remainder of the night to flag down other servers and fend for ourselves.", "Additionally, there were several couples and a large table of diners who came in after us and they all got their meals prior to us getting ours. We wondered why and asked what happened to our food. After about an hour, our food showed up and the steaks were cool, overcooked and generally not very pleasant. Our waiter still had not even thought to look at us or come and ask if all was well, he was too busy taking care of what appeared to be the more important guests.", "During our wait time, we flagged down several other servers and staff to ask about more water, bread, butter, etc., they helped but we did not get the impression that it was willingly.", "At the end of the meal, we spoke with the Concierge and explained out frustration. I explained that there were several other diners who came after us and received their dinner either before or just before we received ours. At first he blamed us and said our meal was so very late due to the fact that my friend had ordered his steak well-done, and that if we had ordered an appetizer, it would have spaced the timing so that the steak would be cooked perfectly. After several minutes of discussion on the falsity of that premise and telling him that we did order an appetizer, he recanted and said \"that is unacceptable then, I will have to talk with the Chef.\"", "I think this is one of the nicer places in Canary Wharf, with the Jazz, Cigar Bar and huge Whisky offering, it is perfect for an after work Business gathering to have a few drinks and maybe enjoy a cigar, if that is your thing. I would hesitate to go there and expect a perfect meal experience though, if the Chef can't handle a simple steak I would hesitate to see what he does with the other items on the menu.", "I must also say that my friend and I, are of a particular ethnicity, I am not sure that that had anything to do with it, but it sure crossed our minds several times during the night, considering we were the only two there of that persuasion. It was not a pleasant feeling and one we would not have thought we would feel in 21st century London.", "Go, enjoy the Jazz, it was great, have one of the Whiskey choices and at least see what the place looks like, I think it is worth it, and, hopefully, you will get better treatment than we did."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r239793838", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Maybe not very Scottish food-wise, but otherwise great!", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "14 November 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Helvin3,", "Thank you for your review. A lot of the produce on our menu hails from Scotland, but there are a lot of British ingredients so I hope we did not confuse too much. I was glad to read the team rectified the error quickly. Hopefully we will see you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Helvin3", "reviewer_origin": ["Auckland, New Zealand"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "211"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "100"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r239793838-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were absolutely intrigued by the idea of a Scottish restaurant which is why we decided to come here.", "It was a bit pricey for me personally but was good food overall - and REALLY great house red wine.", "They overcooked my friends steak but they took it back and replaced it without any fuss, and even gave her a free glass of wine - so great service!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r239367809", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great find!! But what's it called again??", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "11 November 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear mich&co,", "I am very pleased you had such a great night and we were able to accommodate you on such short notice. I was sorry to hear the steaks were overcooked and a few menu items had run out; definitely not a normal occurrence! Hopefully we are able to welcome you again soon and get everything right.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Vacationer803444", "reviewer_origin": ["Harrogate, England"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "74"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "85"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r239367809-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were recommence to Boisdale at Canary Wharf by the receptionist in our hotel and luckily managed to get a late reservation on a Friday night even though we were a party of eight. It was a great find as we had a fabulous night and the live band Oomph were amazing. Food was mostly perfect, my haggis starter was incredible, oysters were stunning, but both mine and my husband's fillet steaks were over done, and they had by then randomly run out of the mashed potato side dish that I ordered. This aside the whole experience was brilliant and we ate, drank, danced and laughed in a restaurant with a fun, lively atmosphere. We would return in a heartbeat!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r240596181", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Excellent Sunday lunch", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "19 November 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Kitto211064", "We are thrilled you enjoyed our traditional Sunday Roast Lunch. Hopefully we will be able to welcome you during the week for soothing jazz evenings at the Whisky Bar.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Kitto211064", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r240596181-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Atmosphere was tranquil with three piece Jazz band playing. Enough space between tables so as not to be disturbed by other guests. Staff were pleasant and polite, just appearing as required. We started with a Blood Mary, just perfect. Food was extremely tasty. We had smoked salmon pate followed by Aberdeen beef roast dinner with all the trimmings. Creme caramel for dessert was delicious. Certainly recommend for a special Sunday out."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r240548068", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Excellent steak, and brilliant service", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "19 November 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Camillymilly1", "I am thrilled to hear you had such a wonderful time. We hope to welcome you again and again!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Camillymilly1", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "26"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r240548068-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I've been to Boisdale's on a number of occasions, mainly with clients for both drinks and dinner - the staff are always excellent and the Bar Manager is very attentive. We also went for a wine tasting evening and it was great. They are very accommodating to any fussy guests ", "Worth the money and would definitely recommend and come back again"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r240920199", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "My local jazz club - Wonderful", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "22 November 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Ibadanboy,", "I am delighted to hear we have become our local jazz venue and thank you for your review. Do not forget to visit our website to check out all the amazing upcoming bands & events.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ibadanboy", "reviewer_origin": ["Nairobi, Kenya"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2399"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1027"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r240920199-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale Canary Wharf is an excellent.long awaited addition to the entertainment & dining options in Canary Wharf/ Isle of Dogs neighbourhood. Overlooking Cabot Square in a space that has multiple floors, this venue is ideal for business functions, private parties, romantic dinners - and the list could go on & on. That live jazz music played here every night is simply awesome. No we have a real option to the Central London venues (Ronnie Scott's, Jazz Cafe, Barbican, etc). Better yet, this place serves up excellent food (we had superb steaks last night, washed down with a nice bottle of Malbec. Yolanda Brown was on last night and she put on a splendid performance. Bosidale is a great place, the restaurant area is spacious, the decor is nice and service is OK. Very highly recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r240374845", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday celebration", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "18 November 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear netty120", "Thank you for choosing us to celebrate with. I apologise if the team did not respond to your comment in the way you had hoped however I am thrilled you enjoyed everything else about your evening.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "annett120", "reviewer_origin": ["Brentwood, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "52"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "39"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r240374845-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a fantastic evening with friends", "Great food and entertainment from jason isaacs and his ambassadors of swing. From starters to desserts the food was delicious amazing steaks the cheese board looked even better but we were to full to have any , I did ask them to move the cheese trolley as the stinking bishop was overpowering and right next to me, they just covered it with a dome but it still bothered me I did ask again but it was only removed later in the evening during the entertainment this reflects in my score for service otherwise a almost perfect evening will definitely be back "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r240743786", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Absolutely Faultless...", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "20 November 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear DeepJet", "I am delighted to hear you enjoy being looked after by Filipe. He has a little present waiting for him; something we do for our team when they are mentioned in despatches! Until the next time\u2026", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "DeepJet", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r240743786-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Food is always great. Great freshly made dishes served in a timely manner.", "Worldclass selection of Cuban Cigars, available to purchase as single cigars or as a box.", "The most impressive aspect of the establishment is the service & attention to detail. The staff all seem happy in their work & this reflects in the service they provide their clientele. One member of staff in particular \"Philip\" cannot rate his service highly enough..."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r234545532", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Food, Fun and Entertainment", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "15 October 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Tony K,", "Thank you for your very kind review. I am thrilled you enjoyed yourself. As for the opening times: They may change once it is easier to travel westbound once the tube runs longer\u2026", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "TonyK646", "reviewer_origin": ["uk"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r234545532-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["3 couples out for my birthday celebrations, and I must say paying the little extra for the better table was well worth it. Food was good all round, and the entertainment (black hat band) were awesome. Shame it didn't stay open a little later !"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r235779048", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Do not go for the Lobster, I was shocked.", "diner_date": " October 2014", "rating_date": "22 October 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear menelik5,", "Thank you for your feedback, though I was irked that you did not rate our fabulous Scottish lobsters. They are indeed dearer than the American counterparts and prices have been rising drastically the past few years. I can only apologise if yours was small and hope that you give us the opportunity to make amends. Hopefully until next time", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "menelik5", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "40", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r235779048-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I been in this nice old-fashion Scottish Restaurant with my partner and her family. The place is quite nice and warm, as a Chef with Michelin star background I can tell the food is good and simple.", "The only bad note of this evening was my Main Course. I ordered a whole Scottish Lobster on the grill, on the Menu priced for \u00a337,50.", "When the main course arrived, I was Shocked!!!!!! The plate was full of watercress salad and I had a very tiny small Lobster on the shell. For almost \u00a340 I just had two bites, the Lobster was tasty but for my point of view really small for a Main Course. Imagine if I was ordering half Lobster!!!!", "If you go at many Michelin & Rosette Restaurants in London for less of that price you can have as Main Course a Juicy Lobster Tail with the Claws with an impeccable presentation.", "I left the Restaurant very Disappointed!!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r236112399", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food & Jazz", "diner_date": " October 2014", "rating_date": "24 October 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Gingabarn,", "Thank you for your review. I am delighted you had a great evening!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Richard D", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r236112399-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went to Boisdale for dinner with friends. Once again great food & excellent jazz. The sirloin on the none was superb. Highly recommend, if a little pricey. ", " "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r236750060", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Expensive but worth it", "diner_date": " October 2014", "rating_date": "28 October 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Conrad c,", "Thanks for your review. I am delighted you enjoyed the dessert. I am disappointed that you felt our whiskies were overpriced as we try hard to make them competitive and keep the prices down, especially for the slightly older stuff that tends to increase in price by the month. We operate a standard 12.5% service charge which is discretionary. The \u00a39.00 \u2018cover charge\u2019 would have been the music ticket which must be purchased in order to stay for the performance on the second floor, and is purely designed to cover the cost of the performing artist. I hope this clarifies the situation.", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Conrad c", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r236750060-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The last time I was here with with office folks, the cheque was picked up by my boss. This time I was here for some dessert and whiskey post dinner. The Choc fudge pudding was just wonderful but the remaining items on the menu were not that appealing. The Whiskey was over priced and the service charges were really high too. Overall i would say go here only if you want to impress someone. There was even a cover charge of 9 pounds on a Thursday night!! ", " "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r238877183", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday Celebration", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "9 November 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Jan P,", "Thank you for choosing us to celebrate. I am thrilled you had such a wonderful time. We all look forward to welcoming you back.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JanP888", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "549"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "279"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r238877183-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Four of us went to celebrate a birthday. Have heard only very good things for other friends that had visited before, and I must say it lived right up to expectations. Loved the feel and looked of the placed real old school, felt like being in an 1920/1930's supper club. The food was excellent (only small gripe was that they bought the courses out to quickly) but think this was maybe because once the singer started doing his thing, the whole place was up and dancing which I guess made it difficult to navigate the restaurant with trays of food. Would like to add there was the most extensive and fabulous cocktail list (Yes I tried one or two) and the biggest selection of whiskeys I have ever seen. Absolutely loved the place in every way and will 100% be going back, hopefully very early next year. Great night, great food, great booze, great music, great vibe."]}
