{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r237721998", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Lovely place to eat and chill out", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "3 November 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Limey91,", "You will be pleased to hear the two course menu is now priced at \u00a311.95 and is available Monday to Saturday on the first floor Bar & Grill.", "We hope to welcome you again soon!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Limey91", "reviewer_origin": ["Oxfordshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "59"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r237721998-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Food was amazing value, 2 courses for \u00a313.95 (dined there on a Monday evening)", "The Cigar library is fantastic, staff very knowledgeable and the Whiskey menu is substantial. ", "Will be going again!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r233351055", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Casual dinner after movies.", "diner_date": " October 2014", "rating_date": "8 October 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear pwd1960,", "I was delighted to read you had such a great time. I am sure the team look forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "pwd1690", "reviewer_origin": ["Grantown-on-Spey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "237"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "129"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r233351055-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We ended up in the brasserie below the main restaurant.", "Met by a wonderful (manageress we think) pretty lady with blonde hair.", "Excellent service and value for money. ", "The two course menu and the extra for the rib eye well worth the \u00a38.00.", "Food was fantastic as was service.", "We will be back and thank you young lady for looking after us.", "The couple from Scotland."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r238627599", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Table with a view", "diner_date": " November 2014", "rating_date": "7 November 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Maggi49,", "Thank you for your review. I am delighted you enjoyed your evening. If you are looking for a more casual dining experience why don\u2019t you try our first floor Bar & Grill?", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Margaret C", "reviewer_origin": ["Orpington, Kent"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "112"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "87"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r238627599-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Overall a very enjoyable lunch with friends - great views, friendly and helpful staff, very reasonably priced and acceptable house wine (the wine list did read like a chapter of the New Testament - ridiculously huge) food prices Ok but once you tacked on vegetables, the bill did seem over the top. Would love to return but next time would search out the deals!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r231834509", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Birthday Lunch", "diner_date": " September 2014", "rating_date": "30 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Kyp K", "I am delighted you enjoyed you Sunday lunch and hope to welcome you again in the near future. Bear in mind Sunday lunches are very popular during the winter months so please do book in advance to avoid disappointment.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Kyp K", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r231834509-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["8 people for a Birthday Lunch on a Sunday.", "The Staff and service was excellent from start to finish. We had the fixed price lunch with wine at \u00a345 per person. We we offered a glass of pink sparkling wine on arrival at out Table. There was live Jazz music playing in the background. My starter of prawns with boiled ekk was fine but nothing special. The Roast Beef and Potatoes was excellent.", "Then a quick visit to the outside area for a smoke and break as we were all very full at that stage.", "Then back upstairs to the restaurant for our desert. I had Apple crumble and ice cream which was very good.", "Finally back downstairs for a cigar smoke and coffees on the terrace. We were there from 12.30 to 4.00pm. The restaurant is not full on a Sunday so you are not rushed and the service is very good.", "I will be going again and think its a great place for Sunday lunch especially for smokers."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r232150908", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Awsome Whsky Bar!", "diner_date": " September 2014", "rating_date": "1 October 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Tokencollector,", "I am so pleased you enjoyed your time with Ernest at the bar. He was really delighted to guide you talk with you and was very impressed with your knowledge. Indeed we too look forward hopefully welcoming you back.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Tokencollector", "reviewer_origin": ["Winston-Salem, NC"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r232150908-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Saw this listed as one of London's top whisky bars. After checking their list online, I saw that I could knock off a tough one from Ian Buxton's original 101 Whisky's book. I was alone at the bar and received wonderful service. The selection of drams is phenomenal and the prices are reasonable relative to any I've seen in the world (perhaps the best). That's not to say they are inexpensive, but they are a great value relative to most other Whisky/Whiskey bar's I've visited.", "I enjoyed a tour of the bar with small tastings of a number of whiskies beyond those I ordered, The sommelier is very knowledgeable and has a real passion for his craft. Given the chance, I'll definitely return here again!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r232392024", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Music Charges ????", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "3 October 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear TripAdvisor Member,", "I was sorry to read that you were not aware of the music charges. We work very hard to ensure we communicate our music charges clearly to all customers. Should this have not been the case is apologise profusely and am happy to hear the team reacted on the night. That said the music tickets are not serviceable and our system does not allow service to be added to music tickets. ", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Coastal298746", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r232392024-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great food good service , very dark ", "Excellent jazz band , we went for a family birthday , be careful when paying the bill they tried to charge for music \u00a37.50p x 7 = \u00a352.50 plus service charge % on the music again total rip-off , be fair after querying the service charges and the music They removed by charges . Left us all with a bitter taste "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r231546456", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Late Night", "diner_date": " September 2014", "rating_date": "29 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Afoxa,", "Thank you for taking the time to write. I was pleased to read you enjoyed your steak and I have passed your comment regarding the sausages & spinach also onto our chef. That said I am delighted you enjoyed the remainder of your evening with us and hope to see you soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Alice F", "reviewer_origin": ["Vacaville, California"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r231546456-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My husband and I went here for a late night, 10 PM, dinner. I had a very nice filet cooked perfectly and my husband had sausage which he said was just okay. He ordered cream spinach which took two tries but was good when it arrived. I had wanted a Pink Cadillac cocktail which the bartender was not familiar with but he came to our table and asked what was in it. I googled it and he went and made it. Very impressive to take the time to do that. The other plus was the band. This is a Jazz place. The music was great with very talented group playing and singing. I top the meal off with a very yummy Sticky pudding, warm and tasty. So I your looking for a late night outing near Greenwich this is the place. Near the tube and we felt very safe walking at night. Enjoy"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r232820482", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Generally good but disappointing this time", "diner_date": " October 2014", "rating_date": "6 October 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear ian_the_bear,", "Thank you for writing your review. I was sorry to hear you did not enjoy your visit thoroughly. I would be grateful if you would contact me directly via falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk to discuss your evening in more detail.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ian_the_bear", "reviewer_origin": ["Curepipe"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "156"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "59"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "10", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r232820482-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This was our 3rd visit but the service was attrocious on this occasion - a Friday night.", "Although the main course was served promptly, we waited over 1/2 hour for the waiter to notice we were ready for the dessert menu. Ultimately our waiter didn't come and we had to summon someone else instead as he just kept walking past without looking towards us. ", "As we'd paid \u00a320 per head music charge in advance, we didn't expect to be seated at a table right next to the bar. Once the music started, our enjoyment was spoilt by the constant drone of people standing at the bar talking increasing loudly to make themsleves heard above the music. All the seats further back were empty - why let them stand right next to diners and spoil their enjoyment?", "When the waiter tendered the bill, we objected to paying for service and when asked if there was anything wrong with the food, we told him it was because the service was poor.", "He didn't apologise - he just said he was busy. Ah OK, that's alright then - when a place gets busy, you can expect poor service - but they still put service on the bill, hoping you'll just pay it?", "Get more staff it it's busy, surely?", "Advice - ", "1 - Check table allocation if paying for music in advance.", "2 - Avoid on busy nights."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r232861846", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great night out", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "6 October 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Sally H,", "I am pleased you had a great night and thank you for choosing us to celebrate. I hope to welcome you again in the future.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "521SallyH", "reviewer_origin": ["Guildford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "21"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r232861846-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Enjoyed a really nice evening here. Food was great as were the staff and they even treated our birthday girl to her favourite pudding."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r232995582", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "First visit wont be last", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "7 October 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Cheryl V,", "I am pleased to hear you enjoyed your night and look forward to welcoming you again in the future. If you contact me directly under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk I would be happy to assist.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Cheryl V", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r232995582-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Service was lovely , not pretensious and food was tasty. meat dishers are mouthwatering and wine selection is very good with reasonable price. Highly recommended this restaurant. My friend and I agreed we would bring our partners along our next visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r233032303", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great restaurant", "diner_date": " September 2014", "rating_date": "7 October 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Paul G,", "Thank you for choosing us time after time. I am pleased you enjoyed the food and I have passed your comment son to the chef who is needless to say happy. I hope to see you soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ShadowPG", "reviewer_origin": ["Exeter, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r233032303-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Love this restaurant. Every time I have been the steak has been cooked to perfection. The burger is excellent too and the service has been great. The added bonus is the whiskys with over 500 to choose from."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r233084264", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Still great food but awful service", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "7 October 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Pochums,", "Thank you for your feedback. I am delighted you visit us so often and have found the service & food previously great. I was disappointed to read that the service has not lived up to our expectations on this occasion. We work very hard to ensure you have a great time every time our customers visit so reading of your experience will make a difference for the better.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Pochums", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "58"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r233084264-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale has always been a solid favorite of mine. Just based on FB check-in's alone I've been there 93 times (and that's only when I remember to check-in!). On this occasion I had friends over from the US and I wanted them to try haggis (and my favorite bar in the wharf).", "As always, the food was amazing! Since we only wanted drinks and bar snacks we sat at the grill. The spicy scotch quails eggs are a small mouthful of heaven. The crackling is yum and the haggis is great. ", "The service, however, was SO disappointing! After I had talked this place up to my friends, I was actually embarrassed with the service we received. ", "First of all we asked for the haggis starter which is no longer on the menu in the grill but they have always been happy to serve it to us downstairs. After much fuss we eventually convinced the manager to sell it to us. Then after the other snacks and drinks were ordered we were met with surprise at how little we were ordering! How ridiculous!!! Then to add insult to injury, we were asked for a credit card before the food and drinks were served! Just absurd!!!", "I'm sure I will be back to Boisdale as this was only 1 out of over 100 visits where the experience has been so terrible. But I really hope they do some sort of review to make sure this does not become the norm."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r227637111", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday delight", "diner_date": " September 2014", "rating_date": "8 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear EastLondonKiwi,", "Thank you for choosing us to celebrate you special event. I am delighted you enjoyed you fantastic Sunday Lunch offer. Next time you return, let us know so we can make sure to go easy on the wine for you, I would not want you to miss out again. ", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "EastLondonKiwi", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "107"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "83"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r227637111-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife took me here for a birthday lunch.", "We had a beautiful view in a window seat out over Cabot Square. A 3 peace Jazz band played on the main stage which was some distance from the tables. This meant music wafted through the large space without drowning out any possible conversation my wife and I were engaged in. It reminded me of something out of a 1950s gangsta movie, it felt very posh.", "We chose to take up the offer of the Sunday lunch special. 3 courses and loads of free wine (listed as unlimited on the menu) for a set price.", "I started with the Beef Carpaccio, I then moved to the roast ribs lunch, then on to the sticky toffee pudding. Everything was well presented and lovely. I was a bit surprised by the rib offering when it arrived as it looked more like slices of beef than the rack of ribs I was expecting.", "The staff are great, and very attentive. They even sent my pudding out with Happy Birthday written around the edge of the plate in chocolate, and a small candle stuck in my pud. We also got an extra glass of champagne each.", "The place has a huge collection of whiskeys and cigars. And had it not been for the special plying us with such a large quantity of wine, we would have indulged in a few drams.", "This is certainly a restaurant I will keep the number of, and I can see myself returning for a go that the selection of whiskeys."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r229840081", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Sophisticated Bar", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "19 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Tanya-N-London", "Thank your for your review and for converting to Haggis! The outside area is not strictly for members, merely divided and one area is exclusive to our members so we can ensure some spaces for them, but we could not possibly not share our fabulous terrace with everyone! Visit our website for great upcoming acts; for example the magnificent Midge Ure is visiting us for his only London date!", "I hope to welcome you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Tanya-N-London", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "68"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "50"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r229840081-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I've been here a few times for drinks after work with colleagues, and it's a great bar with a sophisticated feel. Service is great, and I have to say I've had some of the best chips in this bar! I've also tried the haggis (not my usual choice of snack!) and it's been great!", "There's an outside balcony area for drinks and food (which I believe is for members only), and you get given blankets when it's cold.", "It tends to be less busy here than some of the other bars in Canary Wharf (this is a few more minutes walk from the Jubilee Line station but close to the DLR station), which is always a nice if you want more of a relaxing drink.", "I haven't myself been here for any of the jazz performances but I've heard they're brilliant"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r227711659", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "another perfect visit", "diner_date": " September 2014", "rating_date": "8 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you Raj C.", "I am pleased to hear Filipe looks after you so well. As a thank you to him, courtesy of your review, Filipe will have a bottle of Boisdale 1er Cru champagne to collect; a gift to all members of staff that get mentioned in despatches. We all look forward to welcoming you back again soon!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "409rajc", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r227711659-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["once again I took some guests here and they cant stop raving about it. Excellent whisky, rum and cigars......as always we were given great service by Fillipe who makes the visit perfect every time. Thanks. Brilliant night"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r229606926", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great hearty food, quite expensive", "diner_date": " December 2013", "rating_date": "18 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear RSLAL,", "Thank you for posting your review, though I am irked you thought the food expensive. We do have fine things available, for example our dry aged steaks. It takes time and effort to mature the beef and as a result it is dearer however the flavour is far superior to other steaks. At the same time we also work hard to be great value and it is not difficult to have a two course meal for under \u00a325.00 and a set menu is available for \u00a319.95. ", "For your next visit make sure to also look at our incredible whisky list & perhaps you could also enjoy a cigar on one of our terraces.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "RSLAL", "reviewer_origin": ["Rainham, Kent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "64"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r229606926-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great hearty food, quite expensive", "I visited here with two colleagues for lunch and although the food was great, the price was far too much. I would happily take clients here though and indulge in the bar and the great wine list!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r230104945", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good Food, Great Venue", "diner_date": " September 2014", "rating_date": "21 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear LAG22", "Thank you for your review. I am delighted you enjoyed your evening with us and am pleased to hear your thought on our service. We all look forward to welcoming you again very soon!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Lionel G", "reviewer_origin": ["Krakow, Poland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "86"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r230104945-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This is the second time I have visited this restaurant", "The first visit was for an office XMas party and it was ok, however the place was full of other parties and a set menu", "The second visit was with some work colleagues", "We started with some drinks in the bar - a little crowded but very pleasant lots of choices of whisky and spirits", "We had booked one of the private dining rooms, there was no additional charge for this however we did have to have a minimum number of people", "The staff were very attentive, explaining the menu and making recommendations when asked ", "The meal was very good, fair sized portion and great taste", "They did explain the menu does change with the season to ensure ingredients are as fresh as possible", "It was expensive, not the most expensive for the area, but was worth the expense", "I will be returning at some point"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r230125007", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Love the music", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "21 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear BMSAH", "I am pleased to hear you have had such a wonderful time on your second visit. Please let me know when you plan to return via falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk, I would like to thank you personally", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "BMSAH", "reviewer_origin": ["Scotland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "33"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r230125007-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Second visit and we were not disappointed. We had great seats the band were great and the food excellent. The service was spot on. Our waitress was knowledgable about the food and left us time in between courses to enjoy the show and have a relaxing time. I will most definitely be back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r231544278", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Venue all round", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "29 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear ukfowler,", "Thank you for your kind review. I am delighted you enjoyed Sandy\u2019s recommendation and I hope to welcome you back soon.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ukfowler", "reviewer_origin": ["Yangon (Rangoon), Myanmar"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "245"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "101"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r231544278-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I had dinner arranged at Boisdale for me by a contact in Canary Wharf- Sandy Madhvani @ David M Robinson. Fantastic service- table and champagne waiting. Impressive menu, great food. Great atmosphere later on with music and phenomenal bars.", "I have subsequently visited for drinks only and was extremely impressed with the professionalism and knowledge of the bartenders- Daniele was great and kept me entertained and topped up for a long while.", "Will definitely call back when in CW."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r230463418", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great room, fantastic band, food still average.", "diner_date": " September 2014", "rating_date": "23 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Captain B", "Thank you for your second review. I would like to say that we are not a steak house rather than a British restaurant that serves excellent steaks, which have been on many occasions commented on by customers as the best they have eaten. Still we serve more than fine steaks and offer a wide variety of seafood and turf equally. As with all foods they are natural product and we do have checks in place to ensure that oysters meet a minimum size, should you have felt otherwise, I always recommend customers to comment on the night so we can rectify a situation then and there to avoid a bitter aftertaste; though I can understand that you chose otherwise. The partridge should have been served with a steak knife to help carve it, however cooking it more has a detrimental effect on texture and taste however I am delighted your guest enjoyed our Haggis. I am delighted you enjoyed the Picpoul de Pinet and agree that the price point is excellent. We price our whisky selection very competitively and \u00a315 for a whisky of that age is very reasonable, still it may vary greatly from one distillery to another. We are a music venue and we are restaurant alike so we pride ourselves on great food and music. I am disappointed that you felt the quality of our offer below par on both occasions but am happy you enjoyed the music.", "Do not hesitate to contact me in the future should I be able to assist in any way.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Captain B", "reviewer_origin": ["Bangkok, Thailand"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "160"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "87"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "50", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r230463418-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I came here in July and had what I described as not the best steak in town. Since then I have been to other steak houses, mainly the Hawsmoor chain and each one unquestionly better than here. When I was told the the Bogus Blues Brothers were playing here, my fist thought was that I really wanted to see them but wasnt sure about if I wanted to pay up for average food again. Given the circumstances, I went for it. It was a fairly expensive night, with the food and drinks bill at \u00a3340 for 4 of us but then another \u00a3100 for our table as the band was playing. Im still not sure if thats right, but the place was full so I guess its working for them. ", "First the food... We had Jersey Rocks to start, my wifes favourite oysters. They were surprisingly small, some actually really should not have been served as they were tiny. That sort of soured things a bit for me, My guests had Haggis which was described as excellent and Partridge which was probably a little too undercooked as she was struggling to carve it. My wife and I had the \"special\" Sea Trout, which wasnt. It was really very average and as such very disapointing. ", "We were recommended a most excellent Picpoul de Pinet which came in at a reasonable \u00a332.50 which was pleasing to see listed. The cocktails were under a tenner which was good but the 15 year old whiskies at \u00a315 seemed a little rich, but i cant complain...They were very good.", "The band were wonderful and great fun. The room was beautiful, warm red walls, low lighting and candles made for a lovely atmosphere. Sadly, they decided to put the \u00a350 per head tables at the very front , which was fine for them, but at the expense of the dance area which was about 4 sqm. As you might imagine , it got pretty crowded in there. ", "It has been pointed out to me that generally if you go to a music venue, you should consider yourself lucky if the food is half decent. I dont really consider Boisdales as a music venue , but more a restaurant that has music..As such the food really should be bette rin my opinion. Maybe I shouldnt have such high expectations , it is a great room with fairly priced drinks, which just happens to serve average food. Nothing wrong with that I guess."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r230326910", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good Burgers, Pricey Cigars", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "22 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear AlexA,", "Thank you for your thoughts on our offer. I am happy you enjoyed the terrace and the service. I was sorry to read that you felt the service rushed, we have had some unexpectedly busy night and have taken precautions to counteract. With regards to our cigar offer, I would like to think we are very competitive when it comes to pricing when you compare us to similar cigar venues. Thank you again for your thought and I look forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "aadamopoulos67", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "234"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "156"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r230326910-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["In Canary Wharf there is some great dining. Boisdale isn't ideal for families with children given the artwork and the jazz and bar scene but for covered outdoor seating it's a good choice and has decent food. Burgers are good, service is rushed and if you do venture to the cigar bar area be prepared to pay a premium unless you've brought your own."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r231250507", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "A missed opportunity", "diner_date": " September 2014", "rating_date": "27 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Martijn V,", "I was disappointed to read that the service did not meet the standards we set ourselves. The night in questions was particularly busy with an unusually large number of diners turning up without a booking. Sadly you were the one is suffer. Friday & Saturday nights are our big show nights that have been designed to substitute our customers having to find various venues to attend. Pre-dinner drinks, dinner, show and post dinner drinks all combined into one. It is on these nights the music tends to have more volume than during the week. Should this have disturbed you, you will find that Boisdale is more to your liking during the week. 12.5% service charge is a standard throughout most of the hospitality industry in London and you are, as you have done, welcome to omit it should you feel it was not deserved.", "Hopefully we will have the opportunity to welcome you on another night to show you our other side. Please feel free to contact me directly under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk should you wish to do so.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Martijn V", "reviewer_origin": ["The Hague, The Netherlands"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r231250507-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["At first glance the Boisdale seems to have it all: a great location, a decent menu, fashionable web-site, beautiful whisky cabinet and access to London's cr\u00e8me de la cr\u00e8me of business people.", "In September of 2014 we, a group of eleven former students, flew over to London for a long weekend to celibrate our 25th anniversary. We went cycling, went shopping at Harrod's, had our picture taken at Buckingham Palace and went to the Boisdale for our main dinner event. What a deception.", "About ten minutes into our meal the live band that had been promised started playing. I have to hand it to them: they were on tune, entertaining and had a nice repetoir. The problem was with the Boisdale: the volume was horrendous. For the full length it was virtually impossible to talk to eachother without screaming at one another.", "After the initial pouring of the wine we were left to our own devices. This meant that if someone wanted a refill he had tp get up, find the wine, pour himself a glass and them return the wine. Apparantly the waiters were paying attention at one point, because they did materialize to bring new bottles, but pour them? No sir.", "But the worst was the audience. Don't get me wrong, as a former student, I have been guilty of many a transgretion in restaurants. Maybe I am getting old, but when the other guests start annoying even us, then they are obnoxious. After the live band the Boisdale turned on the standard bunch of golden oldies and around us the guests started singing along and dancing. Enthusiasm is great, but definately not you are looking for in a restaurant like the Boisdale.", "We skipped desert and deleted the 12.5% service fee they give themselves by default.", "In conclusion: delicious food, terrible service and repulsive clients."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r225147355", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Can't recommend highly enough", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "28 August 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for you wonderful review,", "I am delighted you had such a lovely time & that Richard looked after you so well.", "Please let me know when you return so I can thank you personally.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Maggie Z", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r225147355-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I've been to a lot of 'luxury' restaurants all over the world, Boisdale outdid all of them. The food was amazing, the live music and venue were superb and the service was absolutely outstanding. We visited for my father's 60th birthday and our server Rich made sure it was a memorable and enjoyable night. Honestly cannot heap enough praise on this place. Fantastic! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r227379338", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Music and Dining Not To Be Missed", "diner_date": " September 2014", "rating_date": "6 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Ken B,", "Thank you for joining us on Atila\u2019s Sinatra Night. It was a real pleasure to meet you and your charming wife. I look forward to seeing both of you return soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ken B", "reviewer_origin": ["Melbourne, Australia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "30"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r227379338-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife and I have just had a cracking good evening at this smart yet relaxed supper club. Walking in is a bit like stepping back in time. The room is a warm red, with soft lighting and every type of alcohol one has ever heard of, and many more that are both rare and rarified. The walls are covered with unique pieces of art, including photos of movie stars of the 1940's and 50\"s. The entire ambiance announces \"sophistication\".", "The tables are comfortably spaced and candle lit, reminding me of the supper clubs of old movies where each table has it's own small lamp. I half expected to see Bogart and Bacall come strolling in.", "There is an entire room devoted to the finest cigars to be sampled after dinner.", "The menu is largely fine cuisine Scottish stye. The steak was expertly prepared. Wait staff are plentiful, polite and available while never intrusive.", "But wait...it gets better....much better if you like jazz. There is live jazz most nights. We had the pleasure of hearing a young vocalist call Atila who has devoted himself to the American Songbook in general and Sinatra in particular. Tonight was two sets of Sinatra standards, many of them difficult pieces to sing (unless you happen to be Frank). This fellow did an outstanding job. Wonderful voice and presence and backed up by a swinging quartet.", "When you visit be sure to meet the maitre d' Falco. He is a wonderful host who understands the old fashioned art of looking after his guests."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r224325993", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Food is good, staff ....", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "25 August 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear cdi_review", "Thank you for taking the time to review us. I would appreciate further information regarding this incident. Kindly contact me via falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk.", "I look forward to hearing from you.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "cdi_review", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "119"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "48"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r224325993-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The food is good, I mean its an oyster bar... but this review has to do with the staff... rude. Witnessed how a member of staff was treating a person on the elevator that was not a boisdale customer. Mr. if you are still working for boisdale you should get fired. You were rude. The customers, that actually have money, didn't say a word but you thought you had the right.... Disrespectful and a low-class, that is what you are. Hope I'll never see you again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r225246195", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Quality time and time again", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "29 August 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Anthony K,", "Thank you for taking the time (finally) to write a review! I am delighted you enjoy visiting us over & over again. I hope to see you soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Anthony K", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "65"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r225246195-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I've been going to Boisdale now since they first opened about 2 years ago and it's constantly brilliant.", "I've been for the jazz nights , New Year's Eve dinners , valentine dinners , burger and rugby afternoons ,eaten on the first floor many many times as well as popped in for a well needed beer.", "I went again on Wednesday , just a straight forward steak this time with a few sides. Brilliant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r224115756", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fab Sunday roast", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "24 August 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Tennisbanch,", "thank you for joining us on a Sunday. I am pleased to hear you enjoyed the food and service so much! I hope I can welcome you back soon, maybe on another day of the week the music is more to your liking? See our website for all the upcoming acts.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Tennisbanch", "reviewer_origin": ["Brentwood, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "214"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "101"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r224115756-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked for the Sunday 3 course which was \u00a335 or \u00a345 including unlimited wine. Fantastic food one of the best roast beef Sunday meals we can remember, staff were attentive and friendly and atmosphere welcoming. Music was nice as well but it is probably the food we would go back for. Definitely be back on a Sunday"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r225279993", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Just Great!!", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "29 August 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear EliseBanks,", "I am delighted that you enjoyed the First Floor Bar and had such a good time trying to figure all the pictures out. Next time your want to join us let me know under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk . I would love to say hi personally.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "EliseBanks", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r225279993-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I went on Saturday 23 August with a friend for dinner but the restaurant was fully booked BooHoo!!", "But was told we could eat on the first floor Terrace Bar on arrival our waiter was very charming and we ordered burgers that was soooo delicious, that we ordered another one to share between us yummy!! then we had dessert for four people!! Mega yummy!! Great food and lovely wine.", "Will definitely be back!! Great setting amazing pictures had a fun time naming all the stars!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r225579065", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Food, Great View, Great Jazz", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "31 August 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Don T,", "Thank you for following you friend\u2019s recommendation. There can be no better praise for us than others recommending us. ", "When you are next in town, please make sure to stop by so we can thank you!", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Don T", "reviewer_origin": ["Naples, Florida"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "259"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "80"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r225579065-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Friends suggested this restaurant to us, and we were not disappointed.", "Located on the second floor of the Canary Wharf building, this posh restaurant has outstanding decor and fantastic service. We were seated with a nice view of the park outside, and enjoyed both the view and the live jazz.", "But the best part was the food. I ordered salmon and my companion had chicken breast. The salmon was prepared perfectly, and with tangy seasoning. I loved it. My companion said the chicken was the most tasty and tender she could remember.", "The price is a bit on the high side, but not exorbitant and well worth it."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r227342094", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "6 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Kazzer2014", "Thank you for posting your review. I am sorry to hear you did not enjoy the music on the night. We have quite a strict booking policy in which we only commit to book great artists with a proven track record; so it is unfortunate to hear you felt disappointed. On the upside it is great to hear you enjoyed food and drink. I hope to welcome you back soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Kazzer2014", "reviewer_origin": ["Minster on Sea, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "282"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "83"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r227342094-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The whole evening was lovely, we went on a Saturday evening, with a tribute band playing, although they weren't that good it did not spoil the food and wine which was lovely, I had the duck which was cooked to perfection, good choice of wines and if you love whiskey this is the place to go, it has hundreds of them all along the back of the bar, beautiful view they say by the window is the cheaper tables because the view of the stage, we booked for another space to see the stage, but they asked us if we wanted the window seat which we did and was pleased it was a lovely summer evening where we could people watch eat good food and drink good wine."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r226353808", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great night", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "2 September 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for taking the time to review us.", "I am delighted you stayed on for the music and managed to have a great time. Regarding our pricing, the deal you enjoyed is obviously wonderful, however you can manage to have a two course meal and a bottle of wine for under \u00a330.00 per person so I would argue that we are able to provide great value, next to the finer things in life, too. Nevertheless I look forward to welcoming you again soon for one of our exciting upcoming acts.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JANET D", "reviewer_origin": ["Henley-on-Thames, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r226353808-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Dined here on a 50% off the food deal which made it manageable as otherwise it would have been a very expensive evening. The food was very good and the waiter was just the right side of attentive and chatty, which gave a nice friendly feel to what could have been quite a cold formal restaurant. ", "The wine list was very expensive and other drinks likewise. ", "We also visited on a Saturday night when they had a live band. It was \u00a310 per person to stay for the band, but I'm glad we did in the end. It turned a nice meal into a great four hour evening. The staff even (unbidden) reset a table closer to the band when they saw us turning round to see them. All in all a great time. A bit pricey, but if you can get a deal ( which seem to come around quite often) it is well worth a visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r226895561", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice place for the hustle & bustle of the Wharf!", "diner_date": " April 2014", "rating_date": "4 September 2014", "answer_text": ["I am so delighted you enjoyed your evening with is.", "We do strive to give it a cool Supper Club feeling so I could not agree with you more. Make sure to check our website for great upcoming acts & events like our \u2018In 80 drams around the world\u2019.", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "shamitp", "reviewer_origin": ["Romford, England, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "312"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "139"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r226895561-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This review is a tad overdue. Came here for my wife's birthday dinner. Lovely surroundings with a Jazz Club feel (as it is) and outdoor balcony terrace for the cigar aficionados. It was early on a Saturday evening so It wasn't terribly busy. I cannot exactly recall exactly what we both had bit it was off the Fixed Price menu and was delicious. I recall Having the Smoked Salmon with Octopus (yes, OCTOPUS) slices and it was excellent! Our waitress Luz, was very attentive and even though we were perched at the side of the restaurant, she came running to us when needed! Will be back with the boys sometime, as they have a great selection of Cuban Cigars and special Jazz nights to boot!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r223009666", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing night out!", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "19 August 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear RachChap72,", "Thank you for taking the time to write such a lovely review. I am really pleased to hear that you had an amazing time. Please let us know when you return under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk so we can say thank you in person!", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "RachChap72", "reviewer_origin": ["Chelmsford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r223009666-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I had the best night out for a long time at this restaurant. We had a great start with a drink in the oyster bar on the first floor followed by a three course meal in the main candlelit restaurant. We were fortunate to be seated at the front of the restaurant near the stage where we were entertained by an absolutely fantastic jazz session. Excellent food and drink, the staff were friendly and knowledgable of the food and drinks menu, and the music made the night. Can't wait to go back with friends!! ", "16/08/2014"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r216178743", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect for late night cigar on the terrace", "diner_date": " May 2014", "rating_date": "19 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear iDuck85,", "Thank you for such a lovely review. I am delighted you had such a pleasant time on our terraces; thankfully the weather has been fabulous the last few weeks. When it gets colder later on in the year there are plenty heaters to keep you warm, in case you were wondering. We look forward to welcoming you again very soon!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Idun M", "reviewer_origin": ["Oslo, Norway"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r216178743-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went here late in the evening after a theatre. The entrance is somewhat unassuming, inside some sort of shopping center. Staff was very pleasant, and immediately seated me at a good table on the terrace. Whisky selection is of course extensive, and you can smoke both your own cigars, or purchase some from their collection. Staff was very attentive. Pleasant for solo travellers, but would also be recommended for business or friends."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r216527367", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Sunday Lunch", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "21 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear AVLux,", "Thank you for choosing us to celebrate your anniversary. I am delighted that you were looked after by our team and hope to welcome you back in the near future. For all our great music check out our website, one of my personal favourites is coming up on the 6th September for a Sinatra Night when Atila swings easy. Sublime!", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "AVLux", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r216527367-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife and I had Sunday Lunch at Boisdale to celebrate our anniversary, with our friends, Brady and Rachel and it was our first visit to the restaurant. The lunch menu is excellent value, with 3 courses and unlimited wine for \u00a345 per head, however we opted to order our own drinks and the wine and food quality was very good. We were sat on the terrace overlooking the fountain at Cabot Place and we were even offered sun glasses if the glare on the terrace was too bright. On a lovely Sunday afternoon the service was excellent and although the waiter splashed some gravy over Brady, soda water as produced in order to remove the stains and free drinks and the offer of dry cleaning also made, at the end of the meal we we were given a 20% discount on the overall price of the bill. It was a genuine accident but the staff dealt with the situation in the correct way and efficiently. ", "Food", "The starters were tasty and the mains which included roast potatoes cooked in duck fat and side vegetables were very well cooked. The sticky toffee puddings and creme br\u00fbl\u00e9e was wonderful with no complaints whatsoever. Finally we were giver a tour of the cigar lounge and humidor and we are already discussing another visit to the main restaurant in order to take in one of the music shows. A really pleasant afternoon."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r216976409", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Must return", "diner_date": " June 2014", "rating_date": "23 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Renelekonk,", "I am pleased you enjoyed your lunch with us and thank you for taking the time to write a review.", "We look forward to seeing you again soon!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Renelekonk", "reviewer_origin": ["Hornchurch, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "59"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "39"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r216976409-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited here for Sunday Lunch, but booked a late table unfortunately did not realise it closed early on a Sunday. Had a great time here with friends in a very relaxed but lively atmosphere.", "The service was top notch and the food cooked to perfection. I must return to enjoy the ambience and the live music another time, next time I will be booking an earlier table so I can soak up the surroundings a little better. The Bar is quite a spectacle, probably one of the smartest I have ever seen, and believe me I`ve seen a few!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r220140739", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Evening of Jazz", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "6 August 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Linda B,", "Thank you for taking the time to write a review. I am delighted to hear that you enjoyed your time with us. I would like to point out that although we of course have items on the menu that are a little dearer, think Fillet on the Bone, there are however plenty options to choose from that let you have two courses for under \u00a325.00 as well as more than 6 wines prices under the same mark.", "Have a great week and we look forward to welcoming you back soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Linda B", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "56"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "40"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r220140739-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Have been here a few times and if you are a jazz lover it is a good venue. Food is a little pricey for what it is and so to are the wines, but a great selection of cocktails. It is great on Sundays for lunch for all the family. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r220724235", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "I will be back", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "9 August 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you chandler132 for you review.", "I am happy you enjoyed yourself with us. As I have mentioned in the previous review there are also many excellent value wines to choose from. With regards to the waiter keeping your glasses filled, this is a truly personal opinion and we try to walk the fine line between keeping you well looked after and not being too intrusive. Should you feel we get it wrong, just kindly notify the waiter and he or she will happily adjust their service for you.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "chandler132", "reviewer_origin": ["Mondorf-les-Bains, Luxembourg"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r220724235-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["It was an very pleasant experience.", "The lobster cooked to perfection, the wine was good but a bit pricey.", "The service was very good, but waiter was pushing la bit too much into the consumption ! Service & charge!!!", "The music was really good, that create a great atmosphere."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r221777135", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good food with Jazz thrown in", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "14 August 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Batch65,", "Thank you for your review. I am delighted you thought our service to be attentive. For the summer season we have adopted a new menu with more lighter choices available, I am sure more classic dishes will return in the near future as the weather changes. For additional information about the music, do have a peek on our website for exciting upcoming bands.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Batch65", "reviewer_origin": ["Maldon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "135"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "39"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r221777135-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had dinner here recently. The staff were very attentive and whilst the menu is not as varied as some others I have experienced I personally thought it was a good mix of traditional Scottish fare and the usual steaks. I had the potted smoked mackerel and a main of haggis both of which were very good, in fact there were no issues with our food. ", "I would like to agree with some of the other contributors, in that, I thought the wine a little expensive but I think this is the norm in Canary Wharf.", "The addition of the live jazz to the atmosphere was very welcome and the trio we saw were very good."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r217417448", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Power dining in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "25 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Christian D,", "Thank you for visiting us and for taking the time to write your review. I was disappointed to hear that your steak was not cooked to perfection & you thought the salad was not value for money. We have recently changed our menu to provide many lighter and seasonal items that should help make a choice for any preference. I am sorry you feel differently. To address the topping up of glasses you found irritating, I apologise if you felt that way; we try to strike a balance between attentive and discreet, but is remains a highly personal opinion of where that balance should be and it remains at your discretion to notify the waiter.", "In case there is a path that leads you to return to us, I would be happy if you would let me know under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "christiand441", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "114"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "33"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r217417448-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Dinner was a little disappointing. If you do not like steaks I do not think the alternative mains were particularly appealing . The dressed crab starter was good but the minced venison with pasta, while tasty, hardly looked appetising. Extremely dull presentation.", "My partner had a steak. Frankly, it looked dry and unappealing. It was supposed to be 'medium rare' but was more medium-to-well done. Her salad comprised a few items with some oil drizzled them them. Hardly value for money.", "Service was good but the constant re-filling of glasses bordered on irritating.", "OK, adequate, but not a place I'd beat a path to return to. I had lunch at Jamie Oliver's Barbecoa the same week and the choices, steaks and atmosphere were a standard above."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r222233382", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Very good meal and service but mind your ears when the band gets going", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "16 August 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear AmberK,", "Thank you for your review which I enjoyed reading. I am delighted you found the food lovely and enjoyed you evening in general. Depending on the day of the week the music ranges from gentle background tunes to full on live performances on the weekends designed to substitute you having to find a theatre or such. These can be quite loud at times and should you not have been interested there is always to option of moving to our Bar & Grill on the first floor or our heated and covered terraces to continue you evening with us where you can of course enjoy some of our nearly 1000 whiskies.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "AmberK", "reviewer_origin": ["St. John's, Canada"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "500"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "250"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r222233382-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["There are two places to eat in the same building; the oyster bar and the main, upper floor restaurant . We ate in the upstairs restaurant and made a reservation through Opentable.", "We were a party of 5 of diverse tastes and yet everyone was able to find something on the menu that appealed to them. The food is generally sourced from Scotland. The mini haggis as an appetizer was quite tasty and a nice intro to a traditional dish for those who want to try it.", "My companions found the food very good. I was less impressed with my selections but everything was hot and well prepared and presented. Prices were quite reasonable. ", "We were too full for pudding but the cheese tray passed by several times and it looked amazing. Next time I'll forgo the starter and wait for cheese.", "We quite enjoyed our evening until the live band came on stage. Apparently this is customary and somewhat of a draw. It wasn't for us. Far too loud to even shout above. We quickly asked for the cheque and left. ", "That was a shame as the bar has 150 types of whiskey and we would have loved to have sat around tasting various whiskeys. ", "Overall cost was very reasonable. Look for specials on Opentable."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r222356600", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Ditch the music", "diner_date": " August 2014", "rating_date": "17 August 2014", "answer_text": ["SimonPainter123,", "Thank you for your review. I am pleased you enjoyed food and service to such an extent. As I have mentioned in the previous review the music ranges in volume and intensity and I apologise should you have thought it loud and unpleasant. We only book some of the finest artists around in the UK and the styles of music vary. Luckily you did move to the first floor and were able to continue your evening; something I always recommend to customers not wanting the music.", "I hope to see you soon,", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "SimonPainter123", "reviewer_origin": ["Leeds, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "117"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "51"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r222356600-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The food was excellent and the service very attentive. Cannot fault the menu; I had a perfect rib eye after a delightful haggis starter. Good food, good wine, good whisky, good cigars and of course great service from a friendly team.", "Only gripe is the music, it was too loud and a bit rubbish, we escaped to the terrace to get away from it so we didn't have to shout to have a conversation."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r214645928", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Entertainment", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "10 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Zoe W,", "I am delighted you enjoyed the performance but am irked that you thought the food was below the standard we set ourselves. Should you wish to provide me with additional information, please contact me under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk. I look forward to hearing from you.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ZoeJustineWhite1", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r214645928-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Food was average , wasn't overly impressed. The Michael Jackson tribute we saw was fantastic, created a great atmosphere as we were up on our feet dancing the whole evening. Overall a great night"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r216131370", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good food - but overpriced ", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "18 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear SeonaCallanan,", "I am delighted to hear you enjoyed your meal and the drinks. I was however irked that the service did not live up to expectations. Should you wish to discuss you experience in more detail, please contact me at falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "SeonaCallanan", "reviewer_origin": ["Cork"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r216131370-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The food was really good, duck and steak were great. Desert was Devine and so was the baileys coffee! Only downside was having to pay for the service, or lack of..had to flag down the waitress to get stuff - fair enough she was very busy - lack of staff perhaps?? All in all food was good but the bill zoomed upwards with service charge."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r214444783", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What an evening", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "9 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Sue O,", "Thank your taking the time to write your review and also for commenting so wonderfully about our team. I am thrilled to hear you had an amazing time. I look forward to seeing you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sue O", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r214444783-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Heard of this through a friend so gave it a try, food excellent, service great and the entertainment as a bonus was amazing! Was a Michael Jackson tribute with Celena Cherry, they had everyone up dancing definitely a night to remember and better than I expected for a meal out."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r214391575", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent night and entertainment....MJ all the way :-)", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "8 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear turkishtraveller2014", "I am delighted you had such a great evening and thank you to your partner to choosing us! We are conscious to providing excellent value for money and also more refined options, so please do see our website for detailed information on set menus, offers and a tremendous variety of foods and drinks for all expectations and occasions.", "I look forward to welcoming you back soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "turkishtraveller2014", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r214391575-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I had a suprise event booked by my girlfriend in this restaurant.I normally dont like suprises however the guys really put on a good show really got the crowd moving and overpriced food didnt seem that bad by the end of the night...Excellent evening and definetly want to see what other shows this place can conjure up :-)"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r214558594", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Touch of Class", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "9 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear robert j,", "What a wonderful review; thank you! Please let me know when you plan on retuning at falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk, I would like to thank you personally.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "GOM-Grumpyoldman", "reviewer_origin": ["edinburgh"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "42"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r214558594-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Excellent in every way. Quality of food,presentation, surroundings, staff, atmosphere - all were excellent. This is a quality establishment that is most definitely worth visiting. The staff were fabulous, attentive without being intrusive. The food was superb. Quality of ingredients was excellent, very talented chefs. Yes.. you occasionally have to block out the \"white noise\" generated by some of the pretentious City Boys who meet and eat here... but even that cannot detract from a great ambiance and really pleasant surroundings. Meal was good value and pretty much everything about Boisdale feels like quality. If you are in this part of London this should be on your list."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r214487272", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great night out and MIchael Jackson performance was awesome!!", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "9 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you Nima S four your kind review.", "I am delighted to hear you enjoyed your evening so much. We always work hard to make sure your guests have a memorable evening. ", "I look forward to your return.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Nima S", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r214487272-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I loved the food and atmosphere was amazing! The Michael Jackson tribute performers were great!! Loved everything from the costumes to vocals and music in general. Will be back for more!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r214830489", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Michael Jackson show rocked", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "11 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Jack A,", "Thank you for taking the time to review. I am delighted you enjoyed your evening with us to such an extent.", "Hopefully we will see you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jack A", "reviewer_origin": ["St Albans, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r214830489-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great food and the entertainment was top notch. The service was also excellent, I will keep an eye out for the show's return"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r215780938", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great business lunch location", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "16 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Sdwoo,", "I am delighted you enjoyed you lunch with us and the sun shone on you. Being located on the first and second floor only does have its challenges as you point out, but we have added signs around our entrances to make it as easy as we possible to locate us. Hopefully you can agree that finding us was worth your time and I look forward to welcoming you back soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sdwoo", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "982"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "295"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r215780938-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I'd heard good things about this place, so decided to try it out for a lunch meeting. It is not the easiest place to find, unless you know what you are looking for. In Cabot Place shopping centre on the Ground Floor head for the City end, take the last corridor on the left hands idea which has a red Boisdale sign on the roof. Take the lifts up to the 2nd floor. We were shown to our table which overlooked Cabot Square with the Cheesegrater and Walkie Talkie in the distance. We opted for main meals only, I went for the truffle burger, which had a strong flavour, and was very filling, but enjoyable. With some wine we were pretty full and only managed coffees. The price wasn't too bad either. The food was good, the best part was the view out on a sunny day."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r215523577", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Scotch, Steaks, and Cigars", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "15 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear WGibson648,", "Thank you for taking the time to write your review. I am delighted to hear you regularly visit and find us consistent. We work hard to keep our standards up and high to ensure each customer is looked after well. I agree that the whisky and wine lists are expansive, but would like to point out that there are also a large number of wines under \u00a330.00 per bottle and a vast selection on whiskies under \u00a315.00 per large measure. With the exchange rate varying constantly in both directions this will, fortunately for us, affect any other establishment you visit.", "I look forward to welcoming you back soon to enjoy the fabulous weather in London at on our terraces.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "WGibson648", "reviewer_origin": ["Westport, Connecticut"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "188"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "49"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r215523577-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I have visited Boisdale at Canary Wharf (and Boisdale of Belgravia) many times, and have found it a consistent meal. Be forewarned, however, this is not an inexpensive restaurant. The selection of single-malts is extensive, and the wine list expansive (and expensive); the exchange rate in July 2014 is $1.74 to 1GBP, so be prepared. The steaks are from grass-fed animals, so sometimes have a lot of gristle. But they are tasty!!", "The Cigar Bar and humidor is very enjoyable, with a wide selection of Cuban cigars. Enjoy them on the patio, and appreciate the sunset over Canary Wharf."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r216033350", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Not the best steak in town", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "18 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Captain B,", "Thank you for taking the time to review. I was disappointed to hear that your experience did not live up to the high standards we set ourselves. All our steaks are dry aged and have repeatedly been commented on as very tasty indeed. If your steak was below par I do sincerely apologise as well as for the wrong spinach being served. I too believe it was a coincidence that you had to suffer from. I hope you can be tempted to return and if you do please let me know under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Captain B", "reviewer_origin": ["Bangkok, Thailand"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "160"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "87"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r216033350-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["In years gone by, when I wanted a steak, Boisdales in Victoria was the place i went. A lovely and atmospheric place where the food was never great but always fun. When the urge for a steak hits me nowadays there is so much more choice and pretty much all of them are good. I guess over the years i have become spoilt buy Goodmans because the food there is always first class. When considering a steak in Canary Wharf, I thought I would try this moderately new branch of Boisdales to be different but I can safely say it wont be my first choice next time the urge comes. ", "The setting is great, especially on a warm summers day (yes we actually are having some) so we sat outside on the terrace. The table we were offered had zero leg room so we were \"allowed\" to sit in the members area, which offered great room.It was nicely secluded and a perfect temperature.", " We started with Jersey rocks which were excellent and both went for our old favourites..the Rib-Eye. My colleage went for medium rare , which I have always been advised not to do with this cut as the extra cooking produces more flavour from the fat. As such I opted for medium. This as it transpired was a massive mistake as it was overcooked, dry and a little cold. As my colleague was happy with his rarer one I did not send it back...but it resulted in a very indifferent meal. The creamed spinach turned up as wilted instead, which again wasnt the end of the world.", "It could have been just an off day so I am not making this an offical complaint more of a niggle...The wine list was excellent and offered a great range of wines and prices, something I always approve of. ", "Its a nice restaurant..and on a summers day, I might be tempted to return, but in all honesty, if I want a steak...Its Goodmans every time."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r212287189", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Excellent food, but mosquitoes flying around the table and not great service", "diner_date": " June 2014", "rating_date": "27 June 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Gabriella W,", "Thank you for taking the time to write your review.", "I am pleased that you enjoyed our food; however was vexed by your comment regarding flies in the restaurant and our service.", "We take every precaution to prevent such a problem & have rigorous cleaning procedures in place. As a result we have been awarded 5 out of 5 in the Food Standards Agency rating for food hygiene 4 years running. This year we are challenged. We are open from 11am to midnight and as we have had a fantastic start to the summer with high temperatures blessing us daily. The doors to our terraces on the first floor are open all throughout this period. Coupled with the Thames being close by this generates high humidity & provides flies ideal conditions to thrive in. We are working very closely with our pest control contractor to minimise the impact and using all methods available to food premises. ", "Should you wish to discuss in further detail please do not hesitate to contact me under dgm@boisdale-cw.co.uk. I look forward to hearing from you.", "Yours sincerely", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Gabriela W", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "20", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r212287189-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["It is hard to give an overall review to this restaurant because on one hand the food was really amazing, we were 4 people at the table and we all enjoyed our meal very much. However, the service was terrible, our waiter was not providing good attention to our table, for instance there was a period of time about 40 mins where our empty glasses were sitting at the table with no one to offer another drink. ", "We also had the unpleasant experience of having mosquitoes flying around our table, we mentioned this to the floor manager and he said : \"It is the time of the year, is very hot and humid, nobody complained of having mosquitoes AT THIS TABLE before, do you want to switch tables?\". I think, this is an unacceptable at any restaurant.", "We stayed for the jazz band and it was really amazing too. We all enjoyed the music very much."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r211059293", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best Dining Experience at Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "19 June 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear chris l,", "Thank you for your kind review. I am delighted you enjoyed your stay with us. We all look forward to welcoming you again in the near future.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Chris L", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "246"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "91"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r211059293-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This restaurant has it all, formal dining, informal dinning, great oyster/drinks bar and great music evenings. Restaurant is fabulous with stunning views over one of the CW water features. Opt for the table by the windows. Food, wines superb and service tip top. Definitely a place to celebrate a business deal, celebrate a special event or propose! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r211902046", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "World class experience", "diner_date": " March 2014", "rating_date": "24 June 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Agie01", "Thank you for your praise. It makes all of us proud that we were able to make your visit so memorable. I cannot wait to welcome you again very soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Agie01", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r211902046-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Our visit to Boisedale was a wonderful experience. Wonderful food and drink with beautiful music and top quality service. The cigar lounge was also fantastic with a huge range of whisky to choose from. Unforgettable experience. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r214390437", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food and loved the Michael Jackson entertainment !", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "8 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Charliecakez,", "Happy belated Birthday! I am thrilled you had such a great evening and I have already passed your comments onto the team in our daily briefings.", "We all look forward to welcoming you again.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Charliecakez", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r214390437-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went on Saturday for a birthday treat and that it was ! Great atmos , great good, staff were lovely and brilliant entertainment ! The Michael Jackson show was brilliant. Will defo go again "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r212585477", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Solid place for a steak", "diner_date": " June 2014", "rating_date": "29 June 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Mwills2,", "Thank you for your review. I am happy that you enjoyed your stay with us, but would like to hear more. We are currently working on our wine list looking to expand our new world diversity. Please contact me directly under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk should you like to elaborate on your experience.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Mwills2", "reviewer_origin": ["Umina Beach, Australia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "88"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r212585477-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Nice environment, eager service, solid food. You won't have your sox blown off but the overall result is fine. Wine list needs some work."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r214046264", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Great food, disappointing entertainment", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "7 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear J_Anniston,", "Thank you for your review. I am delighted you enjoyed our food and service. We work hard to ensure that all our guests can enjoy the very best of hospitality.", "With regards to the show on the evening, we did have a technical fault of equipment despite a thorough sound check being conducted in the afternoon. We were able to fix the issue and as a result the performance was much improved in the second set and we received a lot of positive feedback for the event. Should you wish to discuss further, please do contact me directly under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk.", "The car park is managed by Canary wharf estate and they do grant 3 hours free parking on weekends and bank holidays when the ticket is stamped; any additional time will need to be settled. I hope this clarifies your issues and I look forward to welcoming you back in the near future.", "Warm regards.", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "beeinbonnet", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "78"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "78"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r214046264-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited Saturday 5/7/14. Service, venue, food faultless. However the Michael Jackson entertainment was so poor we had to leave, his mike didnt seem to be working but his voice was awful so probably a good thing. To add insult we paid \u00a310 each to see the show. We had our car park ticket stamped and when we left the car park it wouldnt work and had to pay for parking. Could have been a great evening if we hadnt had these 2 issues."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r212746619", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Worth the trip", "diner_date": " June 2014", "rating_date": "30 June 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear M W", "Thank you for your kind review. I am delighted that you enjoyed your evening with us. Although we enjoy the finer things in live very much, we also aim to provide excellent value for money and we currently have some great special offers; so do check out our website.", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon to Canary Wharf.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "784mw", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r212746619-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Excellent atmosphere, service, food, entertainment. Not a cheap evening, but something different and worth the spend and trip out to Canary Wharf."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r214054446", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great night out", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "7 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for taking the time to review and for commenting so positively on the evening.", "We aim to provide the best entertainment and service possible and want the staff to enjoy working too. I am glad that it shows. To quickly comment on your thoughts for the tickets, there are different ticket class and prices all varying on the type of show. Some acts encourage dancing, others are more relaxed intimate sets that invite to listen. Our music tickets start from \u00a34.50 upward and rarely exceed \u00a350.00 for the VIP tickets. In any case detailed information may always be found on our website. I look forward to welcoming you again soon", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "1969tina71", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "127"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "59"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r214054446-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I've given this restaurant 5 stars for the whole package, be prepared to spend money. So I would suggest this for a celebration.", "On reserving a table you effectively need to pay for your seat when there is entertainment. You have a choice of \u00a310, \u00a330 or \u00a3100 - the \u00a3100 seat comes with a goody bag. I plumped for the \u00a330, but in fact the \u00a310 one is just as good, yes restricted view/no view of the entertainment, but it doesn't stop you from moving round the restaurant or dancing. Some of the \u00a310 seats also have a great view over Canary Wharf", "The food, service & entertainment were great. With a separate cigar room for those that want to indulge and an outside seating area to have drinks/cigars quite decadent. ", "A really good atmosphere with the waiters/waitresses clearly enjoying their job as well as having a little dance themselves. The whole Boisdale experience comes together perfectly", "Sadly one of our guests couldn't attend so we effectively lost the \u00a330 we paid, it would of been nice to have had that refunded or taken off the bill as I've stated previously a tad expensive. I would definitely go back though"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r214357155", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food - 'Michael Jackson' show a winner!", "diner_date": " July 2014", "rating_date": "8 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Jaydeeman,", "I am delighted you had such a wonderful night and thank you for your comments on our food and service. I look forward to seeing you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jaydeeman", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r214357155-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["First time at the restaurant on Saturday night; came to experience the food and also the famous MJ Eternity show starring Danny Oliver. Food was great; service reasonable, can't really fault it. Amazing intimate setting for the show. Was close to stage; by the end of the evening everyone was on their feet dancing. A real good feel. Let's do this again!!! Credit to all the performers and the team."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r206601222", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Very slow service", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "22 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "Thank you for choosing to visit the first floor bar & terrace with your voucher, I was sorry to hear that the service you received was well below the standard we set.", "The terrace menu has been designed to enable fast production in the kitchen, despite cooking everything to order as the need to be in and out is obviously high on the list of priorities for our Canary Wharf business customers. Getting the waiter's attention and prompt processing of the bill are basics which we clearly got wrong on this occasion. I would like to reassure you that this is certainly not the norm and would be grateful if you could contact me directly on Nathan@boisdale.co.uk so I can have an opportunity to restore your faith in our Canary Wharf business.", "Your sincerely,", "Nathan J Evans"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mengjiaow", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "55"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "36"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r206601222-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went there with some colleagues for a quick lunch at the Bar & Grill. Equipped with a 50% off good voucher, we thought we'd be in for a treat. ", "The food (burgers) are quite good. Main problem was the service. The drinks took 20mins to arrive, the food another 40mins. It was very difficult to get the attention of the staff to get the bill as well.", "We ended up spending well over 1h30mins there and paying 20% service charge on the bill (as the charge is calculated on the non-discounted amount). That is pretty unacceptable for the service we received. But we were in too much of a hurry to get back to meetings to argue it (which undoubtedly would have taken a long time). We are disappointed by the experience as the food is good. But we won't be back for a work lunch."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r213440731", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing", "diner_date": " June 2014", "rating_date": "3 July 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Jenaurelia,", "Thank you for you wonderful review. I am delighted you have had such a lovely visit. We all work tirelessly to make our guests as happy as we can and it makes us proud when we receive praise for it. I would love to say thank you personally when you visit next so please do contact me under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk when you plan on returning.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jenaurelia", "reviewer_origin": ["Buckingham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r213440731-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The staff are literally the most pleasant and professional people I have come across. We bought a bottle of wine for the table and didn't lift it once. A lovely young man kept an eye on the level of our glasses and refilled when needed. It is all the little things that count for example, moving out of the way when someone is coming through and generally just smiling and giving off positive vibes. ", " We watched a blues show which we had to pay extra for as well as an un-restricted view. I'm pretty sure the booking itself cost \u00a310. The restaurant had a really good atmosphere and the food although a little pricey, you definitely got quality. ", " I would absolutely visit again. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r206653545", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Delicious meal!!!", "diner_date": " May 2014", "rating_date": "22 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear IJ83", "Thank you for reviewing your experience with us.", "I am delighted you enjoyed food and service as well as the atmosphere to such an extent.", "I was sorry to read about the oysters and have passed your comments on the kitchen team so they may prevent a recurrence.", "See you soon hopefully!", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ilze j", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r206653545-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Lovely atmosphere, delicious food, excellent wine menu, beautiful live music and wonderful view. (reminded Manhattan)", "Started with oysters (could be little bit cleaner though) accompanied by cup of Boisdales champagne,", "Lobster for main courses with lovely and light tomato&avocado salad, grilled portobello mushrooms on the side\u2026 mmmmmmmm...", "For the first time ever tried as well haggis - reminded me my childhood (my grand mum was making that dish - LOVED it!", "Thank you, Boisdale!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r206896485", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Excellent night - but what is Fabian all about?!", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "24 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Steve B,", "Thank you for reviewing and I am very pleased to hear you had a great night overall especially that you found the team to be so very helpful.", "I would like to also briefly talk about your views of Fabien. It was an exceptionally busy night and Fabien was suffering from toothache and had not slept at all the previous night. His appointment at the dentist was not until the following day; yet he did not want to let the team down by not working. As a result he undoubtedly was not on his finest form. I am sorry you felt that he was rude as I can assure you he is most helpful and always dedicated to ensuring our guests are looked after. ", "I sincerely hope you look past your experience on this occasion and we all look to welcoming you again soon in the near future.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "S3489YOsteveb", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r206896485-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife and I had an excellent night at Boisdales. It's a great Scottish restaurant with some top food and top live entertainment. It's not cheap but worth the money for sure. The staff were also excellent especially the blonde haired manager/sommelier. But they have to sort someone I found out to be named Fabian. This guy was so very poor at his job he made me laugh. He struts around the place like the lord of the manor, refusing to make eye contact and refusing to be helpful. He is clearly too important to work there - or at least he thinks so. Despite the comically bad waiter/manager, I still give this place top marks and highly recommend it. Check out the live music schedule online to ensure you see something you'll enjoy. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r208824082", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Food is disappointing as the service!!!", "diner_date": " April 2014", "rating_date": "4 June 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Nasalean,", "Thank you for taking the time to review us even though I am saddened to hear you did not thoroughly enjoy your evening. Please contact me directly under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk, I would like to hear in more detail of your evening.", "To briefly touch on the music tickets: Prices start from \u00a34.50 but may go up when we have larger shows particularly on weekends. For a quality live band many of whom are part of the finest the UK has to offer, I would argue that this represents excellent value for money.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Nasalean", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "50", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r208824082-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Food and service is very disappointing, the only good thing I could find in this restaurant is the good music which is life, but for this u will have to pay 20 pounds per person......"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r207092951", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "4th Visit, this time Sunday lunch - WOW", "diner_date": " May 2014", "rating_date": "26 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear RickyTracey,", "Thank you for visiting and reviewing again!", "I am delighted we were able to convince you after your first visit to return. You can also look forward to our Sunday Lunch moving to the first floor on the 22nd of June when hopefully the weather is sunny so we may serve our fabulous Summer Sundays on the terraces.", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon!", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "RickyTracey", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "124"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "118"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r207092951-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Thought we would try sunday lunch at Boisdale's so glad we did. Fabulous value, food was delicious and wine flowed very freely, or at least for an all in price of \u00a345. Stefan was our waiter and served us a delicious three courses, it was faultless."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r207077116", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Poor service.", "diner_date": " May 2014", "rating_date": "26 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Jonotter,", "I am sorry to hear you did not enjoy our service.", "We work very hard to ensure that our guests are looked after to very high standards. The team have to reach over the table when the group is seated on banquette seats as we are unable to serve from behind in this instance; still these seats are very popular as they provide a very communal feel to the table. That the petit fours were eaten by other diners is very unfortunate and we would have been happy to replace them for you; I agree that ideally they should have been served with the coffee. I apologise sincerely if you have found our service below par on this occasion. It certainly does not reflect the standard we aspire to.", "Of course our menu has a large quantity of whiskies, wines, spirits and cigars; it is what we are along with great live music known for. There is however also a varied and seasonal menu to dine from and we are able to provide soft drinks and should you wish fresh juices.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jonotter", "reviewer_origin": ["Grays Thurrock, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "108"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "66"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "20", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r207077116-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Food was exceptional, service was poor squashed in and waiting staff who reached across to serve seated customers on inside seats. PetitS fourS served and eaten by other diners before the coffee arrived. Perhaps I should had ordered a Whiskey at \u00a31,368.30 per measure. Menu seem bias towards alcoholic drinks and Cigars."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r207707500", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Jazz, Blues and Soul with Food.", "diner_date": " May 2014", "rating_date": "28 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you Ann P for your kind review.", "I am pleased to hear you enjoyed the evening with the fabulous Elio Pace.", "We work hard to ensure we can provide excellent service and we enjoy our weekends even more when excellent musicians create such an amazing atmosphere. Thank you for choosing us to celebrate!", "We all look forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ann P", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "24"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r207707500-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A birthday night out for husband, with daughter, son-in -law and myself. Beautiful setting excellent ambiance and the live music was fab - Elio Pace / Billy Joel. (Dancing in the aisles).", "The food was amazing, good portions, well cooked and well presented. The staff were super, very helpful and nothing was too much trouble. A good selection of wine was available and thoroughly enjoyed.", "I happened to mention to the Maitre'd what a good evening we were having and that it was a birthday celebration and 4 glasses of Champagne appeared - A lovely gesture.", "You will need to book in advance to secure a table. Look on the website for music schedules.", "We're going back soon for some more. (Jazz next time, I think). I would highly recommend even though it's not cheap - It's sooo worth it.- There is also a Bar and Grill on the lower level with an outside area for smokers and a lovely view over Canary Wharf..", "Ann P"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r208456933", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Average food and poor service. ", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "2 June 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Ryan G", "I was sorry to read about your disappointing experience. This certainly does not sum up what we aspire to. Please contact me directly at you convenience under falko@boisdale-cw.uk. I would like to know more.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ryan G", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "45"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r208456933-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The best aspect of this overpriced and overrated Resturant is the whisky bar and the bar staff themselves. ", "My food consisted of Haggis to start and T-Bone steak for main. Both were average, at least the haggis was moderately priced - the steak was supposed to be rare and came more medium to well done and did nothing to satisfy my taste buds. I suppose that is why Boisdales have a large selection steak sauces.", "The food service was poor. I was forced to to to the bar to get my own drinks.", "I won't be going again. Very unsatisfied."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r208734413", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Surprisingly good Sunday lunch", "diner_date": " June 2014", "rating_date": "3 June 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for you kind review.", "I am delighted you enjoyed it so much. We felt the same way about Sunday lunches, so we launched our own in September. I am very pleased you share our thoughts. From the end of June we will be moving our lunches to our terraces so keep your fingers crossed for great weather!", "We look forward to seeing you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "AndrewR941", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "159"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "81"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r208734413-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Its difficult to get a decent Sunday lunch ( ie not cheap, crowded or just dull and mass produced) but Boisdale pulls it off ! The \u00a345 set menu has a choice of starters ( asparagus and ham, prawn cocktail for the retro amongst you, mackerel terrine etc) and a range of mains ( rare roast beef, chicken, pork, fish and a veggie option) and choice of deserts. The bill includes a glass of pink bubbles on arrival and as much house Sauvignon blanc and claret as you can drink - and they don't skimp ! Never an empty glass. Live music is pleasant inthe background, and a decent dessert selection or \u00a35 extra for the rather fine British cheese trolley, means its a quality, well cooked Sunday lunch in spacious surroundings, and is very good value for money. The service on both occasions we have been was absolutely excellent. Despite being all in for the price, you wait, and want, for nothing. For \u00a355 per head you can upgrade to Sancerre and a Rothschild red but the house option is perfectly pleasant. It's spacious, hot well cooked food ( of a traditional Sunday lunch variety) and good service. Give it a go - better than a pub and. More comfy."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r207889188", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Boisdale or BOOOdale", "diner_date": " May 2014", "rating_date": "29 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "I was sorry to read of your disappointing experience at our Canary Wharf restaurant.", "I have spoken to the team to try and ascertain what went wrong. Firstly with regard your party being accommodated on two tables. This is a pre-requisite if you are not taking one of our private dining rooms as the largest single table in the main restaurant would be 12. The email sent to you on 29th March clearly states that you would be accommodated on two tables. Table 82 and Table 76 where you were sat are indeed next to each other.", "As for the ticket charges, all tables on Friday & Saturday night are required to purchase their tickets in advance. Unfortunately leaving before the show begins, leaves us with no chance to resell the tickets hence we were unable to offer you a refund. Had you bought tickets to see a show at the O2 and decided not to stay, no refund would be offered. The same is true of Ronnie Scott\u2019s or any of London\u2019s theatres.", "I was very sorry to read that rhubarb crumble was well below par, during this part of the season, when the forced rhubarb, which is a lovely pinkish-red colour ceases to be available we use standard rhubarb which lacks colour and could be undistinguishable from the apple, but you should still have tasted it. Clearly the recipe is not right and I have spoken to the kitchen. The dish is being removed as we are heading into the summer.", "Cold coffee is obviously a very basic mistake that clearly should not have happened and for this I apologies.", "I have sent you a private email in the hope that we can restore your trust in our Canary Wharf business.", "Yours sincerely,", "Nathan Evans"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Denny777", "reviewer_origin": ["Romford"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "20", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r207889188-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked in March 2014 for 24 May for a party of 16 for 7.00-7.30 on the 24 May and explained it was for my birthday. Charged \u00a310 a head for 'restricted view' of the band of the evening and told I had to pay a proportion in advance - I paid \u00a3100 on my card. Arrived to find they had seated us on two very separate tables, behind each other, which totally wrecked the atmosphere. When I asked what time the music started I was advised is was 9.45. After more complaints to staff that coffees that were cold and bitter tasting and that a rhubarb crumble, that had no rhubarb, we decided to leave. No apology for any of the above and when I asked for a refund as we would not be staying for the music, I was advised that I could only have the \u00a360 cash back I got asked for as I walked in, the \u00a3100 was non-refundable. Would I recommend it.............absolutely not. If you have a group booking and want to have good conversation (with all members of your party) and a good atmosphere. Give this a wide miss. Awful"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r206033987", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Exceptional evening ", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "18 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Kabir D", "Thank you for taking the time to review us.", "I am delighted that you have had several great meals with us.", "I look forward to welcoming you again in the near future.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Kabir D", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r206033987-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Not the first time I have eaten at Boisdale and each time it never fails to disappoint - food, wine and atmosphere are all exceptionally good! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r202473351", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great restaurant for a special occasion", "diner_date": " March 2014", "rating_date": "23 April 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear godot1,", "Thank you for your charming review. I am delighted you had such a pleasant time with us.", "Hopefully we are able to welcome you back in the near future.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "godot1", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "83"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "39"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r202473351-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I loved this restaurant. My two daughters took me there for Mother's Day and we had a superb dinner. It was 3 courses for \u00a355 and champagne on arrival with all wines included. I had the beef which was delicious. There is a nice homely cosy feel in the restaurant and a good ambience. I especially liked the sole singer who had a great voice. There is a small dance floor which was well used. I would thoroughly recommend this restaurant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r204352532", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "legend", "diner_date": " May 2014", "rating_date": "6 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear oi-roy", "Thank you for joining us on the Bob Marley tribute night.", "I am disappointed to hear that you did not have the seat you had hoped for. We are very careful with the placement of the tables and work hard to ensure that we get it right. If this was not the case I profusely apologise.", "There are many fabulous evening coming up and I hope you will give us the chance to restore you faith in us.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "oi-roy", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r204352532-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Haveing book a table foe four,we went on the terrace to meet our company and have adrink and chat.we was told our table was ready when we were,we went upto the dinnig area and wasshown our table,which was supposed to be primem viewing for the show the table cost \u00a330 a person,our freinds were faceing the stage but did not have a good view,my wife ad self had our backs to the stage and could not see a thing and had to keep turning our heads and necks,which gave us both neck ache", "Book table for four primum veiwing this cost \u00a330 a head,our guests were faceing the stage but could not see to much,my wife and myself had our backs to the stage and could not see a thing with out turning our heads which was uncomthable very disapointed food was good and service not to bad the parking was good value.", ",."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r205063727", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "I have changed my mind!", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "11 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear JanDLondon,", "Thank you for returning! I am delighted we were able to restore your faith in us.", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon and thanking you personally.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JanDLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "595"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "291"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r205063727-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["So I posted a bit of a negative review last time came. Falko the manager picked it up and offered us a comp lunch. It was fabulous. So my last review was all great except food. Now food amazing too. We will be returning again and again. The manager Glen King didn't even know we were a comp until the end and he was amazingly proactive with all the diners"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r203349154", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "excellent food, ambiance and service", "diner_date": " April 2014", "rating_date": "29 April 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear indipendente,", "I am happy you had such a great time. The seats at the front are very popular and often taken by customers who wish to be the first on the dance floor.", "I am also pleased you found the overall food experience good, but was irked that our crab linguine was too salty on this occasion. We have a very wide range of wines available with prices starting at \u00a318.90 per bottle for the house wines, there are however a further 6 wines available under \u00a330.00.", "Our opening times from Monday to Saturday are from 11am to midnight, in my opinion it is quite extensive for a restaurant to close at that time even on Saturdays as we are not a club, we will however on request pass on recommendations on venues that are open longer.", "We hope to welcome you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Marco C", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "460"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "232"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r203349154-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Came here attracted by the good reviews for both music and food and was not disappointed. We had a very good table near the stage and could enjoy the show to the max. Maybe the volume was a bit too high.", "Getting here is easy and the underground parking is convenient. Remember to get your parking ticket stamped to get some free parking time.", "Food was very good. My bisque of lobster was very tasty though it did not contain any bits of lbster, which I would have liked. Reasonably priced at \u00a3 9.50. My tartare was also excellent and passionately prepared by my Portuguese waiter in front of our eyes. My friend had crab linguine which was slightly salty. My other friend had a superb lamb cutlet.", "Good selection of wines, expensive but this is to be expected in a restaurant like this. We had a good Chablis Fevre at \u00a3 49.50 (why not just say \u00a3 50!) and were happy with it.", "As customary in London these days, \"tip\" was included automatically in our bill. Their website advices to \"delete it if you are unhappy\" but that was not an option presented to us and in any case a very impractical one. Anyway we were very happy with our waiters and would have tipped no matter what. In the end about \u00a365 per person, money well spent.", "They have a great choice of cigars to be smoked in a terrace that however closes by midnight. Very strange to close at midnight even on a Saturday night!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r204426697", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic Birthday Treat", "diner_date": " April 2014", "rating_date": "7 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Meekat1984,", "Thank you for writing and thanks to your friend for brining you here.", "I am delighted you enjoyed our food, the service, our lovingly made cocktails as well as one of our many drams. Please do not wait for your next birthday to return!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Meerkat1984", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "51"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r204426697-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I was brought here by my girlfriend for my birthday, predominantly for my love of whisky and their extensive selection.", "We had a lovely table by the window with a view of The Shard. ", "I had a steak with a bloody mary sauce (which was really good with a great chilli kick) my girlfriend had the lamb which she said was delicious.", "Throughout the evening I drank beer, a top notch manhattan and the piece de resistance a Dalmore limited edition that I had never even heard of before going to Boisdale.", "The service throughout the evening was fantastic, we were never rushed and enjoyed soaking in the Friday night atmosphere. I'll definitely be coming back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r205369958", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "didn't manage to get our pre-booked meal", "diner_date": " May 2014", "rating_date": "13 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Jaqueline b,", "I am disappointed to hear of your experience with us and would like you to contact me personally to discuss your experience. Please feel free to contact me under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk at your convenience.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jacqueline b", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r205369958-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked a table a few weeks in advance via opentable -- chateaubriand, lobster, prosecco and dessert - The day of the reservation we received a telephone call that we can not have this offer for that evening and can only choose from the normal menu. Also we have to leave before the Jazz band starts playing.... Can you make up your mind within the next 10 minutes otherwise the table will be cancelled. Not surprisingly we cancelled the booking . 15 minutes later she ( Maya?) called again with the same message. She did not apologize and came across quit rude .", "As we havent seen the restaurant from the inside and most likely will not book again, I am not able to review the food but manners wise the Plateau is a better option in Canary Wharf"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r203444998", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Drinks and a quick meal", "diner_date": " April 2014", "rating_date": "30 April 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Barbara_Yang,", "Thank you for your review and for stopping by after work.", "Our first floor is designed to be a comfortable space to grab a bite of great food. We have now launched a new summer menu providing more healthy and seasonal dishes, whilst keeping our fabulous steaks and burgers. If you want to have a more cocktail and whisky focused experience, why not try to visit the second floor and be looked after by our bar team there with excellent live music every night?", "I hope to welcome you soon,", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Barbara_Yang", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "63"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r203444998-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Came here for a drink and grabbed a quick bite to eat after work. Definitely attracts the CW crowd. Can't say it was anything spectacular but I can imagine that the terrace will be great for the summer.", " "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r205945036", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wow, what wonderful service", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "17 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review.", "I am delighted that you were looked after by the team so well.", "Please visit us again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Claire H", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "24"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r205945036-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were served by Gervais and our cocktail was made by John. They were more than happy to make our Mai Tai's to our own recipe, which after a disappointing evening was very welcome. Thank you very much!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r205787383", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "great place", "diner_date": " May 2014", "rating_date": "16 May 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Raj C,", "Thank you for returning again and again. I am delighted you are looked after by Filipe; he is one of our stars.", "I hope to welcome you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Raj C", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r205787383-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["have been here many times. love the food, the drink, the service and the ambiance. it is well worth a visit. Big thank you to Phillip who is in charge of the cigars....provides a great service every time and goes well above and beyond to look after us. Thank you."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r197617844", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good Food And Live Music", "diner_date": " March 2014", "rating_date": "16 March 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Joan I,", "I am delighted your husband chose us to celebrate your special day with. Obviously, I was even more pleased to hear you had such a fabulous time. With any luck we do not have to wait another year to welcome you back.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Joan I", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r197617844-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My husband booked this restaurant as Ray Gelato and his giant were appearing on my birthday. We had a great table with only one other between us and the stage and centrally placed. Ray is a fantastic entertainer and the dance floor was jam packed with all ages. The food was good too and the service efficient and friendly. A great evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r198151309", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fabulous in every way!", "diner_date": " March 2014", "rating_date": "21 March 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear KarenDenney,", "I am delighted you had such a wonderful evening and enjoyed all we had to offer.", "Why don\u2019t you check out our website for exciting upcoming acts, such as Ben Waters on the 16th May?", "We all look forward to welcoming you back soon!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "KarenDenney", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r198151309-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Myself and three girlfriends enjoyed a wonderful evening here celebrating a birthday.", "We had a great table very close to the stage and we were entertained by the fantastic Jordan Marsh's Rockin Three. To watch him playing the piano is an absolute joy! ", "The restaurant is beautiful, service is spot on with lovely staff and the food is to die for! We all had the 9oz rib eye cooked perfectly and loved the cabbage with chorizo. ", "After dinner we hit the dance floor and were joined by a lovely lady from Sweden who was dining with her husband. She thought the band were great to, and said it was the best night out in London that she had ever had.", "Thank you to all for making it such a special evening and I can't wait to return!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r198742482", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "a jazz evening", "diner_date": " March 2014", "rating_date": "26 March 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear martin g,", "Thank you for your kind review. Ray has been with us many times & always enjoys great attendance. We have received great feedback for his performance so I am happy to say your impression was not shared. With regards to our menu I appreciate your comments & would like to draw your attention to a new summer menu we will be launching on the 15th May with lots of new contents and exciting price points!", "We look forward to welcoming you again soon!", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "622marting", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "91"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "51"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r198742482-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I entertained at the Boisdale, i have been there on a few occasions , Ray Gelato was the attraction for me , although he gave the impression that he was not enjoying the evening. The food was ok but expensive, i would always recommend Boisdale as a venue, with live music good whisky, there is a shortage of good jazz venues in London, go for fun ."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r196751121", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good night out....", "diner_date": " March 2014", "rating_date": "9 March 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Mark G,", "I am pleased to hear that you enjoyed your evening and the resulting complimentary entertainment. I was surprised to hear that you were at no stage informed of the music tickets that are chargeable to all customers. Our staff is well trained on ensuring we communicate this clearly. Our website clearly states the charges, as do all confirmation emails and the reservations team is spot on in clarifying the charges. Still, mistakes are made and we did waiver the charge on this occasion, so I am delighted the team reacted promptly.", "Why not check our website for an upcoming music act that you may enjoy & start planning you return? We look forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Mark G", "reviewer_origin": ["Walton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r196751121-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a very nice meal and the service was excellent. They had a fantastic selection of wine and the waitresses were very smartly dressed in their short kilts. The only thing you have to watch is if you start eating earlier, as us ten did and the jazz band comes on whilst you are eating they want to charge you for listening to the music which we were not informed of. In our case they wanted \u00a375.00 but were very happy to squash the charge once we complained. All in all excellent all round."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r201205936", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great meal, superb music, just a slight niggle", "diner_date": " April 2014", "rating_date": "15 April 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for taking the time to review us.", "I am grateful you are considering us for a family dinner however would also like express my regret for the service not living up to the standards we set ourselves. I cannot bear the thought of the team prioritising guests over others. It is far from what they have been taught; should you have felt that way I do apologise sincerely and will emphasize this with the team.", "Do let me know when you are planning to return under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk. I would be delighted to help with any arrangements needed.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "sunandsailcat", "reviewer_origin": ["East Grinstead, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r201205936-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I had a super meal here with my son . We were seeking avoid food in pleasant surrounding s as he'd just moved into a new flat and for myself having spent all day helping him I had high hopes for Boisedale which is very familiar to me in Bishopsgate. The food did not disappoint at all, and jazz as usual complimented our enjoyment of the evening. However, we did rather feel that the staff paid significantly more attention to the \"suits\" who to be fair are probably regular customers than was paid to ourselves. The bread took some time to arrive and the butter never made an appearance despite a couple of requests. I was considering this venue for a family birthday dinner and I will persevere but I trust that on this occasion the service experienced was just a blip. I would just counsel staff to bear in mind do not always judge a book by its cover and bear in mind that all Customers are equal.!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r199988367", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good food, but less than friendly atmosphere", "diner_date": " April 2014", "rating_date": "5 April 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your feedback.", "I was sorry to hear you felt we were not friendly; usually one of the things we are most praised on. I have already reiterated with the team how important it is to always focus on the customer. While the waitress of course has to prepare for dinner service, her priority should have clearly been on you. Your comments of the food have been passed on to our Executive Head Chef and are appreciated. I would like to add that our steaks are premium dry aged & from grass fed cattle. In terms of flavour they are superior and we feel that we are very competitive in terms of pricing in this area.", "Should you return in the future, please do let us know under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk we would love to show you why so many customers enjoy our service.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Anak_Johor", "reviewer_origin": ["Sydney, Australia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "152"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "65"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "20", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r199988367-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife and I walked in without any booking, as we happened to be in the vicinity at dinner time. We were attended by a young lass who was more interested in setting the tables for the night than waiting on us. Granted that the restaurant is located in a business district and mostly patronised by suits, and we had walked-in in our civvies. But that should not relegate us to less attention that the business-types. The steaks we had were great, but with prices to match. Chips and steamed brocolli were extra, but they could have been a bit more generous with the quantity. All up it could have been a better experience, but it failed to hit the mark for me."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r198822431", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great steak in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " March 2014", "rating_date": "26 March 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your great review; I am delighted you enjoyed your stay here.", "We have just made some excellent changes on our terrace and it now looks like a cosy English garden. You should definitely see it for yourself.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "greedygekko", "reviewer_origin": ["Winchester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "34"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r198822431-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale Canary Wharf is lighter and more airy than its Bishopgate brother, with a glass front over Cabot Square, and an outside balcony for drinks. The great cocktail menu, live music, and fantastic steaks from other Boisdales are still all present. Seriously, this is probably the best steak I've had outside of New York."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r200446862", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "nice one in CW", "diner_date": " March 2014", "rating_date": "9 April 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Westbnd,", "Thank you for your review & for enjoying our offerings. We look forward to welcoming you back.", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Westbnd", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r200446862-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["we were lucky to get a table on a Thursday night, good place, nice atmosphere, food ok, sigar lounge excellent and a rarity in London."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r200564960", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food, music and experience", "diner_date": " March 2014", "rating_date": "10 April 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for you lovely review.", "I am delighted to hear you had a marvellous time and would appreciate you letting me if you are planning to return under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk. I would like to thank you in person.", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mickaveli2001", "reviewer_origin": ["Glenrothes, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r200564960-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Nice atmosphere. The food portions were a little small, but the quality of the food more than made up for that. Nice Jazz music, and followed by a cigar downstairs in the cosy cigar room. Great dining experience and would certainly go to again if in the are in the near future."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r200575515", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Oysters. Steaks. Cocktails.", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "10 April 2014", "answer_text": ["Andrew G,", "Thank you for your review. I am happy you enjoyed it.", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MistersWolfe", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "33"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r200575515-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Recently had dinner at Boisdale's in Canary Wharf. Good Oysters. Good Steaks. Good Cocktails. Enough Said!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r196621469", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The atmosphere made it...", "diner_date": " March 2014", "rating_date": "8 March 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear DorisDiner,", "Thank you for your comments on your visit.", "I was alarmed to hear that you did not find the welcome on the first floor friendly and I will certainly be focussing with the staff on making sure no repeat of your situation arises. That said I was happy to hear that the remainder of your visit turned out to be exactly what we like to achieve.", "We hope to be able to welcome you back soon!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "DorisDiner", "reviewer_origin": ["Redhill, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "164"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "56"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r196621469-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I had lunch here on a Friday with a colleague. As it was my first visit I wasn't quite sure where to go once inside the building and there were not many members of staff around. When I eventually did find someone, they were not particularly welcoming (bordering on unfriendly) so I was starting to regret the choice of venue before I had even sat down.", "That said, the food was good, as was the service and the wine list. The restaurant wasn't at all busy, which surprised me a little - I had expected it to be packed. Overall, the meal itself was really enjoyable. We then went to the balcony area and had drinks - the bar service was excellent. The staff were quite the opposite to the person I had met earlier and this made up for the previous disappointment. I would have happily stayed long into the evening, to soak up some more of the vibrant atmosphere. I'll definitely make a point of going back, most likely for one of the live music events."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r194625244", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great location although service was a little slow", "diner_date": " January 2014", "rating_date": "19 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Charles,", "Thanks for your review.", "I was sorry to hear that service was slow on the day in question, but pleased you enjoyed the food. I would love to have more detail on your booking so I could dig a little deeper and prevent a recurrence. If you get a chance drop me an email at Nathan@boisdale.co.uk.", "Best wishes,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "CharlesH604", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "74"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "135"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "20", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r194625244-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great location over looking Cabot Square. Had a McSween haggis and a Loch Duart smoked salmon to start. Service was slow and impersonal. The claret and the whisky was also impressive. The desserts were also very lovely. Overall we were both mostly impressed."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r194548522", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Gorgeous Sunday Lunch", "diner_date": " January 2014", "rating_date": "18 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Christine,", "We were delighted to read your review of Sunday Lunch.", "Since September last year the lunches on Sunday have gone from strength-to-strength and we are committed to continuing with our set menu with inclusive wine offer so we can deliver a great value Sunday lunch in convivial surroundings, to the soundtrack of classic jazz performed live..", "We look forward to welcoming you back to the restaurant very soon.", "Perhaps your son may consider treating you to our Mother's Day special menu with a bigger band & gift for deserving mothers!", "Best wishes,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Christine S", "reviewer_origin": ["Beaconsfield, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "81"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r194548522-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Following a recommendation, we decided to try the Sunday lunch my son had enthused about and we weren't disappointed. Lovely welcome as we entered the restaurant and at the bar where we were not hurried to our table but allowed to take our time. Great table by the window and we opted for the all inclusive three course lunch with wine priced at (I think) \u00a349 pp. Excellent value as the waiter was generous with the wine (good quality), included a glass of Champagne before lunch and a choice of starter, main course and pudding with a choice of cheese for a small supplement. Worth mentioning is the roast served with lovely well cooked vegetables, delicious pudding and a truly sublime English Cheeseboard selection from a well stocked trolley. Probably wouldn't bother again with the prawn cocktail as this was really rather average. Having the jazz band play throughout lunch was the icing on the cake. We will definitely be making a return visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r194760437", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great venue and food", "diner_date": " February 2014", "rating_date": "20 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for you lovely review.", "It was nice to read that you took advantage of all our offerings. I am pleased to hear you enjoyed yourselves so much. Please let us know when you return under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk. W We would love to say thank you in person.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "BMSAH", "reviewer_origin": ["Scotland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "33"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r194760437-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The restaurant is nicely split up and we enjoyed a drink in the Oyster bar, dinner and Jazz in the restaurant and spent time in the cigar lounge. Staff were attentive especially the whisky master and our host in the cigar lounge. The oysters were very nice and all our courses were well presented and value for money considering the location. I was given a blanket to allow us to sit outside in the terrace while my partner smoked his cigar, you cannot drink alcohol in the lounge itself. all in all nice evening. We will definately be back"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r194892451", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Nice setting however average food", "diner_date": " February 2014", "rating_date": "21 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for taking the time to review us.", "I am delighted you enjoyed the setting and service. With regards to the food I am very sorry we did not live up to you expectations on this particular night. Scallops are sourced from Scotland and are diver caught. It may have been very popular on the day or the weather in Scotland may have been too bad to go out and dive for them. With regards to both salmon dishes, I cannot help but be surprised that you though them flavourless. All of our salmon is hand reared and the closest thing to wild salmon; the fish being able to roam freely in vast waters. We only ever receive positive feedback on the quality of this fish. The crab linguine not only has a crab claw sitting on top, but also white and brown crab meat through the sauce, which is shellfish based, so it should provide you with lots of intense shellfish flavours. Again I would like to apologise if you felt this was not the case. On another up I was pleased to read you enjoyed the crumble and the cheese selection. Mistakes may always be made and I hope you will visit us again in the future. Should you wish to do so, kindly let me know under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Mark M", "reviewer_origin": ["Alton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r194892451-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Walking into the restaurant you are quite over-whelmed with the beautiful decor. A wonderful looking bar decorated with an amazing selection of whiskey. The table was well presented and the staff were extremely attentive. Once seated we looked at the menu and were pleased with what sounded like a lovely choice of foods although we were told that there were no scallops which my wife had been looking forward to. i plumped for the salmon for starters which was average and i must say i have had better when in Scotland. My main selection was the crab linguine which i was very much looking forward to. What came out was a tasty sauce although very thick and one piece of crab sitting on the pasta. My partner went for a second choice potted smoked mackerel which was standard followed by salmon which could have done with more flavour. Desert was the crumble which my wife informed me was wonderful whilst i decided to go for the cheese board which was the highlight for me. A great selection which were all wonderful. Overall an average experience but that it just my feelings although friends i know love the place and are regular visitors."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r194899396", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "desrves 5 stars because of the entertainment but lower because of billing issue", "diner_date": " January 2014", "rating_date": "21 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review of Burns Night.", "I am delighted you enjoyed your evening as well as the entertainment. Our Burns Nights have become more and more popular and it is always on of the busiest evenings of the year. I recall the dance floor being quite crowded, however I always feel it is a good sign if people want to dance. The issues on your bill should not have happened of course and I am very sorry that you feel this spoilt your evening. I am sure that the management were as fast as possible to rectify the problem with your bill; though I appreciate if you felt this took too long. We would all be happy to welcome you back and if you let us know under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk which night would be of interest, we will be happy to assist with all the arrangements.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "PamBDc", "reviewer_origin": ["Warrenton, Virginia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "40"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r194899396-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went on Burns night and had a good time. The rat pack duo were as entertaining as always and the small dance floor was overcrowded but still a lot of fun. The food was good and the service reasonable. The only issue was a dispute with our bill as we had been charged with another tables wine and it took some considerable time for the management to acknowledge the error which totally spoilt the night and as it was my birthday it left a sour taste. We will go back but will be very careful to note what we have next time as we were not the only ones with errors."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r195083129", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Disappointing!", "diner_date": " February 2014", "rating_date": "23 February 2014", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Anna P", "reviewer_origin": ["Bristol, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r195083129-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited Boisdale last night with a large party of people. Booked by another family member who had numerous problems with booking prior to arrival. Told we could have a la carte and then told was a mistake. Then agreed to let us have a la carte provided we pre ordered. No problem but the choice sent to us was less than the original menu - all the cheaper options were removed. Eventually after negotiations were given the normal menu. Then we asked if we could bring a birthday cake for an 80th birthday and were told that they would charge us \u00a32.50 per person. That was going to be \u00a365.00 just to cut a cake and put on plates! What on earth do they charge the 12.5% service charge for.", "As for the food, very disappointing. Braised lamb very fatty, lamb chops very tough, scallops overcooked, chocolate fondant powdery, sticky toffee pudding over microwaved as became tougher when eating. Very expensive too for the quality of the food.", "Entertainment - Frank Sinatra. Also disappointing sang for the very most for 70 minutes and actually wasn't all that good. I have seen many tribute Frank Sinatra/Rat Pack shows and he was not a patch on all the others.", "Overall not good value for money - having said that we had a great night but that was because of the fact we have a fantastic family who always have a great time and make the best of a bad situation. No-one complained on the night as we wanted the special person whose birthday it was to have a fantastic time and thankfully she did!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r196124951", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Pleasant evening of music and food", "diner_date": " March 2014", "rating_date": "4 March 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear SCSLondon,", "Thank you for your kind review, I am happy that you enjoyed your meal and the ambience. When we chose our buns we tried many varieties and collectively chose our bun. We felt that the slight sweetness actually brings out the flavours in the burger better than any other we tried. I am sorry you thought it too sweet. While we do offer finer items on the menu that have their deserving price point, I would reason that we offer house wine starting from \u00a318.90 a bottle and it is easily possible to have a two course meal for under \u00a325.00 per person so while we are definitely able to provide that special occasion, we can also deliver excellent value meals; hopefully you can agree.", "I look forward to being able to welcome you back very soon.", "Warm regards.", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "SCSLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "480"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "226"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r196124951-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We ate in the restaurant as we had booked for a music event and the only way to guarantee a seat was to book for dinner. The decor and ambience of the place was nice with the tables spaced out well allowing for a good view of the stage. We were greeted warmly and quickly given menus. We were given two small pieces of bread each but no butter. The waiter quickly brought us some when we pointed it out. He was very friendly and pleasant throughout the evening. We selected oysters to share for starters, which were nicely presented on ice and tasted fresh. We chose the classic burger and truffle burger for mains. Both were cooked really well and I enjoyed the truffle flavour of mine. I was much less impressed with the burger bun which was too sweet. The fries were good. I would say that the portion size was on the small side, particularly as the burgers are quite pricey. For desserts we had the chocolate fondant and crumble, which were both nice. The wine was a malbec which went nicely with the burgers. Overall we enjoyed the evening but spent around \u00a3100 on top of the price of the tickets, so it is an experience to save for a special occasion."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r195914311", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Very enjoyable Sunday Lunch Celebration", "diner_date": " March 2014", "rating_date": "2 March 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your delightful review.", "I am pleased to hear you thought so highly of us. Naturally we are all looking forward to welcoming you back in the near future, maybe for our Mothering Sunday Lunch or perhaps to enjoy Breakfast on the first floor when we open for the London Marathon this year. You will have great views as the field is running just below our terraces.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LynnieLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "90"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "109"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r195914311-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We book this restaurant as we wanted a Sunday ", "Lunch with Live Jazz and this came up on an internet search!", "Our aunt & uncle were celebrating 60years of marriage and the love Jazz! ", "I was more than pleased with our choice, the food was great,the ambience perfect & the service second to none! ", "We opted for the \u00a345 Sunday lunch with drinks. Sparkling pink wine aperitf and free flowing white & red wine throughout! Excellent value for money I thought.", "I will definitely be back here with my girlfriend to one of the other evenings,", "Thank you for making the oldies feel special! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r195217283", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Everything is right about this place except the food!", "diner_date": " February 2014", "rating_date": "24 February 2014", "answer_text": ["I truly sorry that the food was below standard on you visit to Sunday Lunch.", "I would be grateful if you contact me under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk to discuss the issues further.", "Thank you for taking the time to relay your experience.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JanDLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "595"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "291"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "50", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r195217283-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Sunday Jazz brunch. Roast beef was raw - hey I love it rare but it didn't look like it had even been in the oven. Yorkshires were burnt. Duck fat potatoes were dry (yes, how did they manage that?) and carrots so hard they were almost raw (again I'm loving al dente but you need to cook them a bit). Everything was cold. Such a shame as I would have returned again and again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r193248741", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Disabled Access and Review of Boisdales", "diner_date": " February 2014", "rating_date": "6 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for sharing your thoughts.", "I was disappointed to hear you found the toilets in a poor state; I have already taken this to the duty manager as they perform checks though all areas, this must have not happened & I am truly ashamed of this.", "With regards to your feelings on the service & food I am surprised as we receive so much great feedback on the warmth & quality of the service, and selling in excess of 500 hamburgers a week the vast majority of customers comment that they are some of the best burgers they have tasted.", "That being said, mistakes can happen and it seems that you had to suffer on this occasion.", "Please let me know directly under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk should you wish to return for the mentioned visit to the first floor.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "S W", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "20", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r193248741-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["1930\u2019s splendour greeted me in the vibrant and elegant Boisdales restaurant. On entry the first thing that struck me was a sparkling bar, heaving with top end whisky\u2019s and crystal decanters. We were seated at a leather booth table with a curved glass window opposite boasting dramatic views of Canary Wharf. Throughout the afternoon we were serenaded by live jazz music from an exuberant band on a spot-lit stage.", "Sadly, the impressive d\u00e9cor is where the breathtaking elements of this restaurant halted. Although the service obeyed all the rules of high standards of etiquette, it was cold, and unfortunately so were our orders. The food arrived at different times, was confused and chaotic. The shiny fa\u00e7ade of Boisdales was cracked by the substandard food reflected in the \u00a317 truffle hamburger which was below average and a poorly presented undercooked plate of lamb.", "That said, the encyclopaedic wine list and covetable cocktail menu coupled with a second to none ambience means that Boisdales would serve as a fantastic place to visit for a drinks with friends.", "Should you wish to visit, you will find that the restaurant has a car park below in Cabot Square, although this appears to have no allocated disabled parking. A ramp with automatic doors leads up to the lifts, which take you directly into the spacious lobby of the restaurant. The restaurant is bright and airy and the flooring is wooden. There are no awkward doors or passageways. The tables are a good width apart from each other and there is a free cloakroom. There is a wide entrance to the disabled toilet, though there is an annoying little ridge to get into the toilet, which takes a bit of force to get the wheelchair over. Sadly, the disabled toilet has been neglected, and was dirty, smelly and unkempt. ", "Personally, I would visit the oyster grill on the 1st floor of Boisdales sooner than the restaurant. It boasts the biggest cigar humidifier in the world, a balcony that overlooks Canary Wharf and a selection of the finest caviar that I\u2019ve always wanted to try. In terms of access Boisdales ticks most of the boxes for a fairly stress free night out, although beware it does get very busy."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r193492079", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Very disappointed with the evening poor service poor food", "diner_date": " February 2014", "rating_date": "8 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "I was very sorry to read that you had such a disappointing time at our restaurant.", "We sell hundreds of burgers a week, including between 60 - 100 takeaway on Fridays to the offices in Canary Wharf and normally receive excellent feedback. I can only imagine that you received a substandard product and for that I am very sorry. You will see from the majority of our reviews that service levels are high and we received a tripadvisor certificate of excellence last year, I'm sorry however that the service fell so short on this occasion. ", "Perhaps you could contact the restaurant directly so I can find out more about the booking and respond in an appropriate manner.", "Yours sincerely,", "Nathan J Evans"], "reviewer_pseudo": "planet1965", "reviewer_origin": ["Grays Thurrock, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "20", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r193492079-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a evening booked with some friends had not read any reviews before going and was looking forward to it.", "menu was very expensive not worth the money we paid, I can honestly say I have eaten a better buger in Mcdonalds the service was poor asked for some sauce with my meal but the waiter never even came back.", "I have never writen a review but felt I had to on this occasion,on the train on my way home!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r194428695", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Add on another 20%", "diner_date": " February 2014", "rating_date": "17 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "Thank you for taking time to review our restaurant. We were delighted to hear that you are happy to recommend Boisdale, but did want to clarify the ticket breakdown for Valentines' night and the service charge procedure.", "The \u00a3100 ticket per person (including vat @ 20%) was made up as follows:", "Glass of Dom Perignon 2004 Vintage Champagne \u00a322.50", "Ticket for the show \u00a320.00 ", "Five course dinner (Including Fillet of Beef Wellington) \u00a357.50", "Tea or coffee was included", "I have looked at your bill which shows a final total of \u00a3238.45. The service element of your bill was \u00a322.05. When you deduct the music tickets of \u00a340 from your bill which does not attract service charge the percentage is 9.2% not 20%.", "We have received excellent feedback on the Fil Straughn show and service on the evening and feel that the ticket price represented good value for money.", "We currently have an excellent set menu at \u00a317.80 for two course and house wine starts from \u00a318.90. So outside of special nights like Valentines we are very accessible.", "We look forward to welcoming you back to Boisdale soon", "Warm wishes,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "YarcoNorfolk", "reviewer_origin": ["Norfolk"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "58"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "42"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r194428695-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The Valentines evening set menu with Luther Vandross tribute was quite expensive at \u00a3100.00 / person plus your drinks but when they then add on a 20% service charge it gets very expensive.", "An average meal with good service and a fantastic band / singer was totaly spoilt be getting hit for the service charge.", "Happy to recommend Boisdales but be aware that they realy do know how to charge and what you pay for your ticket is not actualy what they will charge you come the end of the evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r193103515", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "GREAT VENUE, GREAT SERVICE, AVERAGE FOOD, VERY AVERAGE BAND THE NIGHT I VISITED", "diner_date": " January 2014", "rating_date": "4 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for taking the time to share your experience with us.", "I was pleased to hear you visited us on a number of occasions.", "With regards to your ranking of the restaurant values, I would like to address the order of importance to us. We are firstly a British restaurant with Scottish heritage intent on delivering great food & drinks to the highest standards. Our service should go along hand in hand with this. Then additionally we provide the music, which should always be first class.", "We constantly review bands that have joined us. This helps us find the right music for us. As you have mentioned the Strictly Steve show was with us twice in the prior year and both occasions sold out. They have a great reputation and all three visits (including this) have provided great feedback. I am sorry they were not to your taste. Should your wish to discuss your thoughts regarding the food on this occasion further, please contact me directly under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk. ", "I look forward to hearing from you.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Papajohnsmoan", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "66"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r193103515-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Myself and my friends, booked a table for the Stevie Wonder night featuring Strictly Stevie. I have visited Boisdale Canary Wharf 5 or 6 times and Knightsbridge once. ", "I always start off with a few drinks downstairs in the bar and then moving upstairs for dinner. On this occasion I was really looking forward to the entertainment for the evening but after a few numbers with little or no introduction I said to my friend this must be the warm up band or something or maybe the singer has been held up or delayed. No such luck, after a few more songs we realised that this was it for the night, the guy just can't sing and the lady was holding the act together.", "This band may have played to packed houses twice in 2013 but there were a number of empty table this night, 2 right near the stage. ", " My friend commented that they were no better than a pub band. ", "As for the food at venues like this I put the order of importance as Music, Drinks, Food, on this particular night the drinks and service were great the food was average and the music very average, my 3 stars are only for this night in particular as I have had some great nights here but I think if a restaurant is charging a couple of thousand pounds for entertainment I would expect something a bit better. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r194026071", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "What a shame", "diner_date": " February 2014", "rating_date": "14 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review.", "I am happy to hear you enjoyed service and music; though was rather disappointed that you chose to mark us down so heavily. You are the first customer to have raised this issue and I have already taken action to amend the situation.", "E-cigarettes are made predominately from vegetable extract and the vapour is harmless, unlike smoke. They have been specifically designed to enable smokers to care for their needs in places where cigarettes are banned. They do not contravene any smoking legislation and a number of very public places allow their use such as Gatwick & Heathrow airports.", "While it is perfectly legal for their use in any form of restaurant I have decided to restrict the use of e-cigarettes in the dining area of the restaurant, but will still allow their use on the first floor & the second floor bar area.", "I hope this clarifies the situation and hopefully you can see that we take your feedback seriously.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Colin C", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r194026071-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The food was good, the music by TJ Johnson was excellent but the evening was rather spoiled by the person smoking an e-cigarette at the next table who was constantly blowing smoke in my direction. I raised the matter with the restaurant staff and asked, if it was a non smoking establishment, why was smoking e-cigarettes allowed. Unfortunately I just got a shrug of the shoulders."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r193593411", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent!", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "9 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your wonderful review.", "I am delighted you enjoyed your evening and since you live just around the corner I hope to welcome you again in the very near future. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "benbLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["london"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "150"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "117"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r193593411-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great food, great evening...great music, thanks to Si Cranstoun.", "Living across the water in Greenwich, had always wanted to visit Boisdale and finally got the chance.", "Wait was worth it.", "Considering the surroundings, v reasonably priced food and excellent, unstuffy, friendly service.", "Had an juicy rib eye (although could have done with a few more chips).", "Next time I'll go with my daughter's dish, a taste-sensation risotto.", "Make sure u get your car parking ticket stamped before leaving - you get three hours free parking.", "And have a spicy Bloody Mary...bloody delicious.", "All in all, a great venue."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r194252065", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Love this place", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "16 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank your for your great review.", "I am delighted you and your wife enjoy visiting us. We are obviously proud you regard our food offering in such high regard and can appreciate the wide selection of luxuries we have to offer. I would however like to point out that while certain items are dearer than others (grass fed 40 dry aged Fillet Steaks from Scottish beef is more valuable than most corn fed American rivals) there are plenty excellent choices that enable you to enjoy a dinner or lunch on a budget ranging from Crab & Chilli Linguine over Salmon with caponata to excellent Scottish rib steak Hamburgers.", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LondonSE13", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r194252065-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["When working at Canary Wharf, this is one of my wifes and I favorite place. ", "We have tried nearly all the fish and seafood, and it is impeccable, considering that its close to Billingsgate fish market I would expect nothing less. ", "We have been here numerous times, even on a Frank Sinatra night which was really very good. The steaks here are some of the best we have ever had. The selection of wine, cigars and whiskey is extensive and something for everyone's palate.", "The place is expensive, but it is satisfying and very pleasant.", "Would recommend the fruit de mar if you love sea food!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r194278618", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The best value 3 course Sunday roast!", "diner_date": " February 2014", "rating_date": "16 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your charming review.", "I am delighted to hear you have tried the Lamb and as a result joined us. The Sunday roast lunch offer is indeed great value for money. Having only started serving Sundays in September we tweaked our initial offer and are now more than pleased with is and as such we are happy to hear you are too!", "Thank you for also mentioning the service; something I take great pride in on delivering with the team.", "We look forward to welcoming you back.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Atay75", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r194278618-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Having stayed at \"the Lamb\" and enjoying stunning food, come this valentines we decided we simply must try the Boisdale Sunday roast, as a belated valentines dinner.", "Fabulous lively surroundings and lovely staff giving great service.", "We had a lovely afternoon and fantastic food, although we struggled with 3 generous courses the food was simply divine.", "We will definately book again and look forward to our next visit. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r194365192", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Beautiful restaurant", "diner_date": " December 2013", "rating_date": "17 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your charming review.", "I could not help but smile at your surprise of the ambience; it is great to hear the eclectic but classic d\u00e9cor is appreciated. I look forward to welcoming you back soon! ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Gary M", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r194365192-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very surprised at the lovely surroundings and view from tis restaurant : food was lovely and the staff were very helpful: ", "Expensive but worth it "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r188877072", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Loved it, great impressive venue.", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "29 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for visiting us and writing about your stay.", "I am happy you enjoyed food and service to such a degree. I would be delighted if you could join us again soon. Please let me know under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk should you wish to visit again.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Andrew W", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "446"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "390"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r188877072-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited recently for a meal and wasn't disappointed. The food was all very nice and the service excellent. Our waiter was very helpful and pleasant. No complaints at all and would happily return"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r192241929", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "One of London's Best Venues", "diner_date": " August 2013", "rating_date": "27 January 2014", "answer_text": ["Yes! Thank you for your lovely review. I am thrilled you had such a good time & obviously happy to hear the team looked after you so well. Please let us know when you return to visit under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk and we will make sure to thank you personally!", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Coinneach S", "reviewer_origin": ["Dublin, Tipperary, Ireland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r192241929-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["If I'm visiting London any time soon, then this is where I'll head for a good evening. Great food, helpful staff, malt whiskies galore and jazz of course. In particular, the fish is excellent and cooked with care. This is rather a famous club and deservedly so."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r194412172", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Oustanding. Excellent. Exceptional. Impeccable service.", "diner_date": " February 2014", "rating_date": "17 February 2014", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "Thank you so much for your lovely review which filled the team with pride.", "We have passed on your compliments to Jorge - the Portuguese waiter who served you that afternoon and to the kitchen and very much look forward to welcoming you back to Boisdale Canary Wharf very soon.", "Best wishes,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mw741002", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "761"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "487"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r194412172-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We wish it were possible to give a better rating than \"excellent\". Everything about this restaurant was excellent+++ ", "The street level entrance is very modest, but get the lift to the second floor and it opens out into a cavernous restaurant. The first thing that you notice is the stunning central bar feature with several hundred varieties of Whisky!!", "The tables were set with crisp white linen tablecloths and napkins.", "We had booked for the traditional Sunday lunch and had a table for two by the window overlooking the Canary Wharf concourse. For Sunday lunch there was live jazz entertainment. The restaurant filled up quickly - clearly being very popular and there was a lively atmosphere.", "We chose the traditional Sunday lunch three-course menu costing \u00a345 which included a starter glass of Champagne plus unlimited white and red wine and they were most generous topping up the glasses. For non-wine drinkers, the lunch is also available without wine for \u00a335.", "We were served by a Portuguese waiter who was personable, attentive and highly professional", "For starters we had ham hock & foie gras terrine and potted smoked mackerel. Both of these were exceptionally good. ", "For main course we both chose roast rib of beef carved from the trolley, which was accompanied by crisp Yorkshire puddings, duck fat roast potatoes, whole carrots and wilted greens and again was excellent. ", "For dessert we chose the cheeseboard trolley option costing an additional \u00a34.50. The Maitre D' was impressive not just naming but also providing descriptions of the around 20 cheeses on the cheese trolley. - excellent at his job.", "For the overall experience of atmosphere, quality of food, presentation and attentiveness of the serving staff we would say that Boisdale Canary Wharf was definitely the very best Sunday traditional lunch that we have had and we cannot rate this restaurant more highly."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r189176890", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good experience average food ", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "31 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review.", "I am delighted you enjoyed the atmosphere of the venue & the service provided. With regards to your comments on the food I apologise should it not have been to your standards. We sell a great amount of the Seafood Bisque, made only of finest Scottish seafood it displays a rich, intense flavour, and we receive tremendous feedback for it. Over the past 2 years we have seen a big shift in our customer base preferring lighter, healthier & more carefully seasoned dishes, so we do err on the side of caution when preparing our dishes, however Maldon Salt and Pepper grinders are available at every table; so additional seasoning may be added according to personal preference. I am happy to hear that our chocolate fondant hit the sweet spot! Our menu has been designed to provide ample choice for all diners and tastes & a wide variety of price ranges are available starting from 22GBP for a three course lunch. I hope to welcome you back in the very near future.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "nervosa", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r189176890-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I went with my friend to experience a quality scotish sea food. Atmosfear is great abd staff are good too. We ordered lobster seafood soup which was average then we had grilled salmone for the main was okay,salamon was not seasoned and plant with eggplant souce which was nicely seasoned but not going very well with the salmone. We had chocolete foundate for desserts which was lovely. I will go again to listen to the band as we left early that day. I recommend the place for the nice atmosfear though its a bit pricy for what you get. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r189648404", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great place. Great Atmosphere. Quirky - loved it!", "diner_date": " December 2013", "rating_date": "4 January 2014", "answer_text": ["Wow!", "Thank you for you lovely & extensive review.", "We pride ourselves on our service and British food, so your comments went down a treat! I am delighted we were able to compensate for the terrible weather, something I unfortunately cannot control, yet. I am also very pleased to hear you booked because of the review posted by other members of TA. It is nice to know that our reviews are making an impact. When you do get the chance to come again, please let us know under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk and we will make sure to say hello & thank you personally!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Louise P", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r189648404-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I took a chance on booking a surprise dinner at Boisdales for my husband's birthday in December as didn't know of anyone that had been and made my decision on the basis of the reviews here on TA! I was a little apprehensive as we were with two friends, it was a filthy night and due to train problems we drove from Essex. I was therefore hoping we were not going to be disappointed. ", "I need not have worried. We had a fantastic night. The decor is fab with tartan carpet, sounds awful but works brilliantly, moose heads and so many whiskies displayed I thought it was an optical illusion!! ", "My husband had the haggis which was amazing. Two of us had the smoked mackerel which was a delight. For mains my husband and I both had the fillet steak burger with black truffle mayo, field mushrooms and gruyere. Oh my - heaven on a plate. Accompanied with probably one of the best home made fries ever!! They were nicely salted, crispy and cooked with the skins on.", "I had emailed the restaurant in advance to say it was a birthday but had totally forgotten and it was a lovely surprise when a complementary sticky toffee pudding plate came out with Happy Birthday written around the side of the plate. He wasn't going to have a dessert but this would have been the one he would have chosen. Thanks very much for doing this for him, however sadly for him we all dived in and it was delicious.", "There is live music every night here and the patron is Jools Holland so although we had to pay an extra \u00a34.50 per head for this with restricted view, I wasn't concerned as am sure Jools wouldn't put his name to an establishment unless the quality of the perfomers were excellent. And they were. I'm afraid I can't remember their names but they were superb and made the evening such great fun.", "I have no hesitation at all in recommending this great restaurant - really refreshing to have great live music, great food and the staff were very friendly and helpful which is so important and can make or break a meal in my opinion.", "Well done we will definitely be back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r190537385", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Wonderful experience", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "11 January 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your great review.", "I am really pleased you enjoyed the service as well as the band. We have a very extensive menu, thanks to the many wonderful ingredients Britain has to offer. To ensure our services run as smooth as possible & minimise the impact for all our customers, we have to narrow down the choices. This is customary in most restaurants. I hope this clarifies the situation & look forward to welcoming you soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "winniesquare", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r190537385-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Frank Sinatra tribute night with a big band. The entertainment and service was fantastic. The food was good, but as we were a party of twelve the choices were not great"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r190734219", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Lunch", "diner_date": " January 2014", "rating_date": "13 January 2014", "answer_text": ["We have only started serving Sunday lunches at the end of October, so I am delighted you enjoyed the afternoon. The Sunday lunch really is amazing value for money & the dry aged Scottish beef being slow cooked for hours in the oven is just what you need on Sundays. Why don\u2019t you try one of our sharing roasts (whole roast suckling pig, saddle of venison or leg of lamb, just look on our website for more details...)", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Frances21London", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "42"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r190734219-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Four of us went for Sunday Lunch. Started with Bloody Mary's which were excellent then went for the set menu which included as much red or white wine that you wanted to drink. Very good choice of food considering it was a set menu. Two of us had the beef and two had the pork both served with a good selection of vegetables and it was all very good. My friends assured me that the puddings were extremely good but I opted for the cheeseboard and wasn't disappointed despite having to pay a little extra for it.", "Live music playing in the background throughout the lunchtime period also added to the experience. All in all a very nice afternoon !"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r189749081", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A great start to 2014", "diner_date": " January 2014", "rating_date": "5 January 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your charming review.", "I was pleased see you return and more so that you again enjoyed yourselves. I can only agree that Jordan was fabulous and we cannot wait to have him back on the 6th February! Hopefully I will be able to see you then.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LylaPlum", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "59"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r189749081-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Have been to Boisdales before and had a superb evening so reserved a table for seven situated at the front of the stage as we heard the same band, The Jordan Marsh Band, were there again. Once again, the food was great, a new menu with plenty of choice, the lobster bisque is wonderful and the steaks are superb! Our waiter was attentive all evening making sure everything was ok. The restaurant has a great ambience and the atmosphere when the band started playing was electric! Only into the second song of their first set, people we up and dancing and that is how the evening progressed. We all agreed that we had had an absolutely wonderful evening, culminating in the men of our group retreating to the cigar lounge once the band had left the stage. All in all a fantastic evening, can't wait to return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r190647008", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What a night!", "diner_date": " December 2013", "rating_date": "12 January 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your lovely review.", "I am delighted you enjoyed the New Year\u2019s Eve night. We ourselves enjoyed it so much it did not feel like work at all! Suspiciously Elvis really knows how to put on a show. For the next time around we\u2019ve already booked a certain legendary Swedish pop act tribute\u2026 ", "Please visit again soon and let us know under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk when you plan on returning.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "GolfkingKent", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "34"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r190647008-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Absolutely superb night to see in the New Year! ", "Started with drinks in the bar, gambling on the casino tables, dinner in the restaurant which was lovely, food was great, then Elvis impersonator and his band and dancing girls rocked the night away till the bells chimed. Then could see the lights and fireworks across London from the terrace."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r191737246", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "so much better, service was fantastic, food and cocktails oh yes !!!!", "diner_date": " January 2014", "rating_date": "22 January 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for visiting again and sharing your experience with us.", "I am delighted Fernando looked after you so well; he has been wonderful since joining us as a food runner almost two years ago, and now he is one of our most popular waiters. As all our staff are rewarded when mentioned in despatches, Fernando can look forward to a small surprise next weekend. We look forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "RickyTracey", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "124"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "118"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r191737246-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Following my previous review I said that Boisdales had the potential to be my new favourite place. Well after last Saturday night it is. We didn't have the best seats or the best view but we had the best waiter, (Fernando) the best cocktails and the best steak whilst listening to a fabulous singer. Thank you, we plan on visiting on the 30th January, like I said my new favourite place !!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r188729627", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great place for business lunch", "diner_date": " December 2013", "rating_date": "27 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for commenting on your experience & for choosing us to host your Christmas lunch. We roast our Haggis for maximum flavour so I am pleased you enjoyed this. I was saddened to hear your steaks had been overcooked; I can only apologise profusely for this as this should not have been the case. Our meat is cut from highest quality grass fed Aberdeenshire cattle and dry aged between 21 and 40 days depending on the cut ensuring to ensure best flavour and texture, having been slightly overdone will have impacted on the flavour and as such may lead to you preferring others on this occasion. Still I am delighted you enjoyed the atmosphere and the service we particularly pride ourselves on. ", "I look forward to welcoming you back soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "KKCH88", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r188729627-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Took some clients to Boisdale Canary Wharf for Christmas lunch for a group of 8. Most of us had the haggis as starter, which was excellent. We all opted for steaks as the main. The quality of the meat was good, but I'd say probably not as good as Goodman and Hawksmoor. Also they were cooked more well done than we asked.", "Nevertheless the service and the atmosphere was good."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r191992479", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Xmas night", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "25 January 2014", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your kind review.", "I am happy you enjoyed your evening with us. We tend to have a wide variety of music on display ranging from classic jazz tunes over blues, to soul a little rock (&roll)\u2026 so see out website for more detail of upcoming shows. Personally I am looking forward to the return of the \u2018Bohemians\u2019 a Queen tribute; they were just sensational last time.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Paulcurtis", "reviewer_origin": ["Langley, Canada"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "55"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "33"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r191992479-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a chance to get tickets to the Las Vegas night, atmosphere was great and the people there on a Saturday night were all having a great time!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r187821266", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Start to Christmas", "diner_date": " December 2013", "rating_date": "16 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Roger,", "Thank you for your recent review. We were delighted to hear that you are both a frequent visitor and that you find the service 'excellent and very friendly'", "I was sorry to read however of your disappointment with the Fillet Steak on your last visit.", "The pre-cooked steak weights are approximate and we randomly check all the beef at the point of delivery. What you must consider is the weight of the bone which if removed is at least two ounces. leaving the weight of the meat itself at 8 - 10oz. So actually only a few ounces more than the tornado fillet at 7oz. One also has to consider the cooking temperature as the longer it cooks the more prone to shrinkage. What you are really paying the premium for, is the additional flavour that is derived from the bone marrow as it leaks into the meat during the cooking process, giving it, in my opinion a far superior flavour. There is also the possibility that it slipped through the net and was simply under-weight, for this we apologise. ", "I would be very grateful if you could contact us on manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk so we can ensure your next visit is memorable on the beef front!", "Kind regards,", "Nathan J Evans"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Roger C", "reviewer_origin": ["Hereford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "97"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "48"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r187821266-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went here last Saturday night with friends.Have been several times before so knew what to expect.Firstly the service is excellent from very friendly staff.The entertainment like last year was a great way to start Christmas however the ability to dance on these nights which most people enjoy is compromised by the minute area allowed for dancing.The food was generally good with a couple of exceptions from the norm.Two of us had the fillet steak,one on the bone and the other not.The on the bone steak is supposed to be 10-12oz and the other half that.Despite paying a premium of well over \u00a330 it was very small,in fact smaller than the 6-7oz one.An establishment that prides itself on the quality of its meat must make sure that portions reflect the price one is paying,not leaving customers feeling overcharged for a small piece of albeit very good steak."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r187878700", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "everything was 5 star", "diner_date": " December 2013", "rating_date": "17 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "WOW - thank you so much for a lovely review which filled the team with pride.", "We were delighted that you rated it a five star experience and look forward to welcoming you back very soon. ", "Be sure to send us an email on manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk before your next visit so we can thank you personally.", "Best wishes,", "Nathan J Evans"], "reviewer_pseudo": "debra d", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "139"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "126"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r187878700-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to Boisdale with friends for the first time on Saturday, for the christmas show - and what a great way to start the festive season! Everything was superb - the service, the food, the show and the great atmosphere, we just couldn't fault it. ", "At some places with music the food plays second fiddle but not here, both were excellent - I can highly recommend the truffle burger.", "I can't understand how we've only just found this place and we plan to be back soon!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r187980970", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "boisdale canary wharf", "diner_date": " April 2013", "rating_date": "18 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review. I am delighted you enjoy visiting us. Music wise we do have many nights of jazz but will also host bands playing blues, soul and many of the related genres. I feel this way we can provide a more interesting mix of atmospheres in the restaurant while also offering more choice to our customers. I am disappointed to hear that you have had slow service in the bar and want to assure you that we are working hard on improving this. Hopefully you can understand that December has been extremely busy and this should not reflect the norm.", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "justiceleaguebatman", "reviewer_origin": ["london"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r187980970-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very good place for food and drinks. The music is good but not always jazz and the bar on the lower level can be quite busy with office workers with the service sometimes slow. Wide range of whiskeys."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r187979086", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "very good and trendy place", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "18 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "Thank you very much for taking the time to post a review.", "We were delighted that you have enjoyed drinks with us at the bar, but was sorry to hear that you experienced delays on service. ", "We pride ourselves on our attentive customer ethic and we are constantly working to improve the guest experience. ", "Perhaps you could join us on the second floor in the main restaurant or take in our live show.", "Please do email us ahead of your next visit and we will be sure to say hello.", "manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk", "Best wishes,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sylvain_MBK", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r187979086-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I only went for drinks a few times, and the set up and atmosphere ressemble more the city than Canary Wharf area, which is refreshing! Good service, but as the place fills up and gets busy, service starts lagging and orders might get seriously delayed! But definitely worth a visit!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r188188815", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good fun but service only OK", "diner_date": " December 2013", "rating_date": "21 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "I am delighted that you enjoyed the entertainment and thought it good value, I am obviously disappointed that the service fell short.", "Firstly in regard your table: Tables are allocated in two ways, firstly premium ticket holders (these are the front section closest to the stage and were sold at \u00a325 pet ticket, though these sell quickly and may have already been unavailable when you booked) then we allocate the remaining tickets based on the date the tickets were purchased. I appreciate that as a result you were near the back of the room and I would agree that there are better places to sit, though you do still have a good view of the stage from there.", "We are obviously trading very heavily at Christmas, but that should not have been to the detriment of the excellent service that we pride ourselves upon. I am thrilled that you are considering us as your 'new favourite place'. Please contact the General Manager under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk and we can find out more & restore your trust.", "Nathan J Evans"], "reviewer_pseudo": "RickyTracey", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "124"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "118"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "20", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r188188815-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked a table and paid \u00a315 each for entertainment, which was good value and good fun. However the service at the table was not excellent. The waiter was nice but too busy to give any individual attention to us and we waited on many occasions to order more drinks. Food was very good but missing items meant we had to wait to catch the waiter again and again for the missing items to be delivered. This is not marketed as a low end restaurant and this is just not good enough. ", "Our table seemed to be an 'extra' placed in the thoroughfare to the exit and toilet and my chair being bumped constantly did not add to the ambience of the evening but did not ruin it.", "This venue has the potential to be my new favourite place but needs to reduce the number of tables or increase the number of staff if attentive, professional service is their aim."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r188104890", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Mediocre disorganised and expensive", "diner_date": " December 2013", "rating_date": "20 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Yvonne,", "I was sorry to hear that you felt \u00a315 to see ten very experienced and well respected musicians & singers, expensive. Yes they are all middle-aged, and were offended by your ageist remarks.", "The members of the orchestra are some of the best jazz musicians in the UK and play regularly with Jools Holland and as part of the Ronnie Scott's house band. There were no Michael Buble songs in the set.", "The Christmas shows sold out every night for 16 nights and I am delighted to say your view is not shared.", "Our bartenders have had cocktails featured in Difford's guide - the definitive cocktail book, for the quality of the cocktails that they consistently produce. The Boisdale Mojito contains 50 ml of quality rum and it is indeed charged with ice, limes & mint - as all the best Mojitos are. Only badly made cocktails taste of the base spirit to the exclusion of anything else.", "Far from being run by accountants we are a small independent restaurant company still being run by those that started it 25 years ago. What we have never lacked is heart or character.", "The capacity of the restaurant is 250, with additional space in private dining and a further 100 seats in the Oyster Bar & Grill on the 1st Floor. 800 covers is obviously a total fabrication.", "I hope you find somewhere more to your taste in terms of ambiance, cocktails and entertainment.", "Yours sincerely,", "Nathan J Evans", "Deputy Managing Director & Shareholder ", "."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Yvonne016", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "98"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "129"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "20", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r188104890-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Imagine paying \u00a315 each for some middle age men to perform Frank Sinatra and Michael Buble and then another \u00a380 on top. Not a cheap night out to say the least. It was bursting at the seams, apparently they can seat 800 people and felt like more like a bustling airport lunch than relaxing place to eat. I suppose it is Xmas party week so it's out of the ordinary with dozens of office parties. Avoid the mojitos, they were non existent and full of ice, when I complained they said they couldn't remove the ice and put more of the cocktail in because they were measured and it just wouldn't work. I think that sums the place up. It felt like it was run by accountants, working to a money-making formula. No heart or character."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r188059973", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fun Friday night in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "19 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review.", "I was pleased to hear you enjoyed the evening on the whole. During the Christmas period we obviously trade heavily & the weekend in question our busiest since opening. Should there have been a bit of confusion regarding you booking I would sincerely like to apologise, still, I was pleased to hear it was rectified. We constantly strive to better ourselves and your comments on our service have been noted. I hope I can welcome you again soon to Boisdale of Canary Wharf & hope you have had a great start to 2014.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sjhance", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r188059973-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to Boisdale because I won a bottle of wine there and had a good evening - excellent music, very good food, nice ambiance. Two cautions: initially they tried to sit us in a bar which isn't even on the same floor as the music venue until we protested. This isn't 'restricted view' it's 'no view at all and no sound either'. Also service was somewhat variable - sometimes attentive, other times hard to get attention. ", " "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r188313906", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "In summary a perfect evening", "diner_date": " December 2013", "rating_date": "22 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your fabulous review.", "I am thrilled you had such a wonderful time with us. We are very fond of the steaks we serve, mostly from grass fed Aberdeenshire cattle and dry aged for up to 40 days to ensure deep, intense flavours. Equally only British cheeses make sense as the island produces an array of high quality cheeses. I am especially proud to hear you received excellent service from all our staff. We strive to provide the best experience possible and we are all glad to hear our work has paid off for you. Please let me know when you are back under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk, I would like to thank you personally.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "cramorra", "reviewer_origin": ["Isle of Wight, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "377"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "166"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r188313906-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The atmosphere puts you back in time when cruise liners were transatlantic liners and bars were for men and women who smoked", "Excellent food - some of the best steak I ever had (10/10) with simple but matching sides - good chips perfect mushroom sauce", "An Englsih only cheese trolley which was great value and well matured cheeses - expensive but outstanding scotch selection, Bar Men who knew what they were doing. It is worth noting for people loca to the area that they offer a membership which gives significant discounts on the expansive wine list entertainemnt.", "On the evening we went we had despite a late booking an excellent table not too cloe not to far to the music and nice views over cabot place. The Show was good and spirited", "We enjoyed our evening and I will be back", "Outstanding, well trained service staff who know what they are doing and serving- thank you"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r188176687", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Too busy at Christmas time", "diner_date": " December 2013", "rating_date": "21 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "Thank you for your recent review.", "I'm sorry that you found the background noise from other guests disturbing, it is the nature of the time of year that we are at capacity with many very much in the festive mood, which we very much encourage as we seeing us providing a night out not just a romantic dinner. The date in question was the busiest day of the year.", "I am surprised that you were so put off by the band. We have live music every single night and you had purchased tickets at \u00a315 per person for the show. ", "May I suggest a table in our Oyster Bar & Grill next time, where there is no live music and therefore no ticket purchase necessary. You can still see Cabot Square from the first floor. The Christmas Show has received hundreds of compliments and has sold out on all, of the 16 nights. I am sorry you felt it 'not-so-good' & 'not so welcome'. I was also very sorry to hear that your turkey came without gravy. I have spent the last two weeks at the pass, in our kitchen at Canary Wharf so I could see every plate. Maybe you had requested no pork, which would not only have excluded the pork chipolata sausages & stuffing but also the gravy that is made from both pork and turkey stock. We are increasingly seeing a real move towards reduced salt from our customers and as a result we have adjusted the seasoning of our food, airing on the lighter side. We have Maldon salt & pepper mills on the table so guests can adjust to their own tastes.", "I hope this addresses your concerns.", "Yours sincerely,", "Nathan J Evans"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Little-Fruit-Bat", "reviewer_origin": ["England"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "135"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "181"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r188176687-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to this restaurant for a Christmas dinner, mainly because of the scenery such as the lit-up trees that you can see from the windows. However, overall it was a disappointing experience, I guess mainly due to the fact that if you have to cook for hundreds of people at the same time, you can't get it right. The starters were ok, however the \"turkey with trimmings\" was not seasoned, didn't come with any gravy and was basically dry. The roast potatoes didn't taste of much either. We could already hardly talk to each other due to the loud noise of all the other guests when not-so-good and not-so-welcome even louder music started. I know that many people like this place, but I prefer quiet places with good food."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r184045468", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Bar Scene & Jazz Music", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "8 November 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your very kind review.", "I am delighted you enjoyed your time with us. Perhaps you would like to return in December when we will have our fabulous Christmas show running? In any case, please let us know when you plan on returning under manager@boisdale-co.uk and we will make sure to say hi!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "joydeep_das3", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "81"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "29"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r184045468-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited Boisdale for Drinks & dinner on Thu night, fab bar scene with good collection of whiskies & the restaurant above had good jazz music to accompany along with good food! overall great experience:)"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r186507115", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Simple meals but dont exceptionally well", "diner_date": " December 2013", "rating_date": "2 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for taking the time to write about us.", "I was happy to hear you thought our service and food was great. When it comes to the music on Sundays the emphasis is more on accompanying the lunch as opposed to being the main focus, so our musicians generally play with very little amplification. Should the music on this occasion have been too quiet I sincerely apologise. I have already made all managers aware to keep a closer eye on music volumes. When you book next, let us know that you would like to appreciate the music and we will aim to get you a table closer to the stage.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Mark J", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "115"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "88"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r186507115-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Have been here 2/3 times, most recently this weekend, and i havent been able to find much fault, good service (we had a table issue that was dealt with very well), food is well prepared, high standards and excellent meat quality", "my only small bug bear, is with the sunday Jazz event, the place gets too noisy to really appreciate the music", "but as a dining experience, fantastic"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r184156715", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Regular lunch spot", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "9 November 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for you great review.", "I am glad you are enjoying the Oyster Bar & Grill on the first floor & our wonderful Hamburgers (I\u2019m all for the \u201cCaprese\u201d with Pesto & Mozzarella at the moment). The bar on the first floor is also really lovely on a Saturday with low lights and plenty seats at the window available for drinks in the evening; now that the Holiday decorations have been put up on the streets it is an even more magical sight!", "The team and I look forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "R1218ZPpatrickm", "reviewer_origin": ["London, UK"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r184156715-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I work in Canary Wharf, so this is a local haunt. Go lots of lunch to the more casual restaurant for the best hamburgers in town. The bar is nice as well for after work drinks. The restaurant upstairs is very nice, but a bit more formal than i'm usually looking for. However, did take my wife for dinner and jazz for her birthday. ", "As a relaxed place for a good burger with co-workers for Friday lunch, can't be beaten."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r184332200", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Really great night", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "11 November 2013", "answer_text": ["I am delighted to hear you had a lovely evening & thank you for taking the time to review us.", "Our Head Chef is happy to hear you enjoyed the food, especially the Crab Linguine, whilst I am equally pleased that our Service Staff were able to make you feel comfortable. Saturday was a really good night, and Stephen Triffitt, who impersonated Frank, is the best I have seen! There are other nights like our ABBA Magic night on Saturday the 16th that may be civilised, but there is much more energy in the room with plenty of dancing expected, so make sure to check our website for the upcoming bands!", "When you plan on visiting us again, please let me know under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk so we can make sure to say \u201cHello\u201d.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "paulwilkinson1", "reviewer_origin": ["Chelmsford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r184332200-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Took my girlfriend on Saturday and had a really good time. We were sat near the stage where a Frank Sinantra Tribute band were playing and it created a nice atmosphere for dining. I had the steak and chips with green peppercorn sauce which was nice. My girlfriend had the crab linguini which was out of this world. Great food, great friendly service and the atmosphere was just how i hoped from this place. I would recommend Boisdale for anyone who wants a great civilised evening with your other half, she really enjoyed herself and couldn't wipe the smile off her face. Thanks Boisdale"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r184773941", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Great band, great decor, poor service & incredibly poor food", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "15 November 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "Thank you for taking time to review our restaurant after your guest won, one of our social media competitions. I am only sorry that your evening fell so short of your expectations.", "Firstly to clarify the Facebook prize value:", " ", "1. Three months membership to the Boisdale Club @ \u00a320 per month \u00a360.00", "2. Bottle of our excellent Boisdale wines from Chateau de Sours, Bordeaux \u00a312.50", "3. Premium Whisky miniature \u00a35.60", "4. Handmade chocolates \u00a32.00", "5. Boisdale Blue Rhythm Band CD \u00a310.00", "6. Two glasses of Prosecco @ \u00a36.50 a flute \u00a313.00", "7. Two premium tickets for the show @ \u00a320 \u00a340.00", "Total \u00a3143.10", "The three month membership entitles both the member and a guest to attend at least 6 free events over the period and significant discounts off members dinners, 20% off wine & cigars and as such is worth considerably more than the \u00a360 cost for the three months. I am completely confident that the prize offered was as stated.", "That aside, I was very sad to hear that you thought the service, unfriendly and the food to be 'incredibly poor'.", "The Haggis is our best selling first course and we sell over a metric tonne a month across our three London businesses. It is made by Macsween in Scotland and is widely regarded as the best haggis and regularly wins in blind tastings. We roast it for a more intense flavour. It certainly does not herald from a packet. The haggis is very peppery and seasoned by Macsween. We only lightly season the 'neeps' & 'tatties' as customer's tastes vary. There is a salt & pepper mill on every table. I was sorry that the burger fell so short. The meat is Scottish and of the same quality we use in our steak cuts - the best. Again this often proves to be one of the most popular choices. The menu you ate from is our \u00a319.75 set menu for two courses and burger sales run into the hundreds per week, with over 100 sold as take-away most Fridays. It appears on this occasion that the burger and bun was not up to the usual high standard. The chips are hand-cut and fried, never from the oven. While this leaves you with the usual variations from potatoes across the season, they should never be anything other than excellent. I'm very sorry that both the burger and the chips were well below par.", "I would be grateful if you could contact us on manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk where we can deal with your complaint directly.", "Yours sincerely,", "NJ Evans"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Dunmall", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "56"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "93"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "30", "20", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r184773941-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My friend managed to secure a VIP Table, \"\u00a3100 Goody Bag containing a \u00a350 bottle of wine\" that we were told and two glasses of Prosecco.", "Initial thoughts and impressions were good; no welcome of any kind but stunning decor, and a high quality soul band that were of exceptional quality.", "Unfortunately, that was very much the high point of the evening. We received the goody bag when we ordered a table, which contained a cheap looking \"Boisdale\" bottle of Red Wine, a cheap ballpoint pen, a CD of the house band, a pamphlet and a chocolate brownie in tissue paper - I would say that the contents total value was around \u00a38.00. Very disappointing and quite insulting.", "We ordered food, which was very expensive indeed. The service was very poor - a disinterested, miserable waitress attended us - no greeting, no welcome, no smile or kindness of any kind, just a formulaic way of going about their business. I ordered Haggis to start - very poor quality, tasted very much as if it had been taken from a packet or frozen; it was very bland, as were the vegetables - not even basic seasoning of any kind. ", "Then we ordered the main course. The Steak Burger was \u00a315.00 - very expensive but I thought it would be a \"safe bet\" after the disappointment of the starters. It was probably the worst quality meal I have ordered and tasted at a restaurant - the bun was burnt and tasted cheap, again, very much as if someone had taken it from a packet. The burger was incredibly, incredibly ordinary - I have tasted far better in Wetherspoon's and even in Burger King; the chips were just bland oven chips with nothing to get excited about at all. It was astonishingly poor quality - I can't quite believe they would serve this in Canary Wharf. My friend had the chicken, which was also astonishing bland with watery side dishes.", "We didn't bother with desert due to the extraordinary low quality of the food. We had another glass of wine and watched the band who were very good and the best thing about the whole evening. We voiced our concerns at the end of the evening and we were refunded one course, which was appreciated but the whole evening left a very sour taste in our mouths. We travelled a long way from the Kent area on the promise of the table and goody bag, but it felt like a huge con - if the food had any kind of quality, it would have been worth it but it really was much worse than you can get in any chain pub.", "Overall, I certainly wouldn't return or recommend it to any others. Extremely disappointing that a restaurant, which clearly has delusions of grandeur, can't even get the most basic of things right; there can't be many worse places to go in terms of service and food in Central London."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r185065679", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Abba Mania", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "18 November 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your fabulous review.", "I am delighted you enjoyed the food and service. We pride ourselves on our standards. To hear we have hit the spot is very rewarding. I cannot wait to welcome you again soon!", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JamesBowater", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r185065679-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A group of us went to Boisdale of Canary Wharf on Saturday for dinner and the Abba Mania tribute. The food was fantastic - my saddleback pork dish was simply delicious! The atmosphere was so good with the Abba guys doing a really good job. The staff were so attentive and polite - service with a smile goes such a long way. Cannot recommend this place more highly! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r185285072", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Shambles of a Service", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "20 November 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Nina,", "Our booking for, exclusive use of our restaurant tonight was confirmed on the 23rd June 2013, though had been recorded as a provisional booking for a two months prior.", "We do not have anyone named Lisa working on reception and have never taken a dinner booking for 12 without written confirmation, a deposit and pre-purchased tickets for the show.", "I can only imagine that you have made a booking elsewhere in error.", "As you can see from our previous reviews, we pride ourselves on our levels of customer service", "NJ EVANS"], "reviewer_pseudo": "notwitteracct", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r185285072-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["On 24th October I made a booking for a table for 6/7 people over the phone with Lisa. I have called to amend the timing of the booking only to be told the restaurant is booked out. When I made the booking I requested a table by the window, which she clearly stated she said she would try and accommodate, there was no mention of completing form to confirm a booking AND IMPORTANTLY there was there a mention the restaurant was booked out. Today I am being told the restaurant has been booked out for months, this is completed untrue as I recall the conversation quite clearly and if the restaurant was booked out for months why was there no mention when I called on 24th October?. Quite frankly this is appalling customer service from yourself. Just to make you aware I have previously made a booking for 12 + people and never had to complete a form it has always been done over the phone. I do not want to be told by your member of staff - who has made an error that she appreciates what I am saying - when completely she is covering her own mistakes as you have received a booking for the whole night and have not bothered to contact us to cancel our booking. Also, to be told that maybe I was enquiring when I called. I know what my intentions were when making the booking - the difference between a confirmation of a booking and an enquiry. Your staff need to be clear what the process is in a booking and cannot make it up as they go as and when it suits them. Nothing more than a shambles of a service!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r185466703", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A beautiful restaurant with great staff & music!", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "22 November 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review.", "I am pleased that you thoroughly enjoyed yourself.", "I look forward to welcoming you back soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mrsmac72", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r185466703-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A gorgeously decorated restaurant with friendly, efficient staff, lovely food and great music! I can't wait to go back :)"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r185866475", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice Haggis", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "25 November 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your kind review.", "I am delighted you enjoyed the food and our great whisky selection. You shouldn\u2019t worry about joining us for a romantic dinner though! While Christmas time is certainly a bit busier, we have an array of different evening shows so please stay on the lookout for something a little more subtle. Should you plan on visiting for such an occasion, drop me a line under falko@boisdale-cw.co.uk, I would be happy to make a few suggestions.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Frankie-the-Hun", "reviewer_origin": ["Germany"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "120"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "85"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r185866475-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["So this is where the beancounters go to party or so I thought when entering the gaudy halls of Boisdale's at Canary Wharf. I duly enjoyed the evening. Food was great, especially the little Haggis I got with a glass of whisky accompanying it. All in all this place has an overwhelming choice of Scotch and other members of the whisky family. Lovely wines, too. It's great for big group events. Going there for a romantic dinner might fell a little strange."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r186420520", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "FABULOUS ALL ROUND", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "1 December 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your lovely review.", "Richard and Anna also extend their thanks as they have already received a little something from me; as is always the case when staff members are mentioned in despatches. I am absolutely thrilled you have enjoyed your birthday celebration! We all look forward to welcoming you again soon. ", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "shelbelle123Kent", "reviewer_origin": ["kent"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r186420520-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["WOW....we has such a good evening here last night celebrating mu birthday. Excellent food drink and above all service...a special mention to our waiter Rich and our waitress Ana (who was on her 1st night) they couldn't do enough for us.....we chose the Langoustines and Haggis for starters and the Rib Eye Steak for main course all of which were presented fantastically and tasted divine. I was given complimentary glasses of champagne and a beautiful dessert wishing me Happy Birthday. We watched the Motown band and enjoyed it so much they really were fantastic and very professional and did a great job of getting everyone involved. Couldn't recommend this enough....everything 5 star, we will definitely return and recommend to our friends. thank you for a truly brilliant night Boisdale and especially Rich and Ana...you were both stars."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r184023552", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Superb/Stunning/Brilliant", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "8 November 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you!", "Your review makes us very proud. We all work incredibly hard to make your evening one of the most enjoyable you can have; so I am delighted we have achieved just that.", "Kindly let me know when you plan on visiting again under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk when you plan on returning I would like to say \"Thank You\" personally.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ravingeddie", "reviewer_origin": ["United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "355"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "179"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r184023552-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went last night, the service, the food, the entertainment, and the atmosphere was superb...", "Everything for me was 5 out of 5..", "Awsome, will be back regular no doubt."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r182081043", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Bar", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "23 October 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your lovely review.", "We are delighted you think we can compete with the best. As we have recently changed our burger offerings, so receiving great feedback on them is brilliant. We recommend to order different varieties when out with friends and then share them so you can get to taste them all!", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon!", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Konstantin S", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r182081043-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great bar, really enjoyed it! One of the best bars in the area! Great burgers too! Highly recommended!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r183031445", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "what a buzz at Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "31 October 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your marvellous review.", "The Head Chef and I are delighted you had such a wonderful evening and enjoyed our finest grass fed Scottish dry-aged steaks. I can understand your agony at having to choose from the a la carte menu, but when Britain has so much to offer it is difficult to leave items off the menu! ", "We look forward to welcoming you all back soon and your friend so we can add whisky number 19 to his list.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Lynjcecil", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "71"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r183031445-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Just love the cool live jazz, go Thursday nights to hear the amazing soulstress Lizzie Deane and hit the dance floor! The steaks are fabulous, they served roasted fillet to 40 of us, it was perfect-pink but not bloody, and the most delicious flavour and texture. These guys know their meat! Love their oysters and shellfish too, the agonies of indecision when eating a la carte! And if you are a whisky man or woman, choose from over 1,000 different ones at the bar. One friend is up to 18, not all in one evening! This is a very favourite place!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r183045944", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food great music", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "31 October 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your great review.", "I am delighted you enjoyed your night with us. Do check our website for exciting bands coming up & also great events ranging for tastings to dinners to possible fun/nonsense (chopping champagne corks of with a sword comes to mind\u2026)", "We all look forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Brentwalsh", "reviewer_origin": ["Reigate, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "61"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "34"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r183045944-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went for my Brothers 40th Birthday last Saturday. My first time here. I could not fault it. The food was excellent the service first class & a great band playing. ", "Will be back very soon. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r182119379", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Oddness - but set menu good value", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "23 October 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review.", "I was pleased to read you enjoyed the set menu, yet disappointed to hear you did not rate the ambience. I would be delighted if you could contact me under dgm@boisdale-cw.co.uk to discuss your experience in more detail.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "BarristerLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "424"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "254"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r182119379-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["What a strange, strange place. Faux Scottish barn of a place amongst the office buildings of CW. The place is vast - bar & grill, nice terrace area on 1 floor, restaurant above with a jazz band (?????). Table by the window in the restaurant is a must otherwise could be sitting in a fairly grim Scottish hotel from the 70s.", "But....had the set menu on a Tuesday night from an online booking service & was fine - nice gravadlax & burger & glass of prosecco.", "it obviously does well - inclined to think that's a result of the limited offerings around rather than genuine quality."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r182918116", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Highly recommended night out!", "diner_date": " September 2013", "rating_date": "30 October 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your lovely review.", "I am happy that your partner chose us and that you had a fabulous evening. We love the environment we work in as we feel it makes you feel welcome and in the evenings when the lights go down it just turns magical. To hear that the service was spot on and the drink menu could impress is fantastic. I was irked by your comment on the portion sizes; our steaks range up to 18oz, our richly filled Fish Pie I can never quite finish and our Hamburgers are to be reckoned with. I would be happy to hear in more detail about the dishes you chose on the night; I take note however that you thought them delicious and well presented. Visit our website for more details on upcoming events and live music and do let me know when you plan to visit again, I would love to say \u2018Hi\u2019", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Omar A", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r182918116-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My partner booked this venue as a surprise night out. It takes a lot to impress me and this venue did just that! We were made to feel very important as soon as we stepped inside. The decor is modern yet holds on to traditional values. Inside there are different parts which can be used in different ways eg. meet friends or for families or for a romantic night as a couple. We had a sweet table close to the front with other couples. Everyone looked fantastic under the lighting and backgorund deep rich colours. The service was superb, friendly, smiley and knowledgeable. The drinks list was equally impressive. The food arrived well presented, smelling great and tasting just right. the only downside was that the portions were not as big as I would have liked. The live music made everything feel real and special. The musicians were entertaining and skillful. They made us smile, grow closer, wonder in amazement and forget where we were! When we called it a night finally, we were both surprised by how cheap this had all been. I strongly recommend this place. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r183403206", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Boisdale Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "3 November 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for trying us and for your charming review.", "We take every effort to ensure all guest are aware of the ticket charge for the music, if this was not the case with you I sincerely apologise this should not have happened; still I was happy to read you enjoyed music. I have passed your review on to the Head Chef and he was thrilled you enjoyed your meal, in my case especially the steak tartare which we train on a lot to ensure we prepare it jus the way you like it. I am thrilled to hear you enjoyed our service becoming your new favourite before Roast, who run a wonderful restaurant themselves.", "Thank you again.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "drjplawrence", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "66"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r183403206-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Swanky, stylish,brilliant food.", "Gave this place a go on the off chance and not disappointed.", "Piano player came on at 7pm - be warned they will charge \u00a34.50pp to your bill if you are there when music is on - but I did not mind,as musician was good.", "Started with steak tartare,prepared at the table and my daughter had shellfish bisque,both excellent.", "Followed by an exquisite steak and kidney pudding (meat slow cooked for 15 hours) - my daughter had belly of pork,sides of mash,spinach and carrots - all perfectly done.", "Portions are generous too.", "Service good and unobtrusive.", "This is my current favourite restaurant,just pipping Roast in Borough Market.", "Window seat recommended for Boisdale.", "They also do a lot of music evenings which look fun.", "A definite revisit here"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r183421036", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Incredible service, superb food & a lot of fun", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "3 November 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your wonderful review.", "Richard and Jon will be rewarded, as are all members of staff being mentioned in despatches; I am delighted they were able to provide excellent service for you. Our Head Chef is pleased to hear you enjoyed our steaks and specials. The Sancerre is delicious with seafood and the deep, red fruits and medium tannins of Malbec really go well with steaks, so you have made great choices.", "I am delighted you enjoyed the Jive Aces, they are sure to return, but check on our website for more fabulous acts coming up. I am pleased your enjoyed the ambience and service, we work relentlessly to provide an intimate feel in our restaurant.", "I am looking forward to welcoming you again in the near future.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "heididrummond", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r183421036-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The incredible service is what sets this restaurant apart. The staff are attentive, friendly and clearly take great pride in what they do. A special mention must go to Richard, who described in wonderful detail the 10 cheeses we had selected from the cheese trolly and John who gave us an fantastically informative tour of the cigar library. Such theatre on a night out for dinner are too often missed by other restaurants.", "Our group of eight all thoroughly enjoyed the food. The Sea Bass special, Lobster and Fillet Steak were voted among the best. The Sancerre and Malbec we choose to accompany the food were beautiful and served at the perfect temperature.", "The band for the evening, Jive Aces, had everyone up on their feet with a lively and brilliantly entertaining performance. There are very few places in London where you can guarantee such good food, wine, service and entertainment all rolled into one.", "Finally, the ambience that has been created in this restaurant is very special. There must of been over 150 guests dining on the night we visited yet it felt like it was a small intimate affair. The decor, careful spacing of tables, lighting, sound and of course staff must all contribute to this success. From the moment you walk through the door to the point you collect your coats, you are made to feel like the only party in the room."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r183533349", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Highly recommended", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "4 November 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your charming review.", "I am delighted you enjoyed the food & service we provided. There are indeed a lot of whiskies to try but also over 200 cigars & an equal number of wines to suit your every need.", "Every night sees a different group of artists take to the stage, so be sure to look on our website for any acts that could be of interest for you.", "Please do drop us a line under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk when you plan on visiting next!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ChrisandPenny", "reviewer_origin": ["Romsey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r183533349-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went to Boisdales restaurant in a party of 8 adults for dinner on Saturday evening, 2nd Dec. Varied menu and the food was excellent as well as being well presented. The staff couldn't have been more pleasant or helpful. The wine list is a delight to choose from as is the whisky menu. I believe there are over 900 whiskies on the menu. Absolute heaven!!", "I am a non-smoker but I thoroughly enjoyed a trip to the cigar room which is well worth a visit. The young man on duty that night gave us an interesting tour and was most pleasant and informative. One might think that a live jazz band performing in a restaurant is a little strange but it made a very enjoyable and memorable evening and their music was such that it added to the evening.", "I would highly recommend this restaurant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r183688608", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great place!", "diner_date": " November 2013", "rating_date": "5 November 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your review.", "I am thrilled you had such an excellent evening and hope to welcome you again in the near future.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Julie G", "reviewer_origin": ["Loughborough, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r183688608-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["What a lovely evening we had recently. Great food, drinks, atmosphere and music. The band was great fun and the meal was delicious. Service was excellent - can thoroughly recommend a visit here, equally good with couples or groups."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r180517348", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Boisdale at Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "10 October 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your great review.", "I am thrilled that you enjoyed our food and jazz plus the fact that you can spend your whole evening with us!", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "martin f", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r180517348-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Excellent food with some great jazz in toe. ", "The prices are fair considering you can have a table all evening without being forced out.", "Superb atmosphere with lots of choices of well known Scottish highland whiskies."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r182064231", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Quality Food & Great Music", "diner_date": " September 2013", "rating_date": "23 October 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your detailed review.", "I am delighted to hear you have enjoyed our cocktails which we pride ourselves on. Luckily for cigar smokers not all cigars set you back as much as our fine vintage selection and quite a few of them are available for single digits. Mondays to Wednesdays our music is designed to accompany your meal and I am delighted you enjoyed her two sets. Annoyed by the poached egg, I was comforted to hear that you enjoyed the rest of your meal with us, especially our Macsween\u2019s Haggis which we roast rather than boil for fuller flavour. When you do find the time for a whisky make sure you ask or wonderful bartenders for a recommendation; they are sure to find one you will love but never tried before!", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon in the not too distant future.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Diana H", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "48"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r182064231-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["After being shown to our premium seats in the Restaurant which were close to the stage, my husband and I made our way down the tartan carpeted stairs to the Oyster Bar. As the bar tender constructed my Jimmy Roosevelt cocktail I found myself distracted by the magnificent crustacea display behind him. The Oyster Bar & Grill offers an extensive menu of shellfish, caviar, steaks, burgers and sandwiches. We sipped our pre dinner drinks seated on the Cigar Terrace overlooking Cabot Square. We don\u2019t smoke, but having peeked into the impressive Cigar shop we almost wished we did! But a 1988 Vintage Cuban Cigar would set you back a smoking \u00a3275.00 \u2013 enough to burn a hole in anyone\u2019s pocket! We returned to our seats in the restaurant upstairs, passing one or two stag\u2019s heads on the way. Live music was provided by a young Cornish singer songwriter, Jessica Sweetman who was obviously inspired by the likes of Stevie Nicks. The waiting staff were attentive, but not intrusive. The food and wine were excellent, although I had a little gripe about my poached egg that was served with the gravadlax. The chef had managed to achieve a runny white with a firm yolk rather than the other way round, clever \u2013 but not very appealing! I was generously offered complimentary desserts in recompense. My main course of Risotto of Broad Beans, Peas and Courgettes was bursting with flavour and colour. My husband had the Mini Roast Macsween Haggis with mashed potatoes and bashed neeps for his starter and the Wester Roast Poached Salmon for main \u2013 both of which were beautifully cooked and presented. We didn\u2019t try anything from the remarkable display of whiskies which range in price from a reasonable \u00a37.00 for a 50ml measure of Famous Grouse to a staggering \u00a3755.50 per 50 ml measure of Glengoyne\u2019s 40 year old malt! Maybe next time.", "In summary, The Boisdale Club is an ideal venue for meeting up with friends in relaxing, yet extravagant surroundings. Enjoy Scottish fare, fit for a Laird! With live music and great service it provides a great evening out."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r180043810", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Sunday Lunch....", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "7 October 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review.", "I was pleased to hear you thought our set menu was great value, however irked that you thought the portions were meagre. I have spoken to our Head Chef and we have increased our portions size slightly and all vegetables are now being topped up through you meal. I hope this will encourage you to return sooner rather than later! Please let us know under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk when you plan to return and we will make sure to say \u201cHello!\u201d", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ncokey", "reviewer_origin": ["Hereford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "241"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "141"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r180043810-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The seats we had were perfect with a view across the wharf. We decided on The \u00a345 sunday special. This was good value based on the red/white wine was included. The down side was the main course. One slice of beef...one and half roasted potatoes per person and 2 small portions of vegetables ( carrots and wilted leaves) between 4 adults! That is my only fault with the experience.... another slice or half a slice of beef and adult size portions of vegetables would have made it perfect and well worth the money", "Staff attentive and friendly...great atmosphere with the live jazz band...excellent wine", "I will return but will make sure Im served some extra vegetables"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r180148323", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "great night out", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "8 October 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "What a lovely review, thank you so much! I am delighted you had a great time and look forward to welcoming you again in the near future.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "joanne j", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "32"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r180148323-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["it was our first visit to this restaurant and would recommend ,we started off with drinks on the terrace before we went upstairs. we had a fantastic table close to the stage and the whole", "experience with the music and a very good meal is not too be missed.", "The staff are all really lovely and the service could not be faulted we would certainly go back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r180299519", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Amazing customer service.", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "9 October 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for sharing you experience with us.", "Although it was not perfect I am delighted that we were able to make amends. We look forward to hearing from you and changing your perspective completely.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mariogws", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r180299519-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Having won a competition with Boisdale. Was unable to attend due to ill health, so my wife and daughter went for the evening. Unfortunately their evening was not the best experience.", "I sent an email complaining about this. As I have been recommending Boisdale restaurant to my clients for a long time. Within a day, I received a very nice and apologetic email from Mr Nathan Evans.", "He dealt with the matter in a very gracious manner. It is refreshing to see customer service dealt with so promptly.", "When I'm fit and well again in the new year. I will definitely go to Boisdale with my wife to give it another go.", "Also to thank Mr Nathan Evans for his professionalism . "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r179934365", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent!", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "6 October 2013", "answer_text": ["MARVELLOUS!!!", "Thank you for your fantastic review. We are all proud to hear that you enjoy your time with us! Please let me know when you are in next; I would love to say Hi!", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "CCHumphryes", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r179934365-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Absolutely first class. Food is among the best I have ever tasted. Venue is amazing & the Bond tribute band that was playing when we were there were absolutely outstanding. Staff among the friendliest I have come across in London & very knowledgable. If your thinking if going - think no more - just go!! This is my new regular treat."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r181051746", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Boring ", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "14 October 2013", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jane V", "reviewer_origin": ["Crayford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "111"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "74"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r181051746-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Oh dear the group were good but it was a boring night. Nowhere to dance. Just sitting at a table listening is not my idea of having fun. Stop cramming the tables in - give us some floor space - Boisedale is a somewhat stuffy old people's diner "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r181725846", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Decent Sunday Lunch", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "20 October 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for taking the time to review us.", "I was annoyed to hear that the restaurant was not fully tidied by the time you had arrived and have already amended the opening procedures for Sunday Lunches to prevent a recurrence. I am however delighted you enjoyed our lunch menu and would like to point out that I have already agreed with the head chef to increase the main course portion size and we are now topping up the vegetables and roast potatoes. Our live jazz on Sundays has been selected to accompany your meal rather than being the focus; unlike our Friday and Saturday shows. We are all proud you though the service was excellent and we hope to welcome you back soon to fully convince you of our venue.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Crazybiker69", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "142"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "70"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r181725846-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went here today with friends for Sunday Lunch. Arrived to find rubbish and bin bags in reception - these were eventually cleaned away. Food was good - 3 course lunch (I had Onion soup, Beef, and a delice desert). Veg was scarce, portions were adequate rather than generous, service excellent and music (jazz) was subdued. Shame. I'd go again - mainly due to the company, although food and setting was very good!."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r181716697", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Six and two threes.", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "20 October 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your detailed review.", "Such comprehensive feedback helps tremendously with staff training. We strive always to be better.", "I was pleased to read you enjoyed the wine, many of which we ship to our bonded warehouse directly from the wine makers. I was disappointed to read that you did not rate our Martini very highly. We pride ourselves on delivering some of the finest classic cocktails, so hearing it did not live up to standards was a let-down, though I would like to mention that we always serve the olives on the side. We have reiterated which glass to be used for which cocktail to prevent a recurrence.", "I have passed your review on to the Head Chef and we have discussed the points mentioned. The Crab/Chili fight is very much a point of preference, though we do err on the side of caution, should yours have been too intense I do apologise sincerely. The fish pie is a new recipe and we have amended it accordingly to ensure it remains succulent and tender, with firm fish. For the side dish I can only apologise as they should be adequately sized and the cabbage seasoned correctly; we should have replaced this no questions asked.", "To finish on a high I was very pleased to read you enjoyed the service and live performance from Leigh, who had his premier on our stage, though I am sure he will return.", "I would be delighted to be able to welcome you back and ask you to contact me under dgm@boisdale-cw.co.uk to discuss your experience in more detail.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Gary H", "reviewer_origin": ["Shrewsbury, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "47"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r181716697-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["An enjoyable night but a couple of points merit mention. Service: spot on; attentive without being sycophantic, food and drinks were delivered in a timely fashion. Entertainment: Leigh Coleman was a gifted singer and musician. His set engaged us from 2130 until 2330 (ish). Drinks: The Chilean Sauvignon Blanc was zesty and certainly palatable (had a couple of bottles). However my Martini was a bit of a let down, wrong glass and olives on the side; perhaps I had been spoilt by the earlier one in The Plateau (now that was a special Martini) and perhaps I should have said something at the time, but did not want to start the evening on a downer. Food: Average at best. The Venison Carpaccio was OK. My wife's Warm Fig and Goats Cheese was well received. Her Chilli Crab Linguine seemed to hit the spot but I get the impression the chilli won the firefight against the crab in the flavour stakes. My Fish Pie was certainly on the well done side if not over-cooked. Ingredients were all there (inc the quails eggs) but expected better at the price. The side of Cabbage and Chorizo was insignificant in quantity and indifferent on quality; the sausage won out against the veg regarding flavour. So - would I go again? Perhaps but probably unlikely. Was it worth what I paid (inc premium(?) seating? - I think not. In a nutshell - good service and some good tunes mitigated an average-at-best dining experience."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r181478563", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Boisdale Visit as recommended by David M Robinson", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "18 October 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you!", "It is such a pleasure to read that we were recommended and that you too thought it was great. I am pleased to hear you thought the service, food and wine were fantastic. We have live music every night from Monday to Saturday and for our new Sunday Lunches too, so make sure to check our website to read all about the upcoming acts.", "I hope to welcome you again soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Hannah P", "reviewer_origin": ["Manchester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r181478563-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I recently visit Boisdale Canary Wharf upon the recommendation of Sandy Madhvani, Showroom manager of David M Robinson. Fantastic service by superb attentive staff, vast tasty wine and food menu, busy atmosphere and an overall fantastic evening. The Live Jazz Singer was the cherry on the icing on the cake! I would highly recommend anyone in the Canary Wharf area to try!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r176995733", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect, just perfect :)", "diner_date": " September 2013", "rating_date": "13 September 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you Aryna for your lovely review,", "I am glad to hear we managed to convince you that British food can be fabulous! We take great pride in our British produce and serve only the finest Scottish seafood. Also, if you are a fan of Sunday Roasts, you should give us a try as we are starting to serve this wonderful tradition from the 29th September onwards!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Aryna_K", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r176995733-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I thought I\u2019m not really a big fan of British food, especially if there are lot of jokes about how bad British cuisine is even here in UK and this is why I\u2019m particular glad to find such a fine dining place like Boisdale of Canary Warf. Might actually become one of my favourite British and Scottish places in this town.", "Full review: http://adventureaspie.com/2013/09/boisdale-of-canary-wharf-london/"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r175441318", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Music, Food, Wine, Whiskey and Service = Happy customer", "diner_date": " August 2013", "rating_date": "3 September 2013", "answer_text": ["I am thrilled that you visit us again and again Stuart, so thank you for taking the time to review us. We are very proud of this restaurant and work very hard to make it one of the prime locations to enjoy a wonderful evening. We already have many great acts booked for the upcoming months so check on our website for a good excuse to have some more steak and another tipple of whisky!", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "StuartRi", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r175441318-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Honestly - I am not sure that I been to a better place for the entire package. The bar staff and knowledge of whiskey was awesome. Steak was soooo good, and the staff attentive without being over the top. Finally the live music. They are top musicians, and the quality shines through. We have been many times, and will be back again. Attend Boisdale with confidence."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r179839435", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Great Steak, Amazing Act...everything else disappointing", "diner_date": " September 2013", "rating_date": "5 October 2013", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "PatrickF164", "reviewer_origin": ["Gran Canaria, Spain"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "53"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "41"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "40", "10", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r179839435-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["So I have reviewed this place 3 times now. 1 bad experience and 1 terrific experience.", "After our last visit which was great we reserved a table on Saturday the 28th and again we were very unhappy with the service and the quality of some of the food. ", "We had problems from when we arrived and right through every course until we left. ", "This was very disappointing particularly as it was my parents 40th wedding anniversary.", "When we arrived we were seated promptly but waited 10 minutes before anyone came to take our drinks order. 3 of our drinks came but we had to request the 4th drink two more times before it finally arrived nearly 25 minutes after we were seated by which time we already had our starters. This was a recurring theme throughout the evening we served our own wine all night and constantly had to find someone to order replacement bottles for us.", "We were served bread which we had to return because it was stale.", "For starters 2 of us ordered the half lobster, the lobster arrived but we had no cutlery. We asked our waitress for it but she never brought it, so we then we had to ask the manager who finally brought it, some 10 minutes after the food arrived by which time it had started to get cold.", "For mains all 4 of us ordered steaks, they were delicious. However, some of the sides arrived cold and had to be sent back only arriving back to our table at the end of our dinner.", "Then for desserts we ordered the petit four, they arrived but of the 8 petit four there were only 2 types (4 of each) and even these were dry. We asked our waitress if this was how it should be served and she was surprised, said no and took them away and replaced them.", "There was also a catalogue of disasters around our table on the evening. One of the waitresses dropped a prawn cocktail beside our table, the other waitress was clearly very annoyed with her and proceeded to get on her knees and scooped the mess up with her hands throwing it into the tray in her temper. This was quite unpleasant and very unprofessional. Then another waitress dropped a tray of drinks right beside us, the mess was cleared up nut no one even acknowledged that we had been splashed when the tray fell.", "There were many disappointed guests that evening.", "For a bill over \u00a3500 the level of service is simply unacceptable.", "We did speak to the duty manager that evening and he agreed that it was a bad night!", "On another note Kim Mayzelle was brilliant!! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r177526813", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Brilliant", "diner_date": " September 2013", "rating_date": "17 September 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Barbara,", "Thank you for reviewing us. I am delighted you enjoyed your visit & especially the food. If you check our website you can find plenty of different music offerings so you may find one that you are more interested in!", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon!", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Barall", "reviewer_origin": ["Kilwinning, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r177526813-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We saved this restaurant until the last night of our week long stay in Canary Wharf and it did not disappoint . The service was great and we had a lovely table at the window , my son had the grouse which he said was delicious and his wife , my husband and I all had fillet steak which was possibly the best I have ever tasted. All the courses were delicious and there was a band playing with a gentleman singing Sinatra type songs we paid \u00a310 per head extra for this we did not mind as we like Sinatra but are not fans of jazz . It was a delightful evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r178752692", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "awful experience staff slow and food tepid and tasteless", "diner_date": " September 2013", "rating_date": "26 September 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "I was so sorry to read about your poor experience at our restaurant last night.", "While it was exceptionally busy it should not have led to such slow service and for that I apologise.", "I was surprised that you disliked the haggis so much, we sell over a metric tonne a month across our three London businesses and it is purchased from Macsweens, often regarded as the best producer of haggis in Scotland. The skin is natural and we have been serving haggis this way for 26 years which is very much the tradition. To date we have only received compliments about our haggis.", "We add a very small amount of carrot to the 'Neeps' to make it clearly different from the 'Tatties' - a great help when the lights go down for the show and when the time of year renders the neeps paler in colour. Other than that ingredients are turnip & swede only, certainly no sweet potato. ", "I would like an opportunity to restore your faith and would be grateful if you could contact me directly on nathan@boisdale.co.uk.", "Your sincerely,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "crapjac", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r178752692-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["slow service. food terrible. had the haggis which was still in skin. \"neeps \" were not what a Scot would call neeps more like sweet potato."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r177674311", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fabulous evening", "diner_date": " September 2013", "rating_date": "18 September 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Anne,", "Thank you very much for your great review. I too enjoyed the Bohemians who played that night. I can\u2019t remember so much energy in the room\u2026 We are all thrilled that you enjoyed the evening with us!", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Anne-Ca1986", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r177674311-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Me and my friends had a really nice time at Boisdale. The food was delicious for a reasonable price, the service was perfect (the waitresses were really friendly and polite). Then we had the chance to enjoy a fabulous \"Tribute to Queen\" show: the singer had the same amazing voice as Freddy Mercury and we had a lot of fun. We'll definitely go again!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r177493628", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great live music venue", "diner_date": " January 2013", "rating_date": "17 September 2013", "answer_text": ["Natalie,", "Thank you for your review, I am delighted to hear that you enjoyed your evening. Did you know that we have a 2-course set menu for lunch & dinner for 19.75GBP? That way we can ensure as many people as possible are able to enjoy an evening with us. Look on our website for more details on our upcoming acts.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "natalie b", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r177493628-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Its all a bit posh in this venue, known for its extensive selection of Whisky's and world class Malts, but a very nice live music venue, expect it to be pricey as those who frequent this establishment can afford it. I was lucky enough to be invited here by the band who were performing and so got a great ftable at the front of the stage. By the end of the evening the whole restaurant was up on thier feet rocking the whole place out.", "Keep an eye out for great bands performing here if you want a very intimate experiance of live music, great food and wine and a thoroughly good night out."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r178840809", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great staff and great live jazz!", "diner_date": " September 2013", "rating_date": "27 September 2013", "answer_text": ["Many thanks for your great review. We are glad that you enjoyed our great mix of steak, whisky and music! Please let me know under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk when you plan on visiting next; I would like to say hello!", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "BizDevRoadee", "reviewer_origin": ["Hood River, Oregon"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "89"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r178840809-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Wonderful Scottish themed restaurant, with live jazz on many nights of the week. We had a reserved table upstairs just as the band started. The huge whiskey bar was amazing! 900+ whiskey to choose from...! I had the prime rib with veggies and chips. Not bad at all! The staff was great, even folding my napkin every time I got up to use the bathroom. No complaints at all. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r178942470", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Best haggis ever, one to recommend.", "diner_date": " September 2013", "rating_date": "28 September 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review and for loving our food. Our live music is variably priced depending on the days of the week and our team is trained to make everyone aware of the charges incurred. That being said, mistakes are made and I apologise should this not have happened on this occasion. As you are planning on returning, please contact me directly under dgm@boisdal-cw.co.uk; I would love to take care of all the details", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Taggs82", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r178942470-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great food and will definitely be coming back. Only one negative was being charged \u00a37.50 each to hear five songs. More information should be given that there is an extra charge. That said it was a great venue, perfect for a date night or a larger group."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r178791839", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Has potential but was let down", "diner_date": " September 2013", "rating_date": "27 September 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review.", "I was disappointed to hear that you did not enjoy the evening thoroughly.", "When you phoned regarding the ambience I can only presume that at the time there were not many bookings. Other than in the main restaurant, the Oyster Bar & Grill is less reservations led and as such many diners merely walk in, this incidentally contributes greatly to the lively atmosphere.", "The too short pints are simply inexcusable, and thankfully the staff rectified this for you. Our hand & thick cut chips have always been received favourably and we always lightly salt them with salt flakes; unsalted chips are readily available upon request.", "It is unfortunate to hear that you were disturbed by the cigar smoke. You are right in saying that our restaurant is non-smoking; however we provide our guests the opportunity to smoke on out heated terraces. Having looked into the matter I have made sure that the doors leading out to the terraces automatically are held close behind traffic.", "We constantly strive to provide our guests the best experience possible, and our staff is prepared to go out of their way to ensure you have an enjoyable evening so I am happy that you found them friendly. Hopefully you will visit us again and are able to change your mind about us.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "FulhamGemini", "reviewer_origin": ["Fulham"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "20", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r178791839-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Review specific to the first floor Oyster Bar and Grill, not the main restaurant.", "When I rang to enquire about the ambience, I was told it was quiet. It turned out to be anything but, and you had to raise your voice to talk. After a tableload of young fogeys occupied the table next door, had to practically shout to talk. ", "Ordered a pint and it was about one-seventh short with over an inch of head. Had to get it topped up (this recurred in the other bar, but when I complained, I wasn't charged). The food was good, though the special thick chips were marred by having salt thrown over them without asking! We decided not to have dessert as cigar smoke was blowing in, presumably from the terrace bar. I thought restaurants were supposed to be non-smoking by law. As suggested on their website, we declined to pay the service charge as we were not happy!", "I don't actually like complaining; Boisdale is a worthwhile music venue with quality d\u00e9cor, the staff have always been pleasant and friendly, and customers looked contented. Those after a noisy night out and who smoke might enjoy it very much; it is a shame that expectations were not met, and I did not look good in the eyes of my companion. If management can fix these lapses there is no reason why it cannot earn 4 or 5 stars."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r173190917", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Wow what a different experience", "diner_date": " August 2013", "rating_date": "20 August 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Patrick,", "Thank you for your second review and also for giving us the chance to redeem ourselves. I am delighted that you had a much better experience and look forward you welcoming you back in the near future. The Soul Jets will be back later in the year, but do check our website for upcoming acts. There are some great bandsin the pipeline.", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "PatrickF164", "reviewer_origin": ["Gran Canaria, Spain"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "53"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "41"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r173190917-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["so if you read through my previous reviews, you will see my last experience of Boisdale Canary Wharf wasnt great! Well the 6 of us returned on Friday the 16th August and it was a terrific night out.", "The food was well presented, everything we ate was delicious, the lobster and steak being particulary good!", "Service was much improved, attentive but not invasive, staff were friendly, helpful and fun!", "The band was Soul Jets, they were brilliant.", "All in all we had a great night and we will definately be going back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r174868402", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What a night!", "diner_date": " August 2013", "rating_date": "30 August 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for reviewing us!", "I also enjoyed the evening immensely with Jordan playing boogie-woogie. He is one of our firm favourite, so I am thrilled that you enjoyed him and his band. Thank you also for commenting on our fabulous staff. We have worked hard to create relaxed but efficient service. Jordan will be playing later in the year so check out our website for further details.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LylaPlum", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "59"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r174868402-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for a meal with friends and to listen to the band on 28 August. A really superb meal , very relaxed in a lovely setting looking out onto Cabot Square through the huge window. Staff were attentive and asked whether we needed any help with the menu which was extensive. The evening was even better when the Jordan Marsh Band came on stage and started their set. They had the whole place rocking with a bluesy, jazzy first set ending with a fantastic rock and roll finale and had everyone up dancing! Can't wait to see them again and will definitely book for a meal next time they are playing there. You can just sit in the bar area and sample their huge range of whiskys, over a thousand to try!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r174655330", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice terrace and seafood", "diner_date": " May 2013", "rating_date": "29 August 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for joining us on a lovely summer evening to enjoy seafood!", "We work hard on ensuring our price points are competitive and I am glad you thought them good value. Our terrace is also great during the winter months when blankets and heaters ensure you are kept warm.", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Shasha189", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "63"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r174655330-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Good atmosphere, price is usual Canary Wharf. I actually thought the Classic fruit de mer seafood platter was a good deal for \u00a330. Terrace is great for the summer and staff was quite attentive."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r174815110", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Good food, good music and plenty of whisky", "diner_date": " August 2013", "rating_date": "30 August 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you Kevin for your review.", "I am delighted you enjoyed the atmosphere in the room. We work hard on ensuring you have a good time when with us; so I am pleased that you had a great time.", "Please visit again soon.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "KevinSmith348", "reviewer_origin": ["Newbury, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r174815110-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The food was good and the place is set out well for either a few drinks after work or a good night out. It was busy but not too much and the jazz was really good. All in all a decent night out."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r174612378", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Top quality food and service with a smile", "diner_date": " August 2013", "rating_date": "29 August 2013", "answer_text": ["What a wonderful and extensive review!", "Thank you for taking the time!", "I am delighted that we were able to accommodate you throughout the evening and I can only say thank you again! I have read out your review to the team during briefings. We all take great pride in what we do; so to hear great feedback is rewarding!", "Please let me know when you plan on joining us next under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk. I would like to thank you personally!", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JCHappyskier", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "56"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r174612378-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I fancied trying this restaurant with its Scottish menu having seen it feature on a round of Masterchef.", "I had expected some difficulty in booking but found they had tables available on the day (a Wednesday) at any time from 6 through to 9 at half hour intervals. I booked through Top Table which secured a special offer of 25% off all food purchased which was an unexpected bonus.", "On arrival, I realised that through a misunderstanding we had been booked into the Oyster Bar and Grill rather than the restaurant. The table was on a balcony overlooking Cabot Square but not in prime location and there was cigarette smoke wafting around from somewhere. It would have been OK but I thought I would ask if there might still be space in the restaurant proper upstairs. The staff were great, confirmed that we could move and also offered a choice of staying with the menu that had the 25% discount or 'upgrading' to full al la carte. I opted for the latter.", "The new table was right next to the window overlooking the fountains in Cabot Square and perfectly placed to watch the sun go down. Dining at 6.30 secured a quiet restaurant and plenty of attentive staff. As the evening unfolded the tables filled and noise levels increased to create more of a buzz. This was augmented by the live band that commenced at 8pm; sensible volume, easy to hear but not loud enough to destroy conversation.", "The menu was extensive and for the first time in a long time we really struggled to choose. EW both opted for fish/shellfish starters and tucked into some excellent oysters, crab and smoked salmon. For mains the Steaks ( and in particular the special 1kg on the bone for 2) looked amazing but we chose another special, Grouse which was deliciously gamey and smokey and a rib eye burger with truffle mayo which was accompanied by a pot of absolutely perfect chips. We did not order any sides and on reflection perhaps a serving of vegetable or salad would have been even better but that said, the portions were generous and we were certainly comfortably full.", "We had no room for desserts but did split a plate of 5 cheeses from an extensive british cheese board.", "The wine list is substantial (as is the choice of whiskies all lit up like Christmas at the bar - there must be 600 or so). There are some big prices and so we opted to stick with the range listed under Boisdale housewines. An excellent glass of Albarino was around \u00a310 and then a very smooth and fruity bottle of red burgundy \u00a360.", "As the restaurant filled the service was inevitably a little less attentive but it was not difficult to catch an eye of someone and then they were immediately there and very happy to help.", "I think there is an expectation that guests will stay on after dinner and enjoy the live music and I sense that unless there is a pressure for tables, the staff are happy to let diners relax at the table long after the meal is over.", "A final nice touch; we ordered a plate of 5 cheeses but the waiter added a sixth because he was keen we should try it. A little later when he noticed our cheese was gone but a cracker or two remained, he then offered to give us some more cheese to use up the crackers!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r173759364", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic experience", "diner_date": " August 2013", "rating_date": "24 August 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your review!", "You described the atmosphere at the bar perfectly so I hope to welcome you back soon; perhaps to try some of our fabulous dry aged British beef!", "Let me know when you are in next under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk. I would love to say \u2018Hello\u2019.", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Bcbob1969", "reviewer_origin": ["Birmingham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "110"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "60"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r173759364-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Loved this place. In a great location over looking Cabot Square. Went there after a lovely meal at Gaucho's, Sat in the Whisky bar listening to live Jazz music sipping a couple of whisky's from the thousands they have on sale! Great place to sit back, relax and let the world pass you by!", "Couple aged 40-45"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r175314426", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A top evening at Boisdale", "diner_date": " August 2013", "rating_date": "2 September 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Hugh,", "Thank you for your review and for listening to your colleague! To hear that guests recommend us makes me very proud indeed. I am delighted that you had a great evening and you enjoyed the steak as well as the treatment from the team.", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon, and please do drop me a line under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk when you do, so I can thank you in person.", "Kind regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Hugh S", "reviewer_origin": ["Ryde, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r175314426-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked Boisdale Canary Wharf based on a conversation at work with a college, who insisted I check out a restaurant he has visited on several occasions with quality food and great live music.", "I was in town recently and booked Boisdale's for a few friends to get together all of which love their food & music. We arrived and took the lift to the inviting entrance lobby and were greeted by a courteous deputy manager who escorted us to the bar before we sat at our table.", "The surroundings are impressive to say the least the spacious room accommodates a long well stocked bar with an enviable selection of whiskey which is its trademark tipple, The far end sits the stage and to the left the full length windows offer a view over Cabots Square.", "The food is based on Scottish cuisine with a wide selection of steaks, everyone in my party had a great meal and a great time. It should definitely be one everyone's 'go to' list and I guarantee you'll want to go back again and again.", "The live music complemented the evening, the staff were attentive but not overbearing and the evening is one I hope to repeat again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r175086287", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great date night", "diner_date": " August 2013", "rating_date": "1 September 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your detailed review.", "I am glad you hear that you had a good date and you enjoyed our service. We are very proud of the produce we offer so we were delighted you enjoyed the steak tartar and lobster. With regards to the steak I can only assume it was a one off as we have very generous portions and we receive huge amount of positive feedback from guests that love our steaks. Next time you could ask for the guest steak of the day where we present only the very finest dry aged Scottish beef.", "Still I am very happy that you had a good night and I look forward to welcoming you back in the very near future.", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Everlong08", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "76"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "58"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r175086287-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We recently moved to the area and had a flyer put through the letter box for a 50% of food at Boisdale throughout the month of July - August, it would have been silly not to take advantage.", "So last Thursday - date night. I had booked a table a week or so in advance and requested a window table. We were informed that there will be live music from 9pm in the restaurant and there would be charged \u00a34.50 per person for table cover charge. Not a problem.", "Upon arriving at the restaurant they promptly found our reservation and the lady commented on how nice I looked - thumbs up! She took us to a table in the middle of the restaurant and I mentioned that I had requested a window table. She went off to check whether they were available, came back in a jiffy and hey presto! A window table! It was looking over Cabot Square and candlelit (well, it was date night!).", "The restaurant it self is Scottish and had a Gentleman's club feel about it (not in a stripper way - but cigars and whiskey), lovely tables and comfortable chairs. Amazing art and black and white photography. ", "They have a great wine list with a good range of wines and champagnes by the glass at reasonable prices. A glass of 2003 Dom Perignon was \u00a321..now I know where to go and treat myself in the future! ", "I had steak tartare to start, which was prepared at the table to your taste. It was delicious, fresh and clean cut - and my glass of Malbec was perfect for it. My boyfriend ordered half a lobster to start which looked amazing - which it was, as I had a whole one for my main - along with a glass of Albarino - yummy. Boyfriend had the fillet steak on the bone with thick out chips and a side of roast garlic mushrooms with crispy shallots. The steak was okay but there was too much bone to meat ratio for his liking and he preferred Gaucho steak. The mushrooms were divine! I could have eaten more!", "We finished the meal with a 10 cheese platter from the trolley - the waiter explained all the different cheeses and recommended some very good stinkies and a glass of Vinsanto to go with the cheese. ", "We had a great evening. The restaurant is lovely, good atmosphere, a great range of food on the menu, wonderful wine list and very attentive staff that were not intrusive. The live music was very good too.", "Downstairs there is a terrace bar and cigar room - we had a quick walk through and will pay a visit shortly.", "For 3 courses, glass of champagne, 3 glasses of wine and 2 desert wine and water it came to \u00a3168 including service and cover charge. This obviously would have been doubled if we didn't have the 50% off food discount. Which would have made it rather pricey - but if you wanted to treat yourself to some lovely food, wine and music...you can't go wrong. I'm already looking for my next excuse to go back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r175229884", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "A bit confusing", "diner_date": " August 2013", "rating_date": "2 September 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Sue,", "I was delighted to hear that your were impressed by the venue and thought the food very good and service impeccable, I'm only sorry that you found Boisdale Canary Wharf confusing.", "To clarify, we are a British restaurant dedicated to live music. Which is why I was so surprised that you gave such a low mark on tripadvisor - a restaurant review site. You will see that Ronnie's has its listing in nightlife not in restaurants.", "Unlike Ronnie Scott's we don't see selling tickets as a revenue stream and of course we don't have the benefit of two shows on a Friday & Saturday night. Our tickets sales do not cover the costs associated with the band, sound engineers or band hospitality and are on average 30% less expensive than Ronnie Scott's.", "What we actively encourage is our guests to have a good time and dancing is encouraged in the second set. ", "Please don't be disappointed or believe it to be disrespectful to the band to allow conversation during the music. The artists are both made away in advance and all very much enjoy playing at Boisdale because of the relaxed nature of the venue. The band are very well looked after and we have an exemplary record which is well known among musicians.", "The practise of sitting in rows, in silence listening to music is a relatively new phenomenon and not one we subscribe to, but we hope to welcome you back for dinner very soon.", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sue2000000", "reviewer_origin": ["Newport, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "154"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "70"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r175229884-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["As big fans of Ronnie Scotts (which we inevitably compared this to), we found our first visit to Boisdale a bit confusing. On the positive, the venue is impressive - well laid out, etc., the food was very good, wine/drinks list amazing and the staff service was impeccable. We were shown to a great table right at the front. However, we found the dance floor in front of the stage confusing, especially as it may have meant paying for premium seating only to have a bunch of folk 'dad dancing' right in front of your view of the band (luckily we were on the side so were not really affected but if we had been seated a few tables across, this would not have been good). Being used to Ronnie's, we found the amount and volume of chatter from diners as the band drew breath to move on to their next song rather disrespectful and disappointing. Worse, the band (who were clearly a group of very talented musicians) seemed to change their set as they went along to reflect what people who were in that night were dancing to. By the time we'd got to \"Tequila\" and \"Don't Mess With My Toot Toots,\" we felt like we were at a hideous wedding and were ready to leave. So .... we left somewhat disappointed and rather confused about what Boisdale, Canary Wharf really is."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r175304915", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "bad beegee music", "diner_date": " August 2013", "rating_date": "2 September 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Mazip,", "I was sorry to read of your disappointment with the BeeGees show that we hosted on 31st August. We had good feedback from other guests so would point out that it was not a view shared,", "On the subject of ticket prices, I would argue that \u00a310 is a very small sum to pay for a live band.", "I was taken aback at your suggestion that the cocktails had anything less than the advertised volume of spirits in them. We have won a number of awards for our cocktail list and for the bartenders that mix them. It is widely regarded that great cocktails should not be dominated by any one component part conversely poorly made ones often taste of the spirit base.", "What was absent from your review was anything about the food, but then you were only here for drinks.", "NJE"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mazip", "reviewer_origin": ["welling"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "142"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "107"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "20", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r175304915-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["my friend came over from martinique and she wanted to go to the boisdale as she has heard it is very good , well we were so disapointed they had beegees on they could not sing the group were awful so out of tune in fact we had beegees at our local working mans club and they sounded so much better than the boisdale and it was free at the working mans club unlike where the boisdale charge \u00a310 per head and the drinks were extortionate the cocktails started at \u00a39.50 and you could not taste any spirits in then at all"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r170750850", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Immense", "diner_date": " July 2013", "rating_date": "4 August 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your fantastic review!", "I am delighted that you enjoyed your evening with us and look to welcoming you again in the near future.", "Kind regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "FizzyB", "reviewer_origin": ["Hopwood, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r170750850-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Faultless and incredibly enjoyable. Live jazz with amazing seafood. Staff were great, best smoked salmon ive had in years, excellent views of the wharf, MUST TRY"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r171189581", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Delicious but pricey", "diner_date": " August 2013", "rating_date": "7 August 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for your review. I am pleased you enjoyed the food and service you have received. We work hard to offer high quality ingredients as well as excellent value. Any additional feedback regarding price points would be gratefully received. Please contact me directly under dgm@boisdale-cw.co.uk should you wish to explain in more detail.", "I look forward to hearing from you soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "CaroJane", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r171189581-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I visited Boisdale (very) early evening. The service was attentive but not over-bearing and the main course delicious. Dessert (ice cream) a bit ordinary and mysteriously the coffee appeared long before dessert. Overall nice food but over priced. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r168681296", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Atmosphere and Fantastic Food", "diner_date": " August 2012", "rating_date": "23 July 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for such a lovely review.", "I am glad you enjoyed the food, drink and atmosphere. While we have items on the menu that are certainly dearer, we also have an excellent value two course menu for \u00a319.75 available for lunch and dinner as well as several wines under \u00a325.00. ", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon!", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "eurobeni", "reviewer_origin": ["Geneva, Switzerland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r168681296-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This is a Scottish themed Seafood restuarant with a Jazz Cafe feel. I have to say that the food is of a high standard and good service. It's not cheap but the quality is definitely there. They have a good wine list as well. If you don't want to eat in the restaurant then there is a wet bar serving oysters and other shellfish which was very busy on the night we were there. I will definitely go back again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r169757131", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Something to sing about in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " July 2013", "rating_date": "29 July 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your in detail review.", "I am delighted to hear that the team looked after you so well on the evening and that the entertainment was to your liking. Disappointed that the batter was not up to scratch our Head Chef has amended the recipe slightly to ensure crispness all around. I was also pleased to hear you found our cheese trolley offer excellent, we certainly have enjoyed presenting the cheeses since we have had our trolley delivered. When you plan on visiting next, please let us know under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk and we will make sure to say \u2018Hello!\u2019", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "SuffolkYorki", "reviewer_origin": ["Suffolk"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r169757131-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Although London was heaving with tourists the restaurant was not busy, but this is not too surprising as it is slightly off the usual tourist route. We booked our table probably a bit too early (7.00) but staff were happy for us to order cocktails and eat slightly later. There is a charge per person to book a table which in effect is the cost of your entertainment. At \u00a340 for the best table/seats this is reasonable by London standards for a class act. We were entertained by the Callum big band - some wonderful musicians playing great arrangements of Rhapsody in Blue and West Side story. The cocktail menu is a little heavy on the ginger for me but suited the others on the table - they were strong, yummy and under \u00a310 each. Continuing on the alcohol theme - there are some surprising finds on the wine list, featuring wines from small vineyards like \"little Beauty\" a Gewurtztraminer from New Zealand managing to be sweet and yet dry at the same time and just bursting with flavour. A red wine from the Lebanon was a good contrast with a noise giving hints of cigar (quite appropriate for a venue with a whiskey/cigar theme). There are plenty of staff buzzing around creating a busy atmosphere - it's always good to see a happy rapport between staff as well as towards their customers. Service is efficient - staff happily topping up your water glass (with tap as well as bottled water as requested) without being asked. Food wasn't wow factor for me, but it was good - the scallops and black pudding were fine, the turbot in a homemade batter, whilst crispy on the top was soggy and fatty underneath - but the fish inside was lovely. The fillet steak was cooked very well, and couldn't be faulted. Thanks to the lovely waiter who served cheese to one member of our table (putting up with comments from the rest of us) - he knew his stuff. The cheeses were exciting and generous portions - there was enough for 3 of us to \"taste\" each of the five selected and still some left for the person who actually ordered it. All in all, its a great venue for a good night out."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r173030113", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great night out with dinner, live music and wine!", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "19 August 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your review. ", "I am delighted that you have enjoyed your evening with us. I have taken note of your suggestion regarding our service. We work hard to provide you the best possible service and will always try to be better next time. I hope to welcome you back in the near future so you can convince yourself of our efforts.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Paula H", "reviewer_origin": ["Glasgow, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "194"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "81"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r173030113-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale's has a great selection of wine and spirits (particularly whisky). The menu is Scottish and very well cooked (seafood, fish and steaks). I like the rib eye with pepper sauce and buttered spinach. Sometimes service could be sharper, but the staff are very friendly. There is a great bar downstairs and a cigar bar for those inclined."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r170291244", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellence on a plate with whisky on the side", "diner_date": " July 2013", "rating_date": "1 August 2013", "answer_text": ["Joanna,", "Thank you for your review. I am pleased to hear you enjoyed the food, wine & whiskies. I hope you did not have too much trouble picking one of the many tipples. For the days that aren\u2019t filled with sunshine we do have heaters on the terraces to keep you warm!", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon!", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Joanna M", "reviewer_origin": ["London, England, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "111"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "46"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r170291244-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Wow this is a fantastic restaurant - mouth watering scallops and wonderful steak. Well informed staff and great house champagne and wine. Over 1000 malt whiskeys and a stage for the evening entertainment/ Can't wait to go back again. The terrace looks great but on a better day."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r169474536", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "All that Jazz", "diner_date": " July 2013", "rating_date": "28 July 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for your lovely review. Upset that the Turbot Fish & Chips was not up to standard, I have spoken to our Executive Head Chef to prevent recurrence; I was delighted to hear that your thoroughly enjoyed the remainder of your evening. Please contact me directly under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk when you plan on visiting next and we will make sure to say hello!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "RoutemasterCB", "reviewer_origin": ["Cambridge, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "449"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "334"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r169474536-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were greeted with a warm welcome from reception staff on arrival, which was to be a strong theme for the night. Shown to our table and whilst we looked over the menus, we ordered cocktails from the extensive drinks list. ", "Starters were excellent scallops with black pudding and apple pur\u00e9e (2), mackerel pot and smoked salmon. All were superb. ", "Mains were turbot fish and chips (2) let down a little by the soggy batter, broad bean risotto and the most perfectly cooked medium rare fillet steak. ", "Excellent wine list, we went for the New Zealand Gewurtztraminer (little beauty - that's the name of the vineyard), followed by Massaya Silver Selection 2007 from the Bekka Valley, Lebanon and a lighter Paritua Pinot Noir 2008 from Central Otago, New Zealand. ", "Absolutely stuffed, we settled down the the music - an ensemble of 18 talented musicians all in their early 20's - the Callum Au big band. They played music from Rhapsody in blue for the first half and West Side Story in the second. ", "During the interval, almost two hours after our dinner, we ordered deserts which was no problem for the team at Boisdale. A creme caramel was soon served, with a great cheese plate, some fantastic cheeses on offer and fully explained by the head waiter. ", "Overall a great night and something we will be doing again shortly!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r172163991", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Very nice indeed", "diner_date": " July 2013", "rating_date": "14 August 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for your very kind review and a belated \u201cHappy Birthday!\u201d I am delighted that you enjoyed our Scottish beef & lobster as well as the service. Next time you could go for a steak and add half a lobster to avoid any food envy\u2026", "I look forward to receiving you again in the near future.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Clare M", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "41"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r172163991-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I was taken to Boisdale for a birthday lunch with work colleagues. We received an attentive service, but not pushy. The guys opted for steaks naturally, which looked and tasted amazing. I opted for the lobster club which was good but I must admit I had food envy as the steaks were delicious! A little pricy but very nice nevertheless, would make a return visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r171274244", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "No messing solid 4", "diner_date": " May 2013", "rating_date": "8 August 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Mark,", "Thank you for your review. I am pleased that you enjoyed the view, the atmosphere & the food.", "Should you plan on visiting soon, please drop us a line under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk and we will make sure to say hello!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Mark P", "reviewer_origin": ["Hemel Hempstead, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r171274244-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["It has a great view overlooking cabot sq. Full of the usual canary wharf suits. However the staff are pretty good and know their stuff. ", "We tried a sample of the fish selection and frankly it wasn't half bad, not that anywhere in the east end should have a bad selection of fish. ", "Great views, good ambience for a city place, slightly pricey but to be expected."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r172353361", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good but let down by flies", "diner_date": " August 2013", "rating_date": "15 August 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for taking the time to write your review.", "I am pleased that you enjoyed the service and food; however was vexed by your comment regarding flies in the restaurant. We take every precaution to prevent such a problem & have rigorous cleaning procedures in place. As a result we have been awarded 5 out of 5 in the Food Standards Agency rating for food hygiene 3 years running. This year we are challenged. We are open from 11am to midnight and as we have had a fantastic summer with the temperatures soaring the doors to our terraces on the first floor are open all throughout this period. Coupled with the Thames being close by this generates high humidity & provides flies ideal conditions to thrive in. We are working very closely with our pest control contractor to minimise the impact and using all methods available to food premises.", "Should you wish to discuss in further detail please do not hesitate to contact me under dgm@boisdale-cw.co.uk. I look forward to hearing from you.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Steven S", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "100"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "89"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r172353361-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Good venue, good service, good food, a bit pricey but this is Canary Wharf. Would have got 4 stars but let down by the endless flies that exist in the restaurant, fly around you, your table, your food, sat on the cheese board. Disgusting. Needs to be sorted."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r166882564", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Ronnie who..?", "diner_date": " July 2013", "rating_date": "9 July 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your rather lovely review.", "I am delighted you consider us to be a right venue for so many purposes; a feat that we constantly strive to achieve. Thank you so much for taking the time to write. I look forward to welcoming you again very soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Lunchdawg", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r166882564-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Excellent food, the most amazing whisky selection I have ever seen in one venue, wonderfully well kept cigars and a heated terrace on which to smoke them, friendly and attentive service and second to none entertainment. Why on earth would anyone want to go to Ronnies anymore? Boisdale covers all bases. Perfect venue for a romantic dinner in the main restaurant upstairs, business lunches downstairs with a lovingly mixed cocktail. Really 5 star."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r166173338", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Nice, but not outstanding", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "3 July 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "Thank you very much for taking the time to voice your opinion. I am saddened to hear that the team in Canary Wharf did not meet your expectations on this occasion. I would love to hear about your evening with a little more detail and would appreciate if you could contact me directly under dgm@boisdale-cw.co.uk", "I look forward to hearing from you soon.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "anna k", "reviewer_origin": ["Moscow, Russia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "47"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "32"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "20", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r166173338-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We have being in the Canary Wharf place, party of 14, having a set dinner menu. On the positive side - food was reasonably good, trendy decorated place, doesn't feel overcrowded while being absolutely full, very convenient location for the evening drinks and dinner after meetings in Canary Wharf.", "From the minuses - wine was poor ( probably just not the place specialization), very-very slow service ( we deliberately choose dinner set option for the sake of time, but it still took ages to serve), potions sizes are closer to Michelin star restaurants, that to Scottish ones. ", "Overall - nice place, but probably will not go next time, unless the location on Canary Wharf is key choice factor."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r166995908", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Boisdale Jazz, Whiskey, Cigars and superb food", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "10 July 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Graham,", "Your review is very kind and I appreciate you taking the time to write. We are always delighted to hear guests enjoying the venue as much as we do. I look forward to welcoming you again in the very near future.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "GrahamB123", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r166995908-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale canary Wharf is a a piece of new york in London. Incredible atmosphere, great jazz and worth more than one visit. Thoroughly recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r168155550", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great service, fantastic cocktails and whiskeys!", "diner_date": " July 2013", "rating_date": "19 July 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Anthony,", "Thank you very much for your great review. I\u2019m delighted that Erin & Jon looked after you so well. I have read your review out loud in our briefing and the two were able to collect a prize, customary when staff is mentioned in despatches. We look forward to welcoming you and your friends again soon!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Anthony G", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r168155550-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A few friends and I visited Boisdale on a Thursday evening recently and we were all pleasantly surprised by the service especially considering how busy it was. ", "We were served at the bar by Erin who went out of her way to make us extremely time consuming cocktails all the while recommending delicious bar bites to keep us sober. ", "Her margaritas were the perfect summer drink and the burgers she recommended were fantastic!", "After that we started on the whiskeys and after considering the unsparing list thought it was best to seek advice from John, another of the bartenders. His advice was spot on and his recommendations topped of a brilliant night out at Boisdale. ", "Will certainly be recommending this place to friends and colleagues.", "Anthony Gerard"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r166457380", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent service and entertainment", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "5 July 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for taking the time to write your review. ", "You will be pleased to know that there have been some changes to the menu and while we have kept the set menu at an excellent price point of \u00a319.75 we have also added more dishes to our a la carte menu at great value. I hope this can entice you to join us again and would love you to let us know under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk if you do.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "sunshine809", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r166457380-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Go there to experience. Lovely evening for me and my boyfriend. We went for the set menu because we couldn't afford it otherwise, but the food was still amazing!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r165568571", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best night out in London", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "28 June 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Jackie,", "thank you for joining us testing nearly everything that we have to offer. I cannot agree more when you say that the room feels cosy albeit it being quite large. Andy Rose, our Executive Chef, is also thrilled you enjoyed the rib of beef as well as the haggis. I hope your feet did not hurt to much from dancing and look forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JackieE279", "reviewer_origin": ["Brasted, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r165568571-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had an amazing night in this restaurant. There is a great buzz from the champagne bar as you arrive and we were lucky enough to get a seat out on the terrace. The service is friendly and knowledgeable. Had a great champagne cocktail. Then upstairs for dinner alongside the biggest whisky in Europe. The dining area is dark red and tartan and very cosy for a large room. Had the haggis to start with a nip of whisky - delicious. I had beautiful fresh fish whilst my dining companions tucked into the biggest rib of steak I've ever seen. No room for pud which was a good thing because once the music started we were all up dancing! Best night out ever!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r165561803", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Probably the best in London", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "28 June 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Keith,", "Thank you for your beautiful review. I am especially proud that you see us as being your preferred venue in London. The team here have worked hard & with dedication to provide excellent service. A statement like yours makes all the work pay off. I cannot wait to welcome you again to our venue and thank you in person.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "KeithE694", "reviewer_origin": ["Westerham"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r165561803-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I am a regular user of Boisdale. Originally the Belgravia venue, but now more often than not Canary wharf. In my view this simply the best restaurant in London, with the most attentive staff. To be able to create such a warm personable atmosphere on this scale is an incredible achievement. The steaks are incredible, there is a fabulous wine selection to suit most budgets (the Boisdale claret is excellent value) the largest whisky selection on the planet and a cigar selection to die for. If that's not enough, throw in live music just about every night, Whats not to like!! always check out the \"beast of the day\" or Guest steak."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r167161896", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Gourmet burger!!!", "diner_date": " July 2013", "rating_date": "11 July 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you Chloe for your review.", "I am glad that you came in and enjoyed one of our great burgers & that you had the chance to enjoy the terrace at its best! We are looking forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Chloe C", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r167161896-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Dined here last night, as a quick random meal. I must say I was very impressed with my gourmet burger, cooked to perfection! Would definitely dine again. Service was also very good. Sat out on the terrace just before 6pm when it started to get busy, however great atmosphere."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r167010411", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "excellent service and great experience", "diner_date": " July 2013", "rating_date": "10 July 2013", "answer_text": ["Sandy,", "Thank you very much for taking the time to write such an endearing review after your visit. We are incredibly proud when we receive such lovely feedback from our neighbours and look forward to welcoming you again soon on our doorstep.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "sandy m m", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r167010411-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Wanting to have a team outing in Canary wharf I took my team to Boisdale.The service was outstanding and the food was mouth watering...We enjoyed chilled drinks and cigars. It makes me feel happy to have this worldclass experience at my door step and I would recommend them with pride. Thank you from Mr Sandy Madhvani Showroom Manager at David M Robinson Jubilee Place Canary Wharf."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r167976337", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Summer in Havana", "diner_date": " July 2013", "rating_date": "17 July 2013", "answer_text": ["Chris, ", "Thank you for your review and for trusting us with your clients. I am delighted that you enjoyed so many aspects of our business. We are proud that you think so highly of us. When you plan on visiting again, do drop us an email under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk; we would love to say hello.", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Chris O", "reviewer_origin": ["Horley, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r167976337-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great way to entertain clients! Fantastic attentive service coupled with a knowledge and range of cigars rarely encountered in the UK. ", "My clients were able to enjoy gourmet burgers, excellent wine choice, and then able to retire out to the balcony and enjoy a London summers evening with cigars, and the extraordinarily moreish spicy scotch quail's eggs. Us Londoners are incredibly lucky to have a truly world class venue on our doorstep. ", "Thanks to all the team - we'll definitely be back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r163959835", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "beautiful decor, average food", "diner_date": " May 2013", "rating_date": "14 June 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Nic,", "thank you for taking the time to review us. I am very sorry to hear that on this occasion we did not live up to your standards. I would be very grateful if you would contact me directly under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk to discuss your review in more detail to prevent a future recurrence. ", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Nic E", "reviewer_origin": ["Hornchurch, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r163959835-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My friends and I visited boisdale on a Tuesday evening and were initally pleased with the service. We ordered from a set menu and i was diappointed with the food. Although presented well, the taste of the meat was not up to the standard I had expected. The service was mostly good, although not very friendly. Maybe a better choice of restaurant for a date. lovely outdoor seating in the bar overlooking canary wharf."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r164338314", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A great place", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "18 June 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for such a lovely review. I am delighted that you enjoyed your food thoroughly and managed to squeeze in some desserts. While annoyed by the fact that your first choice whisky was out of stock, what are the chances given that we have over 700 varieties? I was happy to hear the team made their amends. I look forward to welcoming you again in the near future.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "cdwc", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "150"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "57"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r164338314-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The mixed reviews of Boisdale made us a bit apprehensive but we still had to give it a try. ", "We went as a group of four on a Monday night. Music was fantastic, as expected, whilst dining experience was also great, much to our relief. ", "Some of the starters ordered were Parma ham and Gravad Lax. Our mains included the truffle burgers, haggis and rump steak. It's true, you can only choose your burger to be cooked medium well or well, but their medium well is more like medium in other places; still pink on the inside. ", "Everyone was full after starters and mains but we managed to kindly convinced ourselves to have dessert. All of which made all of us smile with satisfaction. The special dessert raspberry jelly, sticky toffee pudding, creme caramel and a cheese course. ", "In absence of Marlborough Savignon Blanc, we had their Boisdale French one which was quite nice. We wanted to have a petticoat type of whiskey to finish the meal but it was out of stock. To make up got our disappointment, we were given an alternative as a compliment which was a really nice touch. ", "Great music, good food, drinks and fantastic service. So, would we come back? Oh yes!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r165478620", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Very fine steaks, ideal for business dinner at Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "27 June 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you Hector for your great review and for returning to Boisdale of Canary Wharf to dine in a Private Room with dedicated waiter. If you love our signature steaks, you should join us from the 29th September 2013 onwards when we will start to open Sundays for Sunday Roasts. That way you can enjoy our great grass fed dry aged beef with Yorkshire puddings and goose fat roast Potatoes. I hope to welcome you then or on any other occasion.", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Hector18", "reviewer_origin": ["Shanghai, China"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "49"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r165478620-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This is my second time to eat here with a small group of colleagues/guests in a small private room overlooking Cabot Square. Excellent service, good wines, sound menu -- the best choice being one of their signature steaks!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r164393636", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "fantastic", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "18 June 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Linda,", "Thank you for your short but lovely review. I am delighted to hear that we have on several occasions been able to meet your expectations. With regards to our service charge; an industry standard 12.5% is divided wholly amongst the team. As you state it is optional and should you be dissatisfied will be removed from your bill.", "Kindly let us know when you plan to visit next under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk and we will make sure to say hello.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lindap666", "reviewer_origin": ["Colchester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r164393636-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We have been before and we are never disappointed. great food,great music and lovely atmosphere! there is a high service charge but it is optional."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r163521848", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great Food, Terrible Terrible Service!", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "10 June 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Patrick,", "Thank you for taking time to review our Canary Wharf restaurant.", "I am very sorry that on this occasion the service fell so short of expectations.", "I would like and opportunity to restore your faith and would be very grateful if you could contact me directly on Nathan@boisdale.co.uk so we can discuss your complaint in more detail. ", "Yours sincerely,", "Nathan Evans", "Deputy Managing Director"], "reviewer_pseudo": "PatrickF164", "reviewer_origin": ["Gran Canaria, Spain"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "53"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "41"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r163521848-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went this weekend to Frank Sinatra night, great atmosphere and brilliant setting.", "There is a great and varied menu, all of food was well presented and everything we ate was delicious.", "However, service was poor and not what you'd expect in a place where your paying \u00a330-\u00a340 for a main course (plus sides) Our waitress was unfriendly and unhelpful. There were 6 of us and 5 main courses came together the 6th arrived 20 minutes after everyone elses just as the rest of us were all finishing. We had to order fresh sides as the they were all cold by the time the 6th meal arrived. No engagement from the staff or Managemet on this we had to keep chasing and we were told it was coming. Then the staff just avoided our table. Real Shame but I'd recommend avoiding the restaurant. Service really ruined our evening!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r163447652", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Faultless Boisdale", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "9 June 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear 'Bizzyboy1960' ", "Thank you so much for taking time to write such a comprehensive and complimentary review, for which we are very grateful.", "We are delighted that your chose to spend a milestone birthday for your wife with us & thrilled that you & your guests had a wonderful time.", "I have shared your feedback with the team and have presented Gintare with her Boisdale Champagne (Something we do, when specific team members get mentioned in despatches!)", "Our executive Head Chef - Andy Rose, has passed on your positive feedback regarding the food to the team at Canary Wharf, who were beaming....", "I do hope we will be welcoming you back very soon. Please drop me an email ahead of the next visit to Nathan@boisdale.co.uk, I would like to thank you in person.", "Yours sincerely,", "Nathan Evans"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Bizzyboy1960", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "159"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "52"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r163447652-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I wanted a good location for my wife's 60th birthday and stumbled across Boisedale on the internet and decided to give it a site recki.", "From the point I entered the venue I knew it was perfect. After discussing my requirements with Gintare, who was very informative and helpful in assisting me selecting the most appropriate table for our needs. A cup of coffee was offered and produced while I made my final decisions.", "Although a Scottish themed venue it doesn\u2019t smack you in the face, just the tartan carpet, furnishings and waiting staff attire accent the homeland, the jazz connection is more apparent from the pictures adorned on the wall.", "We arrived to a complimentary glass of champagne in honour of my wife\u2019s birthday - nice touch.", "The menu and wine list is the type that you can have a reasonably priced meal and drink or you can go to town.", "We ordered a selection of starters - steak tartare (expertly mixed at the table to the correct degree of piquanteness), smoked salmon was thickly cut and served with a soft poached egg and delicate leaves - nice change from the flat thin slices covering the plate, cesaer salad and nice looking prawn cocktail with good tasting plump prawns.", "Our main courses ranged from a well flavoured grilled lobster, a manly sized steak and kidney pudding, a huge rib eye steak, a chunky rump steak, a good golden hockey puck shaped Cod and Haddock fishcake- tasty and chunky texture, a grilled dover sole. The vegetable accompaniments are good and interesting not just your boring green beans - we had Hispi cabbage, chorizo sausage & caraway, Steamed Broccoli, Lemon& Toasted Linseeds and Leaf Spinach, Simply Wilted or Creamed with Black Truffle.", "For dessert we had a couple rhubarb and apple nut crumbles (my wife\u2019s dessert plate had Happy Birthday piped in chocolate on it), a selection of cheese\u2019s from a huge cheese offering served with pera slices and honey.", "I had brought a Choccywockydoodaa cake with us with two numeral sparkles. The waiters tactfully brought the cake from the kitchen and light the sparklers close to the table but shielded from my wife to conceal the surprise.", "One of my guests said \"this has been faultless tonight\", and he was right. As a package, from the first meeting, to the champagne reception, the meal, the Jazz music the staff were totally professional, very attentive without being intrusive which all went to make an excellent celebratory evening.", "So whether a business meal, pre-theatre dine or a celebratory dinner I warming recommend it. The management should be very proud of their team.", "To access the restaurant by car its best to go to Cabot car park in Canary Wharf and take the lift directly to the 2nd floor restaurant. If you are not too bothered about the music artist choose a table furthest from the stage as it can be a tad loud."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r163298921", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Birthday dinner", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "7 June 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Lisa,", "We are delighted that you enjoyed your visit to Boisdale Canary Wharf.", "Check out our website for even more great bands to dance to & drop us an email ahead of your next visit so we can be sure to say hello.", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lisa m", "reviewer_origin": ["london"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r163298921-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I was taken to boisedale by friends for my birthday really enjoyed my meal ,decor is very new York in style, band really good even had a room to dance fantastic night will return soon."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r164464017", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "19 June 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your fantastic review as well as for spending your birthday with us. Thank you for mentioning Glen in your review, he was happy to have played his part.", "We all look forward to welcoming you and your friends again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "CamelotKidLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "52"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r164464017-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Wow, this place it the one! The staff are attentive, the food is delicious, the atmosphere is contagious and where do I start about the music...the whole package made for an extra special birthday celebration.", "Want to say an extra big thank you to one of the Restaurant managers Glenn, thank you for making my evening wonderful. This place is defo on my recommend list."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r164432582", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Classy joint!!!!!", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "18 June 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Mark,", "Thank you so much for choosing for your 10th anniversary. I am pleased to hear that everyone on the team did their part to ensure you have had a memorable evening. I look very much forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warmest Regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Mark G", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r164432582-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Having eaten here on a few 'special' occasions in the past and never been disappointed, I decided to book a table here for our 10th wedding anniversary last Saturday. The wife and I think the Restaurant setting is just fabulous with the impressive bar stocked with hundreds of whiskies on one side, the panoramic view from the bay window on the other and the stage / dance floor straight ahead!", "The decor combined with the atmosphere created by the live music, Saturday was a Motown Tribute, just makes this a special place.", "The wife likes to think she is a vegetarian, (I know that she is just a fussy eater) but the food was exceptional and the service was attentive without being intrusive. In our opinion, this really is a classy joint!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r165148726", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Very pleasant evening", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "25 June 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Martin,", "I am delighted you have enjoyed your evening with us & that the team wholly looked after you. Please check our websites for information on future bands playing on our stage.", "I look forward to welcoming you again soon.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MartinSherriff", "reviewer_origin": ["Leighton Buzzard, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "162"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "89"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r165148726-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This restaurant has a really good atmosphere and plenty of space between tables. The view from the windows is extensive.The staff are very good and the food was excellent. I had langoustines followed by Dover Sole and it was top-notch.", "At around 9.30 we had the option to extend our stay at the table for a small fee to enjoy a very good jazz band who played for the rest of the evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r161357490", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Impressive selection of whisky, good food, ok service", "diner_date": " April 2013", "rating_date": "21 May 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Rafael,", "Thank you for the feedback of your visit. I am delighted you enjoyed our whisky range and that you did enjoy our Haggis; we do get lots of excellent feedback. I would be very interested in hearing more of your thoughts regarding the rest of the evening. I would be delighted if you drop me an email under dgm@boisdale-cw.co.uk and outline your views.", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "rafaeltc", "reviewer_origin": ["Seattle, Washington"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r161357490-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I was here mostly to try Haggis (hard to find in Seattle). The selection of whisky is simply impressive, including rare and extinct brands. I tried the Kalkerran (never heard before of it), and was worth the price tag. The haggis was good, but my companion (from Scotland) was not overly impressed. I look forward to try it again a bit further North.", "Service was quite disconnected from an otherwise great experience. Probably our waitress was inexperienced, but she was unable to answer questions about the menu, and was quite slow."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r161185362", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "V expensive meal", "diner_date": " April 2013", "rating_date": "19 May 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for your feedback, and for choosing us on such an important day. I am sad to hear that we did not live up to your expectations. I would be delighted if you would be able to provide me with some detail under dgm@boisdale-cw.co.uk . Our pastry chef was quite delighted that you would return for his deserts though\u2026", "I look forward to hearing from you!", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "leigh30", "reviewer_origin": ["london"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r161185362-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for our wedding anniversary thought the food was over priced for the food Dessert was v good. Service was slow felt like they did not have enough staff. Would go back for the dessert."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r162734437", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Very smart setting very good food and whiskies", "diner_date": " June 2013", "rating_date": "2 June 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Guests, ", "Thank you very much for your review. I am glad you have enjoyed your food. I am very sorry that you had to wait for your salt & pepper. It is part of the standard setup, but we have introduced new procedures to prevent a recurrence . We are very proud of our whisky selection and have a team of enthusiastic and dedicated bar tenders who have lots of tastings and training sessions laid on, to keep their creative brains ticking. I\u2019m delighted they were able to help you navigate through weighty volume.", "I look forward to welcoming you back in the future and hope you drop us a quick email so we can make sure to say hello.", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Mintyburble", "reviewer_origin": ["Chesham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "403"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "129"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r162734437-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Myself and my husband came here for an anniversary meal. We booked a table in their oyster bar and grill when there was a live band upstairs, which made the atmosphere very quiet. I had a lobster club and my husband the bone in rib steak as a main. We had a McSween haggis and a Loch Duart smoked salmon to start. All was nearly excellent, but there was no salt and pepper on the table and we had to wait for that a bit longer. The claret and the whisky was also impressive. An Scotch whisky lover would enjoy flicking though the seemingly endless pages which come as booklet rather than a menu card. The desserts were also very lovely. Overall we were both impressed and will probably come back another time and sit in the main restaurant area."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r161560204", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Romance in canary wharf", "diner_date": " March 2013", "rating_date": "23 May 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "Thank you very much for your review. I am happy you enjoyed the setting and the service from our waiter, even though your arrival was a bit rushed. We are currently training a few members of staff and I am confident that the team will be so much stronger for it. With regards to the music charge, it seems unfortunate that you were not aware of the music ticket charge, as every team member has been trained to ensure guests arriving without booking are made aware of the ticket charge prior to seating. In the event of a booked table, the reservations team ensure you will have been made aware and an online booking can only be made with an acknowledgement of the charge. We are currently working on making this system even more clear and concise to our customers.", "At Boisdale we aim to provide dining opportunities at any price point. While I agree that for example our finest dry-aged Fillet of Beef on the bone may seem expensive, I would point out it is a premium cut of meat of the highest quality. I can only refer to our excellent value Jacobite Menu. This is a 2 course menu available for lunch as well as dinner, all week; for \u00a319.75. When you pair this with one of our 12 wines available for under \u00a325 I hope you can agree that we can provide excellent value.", "Again thank you for your feedback and I do wish to welcome you back in the near future.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "extremehardtoplease", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r161560204-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very nice setting. Good views and romantic decor. Service felt a bit rushed when we arrived but our waiter was great. Not really sure why \u00a34.50 per person is added on for ? Entertainment. I think that really takes the Michael!! poor taste! Overall not bad. Probably most romantic place on canary wharf. Food on the whole was good. Definitely wouldn't pay full price as v expensive."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r160679284", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "This place is awesome", "diner_date": " February 2013", "rating_date": "14 May 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "Thank you so much for your lovely review.", "We are delighted that you think our restaurant is awesome.", "Looking forward to welcoming you back soon.", "Yours sincerely,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "AnonAnon116", "reviewer_origin": ["Anon"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r160679284-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Delicious food, excellent service and great location. I went twice and had a great time. Highly recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r161395544", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Epic lunch", "diner_date": " May 2013", "rating_date": "21 May 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for your brief but splendid feedback!!", "I look forward to welcoming you back again soon.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "eatmoref00d", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r161395544-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["First time here, fantastic food great service, would return, steaks were beyond great!!!!! Live music is always a plus "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r160679916", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Busy Boisdale", "diner_date": " May 2013", "rating_date": "14 May 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "Thank you for taking time to review our restaurant.", "We were delighted that you like the d\u00e9cor, thought the food was excellent & the staff attentive.", "It was disappointing to read however that you scored the restaurant as 'poor' because other guests were talking during Clare Teal's performance.", "I appreciate that the actions of others obviously had a negative impact on your enjoyment of the show & I have taken steps to ensure Clare's next performance will be a Saturday night, due to intimate nature of her set. The absence of any corporate business on Saturdays makes for a totally different experience. ", "Boisdale is a restaurant dedicated to great live music, it would not be practical to cease the service during the performance with so many customers dining. ", "Finally, Clare is both completely at ease & very capable when dealing with a difficult audience. Previous audiences at her show have been quiet enough to hear a pin drop, particularly during her beautiful rendition of 'Chasing Cars'.", "I hope your positive remarks regarding the food, service & d\u00e9cor would convince you to return.", "Yours sincerely,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "996juner", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "608"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "209"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "20", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r160679916-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I went with my husband to this restaurant/jazz club to see Clare Teal. The d\u00e9cor is beautiful. The staff are extremely attentive and friendly and the food is excellent. However, many of the tables carried on talking during the show, as did the staff. Apparently this always happens as a lot of the tables are paid for by companies, so the people aren't bothered about the act. For this reason I would not go back, as it was very irritating and totally inconsiderate."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r162250951", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Beautiful restaurant and food", "diner_date": " May 2013", "rating_date": "29 May 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Sonia,", "Thank you for your great review. I am delighted you enjoyed our Macsween\u2019s Haggis, which we roast, rather than boil as we believe this makes for better flavour. You are quite right with regards to the whiskies and the cigars, both being amongst the best selections in Europe. I hope to be able to welcome you back in the not too distant future.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "SoniaB359", "reviewer_origin": ["Johannesburg, South Africa"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r162250951-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The restaurant was truly beautiful, boasting one of the larges whisky collections and humidors in Europe??", "We had a collection of starters and steak. The haggis starter is divine! As was the quail scotch eggs."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r161669127", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic for Business", "diner_date": " May 2013", "rating_date": "24 May 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you so much for your marvellous review. I am always delighted to hear that the team has performed over and beyond, so thank you for letting us know. Andy Rose, our Executive Chef & his team, are delighted that you enjoyed the food. I hope to welcome you back in the near future not only for business but perhaps to enjoy an evening of jazz and whisky. ", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sirbalkansobranie", "reviewer_origin": ["Edinburgh, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "165"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "143"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r161669127-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I attended a business meal here in the private dining room.", "We had a reception on the veranda which was great. From the start the staff were exceptional - they really went the extra mile to ensure we were look after at every point.", "The dining room was very pleasant, the food was really good and the wine waiters were very professional.", "Afterwards we availed ourselves of one of the biggest selections of Malt Whisky I have ever seen. You could spend some serious money!", "Ideal for business entertaining."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r162503178", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lobster for Lunch", "diner_date": " May 2013", "rating_date": "31 May 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you very much for your review. We try to anticipate the needs of our guests so I am happy the team recognised you were not in a hurry. I look forward to welcoming you again soon in the near future and hope you enjoy your return visit!", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "CDB404", "reviewer_origin": ["Tunbridge Wells"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "29"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r162503178-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Met a friend for a business lunch. We had not seen each other for a number of months so lots of news to catch up. The staff did not hurry us to order, which I had not expected from a somewhere used to doing lunches in Canary Wharf. I will certainly be back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r156491961", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great jazz, disappointing food", "diner_date": " February 2013", "rating_date": "3 April 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Stevie,", "Thanks for taking time to write a review. We are delighted that you liked the venue and felt that the service was excellent all the way through. We are obviously disappointed that the food on this occasion did not live up to expectations. We sell a few hundred portions of the bisque a week but it is clear that this was over-seasoned on the night in question.", "I have taken your feedback on the beef to the butcher, in the hope that we can prevent a recurrence. We only buy the very best Dry-Aged, Aberdeenshire beef and generally receive very positive feedback on our steaks, sadly not this time. It sounds like a poor cut of meat slipped through the net. Happy to hear the fish & chips was good.", "Perhaps you could contact us on manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk and give us an opportunity to show you how good the food can be.", "Kind regards,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "StevieHumpy", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r156491961-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale Canary Wharf is a giant of a venue, beautifully decked out in traditionally rich Scottish colours, an enormous main dining room with a grand bar on the right and a small stage at the top for the musicians. Tables are spacious yet cosy, white table-cloths, sterling silver cutlery, decent glassware. In all, it screams elegance and grandeur and you are anticipating a great meal ahead.", "It is such a shame then that I write this review with very mixed feelings. Certainly the service and staff were excellent all the way through, being very attentive without being intrusive. The wine selection is extensive and their by-the-glass Malbec was very good value. The whisky offering is unbelievably large and I could quite easily while away several weeks just sampling the drams they have. The jazz band on that night were phenomenal (I wish I could remember the band's name!) and made for a great ambience.", "Food-wise however, Boisdale was a real disappointment. The shellfish bisque that was ordered by four out of the six of us was so far over-salted that it was unbearable. All four diners sent their soups back to be replaced by four fresh versions that still were on the salty side. I can understand if one person's salt preference is more on the bland side, but for four people to all comment in similar fashion is more than just personal taste. My steak tartare was as expected, given that the preparation and seasoning is done by myself rather than pre-prepared by the chef.", "Fish & chips as a main course was very good - a huge chunk of lightly battered fish with plentiful chips. The \"untrimmed rib of beef on the bone\" (\u00a325) sadly was offered not such complimentary comments. Flavour-wise, the beef was a little bland and could have done with a bit more seasoning (in strange contrast to the bisque before!) but what is totally unforgiveable is the poor quality of the meat itself. Cooked medium rare to medium, the meat was almost impossible to cut with a steak knife, being far too stringy and tough. The fat simply had not rendered anywhere near enough, even though the steak was of thick-enough stature to allow the fat to melt away without overcooking.", "In comparison to Hawksmoor (which I have just reviewed), Boisdale is a good deal cheaper but on the evidence of this visit, it needs to up its game quite considerably to be acceptable in standard."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r156390669", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great bar, not so great restaurant", "diner_date": " September 2012", "rating_date": "2 April 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Mr Jensen,", "Thanks for your feedback, we are delighted that you consider us to be one of the best places to sit and relax with live music in London. ", "We're sorry our food did not impress you on your visit, we pride ourselves on sourcing the very best ingredients, primarily from Scotland and producing balanced, flavoursome dishes of the highest quality. I'm sorry you felt this was not the case.", "Please drop us an email so we can find out a little more about your experience.", "Yours sincerely,", "Nathan Evans"], "reviewer_pseudo": "runekjensen", "reviewer_origin": ["Esbjerg"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r156390669-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This is one of the best places in London to sit and relax and listen to live music and enjoy a drink or two. The food is nothing special.", "The drinks are not that pricey but a bit small. They have a HUGE whisky collection!", "They have a lot of great live music and the decor setting of the place is impressive.", "On the floor below there is a terrace and a cigar lounge"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r158651975", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Half price seafood platter great - 25% service charge not so", "diner_date": " April 2013", "rating_date": "24 April 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer,", "Thank you for taking us up on our half price seafood offer, which is proving to be very popular.", "I'm sorry that the whelks were not up to scratch. I have spoken to our Executive Head Chef to prevent a recurrence. I have also spoken to the team regarding the recommended amount of space required to enjoy these dishes in comfort. ", "I empathise with your remaraks on the service which is calculated at 12.5% of the bill before the 50% is discounted from the food element.", "All of the service charge goes to the team and we try not to let strong discount offers promoted by the company such as a 50% off food, adversly effect their earnings.", "The service charge obviously remains optional and you were quite within your right to remove it.", "We will make this policy even more clear on-line and when people book, but assure you that this is not sharp practise.", "I look forward to welcoming you back soon.", "Kind regards,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Amyo83", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r158651975-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We recently went to Boisdale to take advantage of their half price seafood platter deal. We went all out and decided on the Royale platter (originally \u00a395), lobster, crab, six oysters, six langoustines, prawns, cockles, mussels and whelks. Good value when you're only paying \u00a347.50.", "The food was good, decent sized lobster for two and a decent amount for two to share. Disappointingly the whelks were nearly all impossible to get into.", "We were sat on a tiny table for two which couldn't accommodate the platter, our plates, drinks and finger bowls so we asked if we could move to a larger table for four. No problem but the staff seemed a little surprised that we wanted to move.", "When we asked for the bill we saw that we were charged a whopping 25% service charge as the service had been calculated before the discount had been taken off. Be wary of this should you go for the deal as the waitress handed over the PDQ without seemly realising the high bill. We had the service charge refunded once we looked into it.", "Overall I'd rate the following: service 3/5, food 4/5, value for money 4/5 (but only because it was half price), toilets 4/5 and general ambience 3/5."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r159227227", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A brilliant night. Not to be missed", "diner_date": " March 2013", "rating_date": "30 April 2013", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Eileen M", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r159227227-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["What a fantastic night. My family went here for an evening out so the age range was varied. My daughter is 20 to my father in law who is 89 years old. The music was fantastic and thank you Mr Ray Gelato who came to our table after performing and gave my father in law a signed cd. You made our visit very special. The food was fantastic. The service was second to none. And my family cant wait to come again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r159885690", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Pie in the sky", "diner_date": " May 2013", "rating_date": "7 May 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Tony,", "Thank you for your wonderful review. The team at our Canary Wharf Restaurant are delighted that you had such a great time on Saturday night.", "We look forward to welcoming you back very soon", "Kind regards,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Tony12345186605", "reviewer_origin": ["Dublin, Ireland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r159885690-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Certainly one of the best places that I have been. Fantastic views elevated over Canary Wharf. There was a Stevie Wonder tribute band playing in the background. The food was beyond belief. After dinner I visited the cigar bar and has a super cigar. There was also an oyster and champaingne bar. This place, you really have to book in advance."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r155951520", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "My favourite restaurant", "diner_date": " March 2013", "rating_date": "29 March 2013", "answer_text": ["Caroline, thank you so much for your review.", "I am happy that the three of you had a good time. It was lovely to see you again and I look forward to the next time.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Caroline R", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r155951520-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This is my 4th visit to Boisdale this year. My sister and I took our mum for a belated mothers day meal and she absolutely loved it! The food was amazing - she had the risotto which was the best she has had before. The waiters and waitresses all work together exceptionally well and come across as very professional at all times. The manager was attentive and makes you feel very welcome. The Congo Faith Healers were playing and they were brilliant. My mum even bought their cd! ", "So to sum up.....great restaurant, food, atmosphere, staff. A great evening enjoyed by all 3 of us."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r157814262", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great all round venue!", "diner_date": " March 2013", "rating_date": "15 April 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your fabulous review.", "It is wonderful to hear you have had a lovely time & I look forward to welcoming you again before long! Do check the website for upcoming events including our Guitar Greats festival and make sure to drop us an email under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk when you plan on visiting us next.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "amphcoop", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "51"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "40"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r157814262-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["visited Boisdale for the first time and was not disappointed . we booked a premium table so we could enjoy the atmosphere of being in jazz club in addition to some fine dining. My first impression was how grand the whiskey bar was with the largest selection of whiskey you could imagine. We were greeted and shown to our table which was lit with candles and well layed out, cosy and romantic. The views were very good looking out over canary wharf, with the rest of the club tastefully decorated with various art etc, stylish. The service was spot on ,as was the food, nothing to much trouble for the waitress who looked after us very well. fantastic wine list, wines to suit every taste at reasonable prices. Great music venue as well , great band , great atmosphere . Also had a cocktail in the bar which is down below the restaurant that was lovely as well. All in all had a great night and can't wait to return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r159617998", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great night out", "diner_date": " May 2013", "rating_date": "4 May 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Bob,", "Thank you for your review, which is greatly appreciated by the team at Bosidale Canary Wharf.", "It is heart-warming to hear that you enjoyed both the food & the ambience. The cigar terrace really comes into it's own now that the warmer weather is here too.", "It was the second time we have run the 'Suspiciously Elvis' show this year and I agree that Ivor gives a splendid performance as Elvis. Saturday's show was one of the best yet.", "He returns in October and we hope to welcoming you back very soon.", "Drop us an email prior to your next visit and we will be sure to say hello.", "Kind regards,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Eatenthere", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r159617998-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["First went here over two years ago. Got a flyer in the post so went to see a jazz band .. And wow what a great place....the decor the ambience the music and the food is great. The great selections of whiskeys are the cherry on top! Went last night to the Elvis tribute night and a good singer who puts on a good show. The food was superb as is the members cigar terrace. For those who like live music, cigars and excellent food then you should pay this place a visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r159227587", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Huge disappointment!", "diner_date": " April 2013", "rating_date": "30 April 2013", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Ben Tommy T", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "30", "20", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r159227587-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My friends and I went to Boisdale for a birthday, all 12 of us were very disappointed with the overall experience. The majority of us chose Haggis for starters, only to be told they had 'run out'. The steak I received for my main course was largely made up of fat (a large amount of weight the steak claimed to be) and did not come as requested it to be cooked. The side dishes were a laughable size but were probably the best thing about the meal. Service was average and dining was slow, we waited a long time for our food to come out. Music was ok, but more of a gimmick than entertainment. Sadly another restaurant you pay the price to eat in a nice location not the quality of food. Overall I would NEVER go back or recommend to anyone... Should have gone to Goodman's or Hawksmoor!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r159260655", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing special night out", "diner_date": " April 2013", "rating_date": "30 April 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Janice,", "Thanks for your detailed review. ", "We are obviosuly delighted that you and your guests had a great night out with us.", "It was the first time the Lamours have performed, but the feedback has been great so I'm sure we will book them again.", "I am also pleased to here that your gluten intolerance was dealt with professionally and that you enjoyed your dinner.", "As for background noise, I do take your point and although I wasn't there on that particular Friday, there have been occasions where a proportion of the audience are there for dinner only and seem disinterested in the music. All of the artist are aware of these difficulties and used to dealing with some background noise. We are however looking at making an announcement before the more intimate performances, requesting guests to keep their conversation to a minimum. We are hoping this will do the trick!", "Please drop us an email before you next visit, I would like an opportunity to thank you for your lovely review.", "Best wishes,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Janice A", "reviewer_origin": ["Birmingham, England, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "24"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r159260655-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["What can I say? What an amazing amazing place!! Lovely attentive staff AND a goody bag! But v-e-r-y expensive. ", "We went on a Friday night to see a band called The Lamours. On our arrival my coat was taken from attentive cloakroom staff and then we were shown to our table (VIP, at the front, and for which you pay lots extra!) and asked if we wanted a drink\u2026we opted for champagne (\u00a323 for 2 glasses). We had arrived early because we wanted to eat before the entertainment began, only we didn\u2019t realise we would have a 3 hour wait! The lovely waitress suggested that we took our champagne to the oyster bar downstairs \u2013 this we did and it was crowded because it was a Friday night, so we went and stood on the balcony and looked at Canary Wharf and all the sights. The drinks there weren\u2019t actually too dear, a pint of real ale and a non-alcoholic cocktail came to \u00a36.10.", "We went back to our table and chose from the extensive menu. There was no problem with the fact that I need a gluten-free diet. I had gravadlax for starters (absolutely delish) and my friend had haggis tatties and neeps with a snifter! For mains we both had steaks, I had a lovely tender ribeye with Bloody Mary sauce (inspired) and he had a sirloin steak. The vegetables were interesting, I had broccoli with lemon juice and almonds and he had cabbage with onion and mushroom. ", "The cheese trolley \u2013 what can I say?? I\u2019ve never seen anything like it. It must have been 3\u2019 in diameter and full of the most wonderful cheeses including Lancashire Bomb (black, spherical and full of crumbly Lancashire cheese) and Stinking Bishop. The waitress actually asks you what kind of cheese you prefer then guides you in the right direction. I had the best cr\u00e8me caramel with a creamy/cr\u00e8me freche type accompaniment.", "We had a very good red wine (there again v-e-r-y expensive judging from the wine list ) and coffee. The bottles of whisky behind the bar have to be seen to be believed.", "I didn\u2019t actually see the bill, but be warned - 12\u00bd% service charge is added automatically and we didn't realise this until afterwards. ", "The only thing spoiling the evening was the chatter made by people who went for a night out and not to hear the band, which is extremely annoying and not very respectful to the musicians. (Note to the Boisdale \u2013 can\u2019t you manage this in some way?? I\u2019ve been to jazz clubs where the management challenge noisy customers. Why should we pay a helluva lot and not be able to hear properly?) Oh, and the acoustics aren't brilliant either, but I was prepared to overlook that. ", "And the goody bag?? Well it contained a \u00bc bottle of Canard Duchene champagne (no rubbish here, obviously!), a miniature of Chivas Regal, a tiny bag of posh chocs and a CD of Cuban music. ", "Would I go again? Oh yes please"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r154000993", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Boisdales", "diner_date": " September 2012", "rating_date": "8 March 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer, thank you so much for contributing. I am very pleased you enjoyed yourself.", "It would be great to see you again soon.", "Kindest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ImagesgwyneddA_13", "reviewer_origin": ["Merseyside, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "193"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "44"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r154000993-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Cool place, fantastic views from the public terrace , food good, larger was the best and staff a bit offhand, but great atmosphere and stopping of place after work ."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r154708017", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Super restaurant - food excellent", "diner_date": " March 2013", "rating_date": "15 March 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your fantastic review.", "Did you know that if you join us on Mondays through to Wednesdays the music starts from 7pm so you would have plenty of time to enjoy it and still be able to be home at a reasonable time?", "I really hope to welcome you again very soon.", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Minnie12359", "reviewer_origin": ["Oxfordshire"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "74"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "49"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r154708017-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My second trip to Boisdale was just as marvellous as the first: excellent food, first rate service and attention to my need to be in and out double quick. My lunch host recommended the steak - WOW! It was cooked exactly as I'd asked and was delicious. Now, not everyone wants to visit Canary Wharf but this place rocks - in more ways than one - they do R&B and jazz evenings - sadly I live 2 hours away from the office so unfortunately I daren't afford myself the luxury of an evening meal -wish I could - one day, maybe."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r155884581", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Our new favourite local", "diner_date": " March 2013", "rating_date": "28 March 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review. I am delighted you enjoyed the food and cocktails. ", "Some of our bourbons are exceptionally difficult to source so please accept my apologies for the inconvenience caused. We are looking forward to welcoming you again soon; hopefully on the terraces with lots of sunshine.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "F9517OSdanh", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "34"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r155884581-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale is a really well run place. The food is excellent, especially the new york strip steak, the sides are very good, and they do one of the best whiskey sours in London. It's not cheap, but its not in the Hawksmoor group of pricing. The Jazz is atmospheric without being a distraction. Cheese board is excellent. The only gripe is the lack of bourbons. Had to go to my third choice before they found one in stock. There is also a cigar terrace which i cant wait to try in summer."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r154383341", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "whats not to like?", "diner_date": " November 2012", "rating_date": "12 March 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "thank you for your fabulous comment on our restaurant. I am glad to see you have come to your senses and agree that tartan is the way forward. Please let us know when you are visiting next (manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk) and we will make sure to say hello.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "p n", "reviewer_origin": ["Leamington Spa, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r154383341-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Once you get over the somewhat twee decor slap bang in the middle of canary wharf, theres nothing not to like about boisdales. Fab steaks, haggis, and great wines. Service was good , and after a nice steak and red wine, i actually started to think tartan wallpaper is the way to go"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r154445181", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Experience", "diner_date": " February 2013", "rating_date": "13 March 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Peter, ", "All of us work hard to make Boisdale of Canary Wharf something special so thank you very much for your lovely review. Please look on our website for information on our upcoming music line up and other events such as whisky and cigar tastings. ", "I hope to welcome you back soon.", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Peter C", "reviewer_origin": ["Westcliff-on-Sea"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r154445181-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Steak was cooked to perfection and seafood bisque was one of the best I have tasted. I can't say that I've ever seen such a huge selection range of whiskeys on the separate list and stacked high behind the bar. Really nice evening with first class and appropriate musical entertainment to dine by."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r153064945", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great night out would highly recommend it", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "25 February 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Catherine,", "I am delighted that you enjoyed the entertainment, the Dry-Aged Scottish beef and the service with us on Saturday night. Thank you so much for your review. ", "We have some fantastic acts in the calendar for 2013, so keep an eye on our website (www.boisdale.co.uk) or better still sign up for our newsletter so you can keep up-to-date. ", "Please drop us an email at manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk before your next visit and we\u2019ll be sure to say hello.", "Warm wishes,", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Catherine P", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "27"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r153064945-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We have just enjoyed a wonderful night of entertainment, food and atmosphere at the Canary Wharf Boisdale. On a previous trip to London we saw the restaurant and then looked it up on the Internet We booked our VIP table which was fun however, some of the dancers nearly set fire to items of their clothing until we moved our candle. The group the Red Stripes were excellent they created a wonderful party atmosphere and we would be happy see them again. The food was excellent in particular the rib eye steak of gigantic proportions and a wonderful melt in the mouth fillet steak. The staff were friendly and attentive, it was a lovely evening that we thoroughly enjoyed. Thank you, we hope to see you again"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r154737994", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent. Utterly excellent!", "diner_date": " March 2013", "rating_date": "16 March 2013", "answer_text": ["I am absolutely delighted by your lovely review. Thank you for taking the time do write these lines. Please drop me a line under manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk when you next plan to come in and I will make sure to say hello!", "Warmest regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "EJH79", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r154737994-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Friday night with beer, oysters, perfect steak, truffled spinach, (a completely unnecessary but excellent) sticky toffee pudding, cigars and jazz.", "With excellent service, really, what's *not* to like about this!", "Excellent evening (and the lady's prawn cocktail and crab linguine were pretty damn good too).", "Cheap? No. Good value? Oh yes!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r155043169", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Happy to be local", "diner_date": " February 2013", "rating_date": "19 March 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Maria,", "Thank you so very much for your lovely review. It is brilliant to hear that our neighbourhood is coming over to enjoy themselves. My favourite steak is the Sirloin on the bone cooked rare with bone marrow sauce. You should try that if you have not already! Next time you plan on coming, please drop me a quick line (manager@boisdale-cw.co.uk) and I will make sure to say hello!", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Mariagor83", "reviewer_origin": ["London, England, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "68"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "50"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r155043169-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["As we are locals our trips to Boisdale happened quite often.", "We love Boisdale because of....STEAK!", "The steak is perfection. One of the best steak you can eat in London. ", "And don't forget about Jazz, you can listen good music and this is wonderful.", "This is not a cheap place, but for the quality and entertainment is a really good value."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r154803219", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent jazz, good food", "diner_date": " March 2013", "rating_date": "16 March 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for writing such a great review. I am delighted you had a great time. Did you know that Canary Wharf is only 15 minutes away from Green Park with the Jubilee Line? So I am glad you agree that it is worth the trip.", "I hope to see you soon!", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Piotr M", "reviewer_origin": ["Paris, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1649"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "782"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r154803219-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A bit remote location but Boisdale of Canary Wharf is a great place, with large main room, located above the bar and cigar room. Very good food with a lot of Scottish specialities (poached salmon, crab, seafood) and great choice of steaks. 20 pages or so long wine list has great matches or most of dishes and a nice collection of port, including few quite old. But you are going there to listen to music (some nice Sinatra-stle jazz tonight) and it is absolutely excellent. Worth a trip to Canary Wharf to enjoy the place."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r155502414", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Evening", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "24 March 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Paul,", "I am delighted that you enjoyed your Friday evening and thank you for writing a review.", "I look forward to welcoming you back very soon. To keep updated check out our website or sign up to our email alerts for details on upcoming events and shows like our Guitar Greats Festival.", "Warm regards,", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "917PaulI", "reviewer_origin": ["Danbury, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "34"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r155502414-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A group of 7 of us went to dinner at Boisdale. We had a great evening. Service was excellent and food superb. My wife had the Linguine with Hebridean Crab which she said was devine and I had the Untrimmed Rib of Beef on the Bone (18-20 oz) and as a meat eater, I was in heaven. Great company coupled with good food and wine (we probably overdid it with the wine but you only live once!!) and finished off with a set by the Soul Sisters made for a fantastic evening. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r150696872", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Burn's night", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "26 January 2013", "answer_text": ["I am delighted you enjoyed Burns Night with us. Regarding the steak we have already agreed that the untrimmed rib of beef had too much fat content for the majority of guests and we will not be using it for set menus again. I am pleased you enjoyed the address to the Haggis, though it was strenuous holding it for so long; still great fun! I hope to see you in the near future and thank you for reviewing.", "Warm regards", "Falko Molitor"], "reviewer_pseudo": "CockneySparrow201150", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r150696872-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked late and couldn't get a table until 9pm on Burn's night. Had to pay for the jazz too but said we didn't need to see the stage so only paid \u00a310 each. Turned out we had a really good table with not too much of a restricted view. The Haggis was toasted at least three times while we there and the piper was great! We had the special Burn's night menu which included a dram of whiskey with the haggis neeps and tattles and a Drambuie with dessert. We had the smoked salmon to start which was delicious. It's was follows by the haggis which again was delicious. For the man course we both chose the steak and chips. We've been to Boisdale Bishopgate before and the steaks there are great, but the ones we had last night were poor and not the usual standard. It was a extremely busy so maybe this was the problem! Dessert was either clottie dumpling with custard or cranachan. We had one of each and they were good. We finished off with coffees. This was \u00a348 a head so not bad. A bottle of my favourite Sancerre rose wine was \u00a345. Staff were good even thought they were extremely busy. Will definitely go back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r150726383", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Elvis Night at Boisdale", "diner_date": " January 2013", "rating_date": "27 January 2013", "answer_text": ["Barry, thank you for commenting on your experience. You are quite right, the Cloudy Bay prices have soared over the last years, but there are many alternatives on the wine list that are equally stunning for example the Craggy Range Sauvignon Blanc as well as the Saint Clair Sauvignon Blanc, both like the Cloudy Bay from Marlborough, New Zealand. Our house Gin & Tonic is priced at \u00a38.50, but as we have eight varieties available, your preference may change that. I am glad that you did enjoy the service and atmosphere though and look forward to welcoming you again in the near future.", "Yours sincerely", "Falko Molitor"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Barry22948", "reviewer_origin": ["Southend-on-Sea, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "40", "40", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r150726383-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went to see an Elvis tribute at Boisdale, Canary Wharf in January 2013. Tribute act was OK however prices were astronomical for what you get. Food very average and overpriced. Steak \u00a322 with no side dishes. A small bowl of 'jacket' chips \u00a34.50. Fish and chips (poorly cooked) \u00a319.50!! Drinks overpriced. A bottle of Cloudy Bay Sauvignon Blanc \u00a375!!!! Gin and tonic \u00a311!!! Service was very good and the atmosphere was also good. However, value for money really poor. Four of us went - \u00a380 entrance fee then a bill for \u00a3254 for food and drink and we didn't over indulge!! How people can afford this on a regular basis is hard to believe."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r150758885", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "A little disappointed", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "27 January 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your feedback! I am sorry to hear that Elvis was not what you have hoped for; I have had so many great comments about him. In fact, he is booked again and I have sold already about 50% of the tickets; most of them on a return visit. I am thrilled however that you enjoyed the service & atmosphere. I would be happy if you would like to provide me with more feedback regarding the food. You can contact me directly.", "Warm regards", "Falko Molitor", "dgm@boisdale-cw.co.uk"], "reviewer_pseudo": "birdieEssex", "reviewer_origin": ["essex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "110"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "77"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "50", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r150758885-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Was really looking forward to this night out with close friends and have to say was a little disappointed. ", "The service was excellent! The atmosphere was very very good. The food hugely disappointing and it certainly wasn't value for money. ", "The entertainment for the night was Elvis- who was average - not the best and not the worst although he did want to try talking and it was just a muffle! ", "The pity is we was here last year and everything was excellent! So hence us looking forward to the night. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r150357080", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent food and atmosphere", "diner_date": " January 2013", "rating_date": "23 January 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your feedback Pearl. I am thrilled that you had such a great time. ", "Warmest regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "moohippomoo", "reviewer_origin": ["Singapore, Singapore"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "25"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r150357080-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We reserved a table through toptable so we had 50% off. It was a great experience which would otherwise be quite costly if we didn't have the 50% off! Atmosphere was really great and romantic for couples. Food was good too. We ordered a Fruit de Mer for 2 as a starter and it was actually a little too much."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r152587414", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "RAISING STANDARDS IN CANARY WHARF", "diner_date": " February 2013", "rating_date": "20 February 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Richard,", "I'm delighted that you enjoyed your visit to our Canary Wharf restaurnat and we are very grateful for your positive feedback.", "Having traded our Belgravia restaurant for over 25 years, we have tried hard to make our latest outpost here in the Wharf as warm and welcoming as possible, in the hope that we could bring a little of the West End to the Capital of the East End.", "Come and see us again soon.", "Nathan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Richard G", "reviewer_origin": ["Ashford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "355"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "154"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r152587414-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Let's face it, the restaurant choice in Canary wharf isn't great - so Boisdale has been a welcome addition. Some may dislike the faux-Scottish surroundings, and the rather cavernous main restaurant, but the service, food and ambience are all up to the best West End standards. Steak is well-cooked and unfussy, and the hand-cut chips are impossible to resist. Good wine list too!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r150332421", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "One of the best steaks I've ever had and definitely some of the best musicians I've seen - a great night!", "diner_date": " January 2013", "rating_date": "23 January 2013", "answer_text": ["It is fantastic to hear that you had a cracking time Lizzy. I agree that Aberdeenshire steaks are the best and I have tried plenty others. Keep checking out our website as Jeremy will soon return with a big band for even more feel good tunes!", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "foxxylizzy", "reviewer_origin": ["Aboyne, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "217"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "133"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r150332421-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Despite the previous reviewer saying that Scotsman don't come to the Boisdale....actually they do - we're from Aberdeenshire! It was the jazz that attracted us and it didn't disappoint, we saw the Jeremy Sassoon quintet and they were simply fabulous - so much so that I persuaded my husband to get up and dance.", "It's not a cheap night out. We booked our music tickets in advance and paid for a 'standard view' dining table at \u00a320 per head before you pay for dinner so it's pretty pricey but I guess that is how they afford to have such great acts on so often. The 'restricted view' tables are \u00a310 per head and I would have argued that ours was a restricted view but we didn't mind as we were sat next to the window with a lovely view out to the sparkling tree lights of Cabot Square.", "The steaks are from Aberdeenshire (as all the best steaks are) and my ribeye was the best I have ever had. All the accompaniments were gorgeous too - thick cut chips, field mushrooms etc (all charged as extra).", "The restaurant is done out in sort of hunting lodge style - deep red and tartan carpet but not overtly so. There's a few stags' heads on the walls and mounted fish and the waitresses wear kilts but it's not at all kitsch. I bet there's not a Scottish waitress there though - ours wasn't, and I bet the majority haven't visited Scotland either......", "I would love to go back with friends sometime."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r150241716", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Food, Great Jazz, Great Service", "diner_date": " November 2012", "rating_date": "22 January 2013", "answer_text": ["Phil, thank you for your kind feedback. I am delighted you had a lovely evening. Please come again soon!", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "PhilAndrews77", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "83"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r150241716-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Last visited in mid November for a business celebration. We had one more than we expected and were still fitted in well by the staff.", "The service was excellent, particularly at the bar where the barman took time out to explain through all the different cocktails available at Boisdale.", "The food was also excellent, in all cases. Steak is cooked to exacting specifications, and the Haggis was just divine for the starter.", "You won't spot a Scotsman here but it makes a good effort at paying tribute to the Food and Drink culture of Scotland."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r150767265", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Average in every way", "diner_date": " January 2013", "rating_date": "27 January 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Jonathan, thank you for commenting. Some of our steaks have lots of fat, especially the untrimmed rib of beef, however some crave them like this. I am very sorry we fell short of your expectations in the service area, but since your comment we have made certain that every private room has a dedicated waiter only looking after your needs. Should you be in soon for another visit, please contact me directly.", "Yours sincerely,", "Falko Molitor", "dgm@boisdale-cw.co.uk"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JonathanT_13", "reviewer_origin": ["Bromley, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "321"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "109"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r150767265-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Ate in the private dining room which you might have expected to be a \"showcase\". Service was slow and drinks not refreshed regularly. Most disappointing was the steak which was fatty and large parts inedible. The haggis though was excellent (it was close to Burns night). Very expensive in my view. Would not return from choice (this was a business function)."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r152555816", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Arctic Air Con", "diner_date": " February 2013", "rating_date": "19 February 2013", "answer_text": ["Dear Reviewer, ", "Thank you for taking the time to write about your experience at our Canary Wharf Restaurant. ", "We have now fixed, the temporary problem with the heating, which was exasperated by the exceptionally cold weather that weekend, please accept my apologies for any discomfort felt. The Oyster Bar & Grill is quieter on a Saturday night as most of our guests are travelling into the Wharf for the show in the main restaurant on the second floor. I'm delighted that you enjoyed the food and found our team to be helpful. ", "The cover charge you refer to for the second floor is actually a ticket for the live performance, much like a visit to the theatre or the O2 and I'm sorry if you thought the act did not warrant a \u00a315 ticket. Unlike places such as Ronnie Scott\u2019s who see ticket sales as an opportunity to make profits, we simple try to recoup the costs associated with putting on World class Jazz, Blues & Soul Acts. The prices vary depending on the night of the week, the act and the proximity to the stage. All upcoming performances can be viewed on our website www.boisdale.co.uk with full details of the ticket prices available. ", "Thanks again for your comments. We hope to see you again very soon."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jane V", "reviewer_origin": ["Crayford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "111"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "74"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "20", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r152555816-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went to the Oyster Bar and Grill. Very nice table by the window but.... drafty and freezing. The aircon meant that I sat freezing in my party dress. Didnt want to sit wearing my coat so hoped the super alcoholic cocktail would help along with the very yummy chicken shnitzel and cauliflower cheese. The staff were friendly and helpful so didnt want to complain. The restaurant did seem quite empty but that was possibly due to the fact that everyone was dining in the main restaurant where we were headed to to see the evenings entertainment. ", "To go upstairs to the restaurant or to dine during the entertainment you are charged a \u00a315 cover charge each. I do think that a bit cheeky as the cuisine and drinks are expensive. The nights entertainment was great and the band excellent. We thoroughly enjoyed ourselves but forgot that it was the Saturday following Thursday valentine day and it was full of loving couples - whoopsie - hey ho we had fun anyway.", "It was warmer upstairs than in the Oyster Bar. Would not consider dining in the Oyster Bar again unless it was sub tropical temperatures outside.... sort it out please!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r151324712", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "live music dining venue", "diner_date": " February 2013", "rating_date": "3 February 2013", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your feedback. It is true that Friday and Saturday have become so popular that waiting times are a possibility. We do mention on our website the ticket prices but are working on making this much clearer for you. I have not been to Loch Fyne myself but this is the first time I have heard of strong fish smell on the 1st floor. I am however delighted that you enjoyed the food and service. I hope to welcome you back soon.", "Warm regards", "Falko"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Pinkholidayman", "reviewer_origin": ["Amersham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "346"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "99"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r151324712-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went in without a booking on Saturday Night, but it is Canary Wharf! went into the Oyster Bar and Grill first, quite strong smell of fish when the lift door opens! I know it is an Oyster Bar, but Loch Fyne doesn't smell like this and they sell fish! So decided to go upstairs to fine dining, was told 1hour and a half wait, that it was \u00a320 per head for the live music (cannot see that on the website) and that there was space downstairs and the food came from the same kitchen. So we went back downstairs and had a very nice rib eye steak, we forgot or did not notice the fish smell, all the staff bar and table s were very good, friendly , happy and attentive, strange menu you could have 1/2 grilled lobster as a sauce with your steak (\u00a320) but not have hot grilled lobster as a main course."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r146327123", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great steak but bad for the wallet", "diner_date": " October 2012", "rating_date": "27 November 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "tasstw", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "66"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "51"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r146327123-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Big fan of Boisdale when I'm in the mood for a steak. The restaurant is split into two with a \"restaurant\" and a \"bar\" although both serve food and drink. The bar has recently expanded its menu to match the restaurant for its popular meals which was a welcome touch given that the bar is normally easier to get a table and you will be charged for the jazz performance if you happen to be in the restaurant whether you wanted to listen or not. ", "The steaks always come well cooked, the rossini being a particular highlight with lovely foie gras, a generous amount of truffles and deep flavoured sauce. I don't normally get starters but am a fan of the haggis which is surprisingly light and fluffy compared to denser offerings elsewhere. The desserts are generally a bit disappointing and remind me of school dinners in their stodginess. ", "Service is rather slow (delivery of food and general attentiveness) and the later you arrive, the slower it will be to deal with the back log in orders. It is also on the toppy end of the price range with a steak, side of fries and a beer setting you back around \u00a350. Wine is also expensive. A great night out if you are a steak fan but you're wallet won't thank you for it!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r146010492", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great steak", "diner_date": " November 2012", "rating_date": "23 November 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "TheScubaDuo", "reviewer_origin": ["Swadlincote, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "535"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "338"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r146010492-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A nice location and a nice restaurant. The meal was very good, the steak being excellent. Good choice of beer and wine. A good place to choose."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r149676372", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "If I hadn't gone through Toptable .......", "diner_date": " January 2013", "rating_date": "14 January 2013", "answer_text": ["I would be happy to hear more about your evening; please do contact me directly. Thank you for taking the time to review us.", "Yours sincerely", "Falko Molitor", "dgm@boisdale-cw.co.uk"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Southofenglandfoodie", "reviewer_origin": ["Hastings, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "337"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "157"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r149676372-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I am unsure if I would have dined here. We were a table of 4 and had selected this restaurant for lunch as it was local for all of us. . The wine started at \u00a318.50 per bottle, the house white wine was pretty average. When we asked for the next least expensive bottle we were advised it was not available leaving us with the next priced bottle at \u00a325. The total bill for 4 of us with two bottles of wine was \u00a3107.00, which was with 50% off food. The service was ok but nothing special. All in all nothing to write home about."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r146409832", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Corporate cattle shed with so few seats you wonder how long they want you to stay.", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "29 November 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "artegall", "reviewer_origin": ["Spalding, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "58"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "32"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r146409832-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["OK. So I don't like modern city bars but this one is designed to allow the maximum number of people to huddle together round small thin stands and pretend they are having a good time. Packed full of folks for whom the ambience of a decent pub is too far away. Yuk. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r146237433", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "My fave London restaurant", "diner_date": " October 2012", "rating_date": "26 November 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Lynjcecil", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "71"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r146237433-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Boisdale would be great without the live music, having it is really the icing on the cake! Love the bar, fun and noisy, you can be out on the terrace in the summer for drinks. Love sitting there having dinner looking over Canary Wharf towards the Thames. The oysters are always good, and the meat is excellent. The steak is so good have nt managed to try anything else yet . Great for a special occasion. Very expensive if you spoil yourself, that's why I don't lose weight!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r147079877", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "A memorable night", "diner_date": " December 2012", "rating_date": "9 December 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Britabroad22", "reviewer_origin": ["BritAbroad"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "115"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "76"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r147079877-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My family and I enjoyed a great night of food, wine and outstanding entertainment in the 2nd floor restaurant at Boisdale. None of us had eaten there before but we will almost certainly return ... if only for the entertainment. The theme for the night was Las Vegas and the big-band-sound and singing were of the highest order ... and certainly got the guests on their feet! The entertainment was preceded by dinner: the starters of fresh Scottish oysters were delicious and we all went for steaks for our mains, all but one of which were well cooked. Service was sprightly and attentive but not too much. A great party atmosphere and we all had great fun."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r147532104", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fun night out", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "16 December 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "GreekAussieChick", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "71"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r147532104-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a really fun time at the Boisdale this week. It was super busy, with a lot of Christmas parties obviously going on but I thought that despite that, they managed to give great service. It's not the sort of place I'd go to every week but I did really enjoy the live music and entertainment. The food is very good and better than I expected! The boys really enjoyed their whiskies - so many to choose from. Will definitely go again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r145338494", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great food, expensive drinks", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "13 November 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Ellie G", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "20", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r145338494-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Been twice, first time as a couple. Food reasonably priced but bill huge as drinks very expensive! I found the service to be over-attentive, put down fork for moment and expect your plate to vanish! Second visit was a business dinner and food was great and we dined in a private room, I wasn't paying this time so less aware of the cost! Nice place though and good atmosphere."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r147539296", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Jazzy tartan oasis", "diner_date": " December 2012", "rating_date": "16 December 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "bobdench", "reviewer_origin": ["Rochester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "32"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r147539296-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Getting to the restaurant early for lunch with friends meant I could have a refreshing Guinness and watch the place gird its loins for a busy pre-Christmas Friday. Even empty the ambiance is good. Photos of dudes and chicks cover the walls, big windows overlook the busy wharf, so there is plenty to occupy you while the hustle and bustle gradually builds up around you. the large, well stocked, oval bar sits centre stage on the first floor with tables for casual dining dotted around, more dining and private rooms upstairs for the serious foodie and drinker. The menu has all the Boisdale standards but we went for a traditional Christmas menu, which was excellent value. The portion size was generous, this was no wafer thin turkey slices but good hefty carvings and extra veg was brought out for the table, all was beautifully cooked. our lovely waitress of the day took great care of us and stayed smiling till the end ... The wine menu was extensive and covered every part of the globe and every sized wallet. By the time we finished it was early evening and although the staff need us to move on by then we were never rushed. Drinks back in the now crowded but happy bar brought the festivities to a close. Thoroughly recommend this bar and restaurant for business and friends. Jazz night next time !"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r147987780", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great atmosphere but inflexible", "diner_date": " December 2012", "rating_date": "24 December 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LondonComfortseeker", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "114"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "76"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "40", "20", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r147987780-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I loved the Boisdale when we went there last year (2011) for our annual Christmassy night out (festive jazz band and singers). The food was great, as a vegetarian I hate it when the only veggie choices are risotto or something involving goats cheese (SO unimaginative!). Last year the manager went out of his way to arrange an alternative main course which was great. This year was a very different story. The manager was rude, told me that my dish from last year was not on the menu, and that I could have a salad as a main dish (just what everyone wants on a cold winter's evening on a special occasion). In the end he \"compromised\" and said they would do a plate of vegetables for me - and that's exactly what I got - think a side of vegetables, but spread over a plate. For the type of restaurant that this place portrays itself as being and with a hefty price tag attached for the entertainment and food, this is very poor. I don't think they will see us again in 2013 for what seemed like it could have been an annual event."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r143378503", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic food, great service, good atmosphere", "diner_date": " September 2012", "rating_date": "21 October 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "YvetteDamian", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r143378503-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The d\u00e9cor is elegant and warm. The service was impeccable. I have eaten there a few times and it has always been good. If you can... try the Lobster..so lovely : ) And the lovely bit of Jazz in the background just really adds to to a great evening out."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r143965672", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good service, average expensive food...", "diner_date": " October 2012", "rating_date": "29 October 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Cristina S", "reviewer_origin": ["Agonda, India"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "40", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r143965672-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Nice place, good service, but the food was not up to the standards and I thought it was very expensive for what we had. I don't think I am coming back"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r147595598", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Another fantastic Night", "diner_date": " December 2012", "rating_date": "17 December 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Denise J", "reviewer_origin": ["Romford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r147595598-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had yet another fantastic night at Boisdale for our Christmas party last week. The staff were absolutely excellent. When we arrived we went to the 1st floor Oyster bar where we had two tables reserved for our Canapes and Champagne. Our waiter was excellent, nothing was too much trouble. We then went to 2nd floor restaurant, the table we had reserved was perfect just in front of the stage, the food,wine and entertainment were outstanding as always. If you are looking for a venue that excels for good food, excellent service with unrivaled entertainment Boisdale is the place."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r143609180", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "STANDARDS HAVE DROPPED", "diner_date": " October 2012", "rating_date": "24 October 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "WFN", "reviewer_origin": ["Quinta do Lago, Portugal"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "418"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "431"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "20", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r143609180-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We have dined in a number of times before and always found that the food and service have been at a pretty good level. We therefore invited friends to join us ona Friday night, when there is music and a better atmosphere.", "Sadly we were let down. Some of the issues:", "'We do not serve Bellini'.", "'Oh, you asked for Rose Champagne, I am sure you said just Champagne'", "'No we do not have white bread'", "Two of our party ordered the bisque to start and both were inedible becuase the butter was left in lumos at the bottom, not melted. When we complained, no apology or explanation was given. They were simply offered a replacement, and is is always the case, the moment had gone.", "The bread was stale and we were told that no white bread existed. Lattely we were given four slices of toast!! It was a chea-end thin cut loaf of bread, amazing.", "The main course were good enough, we passed on dessert.", "An expensive and disappointing night. Good band."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r144315662", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "A ' COOL ' EVENING AT BOISDALE", "diner_date": " October 2012", "rating_date": "2 November 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "silhillianSolihull", "reviewer_origin": ["solihull"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r144315662-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A joint birthday celebration with my daughter ( we share the same date ) so a visit was arranged to enjoy the Modern Jazz and to have a good meal.", "The venue has a sophisticated feel and if you are a whisky enthusiast you will be overwhelmed with choice at the bar. The staff were very welcoming and the service attentive ......... the food was O.K. but not brilliant for the largish bill .", "We pre-booked and were shown to a table in a premiere position close to the stage ( I was a bit worried that when the music began we would be deafened, but it was perfect.", "It was a quintet playing, headed by Karren Sharp and Robert Fowler playing standards by Zoot Sims and Al Cohen ........... The standard was very high and at times ' hot ' when some of the improvisations on the tenor saxophones were in full swing.", "I will treasure the evening as a nostalgic event taking me back to the days as an art student in the 60's when I saw live performances of Gerry Mulligan and Stan Getz ........ Magic !!!", "The whole evening was a great success and my daughter who is late 20's seemed to be converted to the jazz scene .", "I hope to be back sometime !!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r143259580", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Place to see Live Acts", "diner_date": " October 2012", "rating_date": "20 October 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "FreelancerLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "261"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "117"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r143259580-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went with friends to see 'Serpentine Fire'. The place has a great atmosphere. The food was first class, service was smooth considering it is a very busy venue and the two course set menu great value at under \u00a320 per head.", "Drinks are a bit on the pricier side at West End prices, however there is good range of beers and wines. ", "I booked a 'Premium View' table that was about halfway between the band and tables right at the back. Quite a good view, but not exactly premium. This is only a small niggle as we still had a good view and the sound system here really delivered.", "All in all a great night out in Canary Wharf. If you love Earth, Wind and Fire make sure you check out this tribute act. They are fanastic, really entertaining and spot on. Really great musicians."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r144454637", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "If you like mice running around as you eat then eat here!", "diner_date": " November 2012", "rating_date": "4 November 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ilovefood276", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r144454637-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went as as a party of 7 on Saturday 3rd November. We'd just finished our average meal when one member of our party noticed a mouse running around!", "We told the waitressing staff who acknowledged they had a problem with mice and said 'but it is London - there's loads here!'", "The manager came over to discuss and was aware mice were frequenting the resturant. As part of her defence, she told us that the mice were only located in our part of the resturant! Well thanks for seating us there then!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r144563488", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice place", "diner_date": " October 2012", "rating_date": "5 November 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Danny5111", "reviewer_origin": ["Leicester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r144563488-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Food a bit expensive but very nice.The entertainment was very good and the selection of cicars and whiskeys were excellent. the only downfall is that when the entertainment is finished the bar is closed and they want you out. This turns out to be a very early evening in my case."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r144328221", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Cigar place!", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "2 November 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "eso4600", "reviewer_origin": ["Moscow, Russia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "40"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "43"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r144328221-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["That is a great cigar place with humidor and large selection of fine cigars. Something you will not find everywhere in today's London "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r145115516", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "For a nice night out", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "10 November 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Dessler75", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r145115516-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Been there a Saturday night and I simply couldn't have enough of the music, the food, the champagne, the oyster, the cigar, the wine and so on.Warm atmosphere and nice staff.I couldn't wish for better.the only pity is that is a little overpriced."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r145302541", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Hamburger for the hungry", "diner_date": " November 2012", "rating_date": "13 November 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Noktrader", "reviewer_origin": ["oslo"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r145302541-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very nice restaurant to have lunch . Had a delicious hamburger with chips. Cosy Scottish atmosphere and perfect for a business lunch or just a fast meal . Service was good and will definately go back there again . Its nice when in England , to get the typical English , Scottish , Irish atmosphere i think . There are many modern places that are great but nice to try something different at times . "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r137740674", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Not for gourmets - saved by the venue, staff and drinks", "diner_date": " August 2012", "rating_date": "20 August 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Charl0tte81", "reviewer_origin": ["Canary Wharf, England, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r137740674-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My boyfriend and I visited Boisdale on Saturday night for the Blues Brothers tribute. The venue, music and staff were very good and are all reasons why we will be returning. The bar staff in particular were memorable for choosing the perfect cocktails for us. ", "Unfortunately, the a la carte food was overpriced for it's quality. I sent my first duck breast back as it had been overcooked. The second one was 'ok' but still not good. I have overcooked many many duck breasts in my own kitchen and have learnt the absolute necessity of letting them rest for ten minutes after you take them out of the pan before slicing them. I have to assume that the chef was in too much of a hurry to keep up with orders to give the duck the time it deserved but for a 2 course meal (with wine and tip) that cost us over \u00a3230 we'd normally expect a higher standard. We may try the fixed price menu in future but are more likely to perch at the bar and focus on Boisdale's strengths!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r141835262", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "SLOW SERVICE", "diner_date": " September 2012", "rating_date": "2 October 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ldove59", "reviewer_origin": ["tradate"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r141835262-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The setting of the grill bar is beautiful . The menu bounces from good offer for oysters and shellfish to average offer for meat and none for fish. Sides and entries to minimum level.", "What is disappointing however is the (non)speed of the service , Needs to remind waitresses several time for a burger and a steack (!) in a half empty restaurant.", "First time I was there a few months ago it was different as far as the service is concerned", "Given the price level and the expectations this was a delusion -in a place where alternatives are", "available this is a risky approach"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r137883221", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Perhaps I'm a little unfair...", "diner_date": " August 2012", "rating_date": "21 August 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Andy D", "reviewer_origin": ["Reading, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "32"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "41"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Atmosphere", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r137883221-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["But... I booked a table for three... what I forgot to mention was, the three were two adults and a child! When we arrived, we were politely informed, Boisdale cannot entertain children because of 'the Whiskey Bar'! Not entirely sure what that meant, but got the impression Boisdale is not a child friendly zone! Will probably go back though, less child!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r142547072", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazin", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "11 October 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "JoT446", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r142547072-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Took my husband for his birthday on friday with our children, the food was amazin and the staff were fantastic would recommend to anyone who likes jazz, good food and great service. We were treated like we were the only people in there, will be goin back for a 2nd visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r138332857", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great music ! Fantastic Food.", "diner_date": " August 2012", "rating_date": "25 August 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "awp66", "reviewer_origin": ["Stowmarket, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "60"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r138332857-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A fantastic venue with fantastic food. I had heard the food was good but was amazed at the quality. I visited with a party of 12 as a retirement night out. The bar has the largest range of Whisky I have ever seem!!!! The service was really good and we were well looked after. The entertainment was great as well."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r141557948", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "No Respect For Artists", "diner_date": " September 2012", "rating_date": "29 September 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "zasu1", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r141557948-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["On the positive the venue was very lovely. The food was good. The service was excellent. The singer and music brilliant. ", "The primary reason i went is because its promoted as a music venue and this is why i went to listen to the music and singer. If you go to Ronnie Scotts or The Vortex ,The Hideaway, 606 club, they all insist that you show some respect to the artists performing and patrons who wish to listen Not at this venue,there were people at tables shouting and shrieking over the music. I have never known a venue which shows such a lack of respect for the artists and staff and management who accept it. Shame it could have been a be a great addition to the London music scene.A nice restaurant but if your a real music lover i would recommended the other venues i have mentioned and give this one a miss."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r140992175", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Aspiring but quite unexceptional", "diner_date": " September 2012", "rating_date": "23 September 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "honest789", "reviewer_origin": ["St Albans, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "55"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "34"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "20", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r140992175-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We were excited to try the Boisdale's Oyster bar with a bunch of friends last week.", "The interior is truly pretty and grand looking.", "The menus are appropriate with a good selection of steaks and seafood.", "I would reconsider having screw-top wines in a [wannabe] upscale place though.", "The food was very tasty and well presented, the just ordinary desserts were a let-down.", "Service has a long way to go to improve, e.g. spilt sauce, ages to bring drinks/food on not a terribly busy night, 'there you go, babe' etc.", "We had a good time overall, but at 50% off food bill it was still just an average experience/value for money, so most likely will not be back too soon."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r141929629", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Review", "diner_date": " October 2012", "rating_date": "3 October 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LondonTbc", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r141929629-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Overall the venue was lovely, food excellent, service in the restaurant very good. A bit pricey. Given the prices charged i expected more in terms politeness and attentiveness of the staff in the main bar, having to ask for more bread was also a bit disappointing. I also thing they should move away from measuring glasses of wine in the bar. Given the prices charged serving a little extra above the minimum would not hurt."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r143027836", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good food, very good service", "diner_date": " October 2012", "rating_date": "17 October 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "thptrek", "reviewer_origin": ["Houston, Texas"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "185"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "90"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r143027836-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Very good atmosphere in Canary Wharf. I hosted a business dinner and all my guests were happy with the menu, the quality of the food and the service. After dinner we retired to the bar and it was very pleasant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2180904", "id_comment": "g186338-d2180904-r137427733", "resto": "Boisdale_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2180904-Reviews-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "good but not that good", "diner_date": " February 2012", "rating_date": "17 August 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "clubber x", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2180904-r137427733-Boisdale_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I like places that allows you to enjoy your stay from a reasonable amount of money and where you can spend 5000gbp/person as well. boisdale is just the place but honestly if you dont like jazz and whiskey it is just a slightly above average place.", "pros:", "- if you manage to sit at the windows the feeling is awesome - though for date I can recommend this place only when you manage to sit to that area", "- their whiskey selection is stunning, they even have for 1500gbp+ / glass!", "- the design of the restaurant is very nice, you can feel yourself in an old saloon", "- you can keep your expenses down and still enjoy the place", "cons:", "- at the time we were in the bar it took ages to serve our drinks. at this price tag it is unacceptable. hire more people please", "- food is average, e.g. the bone in ribeye is thin and the meat quality is average", "- live music is extremely loud, makes communication impossible", "- you need to leave before it starts because they add extra $$$ to your bill"]}
